(3, 'Pieter L', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r1021878914-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Good atmosphere and friendly service', 'Great place to go for lunch or dinner. You can sit outside in the fresh air and our waiter Stephanie was super friendly and helpful. Food was tasty and portions were well sized :)', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4, 'Ahamada D', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r1016537927-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Best experience .Grace had good service', 'We had very good diner and Grace was very hepful and appreciated her assistance . We will come again and again. The food was delicious', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(5, 'Aay Cee', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r978889800-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Service', 'Nice place with good service, and Albert was very good to us. This is definitely the best place for delicious west African food.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(6, 'Carmeliza R', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r973593468-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Above and beyond', 'The eating area is spacious in a well kept garden. The food is diverse and tasty. All natural products. One just wants to chose it all. Come with an empty stomach! In good African style, share the food. It\'s plenty.\nOur waitress, Grace went above and beyond to accommodate our requests. I highly recommend the restaurant for any occasion.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(7, 'Ken A', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r967641625-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'The most sumptuous Egusi and Pounded yam I have had in a long time...e', 'An absolutely delightful experience.  The restaurant was very clean, the food was so fresh and authentic, and the taste was simply put, divine.  \nA very bigthanks to Ann, the very diligent and professional waitress for making our experience a memorable one. I\'ll definitely come back the next time I\'m in Kenya.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(8, 'Kanini M', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r967018207-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Experience was amazing anytime for will recommend them for west African dishes.', 'Food was scrumptious.Grace served  us exemplary and she recommended the sea food jollof which was mouthwatering,the side dishes were good the plantain,chicken wings,groundnut chicken n fried goat,the fufu was good plus portions were good.Will recommend Grace to serve you anytime you go there.Will go again there a kids play area too and the environment is serene.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(9, 'Stephen M', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r955332388-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Worst service imaginable', 'Visited the Waterfront mall branch. Terrible service. Food took forever. The bill took even longer. Honestly I think they are greatly understaffed. Food was above average but the poor service made it a no-no for me ever again!', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(10, 'e0-i0', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r943648155-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Great experience', 'We had a fantastic group dinner at Mama Ashanti. The server was fantastic, and able to recommend many dishes for us to share. The food was fresh and everyone in our group found something they enjoyed. Would highly recommend!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(11, 'Julius F', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r940560182-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'In my own personal experience, Mama Ashanti dishes was one of the best taste i ever had.', 'Mama Ashanti restaurant is one of the best place i have ever visited. Their services is awesome and excellent with lots of welcoming service providers. More importantly, i want to recommend \"Ann\" one of the service providers in the restaurant. Ann is very welcoming, calm, not aggressive and always attend to customers at every point of call for services.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(12, 'calvinpixels k', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r939711694-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Comfortability and excellent service time management', 'I enjoyed the great ambience of the place, great food and excellent service from Lydia. Keep on the good work You really made my experience here outstanding!!! I was so impressed at how well you did your job.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(13, 'JAMES M', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r939351423-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Magical feeling', 'I never thought I would find a magical place like this until we arrived here...the African food was top notch served by the best of the best Ann...we loved her service and the warm welcome we received from her... looking forward to revist', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(14, 'Jean Paul K', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r939160035-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Best', 'The food was nice especially the goat and fish \nService was perfect \nI recommend Grace anyday\nThe atmosphere was nice \nLoved the place', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(15, 'MICHAEL O', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r938843997-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Home away from home', 'One exceptional place with outstanding service. delicious west African delicacies that made us hooked on the spot. We were served by this Lady called Ann and her level of service was topnotch,food was on time and you could tell she was a people\'s person. we are looking forward to coming back and hopefully be served by her. Well done mama Ashanti for this great West African experience.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\", \"delivery_takeout\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
