(20, 'Stella A', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r905236046-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Underwhelming Experience ', 'I had high expectations but had such an underwhelming experience with the service and the food, being my first time there. The chicken wings were chewy. The plantains were semidry and dark like they had been recooked over and over again. The goat meat as well. Staff doing the bare minimum.\n\nFirst and last time there. Meh experience!', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
