(25, 'Beatrice V', 'Eka Hotel, Mombasa Road, Highway Estate, Nairobi 00623 Kenya', 'Soaring Eagle Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4020263-r899498893-Soaring_Eagle_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Lovely food', 'Visited Spur (Eka Hotel) for a late lunch with a friend after a long time. Enjoyed the T bone steak and fries.\n1) No description as I enjoyed myself, ate to my fill.\n2) I would recommend it any day especially their ribs which have always been my favourite.\n3) No one makes onion rings like they do, \n\n', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"speed_wait\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(26, 'Dukeofthenorth', 'Eka Hotel, Mombasa Road, Highway Estate, Nairobi 00623 Kenya', 'Soaring Eagle Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4020263-r895915913-Soaring_Eagle_Spur-Nairobi.html', '2 x pretty average to poor experiences', 'Food was pretty average and lacking any real flavour. Opted for the ribs and chicken wings combo first night, wings were over cooked and dry. Ribs were not particularly hot and not so great flavour Fries were also pretty average. Went back second night only because we needed something quick as going to the airport (booked into adjoining Eka hotel) ordered chicken thighs. After a long wait food arrived. I was supposed to receive 3 split thighs which were small and not so tasty, but only received 2 of the 3. Told the waitress just to discount my bill as I had finished my meal, but she insisted she would give me 2 more thigh‚Äôs. After another long wait the waitress came back with only one split thighs and nothing else! I would have expected a few fries at least. Very disappointed second visit and left feeling completely underwhelmed.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(27, 'Natukunda N', 'Eka Hotel, Mombasa Road, Highway Estate, Nairobi 00623 Kenya', 'Soaring Eagle Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4020263-r870399064-Soaring_Eagle_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'good food', 'The ribs were nice and the drinks too, i like the services we received , the staff were on time and friendly ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(28, 'Lena', 'Eka Hotel, Mombasa Road, Highway Estate, Nairobi 00623 Kenya', 'Soaring Eagle Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4020263-r867905732-Soaring_Eagle_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Good customer service', 'The ribs were to die for plus the onion rings , there customer service was great and we had a good time', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(29, 'garylynnLiphook', 'Eka Hotel, Mombasa Road, Highway Estate, Nairobi 00623 Kenya', 'Soaring Eagle Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4020263-r862624865-Soaring_Eagle_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent service and food', 'Nice atmosphere with good choice of food.  Friendly professional service from Gilbert. Allowed us the time to sit have have a few drinks before deciding on food.  Highlighted Cocktail 2 for 1 offer. Thank you Gilbert.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(30, 'goblin54', 'Eka Hotel, Mombasa Road, Highway Estate, Nairobi 00623 Kenya', 'Soaring Eagle Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4020263-r856474992-Soaring_Eagle_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Beware what you order', 'Group of 4 adults. 2 had a decent meal, 1 was just OK, but the 4th was a disaster that spoiled the evening for us all. The starters were OK, nachos good, wings with peri peri basting a bit bland. Two 200g fillet steaks good, chicken good, but pepper sauce cold, so sent back. Main problem was 300g fillet, which didn‚Äôt look like fillet, was cold & undercooked - sent it back 3 times, but still not to our liking. By this time other meals had been finished. Complained & initially offered a free coffee! Eventually they agreed not to charge for this meal. The manager didn‚Äôt think they offered 300g fillets ( although it was on the menu) & judging by this experience perhaps they shouldn‚Äôt.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(31, 'Daniel K', 'Eka Hotel, Mombasa Road, Highway Estate, Nairobi 00623 Kenya', 'Soaring Eagle Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4020263-r842001635-Soaring_Eagle_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'AMAZING DINNER', 'I had an amazing dinner the other day. The ambience is cosy, the staff very welcoming and the food is amazing. Special mention of Silas Kevin who had a smile throughout and was very courteous! Keep up the good work!', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
