(35, 'John', 'Eka Hotel, Mombasa Road, Highway Estate, Nairobi 00623 Kenya', 'Soaring Eagle Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4020263-r791864057-Soaring_Eagle_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'The staff was friendly and welcoming, and then very little went right', 'I ordered the steak with the add-on pork ribs.  I ordered the steak medium.  I also ordered the baked potato.  The order took an extraordinary long time to get to the table, but when it did it came with fries instead of the baked potato.  Instead of medium, the steak was practically raw and the ribs were cold.  They agreed to bring me my baked potato, but they did not have the sour cream I requested.  Although I sent the ribs back to be warmed, they still came back cold.  Maybe they were aff their game, but this was not a good dining experience.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(36, 'Jackie Njiru', 'Eka Hotel, Mombasa Road, Highway Estate, Nairobi 00623 Kenya', 'Soaring Eagle Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4020263-r783642799-Soaring_Eagle_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'One of my Favourites', 'If you are looking for delicious food with amazing and super quick service, look no further. This is the place to be. Their barbequed pork ribs are super delicious. Thick creamy shakes, crunchy flavorful onion rings - every dish is absolutely divine.\n\nThe wait staff are very friendly and courteous.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\"]'),
