(38, 'Maryann N', 'Eka Hotel, Mombasa Road, Highway Estate, Nairobi 00623 Kenya', 'Soaring Eagle Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4020263-r776590482-Soaring_Eagle_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Delicious pork ribs', 'I happened to visit the Eagle Spur a couple of months ago with my family. We ordered for pork ribs and fries. From the way they looked you could tell they were super delicious.(finger licking juicy and tender ribs) They have the best ribs in town .', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(39, 'Berend d', 'Eka Hotel, Mombasa Road, Highway Estate, Nairobi 00623 Kenya', 'Soaring Eagle Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4020263-r748352520-Soaring_Eagle_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Nice', 'After having dinner in lodges for over a week it is very nice to have a nice dinner at Spur. Conveniently located within EKA hotel were we stayed for the night. Food is good and restaurant is clean and staff was very friendly. ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
