(87, 'Naomi D', 'Limuru Road The Village Market, Nairobi 00621 Kenya', 'Harvest Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15213862-r1029915237-Harvest_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Great food excellent service!', 'I had a wonderful experience. Great food and excellent service from Onuga who catered to all my dietary restrictions. I loved the food so much I came back a few times on my trip, and Onuga served me well each and every time.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]');
