(162, 'Mattia B', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r905957109-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Una escalation di gusto alla Cascina', '5 stelle ma 10 effettive! Un posto fantastico e una cucina a dir poco invidiabile rispetto all‚ÄôItalia, dai primi ai secondi alla pizza tutto fantastico, per non parlare dei panificati fatti da loro e una cura nei dettagli che ti lascia a bocca aperta! ho conosciuto la coppia che gestisce il locale Paola e Giampaolo due persone fantastiche che oltre a trasparire la loro passione per quello che fanno sono stati degli ottimi amici che sicuramente avr√≤ modo di incontrare nelle prossime esperienze!se passate dal Kenya siete obbligati a fare tappa da loro! Un buon viaggio si vive bene con una buona esperienza culinaria! Top del top', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(163, 'Bannister', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r880079868-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Qualit√† assicurata in stile italiano DOC!', 'Ottimo in tutto. Tornarci e‚Äô sempre un piacere. Personale e proprietari gentilissimi.\nProfessionalita gusto e qualita, una conferma!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[]'),
(164, 'KariTheOld', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r850042544-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Not impressed', 'I have visited La Cascina a few times. Unfortunately, the food has been at its best, at an average level. More often, I have been disappointed with the food. I seriously believe that the chef is not familiar with Italian cuisine. Some of the dishes have a strange combination of ingredients.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(165, 'Ravinder S', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r847488496-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Average steaks', 'Was really looking forward to a nice steak but was left disappointed. Definitely didn‚Äôt feel like a filet! Having said that the rest of the family enjoyed their meals. Ambiance was very nice overlooking a courtyard at The Hub in Karen. Proprietor was friendly as were the staff and service was good. All in all still had a pleasant evening.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(166, 'Byron78', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r843208696-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Established.', 'Great platters,burgers,steak, pizzas and pastas.\nSet in the courtyard to watch the world go by.\nService can be hit and miss.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(167, 'Jessica B', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r827249969-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Tasty pizza!', 'Good food, attentive staffs, I highly recommend the pizza, so organic and tasty. As a wine lover, there is good choices out there. What else more, the price‚Ä¶ very reasonable.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(168, 'Traveling Chopsticks', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r813122554-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Great Wine and Pasta', 'Their mussels pasta is amazing!! They don\'t skimp on the mussels and I suggest getting it with the tagliatelle. Wine had good selection and waiter went extra mile. My friend ordered the duck entree and it was a little dry though. Would love to come back to try other items.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(169, 'DerekClive', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r800023311-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Service doesn\'t hide poor food', 'After hearing good things about La Cascina, my girlfriend and I went for lunch. Attentive service didn\'t alleviate waiting an age for our calamari and prawns. When it finally came it had the consistency and taste of deep-fried cardboard. Old doesn\'t begin to describe the seafood; I wouldn\'t be surprised if the label said 2010 when they defrosted them; thankfully neither of us was taking a trip to the dentist that day! Both had been fried in oil that was incredibly old - Castrol might have been better - leaving a grim taste in the mouth after chewing for an age just to digest the stuff. It would have been better to order a jar of mayonnaise as everything had to be smothered in that to make it edible. Had we not been ravenous after waiting for so long and being pushed for time, the whole lot would have gone back. This pitiful meal was made worse by the fact that hardly anyone else was in the restaurant. Unless La Cascina decide to bring their seafood from the coast on something quicker than an asthmatic tuk-tuk, stick to the pizzas!', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(170, 'nfriesen1', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r789093447-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Incredible Food!', 'We love this restaurant, truly authentic and fresh Italian food. The pizza here is the best in Nairobi and the service is always great!  Highly recommend the Funghi Pizza!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(171, 'Sumeet Garara', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r788799145-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Amazing', 'Amazing food is and amazing place to be good interior inside sitting and the outside sitting is also good the staff are friendly. \n\nPlace recommended.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(172, 'AyushmanD', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r783228855-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'cheating, bad attitude of staff', 'we were a tourist in kenya for few days, decided to oder a pizza from this place. we placed an order of 1000KES and with the delivery fee and everything got a message by saying the total bill is 1400KES.\nafter a while the delivery came with the pizza , since i didnt have the change i asked a change back by paying 2000KES.\nthe driver didnt have change so he said , i quote, ‚Äúi will take the 2000 and the management will send someone with the change of 600. \nlater since no one came with the change and the resturant was nearing closing time , i called the resturant . when i explained the situation, the  cut the line 1st , then i called again and explained the situation again, they said they gonna give me my change in some kind if credit which i can use later . i am not from around here so i didnt know how credit works. then i tried to explain the resturant that i will need the change back as i dont have the account for the credit and i am leaving the next day . they cut the line again, when i then called again , they said the driver already left the place and they cannot give the refund back . after that when i called several times they didnt pick up the phone and also when i called the driver , he said its upto the management to decide and he has no hand in it. he took my money yet still says that he wont give it back .\n\nlater the driver ‚ÄúDAVID‚Äù gave me an option that he will bring my money back bext day morning but he is gonna take a delivery charge of 250KES for delivering my money back to me .\n\nlisting to this , i felt pity at the management and the rude drivers + the workers  at the resturant  who refused to pick my call or help me. I was surprised by the way they can fool and confuse a fellow tourist who came to visit kenya even during this pandemic period . the whole situation is not about money(even 2000KES is just few dollars for me) but the way they treat their customer is horrible.\nthis was probably the worst experience in kenya. being legally robbed.\n\nplease have ur guys train in some customer service and i wish all the best for future of the resturant.\n\noder date : 19/02/2021\ntime: 1930 aprox \nlocation for delivery: the brandy bus, 49 kibo lane, karen \nDelivery guy  name : DAVID', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(173, 'anita w', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r782411775-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'karen hub its always the best place to be,', 'i really love this place, its a beautiful and amazing place to chill out with friends/familly ..everything there its just amazing', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"location_access\"]'),
(174, 'Caroline G', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r780078905-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Hidden Gem', 'Conveniently located within the Hub shopping complex.  Excellent Italian food and services. \nExcellent variety of Italian wine and authentic Italian dessert. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(175, 'Abiud Wekesa', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r779917432-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Experience', 'My stay there was good and am happy i chose this place considering the good service ii received from this place.The meals were sweet and served on time', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\", \"delivery_takeout\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(176, 'beanuibroin', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r887940810-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Never again', 'Just dreadful service. Half an hour waiting for a drink then ignored. Plates and cutlery arrived with a bowl of chilli sauce which was cracked in two places. We ran out of time so we went to leave having been there for an hour. Offered to pay for the drinks which was accepted!!! We then expressed surprise that they would accept payment for such dreadful service. Then followed a two minute meeting with staff and the manager after which it was decided not to charge us for the two drinks. We left. ', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"drinks\", \"service\"]'),
(177, 'Curiosity18917158954', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r884531133-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Not good experience ', 'Very pricy, poor quality food, most of us were sick the following day and slow service, do not recommend this place ', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(178, 'lily wanjugu', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r874632443-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'The small west Africa!', 'Their food will surely fly you back to west Africa. On that particular day I had ogbono soup with amala, it was amazing. The band on Friday evenings is the icing on the cake. Pick Fridays for Family dinners or unwind with a group of friends.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(179, 'Yohanne K', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r845845756-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Ridiculously over-priced, not all that great food,  with uninspiring service!', 'The ambiance at this place is nice, but that‚Äôs about it. The food is crazily overpriced and the service is mediocre at best. I had to go look for the waitress to come serve our table. The girl who served us looked like she had more important customers elsewhere. She barely could even listen while seemingly in a rush to go somewhere else. A bowl of boiled rice, countable pieces of bland diced chicken, and a few scattered vegetables would cost you KES950.  Anything else is 2-3 times that. Maybe if you really want to just try some west African cuisine, but you are much, much, better off going to a proper restaurant somewhere, pay the same, and get a great dining experience. I wonder if they profile customers, but if you are like me, just skip this place.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(180, 'Saratu', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r832816748-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Home in Kenya üá∞üá™', 'Overall amazing experience! Great food, friendly staffs, refreshing environment. Worth it. Best place for West Africa dish. Value for money.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(181, 'Njeru kynn', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r832351361-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Very disappointed üòû', 'Went to the restaurant very hungry almost collapsing, placed my order ,waited for 1 hour only to realise that  they didn\'t post my order so the cook couldn\'t make the food,very unprofessional supervisor who doesn\'t know even how to apologise to the client, I regret wasting my time and energy. Kindly train your staff how to do their duties ...very disappointed', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(182, 'hcb81', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r822144654-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Lovely visit', 'Really pleased to have discovered this place. Tasty food, great friendly service and a lovely garden setting. Great play area for kids too.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(183, 'VioAnne O', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r816282617-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Awesome first visit', 'Amazing first visit for lunch! Relaxing environment, welcoming and courteous staff, and delicious food and fresh juices! Return visit scheduled.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(184, 'Joe.', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r770108263-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Review', 'The best place to be. Serene and cool.\nWouldn\'t think twice. Wonderful service and very warm personnel', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(185, 'tunde daniel', 'Muthangari Gardens Lavington, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mama Ashanti - Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7312222-r748862665-Mama_Ashanti_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'lunch...', 'good meals . great Ambience. best of West African meals combined with Kenyan delight.  Easy to locate and play area for kids. has a functional bar which is pocket friendly', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(186, 'Freedom01071512481', 'Unit RF08, Two Rivers Mall, Limuru Road Kitsuru, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Silver Stream Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12075661-r973990617-Silver_Stream_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'I enjoyed at spur and thenks twe the waitress  i promise i will come back', 'I went too spur on sunday for lunch and i was served by a lady called susan i enjoyed my lunch and also the service given by susan she is more than a waitress and i promised twe come back', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(187, 'Curiosity12372545938', 'Unit RF08, Two Rivers Mall, Limuru Road Kitsuru, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Silver Stream Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12075661-r973743579-Silver_Stream_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'An experience worth repeating', 'Excellent food and valerian was great.\nAlways our favorite place . Valerian and crew keep up the good work.it has become our favorite spot at two rivers to eat out', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(188, 'Baboucarr J', 'Unit RF08, Two Rivers Mall, Limuru Road Kitsuru, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Silver Stream Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12075661-r973586288-Silver_Stream_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Nice experience', 'Valerian was the lady who served us and we got an excellent service from her. The food was also good. We came here last week and got good experience and we came back this week too', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
