(206, 'Bu Rashed', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r711552162-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Nice place to go', 'A good place to enjoy your time and meet new friends in Nairobi. A good food variety to choose from.\nThey treat visitors very well and all staff are customer oriented.\nIt is a safe place and we really enjoyed it and will definitely go again next time we go to Nairobi...', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
