(208, 'Seaside26810470509', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r706265033-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Artistic Vibes', 'The place has a vintage kind of vibe going on. The music is great and the tiny food bars offer great food. Serious parking problems. Might need to park at Sarit.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(209, 'WanderHopefully', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r703709384-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Good burgers and nice vibe', 'More an open air yard with a stage in one corner and surrounded by a selection of bars and food trucks. They have a couple of nice craft beers, the service is good and burgers excellent. What is not to like?', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(210, 'Tiffany c', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r684785159-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Fun Friday Party', 'We went to a fun Friday party there. It was packed and drinks were pricey but good. Only downside was that the DJ played sooooo much American music. (Although the crowd seemed to enjoy it.) Would have enjoyed more afrobeats!!! Definitely a fun place to dance though- if you don‚Äôt mind being shoved in the line to get in and shoved on the dancefloor too. But the crowd was fun otherwise. \n\nPs. Don‚Äôt eat shawama from the food truck though or you‚Äôll be visiting the toilet for sure. ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
