(212, 'cselempo', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r675691116-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Cool and fun clubhouse!!!', 'Definitely worth a visit next time!\nHowever, be warned as the place is cold at night.\nCome wearing warm clothes especially during the cold seasons.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(213, 'Hadeel Oz', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r674519915-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'A fun place to be', 'The open mics are very entertaining, service is great and the overall decor, music choices and variety of food makes this a must visit spot. Had a great time and will make it a regular spot.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(214, 'llansford', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r662241344-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Awesome, buzzing hub with tons of choices', 'We were at first confused trying to find the place--I didn\'t see any signage saying \"Alchemist,\" but did see some food trucks and signs for other bars, so we headed in. We had an awesome time and were completely surprised by how cool of a spot this was! It was an outdoor haven full of young people and honestly felt like our home in  Austin plopped down right in Nairobi: we came during a Pecha Kucha night about design, there were AMAZING food trucks, great outdoor seating and ambiance, a killer little shop, a sweet vinyl library, and of course, beverages galore. Pop in for some Tucker and a burger and you won\'t regret it! Compared to the prices back home and given the high quality of food and ambiance, this place was a steal. It\'s def a tad more expensive than some surrounding joints, but was totally worth it for the awesome noms, great event, and vibes.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(215, 'Tomas Bartas', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r659585133-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Worth to jump in', 'We have jumped in for couole of drinks and it was fine. Good cocktails, nice and friendly staff. It was good time ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\"]'),
(216, 'Amanda', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r770211789-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Prompt, friendly service. Underwhelmed by the food.', 'As a personal lover of Italian food, I was very excited to dine here.\n\nOrdered the pasta with bacon, onions and a tomato sauce base. While the portion was generous, I found this extremely salty and this flavour overwhelmed my palate. This prevented me from enjoying the meal and the bacon seemed to be the cause of the overwhelming salty flavour.\n\nMy friend tried the pasta with spicy salami and a mushroom white sauce base. Overall this was a tasty dish, but was disappointed to not have the salami spicy at all as described in the menu! According to the owner, it is a spicy salami but this was not justified in the flavour of it at all.\n\nTiramisu for dessert was good, yet required more lady fingers and a more prominent coffee flavour, rather than just cream. \n\nI think I should have ordered a pizza as that was what all the other diners around me seemed to be eating.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(217, 'Clarelor', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r753614842-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Great pizzas', 'Good place for a break either before or after shopping, good pasta/pizza menu with attentive service,', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(218, 'Medrine Angelica', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r748989745-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'A chilled Sunday', 'My cousin and I just wanted to go out for lunch and take cute photos and catch on this thing called life. The restaurant wasn\'t our original plan but I am glad we got to dine here.From the entrance i just knew this would be a great experience I mean..first impression matters a lot!! The menu is very friendly and straight to the point.We had a Hawaiian Pizza and red wine. Such a weird combination but we enjoyed it. The winery space is what made me crave for wine because of how it has been displayed. \nHowever, small details like napkins made me question the quality of service because we weren\'t provided with any. Other than that everything else was perfect and i would highly recommend.Especially for couples an intimate dates.Th ambiance gives out that kind of vibe.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(219, 'you54', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r748894518-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Best Italy eatery in Nairobi', 'Authentic recipes, besides very good primi piatti, fantastic seafood and steaks, excellent wine list and friendly atmosphere! What more can one ask for?', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(220, 'Antonello_De_Sio', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r748489363-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Un pezzo d‚ÄôItalia a Nairobi.', 'Girando nel Centro Commerciale ci siamo imbattuti per caso nel ristorante per prendere un caff√®. Il luogo ed i titolari ci hanno ispirato fiducia ed il giorno dopo siamo tornati a pranzo.\nTutto molto buono. Pizza e calzone cotti al forno elettrico e molto gustosi. Piatto di spaghetti al sugo altrettanto buono.\nConsigliato!', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(221, 'Julius K', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r745836190-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Great Experience', 'All that you want...local and global menu. Fresh meals and enthusiastic crew. Located in a safe and secure environment at the Karen Hub. Ample parking', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(222, 'Aleksandra B', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r743422729-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Nice place', 'The food is good. Some of the dishes are excellent and some are just good. I always go for simple dishes. That\'s where they\'re good. Piadine for example. The service is always very good. La Cascina has a few really friendly and helpful waiters. Bravo for the staff!', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(223, 'Loice A', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r739076581-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'What\'s not to love about Italian Fine Dining?', 'The service is great and the food is excellently prepared. Their home made gelato is to die for. They have Sunday brunch as well with a wide variety of foods to indulge in. Difinitely one place where you will get value for your money.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(224, 'Sukesha D', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r736232194-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Casual  Cascina', 'A lovely italian restaurant with ample choices for vegetarians at the Hub in the mall in Karen. Tasty food with excellent service and lovely home made sauces which go well  with the  breads.\nAlways busy and bustling with a cosmopolitan crowd... a sure hit with all ages... lovely soups pastas and pizzas \nThe Fungusso is a hot favorite ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(225, 'Felino', 'Dagoretti Karen Hub, Nairobi Kenya', 'La Cascina', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10140471-r729722858-La_Cascina-Nairobi.html', 'Like this place a lot', 'We are an expat family with new born baby, so unfortunately most of our fun time in weekends is on shopping mall to buy weekly supplies and eat something\n\nLove this place to stop for a good lunch before getting into supermarket, food is very good and fresh (love salads and meats) and desserts are handmade \n\nPortions are big so is also not expensive, as prices are reasonable considering is a good place\n\nCoffee, Icea creams, cheeseckaes or pannacottas mandatory\n\nIs perfect place to stop with family and have convenience and delicious food....', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
