(315, 'Michelle N', 'Limuru Rd, Nairobi Kenya', 'CJ\'s - Village Market', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16659029-r1024203723-CJ_s_Village_Market-Nairobi.html', 'A worthy experience', 'Amazing customer care. Helps customers to make choices. Takes good care of children and keeps smiling at them. Food arrives without having to wait for long. Food tastes amazing. Special thank you to Nancy.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(316, 'Johnnie_Tembezi', 'Village Market, Limuru Road, Gigiri, Nairobi 00621 Kenya', 'Jiko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d2341395-r1037024766-Jiko-Nairobi.html', 'Inventive Kitchen', 'Really an excellent kitchen. Very innovative dishes and great service. A shout out to Daniel. Beautiful setting around the pool', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(317, 'Magda W', 'Village Market, Limuru Road, Gigiri, Nairobi 00621 Kenya', 'Jiko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d2341395-r1036944917-Jiko-Nairobi.html', 'Great', 'Amazing service from waiter Musau . Great ambiance and the saxophone player was really good. The restaurant was really fun', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(318, 'Lindsay B', 'Village Market, Limuru Road, Gigiri, Nairobi 00621 Kenya', 'Jiko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d2341395-r1036609212-Jiko-Nairobi.html', 'Great overall experience', 'The food was okay. I absolutely adore the ambience and service so mcuch. Our waitress Agnes was amazing, fast and helpful. I‚Äôll always come back because of that!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(319, 'Muyiwa F', 'Village Market, Limuru Road, Gigiri, Nairobi 00621 Kenya', 'Jiko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d2341395-r1036529742-Jiko-Nairobi.html', 'Amazing, outstanding, delicious', 'Geofrey was a outstanding waiter and kept the food plus laughter flowing. Food was 5 out of 5 and would highly recommend.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(320, 'Hawa S', 'Village Market, Limuru Road, Gigiri, Nairobi 00621 Kenya', 'Jiko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d2341395-r1036524699-Jiko-Nairobi.html', 'Amazing Staff', 'Visited Nairobi for first time with family and was recommended this place. We were received so warmly by the manager (Phillip) \n\nWe were served by Geofrey who was outstanding. He was so attentive and took time to explain what we were eating and flavours. \n\nThoroughly recommend everyone to visit . Food 10/10', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(321, 'Cruiser31240822588', 'Village Market, Limuru Road, Gigiri, Nairobi 00621 Kenya', 'Jiko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d2341395-r1036522841-Jiko-Nairobi.html', 'Its a good place to be', 'It was nice  being served by Geoffrey. His services are excellent and commendable.I recommend him a hundred times. Good services', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"overall_experience\"]'),
(322, 'Notts I', 'Village Market, Limuru Road, Gigiri, Nairobi 00621 Kenya', 'Jiko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d2341395-r1036522679-Jiko-Nairobi.html', 'Top notch service', 'Took my family for dinner and the experience exceeded my expectations. Shout out to Geoffrey who took care of us throughout the evening, I‚Äôll surely be back and would recommend', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(323, 'Timothy K', 'Village Market, Limuru Road, Gigiri, Nairobi 00621 Kenya', 'Jiko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d2341395-r1036365491-Jiko-Nairobi.html', 'Awesome experience', 'All was excellent. Good service, excellent food. Waiters especially Agness and Nancy, were amazing and extremely helpful.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(324, 'Tracie A', 'Village Market, Limuru Road, Gigiri, Nairobi 00621 Kenya', 'Jiko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d2341395-r1036361357-Jiko-Nairobi.html', 'Good service', 'I had a wonderful experience at Jiko Restaurant thanks to Agnes, our waitress. She was incredibly patient, friendly, and welcoming throughout our visit. Her warm attitude and professionalism made us feel truly valued as guests. I highly recommend her for her outstanding service! and also the food is good.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(325, 'janetwangui n', 'Village Market, Limuru Road, Gigiri, Nairobi 00621 Kenya', 'Jiko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d2341395-r1036360207-Jiko-Nairobi.html', 'Totally worth it', 'I loved the good customer service, tasty and meals delivered on time. I would definitely be a regular here annd come again.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"delivery_takeout\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(326, 'Erland  Schjeld... H', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r1034331605-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Good place for dining, but not as good when ordering food through uber eats.', 'We live near Zen Garden and frequently dine there. The food and service are good. But when we order food through uber eats we often experience that they send only sweet chili or ginger for one portion when we have bought two. This even when we spesifically have ordered more.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(327, 'Brittany_11_10', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r1012915978-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Okay', 'Only ordered for delivery, so can\'t comment on the in-restaurant service or ambiance, but the food is okay. Nothing to write home about, but it got the job done. The chicken gyoza and Shanghai Rice were the best things we ordered. Prices were fair for the quality and quantity of food.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(328, 'zzaf', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r1000705263-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Underwhelming', 'I was very underwhelmed by my experience at Zen Garden. I think because of the name I was expecting to be sitting in beautiful gardens, of which there are many in Nairobi, however this was not the case at Zen Garden. There are some pretty gardens there but the restaurant seating is not in them! Such a shame. All the seating is in a very bland area which feels quite corporate. Very black and grey with no plants or flowers. It was very lacking. I ate sushi and pizza.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(329, 'josephine m', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r989906857-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Terrible', 'very unprofessional service. we waited for over 30 mins just for a waiter to come pick our order.Mind you, several waiters were idle just standing around with nothing to do.After giving out our order, the waiter never placed it and disappeared.  We had to place it once again. Go to this place if you want to be racially profiled as a black person..of you are white, you\'ll have more than 3 waiters at your service including taking your pictures.  I wouldn\'t recommend ', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(330, 'Howard K', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r987096770-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'A relaxing evening with great food in a sereen setting', 'We tried several quality restaurants in Nairobi this Christmas and during previous New Year breaks in Kenya; none exceeded our expectations. However, that was not the case after visiting ZEN GARDEN this last Monday; the food and the service were superb. The Asian-style menu is vast, comprehensive and reasonably priced, ensuring a host of untried delicacies awaiting a next visit. Eating out in one of the garden seating areas amidst the tranquil surroundings just added to the location\'s ambience, creating a sense of peace and relaxation. Our waiter, Antony, added the all-essential friendly touch to a magical dining experience.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(331, 'Voyage to Kenya', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r981808034-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'A Hidden Gem for Families and Special Events', 'Zen Garden in Nairobi is a slice of paradise! The beautiful atmosphere with its lush greenery and serene vibes makes it perfect for relaxation or celebration. On Sundays, kids can enjoy painting activities for an extra fee, while the playground, tennis/paddle court, and expansive grassy area for soccer offer endless fun for the little ones.\n\nThe staff and owners are genuinely friendly and accommodating, making every visit feel special. Whether you\'re planning a birthday party, a family gathering, or a special event, Zen Garden provides the ideal setting.\n\nIt‚Äôs not just a restaurant; it‚Äôs a destination where every member of the family can have a great time. Highly recommended for anyone looking for a welcoming and versatile spot in Nairobi!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(332, 'Helga W', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r967293059-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Find a peaceful place, eat wonderful.', 'Peaceful surrounding wonderful food. Zen garden has very very friendly waiters and delicious food. We had sweet and sour chicken and fried Rice vegetable. Patisserie very good as well. I took cheesecake with Belgium speculoos. Expect to hear birds singing. See a lot of flowers in the garden. And enjoy! It was very good.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(333, 'Shemina S', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r959664764-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Zen gardens', 'Clear signage at entrance.\nParking available. \nPadel available. \nBeautiful gardens and colourful flowers.\nAmazing selection of food from veg to nonveg , yummy üòã starters to main meal, and not forgetting desserts ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]');
