(334, 'Dania27', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r950635410-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Not worth it at all, pricey and not that yum', 'Didn‚Äôt enjoy it all, food is really average, super heavy (feels unhealthy) and so not worth the price. We paid 16k ksh for 2 adults and 2 kids. We ordered 8 dim sums, 1 pizza, crispy chicken, one prawn toast and 1 prawn tempura. Prices are just ridiculous for what you get. For this price, you can get an amazing meal at Hero (village market) or Cultiva (Karen). \nI won‚Äôt be back again.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"price_value\"]'),
(335, 'Jasmine A', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r940759762-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Disappointing', 'I am a regular at Zen because the food is usually always good but I was highly disappointed in my recent experience there due to the poor attitude of the management. I had specifically called the day before to book a table for six adults and two children, requesting a table next to the garden as I knew our toddlers would want to run around. Once we had entered and were settled at our table next to the garden the manager came and asked us to move claiming that a group of 9 people had reserved the table we were sitting on prior to us. We were moved to a location closer to their inside section, far away from the garden and it didn\'t even have a view of the garden. The people who had apparently \'reserved\' our original table were a group of 5 people (including children who were running around in the garden). Clearly they had some kind of connection to the Manager and he had showed preference to them over us. I was appalled as in the past I\'ve had pretty good experiences at this restaurant. The food is good (not incredible but pretty standard every time) and usually the service is on point. Our waiter was actually good but the whole experience was just ruined by the Manager who was completely unapologetic and did not compensate us in any way whatsoever. Arrogance will get you nowhere in the hospitality industry - in fact it will just encourage regular clients like me to no longer visit your establishment.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(336, 'Subhash sethi', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r923343256-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent', 'The restaurant is quite nice and with wonderful natural beauty . The food quality is superb and offer many varieties .\n\nWhen in Nairobi one must visit this restaurant if somebody is fond of Asian food ..', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\"]'),
(337, 'SOTIRIOS S', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r922668689-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Fantastic sushi ', 'Fantastic sushi and really good garden. Price was good for the quantity and quality of what we got. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(338, 'Thomas', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r920715834-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'H√§ftigt och gott', 'Vi avslutade en grymt bra dag med inspirerande arbete p√• Zen Garden. Ett stort och fint st√§lle centralt i Nairobi. God asiatiska matr√§tter och trevlig milj√∂. √Ñven servisen var bra. En klar fyra och v√§rt ett √•terbes√∂k.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[]'),
(339, 'CarolDaniel', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r917912189-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'The restuarant has very poor services esp if you are black.', 'Racism on the highest level!\nWaited for a whole 30mins to be served!\nWaiters are so rude\nI honestly hated my experience af this place!\n1/10\nDisgusted!', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(340, 'Jonathan Kithyoma', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r911245257-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Birthday Dinner', 'My wife made a dinner reservation to celebrate my 33rd birthday at Zen Garden. The place is very scenic and service is great. I enjoyed their spicy chicken soup as a starter and it was amazingly refreshing.\nFor the main we ordered Dry spicy Pork served with Spicy Chicken Rice; this was so delicious.\nDefinitely recommend it if you‚Äôre looking for a quiet and intimate place for dinner or brunch.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(341, 'Cinzia M', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r910287893-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'da provare', 'Posto splendido! un giardino con fiori e piante bellissimi. buono il cibo e ok i tempi di attesa. consigliatissimi, torneremo. \n', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[]'),
(342, 'Reined Incognito', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r905454812-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'First and definitely not the last time', 'First time visiting this establishment and I loved the food. The pork and the rice were my favourite. I am definitely going back.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(343, 'Mr P', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r893945863-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Expected more but still okay', 'Once one of the few spots for authentic Asian cuisine against a backdrop of lush gardens, sorry to say that standards have slipped a bit...but still salvageable. The sushi is okay, though a bit one note. The rest of the fare is okay with various dishes for non-Sushi lovers...the pizza though leaves a lot to be desired. That said, the service is excellent and the restaurant very child friendly and with great ambience. Expected more but still okay', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(344, 'Chandni', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r893699902-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Missing that \"Je Ne Said Quoi\" ', 'Zen is like a household name to almost every food enthusiast in Nairobi because it\'s been there forever! I don\'t mind it. I\'ve been to Zen countless times for work events and meetings mostly. It\'s perfect for a business cocktail event or a meeting. The service is very good and the staff is friendly. You are assured good service each time. Although I recommend making a reservation because it can get quite busy. \n\nThe food isn\'t exciting or particularly out of the ordinary. The times I go with my friends I only order sushi, because again, I feel their food misses that je ne sais quoi that would get me excited to order again. \n\nIt\'s a safe bet for a business meeting or a drink in the evening with a friend because the ambiance is decent. ', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(345, 'Maria', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r876028075-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'An embodiment of Peace and Calm with a bonus of flavourful dishes ', 'Excellent Customer Service by:\nJacob (waiter), Elizabeth (Reception) and Ruth (on phone)\nAmbience: Dreamy, Heavenly \nMenu: Good variety of dishes We ordered as per Jacob\'s recommendations and wow he did choose well Prawn tempura, Sizzling beef, Spicy chicken rice and Seasonal greens Wow just the best And not forgetting the desserts mmmh mmmh mmmmh yummylicious \nZen is definitely on our repeat list ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(346, 'John M', 'Imaara Shopping Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Cjs - Imaara', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d25184060-r1034824965-Cjs_Imaara-Nairobi.html', '‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê 5/5 ‚Äì Exceptional First-Time Experience at CJ‚Äôs!', 'Our first visit to CJ‚Äôs Restaurant was nothing short of amazing! From the moment we walked in, we were warmly welcomed and made to feel completely at ease.\n\nA special shoutout to Yusuf, who provided exceptional service throughout our meal ‚Äî attentive, friendly, and genuinely passionate about making sure we had a great time. He patiently guided us through the menu and gave perfect recommendations that we absolutely loved.\n\nWe also want to appreciate Valentine, Yusuf‚Äôs supervisor, for stepping in with such professionalism and warmth. Together, they made our first experience at CJ‚Äôs not just enjoyable but truly memorable.\n\nThe food was fantastic, the atmosphere relaxed, and the service top-tier. We‚Äôll definitely be coming back ‚Äî thanks to Yusuf and Valentine for setting the bar so high!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(347, 'Beats B', 'Imaara Shopping Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Cjs - Imaara', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d25184060-r1034029296-Cjs_Imaara-Nairobi.html', 'If I could give a thousand stars, I would!', 'I wanted to plan a surprise at CJ‚Äôs Imaara Mall, and thanks to James, it turned into an unforgettable night! I gave him very short notice, but he handled everything with such ease, grace, and professionalism.\n\nJames truly knows how to deliver top-tier service. His attention to detail, warm demeanor, and ability to make magic happen under pressure are unmatched.\nIf you\'re ever planning something special or even just grabbing a bite ask for James. He‚Äôll turn an ordinary evening into something spectacular. üí´', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(348, 'George G', 'Imaara Shopping Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Cjs - Imaara', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d25184060-r1032048205-Cjs_Imaara-Nairobi.html', 'Best Service', 'Visited cjs on Wednesday and got the best service all thanks to waitress Naomi. She\'s welcoming and perfect at what she does. The food was really nice. I look forward to visiting again.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
