(356, 'patwell M', 'Imaara Shopping Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Cjs - Imaara', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d25184060-r1022952067-Cjs_Imaara-Nairobi.html', 'CJs for me', 'I had an incredible experience at this food spot! The food was absolutely amazing‚Äîflavorful, fresh, and beautifully presented. From the moment I walked in, the customer service was outstanding. The staff was friendly, professional, and super quick with taking and delivering orders. I didn‚Äôt have to wait long at all, which made the entire visit even more enjoyable. One thing that really stood out was how clean the entire place was. From the tables to the restrooms, everything was spotless. You can tell they take pride in maintaining a high standard. I‚Äôll definitely be coming back. Highly recommend!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(357, 'Jesstrotter', 'Imaara Shopping Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Cjs - Imaara', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d25184060-r1021110182-Cjs_Imaara-Nairobi.html', 'Bad food experience', 'I have been a loyal customer of CJS Imara, frequenting the restaurant four times a month, and I used to commend the staff for their excellent, receptive management and quality ingredients. However, I am disappointed to report that there has been a significant decline in both in quality since the management change. \n\nDuring my latest visit, I experienced a terrible issue: I ordered feta cheese, which was clearly expired. Instead of addressing the concern professionally, the manager argued with me and invalidated my experience, claiming to be an expert on cheese. This was not only dismissive but also unprofessional. We are experienced with cheese, even hosting cheese tasting events, so his dismissive attitude was unacceptable. If there was a change in supplier or quality, a simple explanation would have sufficed, but instead, I was met with arrogance and disrespect.\n\nThis incident, and the overall decline in food quality is gone significantly down, suggests that something is not right within the Imara unit. The management\'s attitude particularly a manager arguing over a straightforward issue raises concerns about the standards and customer care at this location. I am losing confidence in the new management and the direction the restaurant is heading.\n\nOverall, the standards have gone downhill, and the service recovery has been lacking. Something is clearly not working, and I hope the management takes this feedback seriously to restore the quality and experience we once enjoyed. FYI the service team is phenomenal i love love your waiters the service is exceptional.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
