(386, 'Dania27', 'Shop B1, The Hub, Dagoretti Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Eagle Peak Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10804717-r958003501-Eagle_Peak_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Didn‚Äôt enjoy it all and ended up sick', 'Food is terrible (tasteless, very fatty and heavy, ingredients of very poor quality) and overpriced for what it is. \nIf you wanna eat junk food, go to Burger kings, much more tasty and so much cheaper. \nWe spent over 10,000 ksh (family of 4) for a meal that wasn‚Äôt great at all. \n\nI had a very bad tummy right away and ended up vomiting home. \nWon‚Äôt be back. \nService was good though.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(387, 'Murtaza B', 'Shop B1, The Hub, Dagoretti Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Eagle Peak Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10804717-r931291341-Eagle_Peak_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'MUSLIMS BE AWARE. ALL MEAT BARBECUES HAPPEN ON THE SAME GRILL. ', 'THIS PLACE USES THE SAME GRILL TO BARBECUE THE BEEF AND PORK. THEY ARE DISHONEST THAT THEY COOK IT SEPARATE... I CHECKED AND MADE SURE..OTHER GRILL THEY CLAIM TO SHOW CANNOT BARBECUE THE STEAK, ITS THE ONE WHERE YOU FRY EGGS...I KNOW BECAUSE I HAVE WORKED AT A FAST FOOD JOINT.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(388, 'Repher M', 'Shop B1, The Hub, Dagoretti Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Eagle Peak Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10804717-r924943822-Eagle_Peak_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'I had the best experience with my family over dinner ', 'Perfect ambience, excellent service, mouth-watering meals! Their pork ribs are to die for. Definitely coming back ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(389, 'Martin Mutua', 'Shop B1, The Hub, Dagoretti Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Eagle Peak Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10804717-r923059225-Eagle_Peak_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent service ', 'Excellent service from Susan. She knows the menu well and is very confident. She went the extra mile to ensure the babies were comfortable and busy. Will definitely be back because of her warm  and excellent service', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(390, 'Jerome S', 'Shop B1, The Hub, Dagoretti Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Eagle Peak Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10804717-r878290153-Eagle_Peak_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Good food', 'I visited the restaurant last week Saturday, great customer service the blueberry milkshake was just as good as I remembered it to be. Paul was our server for the night and he was great. Enjoyed mt time there.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(391, 'Peter M', 'Shop B1, The Hub, Dagoretti Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Eagle Peak Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10804717-r857038842-Eagle_Peak_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Good location; OK food', 'Spur has been a long-standing favorite of mine; for 20+ years. I have always enjoyed the chicken and rib combo. In this particular instance, the chicken was burned and the ribs appeared to have been boiled and dipped in sauce. \nGranted the restaurant was very busy; with lots of patrons. However, given my high expectations, I was quite disappointed by the meal.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(392, 'Caroline W', 'Shop B1, The Hub, Dagoretti Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Eagle Peak Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10804717-r772060237-Eagle_Peak_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Beautiful family experience', 'I took my son\'s birthday at the spur hub..the staff were so kids friendly and made the day worth at the place..the customer service is tick, Very fast and efficient..the ribs were well done and very tasty.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(393, 'Repher M', 'Shop B1, The Hub, Dagoretti Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Eagle Peak Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10804717-r772058783-Eagle_Peak_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Best ribs I have tasted!', 'I visited Eagle Spur Karen last Thursday and I must say my friends and I had a wonderful time. Those ribs üòãüòãüòãüòã,top notch customer service, beautiful sitting arrangement. We shall be back', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(394, 'Livono', 'Shop B1, The Hub, Dagoretti Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Eagle Peak Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10804717-r744175419-Eagle_Peak_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Twice disappointed third time its a wrap. ', 'Happened to be at the hub and since was hungry needed something quickly. We had done a breakfast at this place before so it was easier to just pop in. Our server Josephat was friendly. We ordered for usual coffee which was done well and honestly that was the only good thing we liked. For starter we had their prawns in cheese served with garlic bread. The prawns were so tiny and really bland and just immersed in heavy cheese sauce. We did their burger 2 in 1 for 1k as recommended by Josephat. My partner wanted hers medium rare but Josephat advised her to do medium well cause he thought she doesnt know what medium rare isüòÇüòÇüòÇüòÇüòÇ. Out of respect to him and not to burst his bubble we asked for medium. The burger came well done, fries soggy and the supposed onion rings bland and not palatable.The beef patte was very cold. Honestly the meal really looked horrible and ruined entire experience. \nJosephat was quick enough to apologise and was professional enough to want to do service recovery. We wanted to meet the manager and share feedback and since she was sitting with her assistant she was kind enough not to talk to us and all of a sudden became busy to go bring our check. \nFew things to note: \n1. This is the third spur have attended and seems all of them dont understand doneness of meat\n2. Customer care is wanting and so is attention to details \n3. Its easier to be stereotyped when wanting a certain doneness of meat. I guess africans we dont take meat medium rare or rare....\n4. There is always hesitation by management to get feedback. \n\nFor me its wrap. Am WELL DONE with spur restaurants. I guess am jinxed with them.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(395, 'Mark Ngugi', 'Shop B1, The Hub, Dagoretti Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Eagle Peak Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10804717-r707436795-Eagle_Peak_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'BEST RIBS EVER! I had an amazing experience at The Eagle Peak Spur! Can\'t wait to be back!', 'It was super warm, the customer  service was really on point and the food was incredibly tasty! I enjoyed and so did my friends!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(396, 'Dany K', 'Shop B1, The Hub, Dagoretti Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Eagle Peak Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10804717-r686328450-Eagle_Peak_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Birthday lunch', 'I went with my family(table for 12) for my daughters birthday on 30th June at the hub Karen branch and the service was great and we enjoyed the food and the way you guys sing happy Birthday.It was second time having a birthday lunch there and we might come back again for more', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(397, 'Margaret H', 'Shop B1, The Hub, Dagoretti Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Eagle Peak Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10804717-r611031030-Eagle_Peak_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'LOTS of meat', 'This restaurant specializes in MEAT! I went with a fairly large group and saw various meat dishes. I semi enjoyed my steak though the french fries and onion rings with it were not great. The Kenyan men in our group appreciated the amount of meat they could eat, I would have liked a bit more quality over quantity. Good pleasant service. Try the Dawa  - a hot drink with ginger and honey.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(398, 'AamirSK', 'Shop B1, The Hub, Dagoretti Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Eagle Peak Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10804717-r584545137-Eagle_Peak_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Whata steak ', 'No doubt the best steaks in town! We went to the Hub branch and really enjoyed our meal. Would definitely go again to try other varieties of steaks they have. However, they need to only improve on their onion rings-they were soggy and oily-need them to be crispy & their fries also need a bit of improvement.. otherwise one word for spurs-awesome!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(399, 'Rora B', 'Shop B1, The Hub, Dagoretti Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Eagle Peak Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10804717-r560277630-Eagle_Peak_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Great Ribs', 'My baby and i went here for lunch while shopping at the hub. It was a work day so the place wasnt full;we easily got a table. We sat in one of the booths...\nWe had the ribs and a combo meal both served with chips and onion rings..The ribs are to die for...\nThey are fairly priced..\nWill definitely go back..üòäüòä', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(400, 'Basm21', 'Shop B1, The Hub, Dagoretti Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Eagle Peak Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10804717-r515243485-Eagle_Peak_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Disappointed ', 'Went there for dinner with the family. \nOrdered the T-bone steak and kids ordered the kids steak. \nBoth were disappointing. I wanted my steak well done and got is a bit rare. The baked potato was dry and onion rings a mess. \nThe kids fries were also dry. \nThe staff were not that attentive. To pay the bill had to ask a few times for the bill. At the end went to the counter to tell them wanted to pay. \nDon\'t think will be going there again. ', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(401, 'Expectmoretoday', 'Shop B1, The Hub, Dagoretti Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Eagle Peak Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10804717-r450383604-Eagle_Peak_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Good service, tasty food', 'This is a restaurant looking onto to the open courtyard where there is plenty of activity. The food is served quickly and the children loved their pork ribs. The portions are large so there is plenty to take home. My fish was a little underwhelming and perhaps one should stick to the core part of the menu (meat). The lamb was also much appreciated.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(402, 'Aliasgher Z', 'Shop B1, The Hub, Dagoretti Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Eagle Peak Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10804717-r431709146-Eagle_Peak_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Steak & Burgers Par Excellence', 'Have visited this restaurant a few times since they opened.\n\nThe set up of the restaurant is likened to a typical fast food joint. The atmosphere is very informal. I like the open plan seating and kitchen.\n\nThe steaks like all the other Spur restaurants in Kenya are excellent.\n\nThe gourmet burgers are awesome.\n\nMake sure to take advantage of their Monday Burger Deal and their Wednesday deal.\n\nOverall great experience.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(403, 'Sheela V', 'Shop B1, The Hub, Dagoretti Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Eagle Peak Spur', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10804717-r413120272-Eagle_Peak_Spur-Nairobi.html', 'Experience', 'Eagle Peak Spurs is located within the newly opened shopping Mall called \'Hub\'. They have very good environment for people. For the meat eaters Eagle Peak Spurs is the answer. There are othe cuisines available, exclusive wines available, free wifi available. Lot of open air available , relax in water gardens.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(404, 'richj65', 'Uniafric House Koinange Street, Nairobi 00505 Kenya', 'Java House Uniafric', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3339969-r1009221094-Java_House_Uniafric-Nairobi.html', 'Not a real mexican restaurant ', 'The service was slow, but the restaurant was busy. The food was nicely prepared and tasted will. The price was reasonable, and the portion size is generous. Many items on the menu to choose from.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(405, 'Clever', 'Uniafric House Koinange Street, Nairobi 00505 Kenya', 'Java House Uniafric', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3339969-r942277593-Java_House_Uniafric-Nairobi.html', 'Saturday Lunch', 'Called in Saturday lunchtime and surprised how quiet it was, which was to our benefit in being more relaxing. Our meals and drinks we found to be to our satisfaction.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(406, 'Lpoko258', 'Uniafric House Koinange Street, Nairobi 00505 Kenya', 'Java House Uniafric', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3339969-r850659925-Java_House_Uniafric-Nairobi.html', 'A nice place for an afternoon rest', 'I came in for a coffee and a brownie and I wasn‚Äôt disappointed! They were both large portions and very tasty. (Ask for the brownie to be warmed up a little!) the price was very good for both items.\nService was efficient and with a smile! If I had more time in Nairobi I‚Äôd definitely return again.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(407, 'Gathigia Murimi', 'Uniafric House Koinange Street, Nairobi 00505 Kenya', 'Java House Uniafric', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3339969-r816979320-Java_House_Uniafric-Nairobi.html', 'Undercooked food', 'I ordered take out from Java Koinange Street and I was very disappointed. Their french fries were under-cooked and the burger was lacking taste. I would advise not to order out from them but eat in; in order to raise any concerns one has.\n', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(408, 'Goldie S', 'Uniafric House Koinange Street, Nairobi 00505 Kenya', 'Java House Uniafric', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3339969-r776133787-Java_House_Uniafric-Nairobi.html', 'One of the best restaurants', 'I mean Javaüôå they really  do a good job  but....sike I know you guys thought I was gonna say something bad but nah good coffee,food and customer care that\'s all that matters right now in this period so thanks Java, without the restaurant it would have been boring and it\'s where i hangout with my gs so thanks. ‚ù§Ô∏è‚ù§Ô∏è', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\"]'),
