(421, 'Andrew H', 'Uniafric House Koinange Street, Nairobi 00505 Kenya', 'Java House Uniafric', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3339969-r535368198-Java_House_Uniafric-Nairobi.html', 'Great place', 'Lovely place to relax and unwind after walking the city.  Free wifi and a very comprehensive menu.  Called in regular on our city visits for teas, coffee and the local \'gawa\' which was the ginger, lemon and honey drink.  You certainly knew it had ginger in and certainly pepped you up!!  Tried some of the pastries which were very nice.  Quite a few of the Java Houses around the city... worth a try', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
