(423, 'Mama\'s Devil', 'Uniafric House Koinange Street, Nairobi 00505 Kenya', 'Java House Uniafric', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3339969-r512723346-Java_House_Uniafric-Nairobi.html', 'Bad bad food', 'Went to buy sandwich for me and my colleague at prestige mall 1 was turkey sandwich which I ate it\'s mad me horribly sick I\'m shocked that java can sell bad food first and last time I walk into java my colleague got a chicken sandwich well it was only bread and chicken no salads notjing total rip off you\'ve lost 2 customers I\'m nauseated by just recall your food I bought today at 2 pm it was so bad  ', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\"]'),
(424, 'LondonMet22', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r875163509-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Jade at Zen Garden', '3 of us arrived for the first time there.  Reviews were good so thought it\'ll be amazing but service was shoddy, everything takes long.  First they forgot our order (first item) after telling us to wait, so we replaced it with something.  We still wanted our Puff pastry that they forgot about so we reordered and it arrived with plastic inside.  To add insult to injury, they tried to charge us more.  The manager looked like he doesn\'t really care when we told him that there is plastic in our food, all they did was remove the item from the bill but not compensating anyone for their wait and that there is plastic inside the food.  Its a place only to enjoy the garden if thats your thing but everything is overpriced and not worth the value.  Nairobi is bursting with better places!!!! Dont bother going!!!', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(425, 'Icareforquality', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r874012149-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Oasis of great good in Nairobi', 'Lovely meal - with outstanding beef such roll (chef recommendation). We would certainly visit again!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(426, 'Gurpreet B', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r870574492-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'SUPERB EXPERIENCE ‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è', 'We went for dinner and had a great diner experience, cozy ambiance, our food was served within 15mins and it was all extremely pleasant! Couldn‚Äôt say more about the staff, they are friendly and the Head Chef was so accommodating, nice and always approachable.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(427, 'bd', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r867393098-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'The head chef is rude and only cares about her position!', 'I always go to zen for meals and always had a great time. The last time I went I had an issue with my order. The head chef doesn‚Äôt even regard it. All she talked about is how she is the head chef and knows what‚Äôs right! She messed up the entire order and was so rude to us ! When I tried to speak to her she said whatever and walked away! \n\nI wanted to throw the plate at her face since she all she cared about was that she is the head chef! \n\nIt then took them another 45 minutes to bring the bill.\n\nIt used to be an amazing g place and I would always take my friends there. But now it‚Äôs become like pigsty', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(428, 'hcb81', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r864001024-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Overpriced and underwhelming', 'Uninspiring menu. When the food arrived it was decidedly average (with the exception of an excellent prawn toast), particularly given the price. At this price I expect the food to be a cut above and it was nothing special at all. It was bog standard Chinese food at Michelin prices. My cocktail was rubbish, it was so watered down it was more like a mocktail. The restaurant was also really dirty, they had obviously had lots of large parties in and hasn\'t been able to keep on top of the cleaning so it felt grubby. The service was ok, not great, the waiter seemed over stretched. I also found the place lacking in intimacy, it was so huge it felt like a conference centre but maybe that is personal taste. It also made no sense to me that there was a playground which you couldn\'t see from the tables. Not ideal for small children. I won\'t go back.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(429, 'AvdV80', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r859429075-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Great service and quality!', 'What a great first time experience at Zen Garden!\n\nGreat location with options for seating ranging from family area to romantic seating. As we came in the afternoon we opted to sit outside. \n\nFrom arrival here to departure we were well taken care of by our excellent waiter which treated us like family!\n\nThe menu is extensive and there are different options. I opted to go for sushi and did not regret this choice. Excellent quality and portion size.\n\nAs mentioned service during our visit was exceptional.\n\nDefinately will be back in the future!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(430, 'B.R', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r852392395-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Substandard ', 'Substandard food, poor service. I think this is one restaurant where your judged by your appearance. 5 to 6 idle waiters but you can only draw the attention of them if you jump and shout or happen to have several bottles of booze on the table.\nHalf fried tempura and the most revolting dimsum. Wet, smelly and the tempura the inside cornflour was soaked in oil and improperly fried.\nHeard a crunch (no it wasnt the soggy batter) but was part of an egg shell.\n\nCouldn\'t be bothered to complain, hardly got an interested server!', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\"]'),
(431, 'Ruhi Patel', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r850019367-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Fun and Food', 'It is a great place as there are several dinning places such as outdoor and indoor with fresh air enjoyment and great for kids to run around. Everything is offered including tea and coffee and the Thai is a must to have!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(432, 'Ravinder S', 'Lower Kabete Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Zen Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13089847-r847486823-Zen_Garden-Nairobi.html', 'Impressive ambiance', 'This place is a gem of a find located in lush manicured gardens. Service was very impressive with polite staff. Food was great, well prepared and full of flavour. Really enjoyed our lunch, plus it‚Äôs always good when a place is busy.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
