(445, 'Makiya R', 'Imaara Shopping Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Cjs - Imaara', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d25184060-r941703096-Cjs_Imaara-Nairobi.html', 'The Imara Cj Immaculate Experience', 'Of all Cj restaurants Cj Imaara customer experience is Stellar, the ambience Immaculate, the service per excellence. Being served by Valerie M was divine. The manager was Jolly and with positive empathy, great with customers and his staff, I would go back a million times because of them. From Eli, Stellar, Tecla, Sally, Kelvin,Baraka & Makiya , we would implore you visit this place if you want tobe thawed by the Cj exquisite experience. If you ever think of Cj, Imaara is certanily the Standard Measure :)', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(446, 'Musyoki M', 'Imaara Shopping Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Cjs - Imaara', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d25184060-r938789394-Cjs_Imaara-Nairobi.html', 'Best all rounded Restaurant Experience in Nairobi!', 'CJs gave us a good to better to bestest! What makes a place great is the people. I was skeptical going in because we have a 10 month in the \'grab everything\' stage and a 10 year old,the lady who received us told me that my baby  is welcomed and can grab any of them! And from then on everything went uphill! Esther our server was exceptional giving tips and answering our zillion questions and \'driving\' our baby girl around,then the very humane and wonderful gentleman manager whose name starts with a Z just capped our night. He brought us hot water to soak our baby\'s bottle nipple when it fell down! As a mother and Kenyan American,he was our hero and true representation of my country\'s hospitality. Thank you Mr.Z,thank you Esther and thanks to the chefs for sumptuous meals that are well priced. We definitely are coming back as a bigger team. Make this your stop from their airport when you land in Kenya.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
