(616, 'Rebecca M', 'Lonrho House Standard St, Nairobi Kenya', 'Cafe AMKA', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d25398977-r1001676761-Cafe_AMKA-Nairobi.html', 'Amazing food + service = a very happy me!', 'Service: 10/10. I was served by Wayne and he was attentive and so lovely. \nThe food 100/10. I had the steak and eggs breakfast with a side of fries and whoa! The salad on this meal is really the star, just a bit sweet and fresh, the perfect balance to the savory steak and eggs. It also comes with a really flavorful butter to drench you whole meal in. I had an amazing time here! Definitely coming back for seconds and thirds!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(617, 'Caren K', 'Lonrho House Standard St, Nairobi Kenya', 'Cafe AMKA', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d25398977-r1001162674-Cafe_AMKA-Nairobi.html', 'Lovely space but the service could be better', 'I recently visited Caf√© Amka in the CBD and was really impressed by the ambiance. It‚Äôs a beautiful, cozy space with lovely music playing in the background, a perfect spot to relax or catch up with friends. However, I found the service quite slow, which took away from the overall experience. I hope they can improve on their service speed because the place has so much potential. I would still recommend it for the atmosphere alone, but be prepared to wait a bit longer than usual.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
