(655, 'Ronnenb', 'Karuna Road Behind Sarit Centre, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asiatic', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d24091722-r961930237-Asiatic-Nairobi.html', 'Positive palate experience.', 'We stayed at the Best Western and for some reason aimed for restaurants elsewhere first whilst we had a pearl of a restaurant just on the 11 floor of the hotel \n\nFirst, I‚Äôll start with the bar, not only that it‚Äôs very cool they also mix very good cocktails and if you arrive between 5pm to 8pm you may get the happy hour, but don‚Äôt be late as we came a few minutes after 8pm and they refused to flex the happy hour time \n\nThe dinner itself was full of surprises, my daughter swore that she had the best curry - her dish was certainly amazing but the other dishes were also of high quality \n\nThe service was good and caring, I do think there‚Äôs still some small room to make it more attentive as we sometimes had to look for our waitress \n\nIf we had more days we would probably come back and try other dishes', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
