(660, 'Elizabeth', 'Karura Forest at Amani Gardens, Off Limuru Road, opposite Belgian Embassy, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'The River Cafe - Karura', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10806639-r783305585-The_River_Cafe_Karura-Nairobi.html', 'I visited this restaurant', 'I visited this restaurant for a late lunch early dinner with friends. The ambience is nice and classy. However food is a bit pricey for the portions. The menu was also a bit limited in choice. However, the staff were nice and friendly', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(661, 'Ashu S', 'Karura Forest at Amani Gardens, Off Limuru Road, opposite Belgian Embassy, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'The River Cafe - Karura', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10806639-r782903449-The_River_Cafe_Karura-Nairobi.html', 'Overview of my visit the River Cafe', 'We decided as a family to visit River Cafe for Breakfast. The atmosphere, location, customer service is prefect, really nice. However, the food quality was very very below average, I think the standard and quality of the foods has gone down at River Cafe.\nIt is a real shame the place has so much potential, but the food is disappointing, even though your paying top prices for the meal. Hope the owners do read this review and do something about the quality of the food.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(662, 'pd1032015', 'Karura Forest at Amani Gardens, Off Limuru Road, opposite Belgian Embassy, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'The River Cafe - Karura', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10806639-r781247673-The_River_Cafe_Karura-Nairobi.html', 'This restaurant is in a nice', 'This restaurant is in a nice place to relax after walking the trails of the Karura Forest. Service was a bit slow. Food and drinks are pricey for Kenya. A $25 shrimp, mango and avocado salad was served with questionable shrimp. Definitely not fresh. The mango and avocado were fine. ', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(663, 'MaRoChPa', 'Karura Forest at Amani Gardens, Off Limuru Road, opposite Belgian Embassy, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'The River Cafe - Karura', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10806639-r778181696-The_River_Cafe_Karura-Nairobi.html', 'Bad service', 'The service is horrible. Waited over 10 minutes to be acknowledged. Finally had to flag down a waiter despite the fact that they were just standing around. ', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"service\"]'),
