(684, 'athandile g', 'Nairobi Serena Hotel Processional Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Cafe Maghreb', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1972492-r1036668513-Cafe_Maghreb-Nairobi.html', 'Amazing Food and Service!', 'The food was amazing!! I enjoyed the Indian cuisine that was served! The service was great!! The food recommendations was as recommended and my expectations were met!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(685, 'hedia b', 'Nairobi Serena Hotel Processional Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Cafe Maghreb', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1972492-r1036589357-Cafe_Maghreb-Nairobi.html', 'Exceptionnel', 'Review for Serena Hotel Nairobi\nI had a wonderful stay at the Serena Hotel Nairobi. The room was very good ‚Äî spacious, comfortable, and perfectly adapted for a disabled person. The bathroom was completely equipped for accessibility, with ramps and everything needed, which made my stay easy and pleasant.\n\nThe hotel itself is beautiful, calm, and very well maintained. It truly feels like an oasis in the middle of Nairobi ‚Äî surrounded by nature, with excellent facilities and a warm atmosphere.\n\nThe staff were exceptionally kind and professional. I would like to give a special mention to Irene from Guest Relations, whose attention and kindness made a real difference, and to Diamantine and Charity at the restaurant, who offered outstanding service with their constant smiles and care.\n\nI sincerely recommend the Serena Hotel Nairobi for anyone visiting the city ‚Äî for its comfort, accessibility, and the exceptional quality of its hospitality.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(686, 'Bile A', 'Nairobi Serena Hotel Processional Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Cafe Maghreb', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1972492-r1034955699-Cafe_Maghreb-Nairobi.html', 'Loved it.', 'Terrific food and service. Food variety and staff is unmatched. Nelly especially, is great. She is very helpful and gracious.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
