(688, 'Culture216403', 'Nairobi Serena Hotel Processional Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Cafe Maghreb', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1972492-r1034632477-Cafe_Maghreb-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent service at Cafe Maghreb', 'Staying at the lovely Nairobi Serena for 3 nights. This morning\'s breakfast experience at Cafe Maghreb was so enjoyable due to the wonderful buffet and excellent service provided by every staff member. We appreciated the wide variety of food and drink, plus the gluten free and non dairy choices. Looking forward to the remainder of our stay at the Serena!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(689, 'tabitha w', 'Nairobi Serena Hotel Processional Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Cafe Maghreb', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1972492-r1034528662-Cafe_Maghreb-Nairobi.html', 'Magnificent', 'Hello Nairobi Serena  Hotel team, I recently visited your hotel for brunch and had a wonderful experience! The food was delicious and the service was top-notch. I particularly enjoyed the pasta , fried butternut and The green tea  brulee . The atmosphere was lovely and the staff were friendly and attentive. Thank you for a great meal, I\'ll definitely be back! \nSpecial thanks to Madam  Ann very Top notch ,Chef Joel M at the dessert sector and Chef Nelly M üéäüéä', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
