(692, 'Amy C', 'Nairobi Serena Hotel Processional Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Cafe Maghreb', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1972492-r1033393856-Cafe_Maghreb-Nairobi.html', 'A Wonderful Experience at the Cafe Maghreb at the Nairobi Serena Hotel', 'The Cafe Maghreb was simply beautiful. The atmosphere was elegant yet relaxed. The staff were friendly, happy and they did a wonderful job making us feel welcome and special. Our server, Raphael, helped us choose dishes that we absolutely loved and all of the food was delicious and plentiful. The night sounds of frogs singing in the beautiful gardens surrounding the Cafe will be unforgettable for us. I would highly recommend this restaurant and the Nairobi Serena Hotel to anyone visiting Kenya!!!!!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(693, 'Pauline M', 'Nairobi Serena Hotel Processional Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Cafe Maghreb', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1972492-r1033235974-Cafe_Maghreb-Nairobi.html', 'Had a wonderful dining experience ‚Äì exceptional service, warm hospitality & great attention to detail.', 'Excellent service from Joseph ‚Äì a humble, kind-hearted & professional young man. Truly a pleasure to deal with. The dinner too was delicious', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
