(695, 'Judith Muloki', 'Nairobi Serena Hotel Processional Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Cafe Maghreb', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1972492-r1032543293-Cafe_Maghreb-Nairobi.html', 'The Simple joys of life that lead to Memories that last a lifetime.', 'We had such a beautiful birthday brunch at Nairobi Serena for my friend. Special thanks to Ann Kimani for the making the booking seamless from beginning to the end. We got in to an already reserved table, perfect place to be able to watch over the littles ones as they swam! Ooh, they had a time of their lives, thanks to you Ann üòç. Serena is now engraved in their minds. Thank you to the team as well for making our day memorable, we enjoyed the singing. We left happier and with brighter faces. We shall definitely be back again soon, and we love everything about Nairobi Serena üòçüòçüòç', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
