(704, 'Bob T', 'Lavington Green Shopping Centre, Nairobi 00603 Kenya', 'Kengeles Lavington Green', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3314018-r885074080-Kengeles_Lavington_Green-Nairobi.html', 'Over billed and dissatisfied ', 'We have enjoyed Kengeles for years. We did enjoy the experience today and asked for the bill. We paid the bill ok only to be given another bill that was larger. We paid the extra large bill and politely querid why we were being charged extra. The manager didn\'t answer our question and actually walked off. We left it but we certainly will not be going back and certainly do not recommend Kengeles as a good joint PEOPLE!!¬∞', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"service\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(705, 'Ole', 'Lavington Green Shopping Centre, Nairobi 00603 Kenya', 'Kengeles Lavington Green', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3314018-r763380327-Kengeles_Lavington_Green-Nairobi.html', 'Quite delicious ', 'Came for lunch+dinner cos I was hungry. Very friendly staff, served very fast - due to Corona there are no people - but still the chef was so fast. And the chicken wrap was perfect - size, taste everything. Had pebersteak 15 min later and it was also very delicious - and the best fries I\'ve tried in Nairobi üòÅ. Nice Mocktails too. Due to curfew there could only be dimmed light (its a normally very lit as it is a bar place), so they brought a candle. The price was very good for what I had. Cannot say anything bad about the visit and will for sure come again. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(706, 'sdmmb', 'Lavington Green Shopping Centre, Nairobi 00603 Kenya', 'Kengeles Lavington Green', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3314018-r748444638-Kengeles_Lavington_Green-Nairobi.html', 'Nice atmosphere and setting', 'Nice atmosphere and setting and great place for a drink and to watch a match.  But the food really was not good at all.   ', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
