(710, 'Byron78', 'Lavington Green Shopping Centre, Nairobi 00603 Kenya', 'Kengeles Lavington Green', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3314018-r688064256-Kengeles_Lavington_Green-Nairobi.html', 'Bubbling with calm energy', 'Met a friend here.Superb band playing a variety of tunes.Can be very noisy depending where one sits.Bar area gets crowded.Varied crowd of expats and locals.A few tables outside adjacent to the front entrance and a smaller section inside next to the inner bar.\nNice chilled out place to catch some tunes and catch up with people.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
