(715, 'Stephen L', 'Lavington Green Shopping Centre, Nairobi 00603 Kenya', 'Kengeles Lavington Green', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3314018-r623954844-Kengeles_Lavington_Green-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent evening with friends', 'Arrived amidst a deluge of rain that had the local roads flooded but were greeted by friendly staff who ushered us to our table and took care of wet umbrellas etc. \nService was very good and the menu duly arrived, both of our meals were very tasty and well presented with the Schwarma being particularly good. \nIf ever in Nairobi and just wanting a relaxed informal meal you will have to look far to find anything equal to this fine establishment. There are many deals offered during the week and details are often posted on social media, their response time to questions on social media is also commendable.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
