(719, 'Liam O', 'Lavington Green Shopping Centre, Nairobi 00603 Kenya', 'Kengeles Lavington Green', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3314018-r565052869-Kengeles_Lavington_Green-Nairobi.html', 'Best Bar in Nairobi by far!', 'Great bar, great staff, great food! I especially love the Sharmer! Very tasty and perfectly spiced. This place has a great atmosphere every night of the week. And a great place to watch football, rugby or cricket. And the staff always greet you with a smile. Very welcoming!! Well done to all involved! Great place.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
