(725, 'Triple A', 'Mawensi Road, Upperhill, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taidy\'s Tavern - Upperhill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23061223-r807211409-Taidy_s_Tavern_Upperhill-Nairobi.html', 'Nice little surprise in the middle of Upper Hill', 'I had lunch here with a friend last week and was pleasantly surprised by the nicely done decor, the friendly ambiance and best of all the food.  A great step up from their previous location near Nairobi West which left alot to be desired.  The service was good, and I loved the spacious set up outside.  Not too bad on the pocket either.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(726, 'Catherine M', 'Stellato Mall, 42, Muthithi Road 2nd Floor, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ezo Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27128080-r1038072575-Ezo_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Aweeeesome Experience!', 'Awesome experience as always! But this time‚Ä¶it was even better üòä\n\nDaniel‚Äôs service was 5 star and the meals engineered by Chef Carlos Wong looked and tasted amaaazing! \n\nLooking forward to attending their popular evening events  tooüíÉüèªüíÉüèªüíÉüèª', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
