(728, 'tyra a', 'Stellato Mall, 42, Muthithi Road 2nd Floor, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ezo Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27128080-r1038072300-Ezo_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Delicioso! Yum yum! Scrumptious üòÅ', 'I enjoyed all the courses, especially my mainü§≠ü§≠üòö. The chef Carlos Wong really outdid himself..he engaged us just to know if we enjoyed our mealü§è. Our waiter Daniel really served us with love and ensured we got everything we needed. My experience was 10/10 minus nothing üòö', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(729, 'Antoinne k', 'Stellato Mall, 42, Muthithi Road 2nd Floor, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ezo Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27128080-r1038072199-Ezo_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Top-Tier Service', 'Had a great experience at Ezo today. The head chef, Carlos Wong, personally came over to talk to us about our experience and asked for feedback, which really showed how much they care about their guests. The waiter, Daniel, was also really friendly and attentive great service overall. The food and atmosphere made the whole visit worth it. Definitely a place I‚Äôd come back to.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
