(732, 'frank v', 'Stellato Mall, 42, Muthithi Road 2nd Floor, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ezo Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27128080-r1037314811-Ezo_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Best dinner in nairobi', 'Great quality of food. With good service. The wait time is good and If you want to slow down its no problem. They give you great value for money.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\"]'),
(733, 'Al B', 'Stellato Mall, 42, Muthithi Road 2nd Floor, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ezo Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27128080-r1036665840-Ezo_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Absolutely FABULOUS!!!', 'Absolutely fabulous! The food was out of this world. My wife and I came here after another restaurant didn\'t have the advertised steak. Ezo saved the night. I had the Nasi Goreng chicken and shrimp (delicious!). My wife had he ribeye, medium well with garlic mashed potatoes (delicious!). We finished dinner off with a dessert pina colada Leche Flan (Absolutely DELICIOUS!!!). We have been celebrating our anniversary for the last few weeks in Africa. We\'ve eaten at some pretty amazing restaurants. Ezo is at the to of our list as the best so far. Agatha, our waitress was superb. She was the most attentive yet. We actually had new silverware AND napkin exchange service for each course (3). Amazing! Thank you for making this night special for my wife and I. We spent roughly $80 for everything. We will definitely return.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(734, 'Elizabeth K', 'Stellato Mall, 42, Muthithi Road 2nd Floor, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ezo Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27128080-r1036518241-Ezo_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent service', 'The ambience is everything.  Daniel served us perfectly and I enjoyed every moment of it!!! I love love Ezo restaurant.\nWill definitely revisit.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"atmosphere\"]'),
(735, 'Njuguna E', 'Stellato Mall, 42, Muthithi Road 2nd Floor, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ezo Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27128080-r1000049735-Ezo_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', '200% good service', 'Daniel, Christine  and Denis they offered really good service. Thank you for making my birthday a dream come true. \nTill next time, keep it up.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(736, '–≠–ª—å–≤–∏—Ä–∞ –ê', 'Stellato Mall, 42, Muthithi Road 2nd Floor, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ezo Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27128080-r988872490-Ezo_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'The best gunkans in the city!', 'We recently ordered sushi delivery from EZO and were very pleased! The best gunkans in the city, that\'s for sure. We especially want to highlight the gunkans with red caviar and shrimp, their flavors were incredibly rich. Even soy sauce wasn\'t needed, as the rolls were so delicious!\n\nOur cat didn\'t miss out either; she really wanted to try a piece! We will definitely order again. We recommend it to all sushi lovers!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"delivery_takeout\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(737, 'Richard M', 'Stellato Mall, 42, Muthithi Road 2nd Floor, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ezo Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27128080-r983889644-Ezo_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Best Restaurant in Nairobi - Fine Dining', 'From the hostess to the Waitstaff, the service was phenomenal. The design of the dishes is creative yet heartwarming. For starters, I had the eel, rice, pumpkin and chamomile mousse. My date had the shrimp tempora roll with avocado. These two dishes were designed to perfection. The flavour profile was absolutely brilliant leaving us impressed and in readiness for the main meal.\n\nFor main, I had red snapper katsu with passion fruit dashi sauce, asparagus and green beans. My date had tonkatsu ramen, pork chashu, wheat noodles and egg. Brilliantly balanced, our socks were knocked off our feet.\n\nAnd the matcha cheese cake!\nOh my! What a dessert!\n\nThank you Maggie, Christine, Rahab and all the staff working dinner service on 10th December 2024. You made our 8th marriage anniversary dinner perfect!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
