(756, 'Jane B', 'Lavington Green Shopping Centre, Nairobi 00603 Kenya', 'Kengeles Lavington Green', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3314018-r564474553-Kengeles_Lavington_Green-Nairobi.html', 'The place was humming', 'I could not resist ordering my favourite starter, barbecued spare ribs, the generous portion together with two baked potatoes, was enough to satisfy me for the evening. I was not disappointed. The taste exactly as I remembered it, probably thirty years ago. How\'s that for consistency!\nThe place was humming, brimful pubby atmosphere, with TVs strategically placed displaying current internationally sports events. Although few people seemed to be watching.\nEfficient, pleasant staff and service despite the crowd. The bill is placed in a glass on your table when the order has been made, saving delays at the end', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
