(759, 'Kevin M. D', 'Lavington Green Shopping Centre, Nairobi 00603 Kenya', 'Kengeles Lavington Green', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3314018-r555389195-Kengeles_Lavington_Green-Nairobi.html', 'Small portions, Overpriced', 'Kengeles is a favorite bar of mine to hang out, but if you are hungry, the value for money to eat there is not a good proposition. The portions of things such as chicken wings are quite small, yet quite pricey. The nachos are way overpriced and leave you wanting for cheese and guacamole.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"portion_size\"]'),
