(763, 'Koosb', 'Lavington Green Shopping Centre, Nairobi 00603 Kenya', 'Kengeles Lavington Green', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3314018-r545687780-Kengeles_Lavington_Green-Nairobi.html', 'Lively place to meet for after work drinks.', 'Great  place in Lavington to meet friends for an after-work drink or listen to live music on Thursday nights. This can be classified as a sports bar since they screen live football and rugby matches but it also serves very nice food. Can be a bit noisy at times but has a lovely vibe.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
