(770, 'Daisy K', 'Woodvale Grove, Nairobi Kenya', 'Havana Bar & Restaurante', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1143745-r956450237-Havana_Bar_Restaurante-Nairobi.html', 'Regretful', 'Worst food and pineapple juice ü§Æ ever. I\'ll never consider them again.\nI and my mzungu boyfriend looked up online and they appeared with the enticing photos. The order delayed so we expected something nice. To our surprise the barbeque steak was bloody by bf couldn\'t eat it, and my pork tasted like failure. The pineapple juice wasn\'t fresh and had a rotten taste. Paid, left the food and went home to order some chicken cottage.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\"]'),
(771, 'Safe Adventures and Expeditions', 'Woodvale Grove, Nairobi Kenya', 'Havana Bar & Restaurante', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1143745-r945961658-Havana_Bar_Restaurante-Nairobi.html', 'A Taste of Cuba in Nairobi Havana Bar & Restaurante', 'Located in Woodvale Grove, Nairobi, Havana Bar & Restaurante offers a lively escape to Cuban flavors and rhythms.\n\nThe vibrant ambiance transports guests to Havana\'s streets, with colorful decor and Latin music. Ideal for casual outings or intimate dinners.\n\nThe menu showcases authentic Cuban cuisine, from savory tostones to tender ropa vieja. Don\'t miss the signature Cuban sandwiches.\n\nThe bar features a variety of rum-based cocktails, including classic mojitos and pi√±a coladas, crafted with fresh ingredients.\n\nThe warm hospitality of the staff makes guests feel at home, ensuring a memorable dining experience.\n\nHavana Bar & Restaurante is a favorite spot for locals and visitors seeking an authentic taste of Cuba in Nairobi.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(772, 'T.O. Baby', 'Woodvale Grove, Nairobi Kenya', 'Havana Bar & Restaurante', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1143745-r945701231-Havana_Bar_Restaurante-Nairobi.html', 'B+', 'Good bar, shareable portions food. Drinks fair priced and good. Decent atmosphere although no photos or vids allowed. At least at night', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(773, 'IGOR J', 'Woodvale Grove, Nairobi Kenya', 'Havana Bar & Restaurante', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1143745-r878232602-Havana_Bar_Restaurante-Nairobi.html', 'nice experience', 'fully satisfied my expectations, they are very caring, everything is as it should be, just let them stay as they are', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(774, 'Capellanus', 'Woodvale Grove, Nairobi Kenya', 'Havana Bar & Restaurante', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1143745-r783705769-Havana_Bar_Restaurante-Nairobi.html', 'Great Spot of a Busy Lane', 'Havana\'s is in the heart of Westlands, a busy neighbourhood with lots of traffic and places to visit. I stopped by Havana\'s for a couple of drinks early February and returned to try the food.\n\nThe downstairs is divided into the non-smoking bar and quiet restaurant. You can have the full menu in either location and the menu is worth trying.  For the size and quality of the portions, the price is exceptional. They usually have daily offers that are even better.\n\nTry the short ribs is they are available.\n\nThe wine list is small but does the trick; and it is not overpriced at all relative to the market.  The staff are fund and friendly.\n\nThe bar/restaurant is dark, so be prepared to leave the sunshine behind.  It can get a bit crowded and noisy at times, but this just adds to the energy in the room.  Decent mix of people.\n\nWill definitely return.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(775, 'Gugi', 'Woodvale Grove, Nairobi Kenya', 'Havana Bar & Restaurante', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1143745-r745463602-Havana_Bar_Restaurante-Nairobi.html', 'Cool place', 'Good music, excellent cocktails, friendly but a bit slow staff. Friend of mine asked for an ashtray and bartender gave her a saucer which made us laugh aloud. I\'ll definitely visit Havana again.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(776, 'SaxbyHawk', 'Woodvale Grove, Nairobi Kenya', 'Havana Bar & Restaurante', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1143745-r740031280-Havana_Bar_Restaurante-Nairobi.html', 'Serata ......', '.....aggressiva per la musica che si sente fuori dal locale, una musica stupenda gestita da un Dj giovane ma veramente in gamba con una scaletta musicale invidiabile.... abbiamo mangiato un filetto alla Wellington veramente molto buono cucinato alla grande... una birra rossa doppio malto stupenda e fredda al punto giusto.. il servizio al tavolo fatto da una ragazza sempre con il sorriso sulle labbra e molto preparata curando i particolari del tavolo al quale rivolgo il nostro grazie per come ci ha trattati.  il prezzo finale molto equo quindi rapporto qualit√† prezzo perfetto ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[]');
