(934, 'AKatana', 'Riara Road Inside the Kenya Nairobi Museum, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Valencia Gardens', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4101759-r246644842-Valencia_Gardens-Nairobi.html', 'Good food, great ambience', 'Great Brand, good food, great ambience. Having been there on several occasions, O wouldn\'t say the food is out the ordinary. However, the ambience make up for it. I particularly like the upstairs rooms and outdoor seating', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(935, 'Larissa C', 'Riara Road Inside the Kenya Nairobi Museum, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Valencia Gardens', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4101759-r235087274-Valencia_Gardens-Nairobi.html', 'Muito bonito', 'Lugar muito bonito... Dei uma passada bem r√°pida e n√£o pude aproveitar o lugar todo, mas pude ver o quanto √© lindo! ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[]'),
(936, 'Smilin555', 'Riara Road Inside the Kenya Nairobi Museum, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Valencia Gardens', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4101759-r232144066-Valencia_Gardens-Nairobi.html', 'Nice place to visit', 'I was pleasantly surprised at the ample parking, large garden area and private rooms.\nIt is in a good location in a residential area near Junction Mall. The food was good and the service was good too. A nice place to hang out but if you don\'t like noise or crowds, avoid weekends as they are busy with weddings, private parties, etc. Worth a visit on weekdays for late lunch or snack or a drink.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(937, 'Philip B', 'Riara Road Inside the Kenya Nairobi Museum, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Valencia Gardens', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4101759-r231789767-Valencia_Gardens-Nairobi.html', 'An oasis, fantastic food and service', 'We normally have dinner in the evening and unfortunately haven\'t had the opportunity of checking out the gardens and additional seating area, however the food is excellent. The menu isn\'t large by any measure but what there is to choose from is excellent, well presented and delicious. Try the Chicken Curry Valencia, it\'s Chinese style which I have enjoyed many times. Also the beef shred with onions and spinach is also excellent. I have tried most dishes on their menu and I have never been disappointed. Adequate seating both inside and outside and the staff are friendly, know the menu well, very polite and attentive. An informal, relaxed setting, you feel unhurried. I have tried a number of restaurants in the area and Valencia Garden is by far the best.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(938, 'smwelu', 'Riara Road Inside the Kenya Nairobi Museum, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Valencia Gardens', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4101759-r202400466-Valencia_Gardens-Nairobi.html', 'Nice tucked away restaurant', 'If you want to get away from the hustle and bustle of traffic and city, this is just the place to retreat to. You can enjoy the garden area and the music played is always great wanting to make you dance :)\n\nGreat for family, friends, groups etc and ample garden space for you to spread out to.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(939, 'PaulArts', 'Riara Road Inside the Kenya Nairobi Museum, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Valencia Gardens', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4101759-r183461061-Valencia_Gardens-Nairobi.html', 'Beautiful setting, food not too special', 'We were here yesterday with our boy to have an early diner. The setting of the place is beautiful. There\'s a lot of space for the kids to run around. There\'s a nice play area and great entertainment for the kids. \n\nThe layout outside is very nice as well, it\'s very open but because of the limited number of tables there\'s lot of privacy, which is nice. The food is okay, not too much choice but then again the prices are very nice.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(940, 'JudithMbogo', 'Riara Road Inside the Kenya Nairobi Museum, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Valencia Gardens', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4101759-r183024412-Valencia_Gardens-Nairobi.html', 'Lovely cuisines and wonderful outdoor ambience', 'This place looks quite beautiful at night, however, have never been there during the day. The gardens are wonderful and look even better with the night lights. The place has both indoor and outdoor settings depending on what sort of visit one has made (private rooms are also available). The gardens are best for parties where tents are usually put up. Otherwise on a random evening like a Friday night it is such a good place to unwind over a meal and drinks. It is also a nice venue for events, parties and outings. Then we come to the food, amazing continental meals are usually prepared. They have a wide selection of food and also prepare for large numbers say when there events and such like things. Th ambiance is lovely for families, couples, friends and various events. I would recommend it any day, mostly on weekends.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(941, 'Robert K', 'Riara Road Inside the Kenya Nairobi Museum, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Valencia Gardens', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4101759-r169623806-Valencia_Gardens-Nairobi.html', 'My favorite spot in Nairobi', 'This is a great restaurant with keen and friendly staff. I come here regularly and I must admit it is my favorite spot in Nairobi. ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(942, 'Richard K', 'Odyssey Plaza, Mkoma Rd, South B, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Posh Bakery', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23063644-r936593377-Posh_Bakery-Nairobi.html', 'Service was excellent', 'The best snacks and cakes...loved every bit of it... Highly recommend\nThe ambience is top notch.... everything about the place is amazing', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(943, 'Expat Kate', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r985247749-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Great experience', 'Let me start by saying that at first I was annoyed with this restaurant because most of the dishes that I wanted to order were not available. \n\nHowever, I was not disappointed with the orders I made. This is a great place all round. I don‚Äôt know why I‚Äôve never made a stop here on my frequent visits to Westgate Mall. \n\nWhenever I am dining out, I also consider the speed of service to be a significant factor. The server was very friendly and super efficient. \n\nOver all the menu is surprisingly reasonably priced. I can‚Äôt fault the food. My dishes were all spot on. The place has a really great atmosphere with a great selection of chilled music. \n\nThe chicken skewers with salsa verde were excellent. The chicken was moist and very flavorful. The sliced pepper beef was a tad too peppery for me but it was nice. Absolutely delicious paprika potato wedges with homemade garlic mayo. Any fussy eater would enjoy this üòã.\n\nMy experience at Tapas was nothing short of exceptional. I will be definitely be back.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(944, 'Thomas K', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r958524815-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Great place for tapas in Nairobi', 'Many dishes to choose from. Remember each dish is not full size, you need at least 3 dishes. During lunch they have a set menu at a good price, but I was too late for that. The food was delicious and good service too. My favorite was the coliflower and the tuna and avocado', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(945, 'AS', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r931760233-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Great food, team were amazing. Must visit.', 'Really impressed with food, authentic and tasty, nice menu which was easy to navigate, chorizo, paella and cauliflower dishes were stand out. Also very impressed with the cocktails, theatrical but also very well balanced.\nDecor was charming, my table of 8 sat on a large table. I also have to mention the team they were charming, attentive and had personality which I haven\'t really seen around town. Must try', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(946, 'Robin D', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r908811876-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Lecker, faire Preise und guter Service', 'Super leckere Tapas zu fairem Preis. Der Service war schnell und sehr nett. Wir k√∂nnten sogar das Mittagsangebot noch nutzen, obwohl wir au√üerhalb der Angebotszeit waren.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(947, 'Biruk K', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r896368026-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent place, super friendly staff', 'After shopping at Westgate, someone recommended this place for dinner and drinks. My wife and I loved the place. Good ambiance, good cocktails, and food. Don\'t be shocked if the staff suggests you order 5 or 6 dishes. The food is for sharing and comes in small portions. The owners are super friendly couples who make you feel welcome.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(948, 'AvdV80', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r855477334-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Great dinner at the outdoor area!', 'First time dinner experience at Tapas while staying in Nairobi for a couple of days.\n\nThe restaurant is conveniently located in the Westgate Mall. Tapas has both indoor and outdoor seating available.\n\nIt was a nice evening so we opted to sit outside. Service was great from the moment we stepped in to our farewells. Great suggestions from the menu and food came out quick and was of good quality. We ordered several times and never got disappointed.\n\nGreat food option when you are staying in the area!', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(949, 'hcb81', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r852406923-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Lovely food', 'Really enjoyable, tasty meal. Each of the tapas dishes we ordered were lovely. The sangria was great. The churros excellent. Lovely staff who were super friendly to our little person.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(950, 'Shane Bishop', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r851063329-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Enjoyable Drinks.', 'Visited here for drinks after the Westgate Mall. Very good ambiance very friendly staff. Good value during happy hour. Would definitely recommend for a chilled out hour.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(951, 'Meenah', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r842644101-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Ceviche and happy hour', 'Enjoyed happy hour at tapas ceviche bar. Food was good and ambiance was great as well. Ordered a tuna and avocado ceviche and the beef carpaccio. Both tasted good and overall i was happy', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(952, 'beachbummer75', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r812830763-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'nice dinner getaway with great service and good food', 'it was full but the waiter took effort to find a nice outside table for us by making some adjustments\n\nWe had - Peruvian cerviche, prawns calamari, lamb meatballs, salad \n\nWe didn‚Äôt have dessert as we were too full \n\nOverall it was good and recommended', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(953, 'Stephanie', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r809562122-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Simply divine', 'We had gone with our 2 year old and the waitress Janet was very accommodating when it came to our child. She had provided really good service and was very helpful with recommending food. The food was very good as well. It has been two years since we went to tapas and the standard of food is equally as good now as it was then. Not a fan of the sangria but that is just my personal taste. Hubby enjoyed it. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(954, 'Ben B', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r809027719-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Fantastic Tapas', 'For whatever reason, I have reservations about eating in Malls. \nTapas Ceviche is situated in Westgate Mall, so I didn\'t hold much excitement when I visited.\nThat said, this place completely changed my mind and when you\'re inside the restaurant, you\'re certainly not going to feel like you\'re a mall.\n\nOur service was fantastic, a really great waiter with great knowledge and enthusiasm. \nWe opted for the lunch special offer which is 3 Tapas dishes, we had twice, so 3 dishes each and the food was excellently prepared, fresh and all good portions.  \n\nThe wine is pricey, so  stuck to Tusker, my wife had the pineapple cocktail served in a pineapple, think that\'s one of their best sellers, it\'s worth the money and really tasty. \n\nI\'d definitely visit again.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(955, 'Melsa O', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r776377158-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'A place to visit', 'I loved their sangria, delicious and generous! The pineapple cocktail was beautifully presented. Food wise, I explored a number their tasty tapas and was not disappointed.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(956, 'wandis2020', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r752587247-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Sensational Sangrias!', 'Popped in late night after the mall had long closed, to discover this gem within walking distance of our hotel.  The kitchen was closing soon, but the chef sent out a few simple tapas and the most amazing (an generous) sangrias I\'ve ever had!  We couldn\'t finish the pitcher!\nWe were quite festive and loud, however the staff remained gracious throughout our visit.  Our waitress was particularly amusing with her delight sense of humor. \nAfter enjoying a multitude a delectable nibbles and waaaay too much sangria, we stumbled back to our hotel, satiated and happy!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(957, 'Ann M', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r752208302-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'It is up market and deliver like a local.', 'The Tapas is a favourite of mine, friendly service and good wine. Although the wine is expensive which being Scottish meant I explored some cocktails. Thanks to the bar staff, They will know who I am. Much appreciated,', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(958, 'janki', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r750591181-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'A place to visit for sure', 'I am in love with their pineapple cocktail..it\'s a shame I can\'t remember the name on the menu, but the waiters know the drink if u mention the pineapple drink.. it\'s my all time favourite...  \nFood wise - not a fan, but still rate it 4 stars due to their service and the drink that makes up my mood for all occasions..', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(959, 'Gugi', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r745705679-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Amazing tapas!', 'Prawns, eggplant or tuna? I can\'t say what was better. Absolutely amazing food! Ambience ok, staff very professional, prices bit on a higher side (for tapas) at least comparing it with K\'la restaurants prices. Happy hour is a must, but not all drinks are on special during happy hour, so ask for recommendation from a waitress üòâ I\'ll definitely go back when in Nairobi.Big like!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(960, 'Whitney', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r723163817-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Happy hour and tapas!', 'A great place to stop after a day of shopping! They have happy hour everyday from 4pm-7pm where you buy one drink and get one free. They have a wide selection of tapas to choose from. Lot of vegetarian options! I got the fried cauliflower, fried potatoes and grilled eggplant! They all were tasty and great for sharing as we sipped our drinks.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(961, 'Larry4Africa', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r717926062-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'NIce Atmosphere', 'A relatively new establishment, (owned by Artcaffe) located in the Westgate Mall, has a great outdoor patio and indoor seating. They serve tapas and the price was right, and food delicious. The staff was excellent, and the tunes were upbeat.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(962, 'desire_ph_nbo', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r716072164-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Cheers to happy hour and sangrias!', 'Your sangrias are the best & your cocktails served in a pineapple fruit is a delight to drink. But please make sure you have enough of the fruit so presentation is not compromised. Please have chorizos available.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\"]'),
