(981, 'Ellen A', 'Nairobi Serena Hotel Nairobi Serena Hotel, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Aksum Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d28043573-r1030041129-Aksum_Bar-Nairobi.html', '5 stars!', 'Vincent, Eric and Stephen were an absolute dream! They looked after us so well, were so attentive - making sure we had all we needed, were quick with the service and so kind & friendly. We also had the Nyama Choma which was delicious! Cocktails are also lovely. Thank you to Aksum and the team for making our anniversary and birthday celebrations so special! I\'d definitely recommend!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
