(987, 'wayne y', 'Waiyaki way Shell Service Station opposite Safaricom HQ, Nairobi 00505 Kenya', 'Java House Waiyaki way', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d14029194-r604862445-Java_House_Waiyaki_way-Nairobi.html', 'Great Location, Food and Service!', 'This Java House is within walking distance of a Hampton House (A Missionary Guest House), where we frequently stay when we are in Nairobi.  The atmosphere is great as are most Java Houses.  This one features an indoor section as well as a semi-outdoor dining area.  The staff is friendly and the food is good. Java House is a great choice for those wanting \"American\" food and is often frequented by expats.  They offer a variety of foods from African, American to Mexican.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(988, 'karana o', 'Waiyaki way Shell Service Station opposite Safaricom HQ, Nairobi 00505 Kenya', 'Java House Waiyaki way', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d14029194-r580978871-Java_House_Waiyaki_way-Nairobi.html', 'Great vegetarian and vegan fare', 'My wife and I had a delicious lunch there. I am vegan and she is vegetarian and we ordered the curry vegetables. It was delicious. We loved the atmosphere as well. The only problem was the service. It is super busy and the service was a little slow. But we returned at off-peak time and had no problem getting good service here.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(989, 'Benedict B', 'Galana Road Ground Floor, Senteu Plaza, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ankole Grill Kilimani', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12626874-r1014197201-Ankole_Grill_Kilimani-Nairobi.html', 'A Rib-Eye Steak Experience Worth Savoring at Ankole Grill!', 'Ankole Grill truly delivers a memorable dining experience! The ambience is cozy, elegant, and welcoming ‚Äî perfect for a relaxing lunch or a quiet dinner.\n\nI tried their Rib-eye steak and I must say, it was absolutely delightful! Juicy, tender, and perfectly seasoned, each bite was full of rich, smoky flavor that made the whole meal unforgettable. You can tell they put care into the grilling and presentation.\n\nThe staff were kind, attentive, and made sure everything was just right from start to finish. I also loved the little touches ‚Äî the beautiful setup, the warmth of the place, and the way they make you feel at home.\n\nIf you‚Äôre looking for a great spot to enjoy a well-made steak in Nairobi, I‚Äôd definitely recommend Ankole Grill. Their Rib-eye is a must-try!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(990, 'Azimi R', 'Galana Road Ground Floor, Senteu Plaza, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ankole Grill Kilimani', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12626874-r932204158-Ankole_Grill_Kilimani-Nairobi.html', 'Great', 'The service was exceptional, and the cuisine was exquisite. I indulged in the tantalizing spicy mbuzi (lamb), and it was truly delightful.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(991, 'Liv', 'Galana Road Ground Floor, Senteu Plaza, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ankole Grill Kilimani', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12626874-r931274758-Ankole_Grill_Kilimani-Nairobi.html', 'Amazing service üëè ', 'Perfect for an intimate, relaxed day out. \nI love their sorbets. Mango is my favorite, but I decided to try passion and I absolutely loved it. Highly recommended. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"menu_variety\"]'),
(992, 'Salma F', 'Galana Road Ground Floor, Senteu Plaza, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ankole Grill Kilimani', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12626874-r927020553-Ankole_Grill_Kilimani-Nairobi.html', 'Bad customer service ankle grills pls do better I came home very angry ', 'Terrible experience and I would never go back there we met with a very rude waiter( she was a female)who told us that we couldn‚Äôt sit near the fireplace if we weren‚Äôt buying wine. We sat there for an hour without any waiter coming to us. The food we ordered took another 45 minutes so overall it wasn‚Äôt worth it bad customer service but good food!', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(993, 'Messi S', 'Galana Road Ground Floor, Senteu Plaza, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ankole Grill Kilimani', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12626874-r922114610-Ankole_Grill_Kilimani-Nairobi.html', 'Great experience ', 'Great service from Ivan\nHuge and filling portions. Great customer service. Loved the place and the service so much ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(994, 'Videogreg', 'Galana Road Ground Floor, Senteu Plaza, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ankole Grill Kilimani', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12626874-r920106894-Ankole_Grill_Kilimani-Nairobi.html', 'Understated sophistication featuring great food.', 'First class food, ambience, and service. One of the few times in my life I\'ve been able to cut a prime rib steak with my fork. And if the entree wasn\'t good enough, the ice cream and cake for dessert we\'re just delectable. One of the finest dining experiences of my life.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(995, 'cnmtny', 'Galana Road Ground Floor, Senteu Plaza, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ankole Grill Kilimani', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12626874-r917987504-Ankole_Grill_Kilimani-Nairobi.html', 'Steak place?', 'Came with family, highly recommended.  Most of the dishes were well received.  I ordered the Sirloin Steak, medium rare.  When it was served, I cut just the end and it was raw.  I called the waiter to complain and he took it back to be done properly\n  A full 15+ minutes later and they brought me the same steak.  Worried that it might be overdone, I cut it through the middle, and it was raw again.  I do not know what they did with that time.  I gave up and just returned it.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(996, 'Benji N', 'Galana Road Ground Floor, Senteu Plaza, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ankole Grill Kilimani', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12626874-r888078709-Ankole_Grill_Kilimani-Nairobi.html', 'Great place, sumptuous meals.', 'Great warm friendly service, I wish to commend Vincent. Wonderful experience, absolutely! Awesome...', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(997, 'Erika Roman Saint-Pierre', 'Galana Road Ground Floor, Senteu Plaza, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ankole Grill Kilimani', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12626874-r879813000-Ankole_Grill_Kilimani-Nairobi.html', 'Great Food!', 'One of the best restaurants I‚Äôve visited in Nairobi. The food was REALLY good, fresh, and well presented. I highly recommend it.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(998, 'Shera201', 'Galana Road Ground Floor, Senteu Plaza, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ankole Grill Kilimani', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12626874-r877775595-Ankole_Grill_Kilimani-Nairobi.html', 'Reviewing again this restaurant that has a hard time improving', 'Ankole continues to be a let down. Since my last review, they hoard tables less, so I suppose that is a plus (it took an internet review, instead of several in-person complaints from customers to do something).\n\nService continues to be poor, with generally inattentive staff. I was there last Friday afternoon and it took several minutes to be served inspire of us being only the second table to be occupied (I had to walk to the bar area to get help as the team members we in the side room doing some other work and the floor was unattended). \n\nI have found Kate, one of the waitresses, to be the only staff member who both is consistently very quick with customers and also listens to customers. Everyone else is a high-friction experience, including the manager (tried to have a slight change to something as I\'m diabetic, and it took a while to be heard).\n\nSummary: Restaurant is still not good. Kate is great. Best staffers are always moved to Kitisuru / new branch development, so she may disappear, too.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(999, 'TheHedgies', 'Galana Road Ground Floor, Senteu Plaza, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ankole Grill Kilimani', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12626874-r877676491-Ankole_Grill_Kilimani-Nairobi.html', 'Don\'t have the steak...!', 'We arrived early, had a drink at the bar and were then given a nice table. Audrey was our waitress and was very friendly but efficient. I ordered the 290g fillet steak and my partner the 350g ribeye. Both were as tough as old boots - not what you expect in Nairobi.\nWe ate everything else and enjoyed it. We would have let it go as we were enjoying ourselves but then near the end of the meal we noticed the floor manager attending each table but avoiding ours. We paid the bill  but I was annoyed at being ignored so I sought the manager out who then, and only then, offered to refund the steak. We declined and left saying we would let review readers decide.\nI\'d try the burger or pizza, if I was you!', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1000, 'Essie S', 'Galana Road Ground Floor, Senteu Plaza, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ankole Grill Kilimani', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12626874-r875405651-Ankole_Grill_Kilimani-Nairobi.html', 'Dinner', 'Had a great evening with the best meal.\nOur server was Joyce. Appreciate the service and looking forward to dine again', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
