(1005, 'moq', 'Galana Road Ground Floor, Senteu Plaza, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ankole Grill Kilimani', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12626874-r863180208-Ankole_Grill_Kilimani-Nairobi.html', 'Bell\'ambiente', 'Capisco che la gente di nairobi dia la priorit√† alla qualit√† del cibo, ma chi viene qui da qualche paese pi√π freddo non africano ama stare nel verde. Il posto √® incantevole e ben arredato. Per questo un pallino in pi√π. La bistecca era sufficiente. La pizza √® gli antipasti vari buoni. ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(1006, 'Ogake M', 'Galana Road Ground Floor, Senteu Plaza, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ankole Grill Kilimani', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12626874-r862024893-Ankole_Grill_Kilimani-Nairobi.html', 'My Favorite Spot', 'Being very close to my home and office, Ankole offers the perfect loca for a nice afternoon work space with good ambience, great wifi, amazing bitings, and fantastic service. In the evening it‚Äôs a vibe, and I frequently come here with friends for dinner too. The food never disappoints and Josephine knows my top orders by heart. She‚Äôs warm and friendly, and another reason I am loyal to this restaurant. The rest of the staff are amazing too! I only have good things to say about Ankole Kilimani.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
