(1008, 'S H', 'Galana Road Ground Floor, Senteu Plaza, Nairobi Kenya', 'Ankole Grill Kilimani', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12626874-r860627108-Ankole_Grill_Kilimani-Nairobi.html', 'NOT HAPPY AT ALL', 'Brought wrong drink ( Gordon\'s Gin & Tonic instead of Tanqueray,) my wife asked to change so they did, but charged both. Upon her protesting ,the waiter said that if we would not pay for it she was told she would have to pay it for herself!!!!!! Certainly this attitude towards customers and staff is not consistent with the class the establishment claims it belongs!! Morality: STAY AWAY!', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\"]'),
