(1010, 'DRD01', '320 Ngong Road Karen, Nairobi Kenya', 'The Talisman Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1059634-r1035436478-The_Talisman_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Exceptional dining experience at The Talisman!', 'We dined as a group of eight and couldn‚Äôt have been more impressed. From the warm welcome to the final course, everything was first-class. The food was outstanding ‚Äî creative, perfectly cooked, and presented with real flair. The ambience was stylish yet comfortable, and the staff were attentive, friendly, and professional throughout.\n\nIt‚Äôs also great that the restaurant offers secure parking, which added to the convenience of the evening. Overall, an exceptional dining experience ‚Äî we‚Äôll definitely return and highly recommend The Talisman to others.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1011, 'Erik R', '320 Ngong Road Karen, Nairobi Kenya', 'The Talisman Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1059634-r1033508395-The_Talisman_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Super Abendessen f√ºr gro√üe Gruppe', 'Wir waren mit einer Gruppe von 35 Personen in Talismann, alles hat super geklappt. Service super freundlich und schnell. Das Team hat es geschafft die 35 Essen gleichzeitig zu bringen. Qualit√§t und Ambiente super. Waren begeistert', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1012, 'Gill N', '320 Ngong Road Karen, Nairobi Kenya', 'The Talisman Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1059634-r1031136874-The_Talisman_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'A must visit restaurant in Karen (Nairobi)', 'Whenever we come ‚Äòback home‚Äô to Nairobi, the Talisman is always our first stop. We just love the ambience, decor and of course the food!  Those feta and coriander samosas are worth coming for alone‚Ä¶.  The waiters are very friendly, helpful and knowledgeable which makes the experience all the nicer.  We returned for a second visit at the end of our holiday and were taken to ‚Äòour table‚Äô and greeted like lost lost friends.  Hopefully we shall be back soon.\nTutuonane baadaye üòÅ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1013, 'Regina e', '320 Ngong Road Karen, Nairobi Kenya', 'The Talisman Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1059634-r1029918401-The_Talisman_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'The credit goes to Chef Micah for preparing one of the best succulent salmon we‚Äôve ever had..', 'Beautiful and serene  ambiance ever since we stepped our foot there couple of years back. All the service staff are friendly and professional Lord Williamson and I are always privileged to dine with you.. It feels like home away from home .', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1014, 'John B', '320 Ngong Road Karen, Nairobi Kenya', 'The Talisman Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1059634-r1029554195-The_Talisman_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Delicious in a beautiful setting', 'We had a fabulous lunch here. It‚Äôs set in a beautiful garden area with plenty of inside and outside seating. The food was tasty! With the standout dish Beef Carpaccio with crisp beetroot and a truffle cauliflower puree. Our server Stephen was very pleasant and taught us some local language‚Ä¶ Asante sana!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1015, 'Bounce B', '320 Ngong Road Karen, Nairobi Kenya', 'The Talisman Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1059634-r1029180994-The_Talisman_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Yum is the word', 'Yum is the word for all the food you will eat here. Chefs with magic fingers and even the vegetarian dishes like the feta cheese samosas are something that I will be back to savour', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(1016, 'Janet W', '320 Ngong Road Karen, Nairobi Kenya', 'The Talisman Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1059634-r1022394579-The_Talisman_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Girlies Lunch Done Right!', 'Though fully booked and a rugby game going on our waiter Tony was on top of his game constantly checking in on us, the chocolate martinis from Andrew were so good we had 4 üôà definetly coming back! Though the ceviche could do with a bit more tigers milk, but othet than that i would highly recommend!', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1017, 'Joel Solomon', '320 Ngong Road Karen, Nairobi Kenya', 'The Talisman Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1059634-r1022092515-The_Talisman_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Great meal in Nairobi', 'We visited Talisman twice while in Nairobi, once for lunch and once for dinner.   The place was busy.  There were many tourists both times. At lunch there were a few tour groups.  At dinner it was more small groups.   The restaurant is pretty.  There was a lot of art on the walls, all for sale.  We watched someone paint during our lunch.  The staff were very nice.   Beer and wine were very good.  The food was excellent.  The menu is eclectic.  Over the course of our two meals we tried the crispy Szechuan eggplant, the chicken wings, mild with a side of Taliban sauce (it cracks me up how almost every restaurant in the world that serves chicken wings has a hot sauce with a transgressive name) and the  squid.   For dinner I had the excellent lamb kofta and for lunch I had a special pork chop.  The sticky date pudding and afogato were both great.  Highly recommended!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(1018, 'Kianjui', '320 Ngong Road Karen, Nairobi Kenya', 'The Talisman Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1059634-r1021686583-The_Talisman_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Good', 'The restaurant is very good, clean and delicious, but so noisy i could not even her my girl as she talking. It‚Äôs good but i think it‚Äôs better to avoid the night period because of the loud music', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1019, 'Quest19995856385', '320 Ngong Road Karen, Nairobi Kenya', 'The Talisman Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1059634-r1014262619-The_Talisman_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'GF options? In the description. Take that with a pinch of salt.', 'Great restaurant as long as you are not GF. If you are and want a hot main course it‚Äôs Lemon Chicken‚Ä¶. And that‚Äôs it. GF options otherwise are all cold. Everyone else had a fabulous meal. I felt limited and cross, ‚Äúvery sorry‚Äù from the staff, but‚Ä¶.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1020, 'Mark S', '320 Ngong Road Karen, Nairobi Kenya', 'The Talisman Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1059634-r1013794341-The_Talisman_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Call ahead to check if karaoke night', 'Been going for over 15 years and still one of a kind. Menu a little long now, choose carefully. And avoid nights with live band / karaoke if you want to enjoy conversation. Totally worth a visit if you‚Äôre passing through.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1021, 'Jorn Horaczek', '320 Ngong Road Karen, Nairobi Kenya', 'The Talisman Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1059634-r1003467838-The_Talisman_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'A bit too touristy for me.', 'We tried thias restaurant in Nairobi as it was highly recommeded.\nThe place is a bit out of the way if you live in the central business district. There  are plenty of tables and staff were friendly. The clientel seemed to be mostly tourists and expats. The food was ok, but not extraordinary. Service was quick and efficient.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1022, 'Chichicastenango', '320 Ngong Road Karen, Nairobi Kenya', 'The Talisman Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1059634-r1001191710-The_Talisman_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Unique Cuisine and Atmosphere', 'The Talisman Restaurant ‚Äì Nairobi\n\nEverything from the atmosphere to the cuisine is unique at The Talisman Restaurant. You find a nook with stain glass reminding you of a pub, a tented area with palms, a patio with large tables of exotic wood.  Bold artworks and wooden sculptures from near and far.\n\nThe service was impeccable and the offerings were creative plated and delicious.  We tried the feta and coriander samosas, tempura prawns, asparagus salad, fish and chips and salmon.  \nNot to be missed!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1023, 'zzaf', '320 Ngong Road Karen, Nairobi Kenya', 'The Talisman Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1059634-r1000707763-The_Talisman_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Top notch service, beautiful setting', 'Love the setting of this restaurant, and the service is excellent.¬†Top notch! I heard about¬†this restaurant before my trip, and it really didn\'t disappoint.¬†The samosas are delicious and I had the kofta kebabs which came with chapatis - so tasty!¬† I also recommend the ceviche. I loved that they show artwork from local artists¬†on the walls, which can be purchased.¬† I‚Äôve been there for both lunch and dinner and the ambience for both was magic. Can\'t wait to go back.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1024, 'Dwhits125', '320 Ngong Road Karen, Nairobi Kenya', 'The Talisman Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1059634-r999040264-The_Talisman_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent Food', 'We went here on the recommendation of several friends who have lived in Nairobi. We are very glad we did. The food was truly some of the best I have ever had! I had the chef\'s special Lamb Pastilla and it was phenomenal. My wife had the veggie bao buns and was also very impressed. Would definitely recommend!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1025, 'Luca F', '320 Ngong Road Karen, Nairobi Kenya', 'The Talisman Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1059634-r998989207-The_Talisman_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Unforgettable Culinary Delight!', 'Absolutely loved my experience! The flavors were incredible, and the service was top-notch. Every dish was a delight, and the ambiance made it even better. Highly recommend for anyone craving authentic cuisine!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
