(1027, 'SEB06000', '320 Ngong Road Karen, Nairobi Kenya', 'The Talisman Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1059634-r994408527-The_Talisman_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Nice place for Chirstmas eve', 'I spent the 24th of December here with my girlfriend, and it was a lovely experience. The atmosphere was great, and the garden looked beautiful at night. There was even a chimney in the garden, which helped beat the cold and made the evening more comfortable. They also had a choir for Christmas Eve, which added a nice touch. The food was very good, although a bit overpriced. Still, it‚Äôs a nice place to visit once in a while. I recommend it.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
