(1069, 'Neil R', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r701709357-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Pricey but first class', 'A great place to eat as a solo traveller because dishes were small enough for one. I had a lovely tagine and excellent aubergine with a beer and bread for around ¬£15', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(1070, 'Amu', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r680215746-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Great. ', 'The place has a great ambience. The food is always spot on. The roasted garlic and prawns is a must try. The smoked eggplant is also great. The wine collection is good too. The waiters know the menu well and have some very good suggestions for food and wine pairing. Sit by the bar and enjoy good music over weekend. Great job and keep it up üëçüëç', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1071, 'Emiliano C', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r660521692-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Aperitivo', 'Ci sono stato per un aperitivo. Cibo e bevande buone e atmosfera non male. Il servizio lascia un p√≤ a desiderare soprattutto per la lentezza nel portare i piatti e i drink al tavolo. Ad ogni modo consigliabile per mangiare qualcosa di diverso dal solito a Nairobi', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\"]'),
(1072, 'Rebecca Vedova', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r653612279-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'White wine and ros√© sangria', 'We like going to Tapas once in a while as a couple to catch up around a drink. The drink would be sangria. Tapas\' sangrias are the best in Nairobi. I haven\'t had a chance to eat there yet but I\'m sure I will soon. The ambiance is great, the deco is very rustique with a huge latin touch which is what i love. If you love latin music like I do, that\'s the best place to go to as well. The staff is very very professional and very kind. Great place', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1073, 'ShazNL', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r649964710-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Yummy ', 'Nothing beats a big menu, with variety to choose from and good service.. a favorite.. Try the cocktails.. Interesting.. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1074, 'Halima G', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r644057823-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Went there twice over my stay in Nairobi, always enjoyed myself', 'The tapas are really delicious, they even have vegetarian options and the food is very fresh. As for the drinks the cocktails are very original and pretty good. This place is a great for a chill night.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1075, 'gmc_pinas', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r638019316-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Great tapas', 'Food is good in general. The tapas are great and I really enjoyed trying out all the tapas in the few times I came here. I like their house drinks.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\"]'),
(1076, 'Priceless668', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r634429708-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Always an enjoyable experience!', 'I usually don\'t like to eat at shopping centres/malls, but the fact that this place has an outside seating area makes you forget that you\'re in a mall.  The ambience is really nice.  The sangria and tapas dishes are excellent, and not too expensive for a place of its kind in Nairobi/Westlands.  I\'ve always enjoyed meeting friends here - we stay for hours, have some sangria, and the staff is never trying to rush us out or anything.\n\nThe service is always quite attentive, and the happy hour deal is awesome - buy one get one sangria from 4pm to 7pm.\n\nThe only downside is that they give you the itemized bill without the taxes included (except for the total of course), similar to how bills are presented in the US for example.  So if you\'re with a big group and paying individually, it\'s probably best to either request separate checks or make sure you have a menu on hand to check and add up the exact prices of the items you\'ve ordered.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1077, 'wanderlustciru', 'Westgate Mall, Nairobi Kenya', 'Tapas Ceviche Bar Nairobi', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4421811-r619463234-Tapas_Ceviche_Bar_Nairobi-Nairobi.html', 'Nice spot ', 'Always a good experience at this Bar. Food was really good and drinks very creatively made and served.\nWe had a great server (can‚Äôt believe her name has slipped my mind üò©)\nPrice range mid/upper range.\nWould recommend ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
