(1079, 'Caroline M', '165 Ngong Road Next To St Christopher\'s School, Karen, Nairobi 00200 Kenya', 'Tamarind Brasserie', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d24915583-r1037498183-Tamarind_Brasserie-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Perfecto!!!', 'We went toTamarind as family and the experience was excellent. We were received by Peace who was really helpful and accomodating to our request. Chef Alex adjusted the menu package to suit our need and not to mention Antoine and Mumbi, assigned to wait on us did an outstanding job.\nWe loved the experience and we definitely will return for more.\nBy the way, the place is serene and posh.\nCarol', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"delivery_takeout\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
