(1162, 'kiriinya n', 'Radisson Blu Hotel, Nairobi Upper Hill Elgon Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Humidor Bar & Lounge', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d24091389-r912217617-Humidor_Bar_Lounge-Nairobi.html', 'Awesome and amazing. No rigidity on the menu. Great service', 'The ambience is great. Awesome customer service. Great food. We ordered food that was not im the menu and the waiter was very helpful in passing our requirements to the chef. This was delivered beyond our expectations. Being 5 weeks pregnant, i am very sensitive and picky pn what i would be able to eat. The chef did me justice!!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
