(1174, 'Safe Adventures and Expeditions', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r946406797-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Vibrant Night at The Alchemist Bar, Nairobi', 'Located on Parklands Road, The Alchemist Bar offers an unforgettable night of music and drinks.\n\nThe atmosphere is vibrant, with stylish d√©cor and cozy outdoor seating.\n\nMusic is eclectic and keeps the dance floor lively.\n\nDrinks are varied and expertly crafted.\n\nThe sense of community adds to the experience.\n\nOverall, The Alchemist Bar delivers an exceptional night out.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1175, 'Floicy A', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r941133566-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Very nice bar ', 'Nice place, good vibes, good drinks. Good people.  Enough security. Fairly clean toilets. I love it a lot . I\'ll definitely be going back', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1176, 'YoJat', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r920184435-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'A nice place for drinks, good vibe', 'Great place for a casual night for drinks, relaxed, good music, chill vibe.\n\nGood cocktails, happy hour price is good but the hours are in the afternoon not evening which is silly.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1177, 'DD S', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r919632349-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Tasty refreshing cocktails,  chilled rooftop bar vibes and good music!', 'Tasty refreshing cocktails and this cool bar also has happy hour :-) There\'s also some great music inc. some classic rnb and hip tracks thrown in. The live DJ set adds to the atmosphere, and there is a good mix of people, chilled rooftop bar vibes and tasty drinks! Excellent choice to catch up with friends or date night ;-) The staff are really friendly and the service was on point. We will be coming again when next in Nairobi for sure!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1178, 'JNelsonRedSoxFan', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r910159052-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Best cocktails in Nairobi', 'Having tried several of the places in Nairobi, Alchemist stands out as my favorite among pretty tough competition.  The huge subdivided venue has something for everyone, but I found my home in the upstairs lounge where they make proper whiskey sours and old fashioned.  ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1179, 'Nora T', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r909872381-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Letting in Minors', 'Absolutely horrible. They don‚Äôt check ID‚Äôs properly, and are inconsistent when letting people in. Multiple minors have been let in (specifically girls), who can easily get inappropriately approached by older men. Meanwhile people over the age of 18 are held back, which are people who are adults; allowed to legally drink according to the Kenyan Law, and who can give consent. This is despicable, and they need to put a new reasonable system in place! ', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"drinks\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1180, 'Lonelynomad', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r830477957-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Just Electric!', 'The place is simply lively throughout. The food and the drinks all are at par with the ambience and the music and fun in this club!! They also have a saloon on the 1st deck... The juggling, drinks and the food all are just just amazing!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1181, 'Aditya M', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r823016537-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Active and fun', 'The place has the vibe ...it has energy and is fun ... a cool hangout . The burger shacks had good juicy fresh burgers . Music is good , the place is divided in sections and has corners with interesting stories.  will be back . Definately recommended .  \n  ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1182, 'Mahaut', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r796483154-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Bar sympa ', 'L‚Äôambiance de l‚ÄôAlchemist est g√©niale, avec diff√©rents DJ qui font danser tout le monde. Les prix sont raisonnables mais les cocktails ne sont pas vraiment bons... Cependant le vin et les bi√®res sont bons. Le cadre est tr√®s agr√©ables, les canap√©s sont confortables et vous rencontrez facilement de nouvelles personnes. \nJe recommande ce lieu si vous voulez passer une bonne soir√©e entre amis. ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"atmosphere\"]'),
(1183, 'Capellanus', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r783705605-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'The Best Bar in Westlands', 'The Alchemist is a great place to spend a few hours and worth the repeat visits.  Set up in a courtyard among large trees and plants, it really gives you an great outdoor feel, enjoying the sun and breeze in comfort.\n\nThe bar has access to a few food vendors, all of whom will visit your table with a menu and take your order.  Spanish tapas, pizza, wings and one of the best burger experiences in Nairobi are all there.  \n\nThe Happy Hour runs from 1pm to 6pm and the prices cannot be beat.  Weekends get rather busy late afternoon, so come early to grab your favourite spot; but there is usually lots of room upstairs.\n\nA must see.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1184, 'Marija J', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r735374273-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Nice place', 'I love this place because I ate there best deep fried bananas :) I enjoyed bars and few nice shops, really good place to take a break.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1185, 'Janelle J', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r734663211-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Night at the Alchemist', 'I went here for my last night in Nairobi. The popular African pop group Elani was the live music for the evening. There are food trucks and vendors when you first enter the bar. Waitstaff was a bit rude but the veggie burger was tasty. Visit the Alchemist for a taste of Nairobi nightlife! ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1186, 'Whitney', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r723165558-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Great spot on a Friday night !', 'It a great place to go for the evening or at night!There are 3 bars and 3 food trucks all in one compound. We got there around 7 and first ate dinner and chilled. The Mexican food truck had good vegetarian tacos although they are spicy which they didn‚Äôt tell us when we ordered. The Kenyan chicken burger at the burger food truck was excellent! One of the best burgers we have had in Kenya!  Overall the place has great customer service! You can sit anywhere in the compound and services from all the food trucks will  come to your table and you order from them. We went on a Friday and around 9 the Dj starts playing and the place turns into a club so you can hit the dance floor. It was a great evening ! ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1187, 'TheTaskin', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r717398219-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Nairbo‚Äôs hottest chilling spot', 'Nairobi, with its security issues, still has some fantastic places. \nThe alchemist has 3 bars and 3 food carts inside a compound. Nice place with fun cocktails n bears. They also do great burgers. \nWe went to Mulberry which is on level 2. I had really good old fashioned ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1188, 'Besa', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r715730978-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Be sure you check your bill', 'Awful food from the German Sausage place. Cold und not cooked. After complaining about it you will still get the full bill. \nThe Alchemist Bar waiters a ripping you off and you better check your bill and at what time the happy hour starts. And if you complain you will be called a liar. I‚Äôm was going there for more than a year now, but the quality and service is going down. This is also including the hygiene. ', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1189, 'Mark W', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r1029855726-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Wonderful place to get a fantastic meal', 'Superb restaurant.  Best meal we had in Nairobi.  We were warmly welcomed and shown to our table.  The waiting staff were happy to make recommendations and as it was a quiet Monday evening even the Chef came to see us to give his recommendation which was a lovely gesture.  The menu was varied and we each really enjoyed our meals.  \n\nThis is fine dining (and hence more expensive than many Nairobi restaurants) but was significantly better than one would get in London for the same price, where it would probably be double the price.\n\nI would definitely recommend coming here if you want a world class meal in a lovely restaurant; I would definately go again if back in Nairobi.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1190, 'Kevin O‚ÄôLeary', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r987523994-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Yummy', 'One of the best meals we had in Africa. The red snapper and the lobster gnocchi were both outstanding. Service was excellent and drinks were very good as well. Highly recommend', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1191, 'Carl Tornell', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r983362699-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Best Oysters in Nairobi', 'Probably the best restaurant in Nairobi, certainly the best oysters. The small, but incredibly delicate, Kilifi oysters are difficult to beat. The Filthy Martini is the stuff of dreams. Add the nice selection of steaks, and a glass of Malbeek with that. To finish, Espresso and R√©my Martin in a glass that is warm, and that\'s it. Outstanding design and wonderful staff. I go back as often as I can.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(1192, 'Daisy B', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r961161899-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent food and service!', 'This restaurant came highly recommended to us from friends that lived in Nairobi a few years ago. We visited twice in our short time in Nairobi, and were not disappointed! Food was fantastic. Lobster cappuccino was one of the  best starters I think I have ever had! Excellent service from Bonfice on both visits. He was extremely attentive, helpful with the menu and friendly. Wilfred also made delicious imaginative cocktails. We will most definitely be recommending this restaurant. Thank you.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1193, 'Little_Summers', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r960860500-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Great choice with abundant variety', 'A great restaurant with a variety of choices. Whatever we tried was very well cooked and presented. The ceviche and the fried prawns were very balanced and tasty. We also had the goat and the fish. Both succulent and abundant. A very good choice.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1194, 'iTraveller', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r958362790-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Seventh heaven at Severn seafood', 'Had a fantastic time and dining experience at the wonderful place.\n\nFood was delicious and plentiful and the staff were very attentive.\n\nSpecial note to Joyce who looked after us so well making us feel special and the Chef Victor that came out to say hello', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1195, 'Kav B', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r954023972-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'No value of hospitality', 'Food is good but could be presented better but the service is a total disaster. That\'s the only reason I wouldn\'t go back. The wait staff had a don\'t care attitude. Got our order wrong & didn\'t even bother acknowledging the same. No manager & felt like no one wants to assist. They don\'t even come to check if you are okay or need anything else.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1196, 'Mzungubabe', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r946714998-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Modern seafood restaurant', 'Wonderful seafood restaurant with a few vegetarian options. Very friendly and professional service. It\'s worth saving room for dessert!', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1197, 'Mrjlangton', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r932341402-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Great food fantastic service', 'We went to 7 last night for a birthday celebration.\n\nThe food was exceptional with all the Mel‚Äôs being fabulous.\n\nGreat wine selection.\n\nThe service was superb with Grace going the extra mile to ensure we had a great night.\n\nA massive thank you from us for making the birthday celebration extremely special.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1198, 'Rod Ryan', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r926362037-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Good but used to be great?', 'Still a nice spot for a small rendezvous and gentle meal but they need to hold the line on attention to customers\' orders. ', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(1199, 'vonEllwangen', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r915790841-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Empfehlenswert', 'Sch√∂nes Restaurant. Saubere WC\'s. Das Essen kostet mehr als √ºblich, aber ich empfehle dieses Lokal - ausdr√ºcklich. Der Service ist sehr freundlich, zuvorkommend und kompetent.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(1200, 'Linda R', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r892661333-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Dinner experience', 'Amazing amazing food, had the sea food platter, butter prawns,risotto, bao buns, seasoning was perfect, portions were üëçüèΩ, service  was great  , I recommend this  restaurant  for foodies, the sea food items were all fresh tasting', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1201, 'Xiumei2012', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r881357596-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Dissatisfied', 'Sevens is located in a very vibrant area in Westlands Nairobi . \nThe ambience is great , the washrooms very clean , but my goodness the service is just not up to standard , we ordered sparkling water we got still water the waiter realized when she just placed the bottle on the table , what does it take to check the correct order before dispatching  ? \nThe fish fingers were too crunchy our mains were ok not great . Now imagine an empty restaurant with poor service ‚Ä¶ I just don‚Äôt get it \nLots of staff walking aprons and not paying attention to the only busy table in the restaurant, we literally had to request for everything. \nSad !!!', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1202, 'Keli Kituku', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r878694905-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Not So Valentine', 'Horrible Horrible! ‚Ä¶ from the horrid attempt to decorate the table to the chewy over cooked calamari to our main course that took two hours. And not for getting the manager who won‚Äôt engage clients. Stay away from this place!\n\nThe couple next to us walked away after they had only been severed water in an hour!', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1203, 'marco c', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r873669981-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Bad not good', 'Bad not good..just ceck chips...is answer to all they serve food is rediculus. Never had so bad food', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\"]'),
(1204, 'Joy M', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r855088248-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent', 'An amazing restaurant with great food, beautiful ambiance and wonderful service! We will be back for sure.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]');
