(1205, 'Carmen_Davids', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r853516971-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Impressed South-African in Kenya', 'WOW as a South African who loves to travel and enjoy fine dining I have to admit i was blown away by the food. I had prawns for starters, red snapper for mains and a pineapple cake with caramelized pineapple for dessert.\n\nThe manager was so friendly and the service and drinks choice just excellent.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\"]'),
(1206, 'Charley C', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r852330458-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Lovely birthday lunch', 'Had my family birthday lunch at Seven and what a great lunch experience! I had the lobster risotto which was sublime. The waiter was extremely friendly and special mention to the fishbowl cocktail! Highly recommend for the most delicious seafood cuisine. Thank you from Ololo Safari Lodge family.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1207, 'Mukuma', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r845922737-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Delicious food, excellent service ', 'From beginning to end, the service was faultless. \nOur server, Samson, was out of this world. \nAttentive and friendly and very knowledgeable about food. \nThe seafood platter for two was really tasty,  a bit on the large side. \nMy other half had sirloin steak which he said was perfect with lovely house fries. \nEverything was faultless and if you love seafood,  this is the only place to eat in Central Nairobi. \n', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(1208, 'Natalie T', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r829120952-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Year afternyesr, disappointing‚Ä¶', 'Chef talks a lot but the food has never been impressive. It‚Äôs dated and poor quality and no where near the standard of the absent and ego driven ‚Äútalent.‚Äù', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\"]'),
(1209, 'GMd', 'The Hub, Karen, Nairobi 24815 Kenya', 'The Mayura', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d11949016-r711725015-The_Mayura-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Review of the Mayura in Westlands', 'The staff welcomed us and seated us quickly.  We sat in the covered courtyard.  Once we ordered, the waiter came back with hot towels which was really good. \nWhile the service was good, we were not too happy with the the quality of food. The chicken lollipop\'s were full of flour/bread crumbs and the meat was half the size.  We also ordered a unique south Indian meat dish and it was served quickly enough after we ordered. There is absolutely no way it could have been prepared fresh.  The dishes are priced on the high side which would have been okay if the quality of the food was good. \nAfter the meal the waiters bring a finger bowl.  While we were still eating I noticed that the waiter was dipping his fingers in the bowl to check the water temperature. He was then taking the bowls to the guests at the other table. When it was out turn I kept a close watch and didn\'t see the waiter dip his fingers in the bowl he brought to me. When he brought the bowls for my kids he dipped his fingers in the bowl. It was totally disgusting to see restaurant staff with such indifference to hygiene. We didn\'t let our kids use the bowl. My wife made an excuse to use the washroom and she didn\'t use hers either.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1210, 'ntsven', 'The Hub, Karen, Nairobi 24815 Kenya', 'The Mayura', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d11949016-r710897665-The_Mayura-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Good Indian Food', 'We went to this restaurent with family. We love spicy Indian food and they didn\'t upset us. If you are looking for Indian spicy food, this place satisfies your appetite.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1211, 'Wanderer13925221426', 'The Hub, Karen, Nairobi 24815 Kenya', 'The Mayura', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d11949016-r708721275-The_Mayura-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Well well', 'need a calm, relaxed easy moment then be sure to know it suits thats... not fully ther but you cant miss a positive word to mention when you leave the place ', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1212, 'Amanda O', 'The Hub, Karen, Nairobi 24815 Kenya', 'The Mayura', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d11949016-r707109076-The_Mayura-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Simply Amazing', 'From the service, the decor to the food, everything was on point.\n\ni have been to both branches in Westlands and the Hub and i must say never been disappointed.\n\nFor fresh, fairly priced, tasty authentic Indian dishes definitely the place to try.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1213, 'optical_11', 'The Hub, Karen, Nairobi 24815 Kenya', 'The Mayura', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d11949016-r706700423-The_Mayura-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'The restaurant provides Indian Dishes catering to Indians as well as Africans. To get what you like, call the Chef .', 'We have been having lunch every week at this restaurant and make it a point to call the Chef for the type of dishes we want and they have never failed to deliver.  Fresh juice is prepared in the morning, sugar syrup added and served for the rest of the day was not palatable. Waiters are quite courteous.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(1214, 'Cynthia A', 'The Hub, Karen, Nairobi 24815 Kenya', 'The Mayura', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d11949016-r704318632-The_Mayura-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Tandoori Chicken üòã', 'I am a huge fan of Indian food and The Mayura definitely delivered when it came to my all time me favorite chicken. The chicken was perfectly marinades and hit all the right spots. Also had the butter chicken and yum üòã. The naan could do with a bit of improvement but it still was a good accompaniment. ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(1215, 'winnieb', 'The Hub, Karen, Nairobi 24815 Kenya', 'The Mayura', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d11949016-r701382978-The_Mayura-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Mixed feeling', 'I hate burnt naan and getting served that three times is a no no for me... The service is worse at peak. \nbesides that, it is a good place for a family meal or large groups. ', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1216, 'khensa@gmail.com', 'The Hub, Karen, Nairobi 24815 Kenya', 'The Mayura', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d11949016-r699990598-The_Mayura-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Poor service', 'For a restaurant at the hub with such good competitions around they are just getting customers interested in Indian food nmy personal experience was poor .. the waiters weren‚Äôt attentive the lassi ( salty yoghurt drink)was over salty and even after returning it it dint come any different they just added water to it , food was okay some one had dropped food and the waiters weren‚Äôt even bothered to clean up the mess me as a customer had to point as it was in my eyes and annoying me that some one had even stepped on it and the manager was no where to Be seen\n\nThey‚Äô better twist around their whole Game .', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1217, 'Kim K', 'The Hub, Karen, Nairobi 24815 Kenya', 'The Mayura', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d11949016-r698831350-The_Mayura-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Best at the Hub', 'A good restaurant when visiting the Hub in Karen Nairobi. The food is very tasty Indian cuisine. Service is friendly and fast. ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\"]'),
(1218, 'Anil Gupta', 'The Hub, Karen, Nairobi 24815 Kenya', 'The Mayura', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d11949016-r696294788-The_Mayura-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Good Indian Food', 'Tasty and variety of food items. Value for money. Their packed lunch is also very good and makes sense for one person to have a variety without wastage and enough for 1 person.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1219, 'Nadine W', '154 James Gichuru Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'The Other Room Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d21236043-r1037082438-The_Other_Room_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Worth every shilling', 'The atmosphere and location was great. The food was delicious (their sushi is to die for) and the service was the highlight of the night. Special thanks to Mercy and Muraguri for being so warm, friendly and attentive!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1220, 'rash r', '154 James Gichuru Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'The Other Room Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d21236043-r1037080552-The_Other_Room_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Superb', 'She served us wholeheartedly and kindly. The service she provided, food and her atmosphere were all amazing, thank you very much!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1221, 'Jeremy W', '154 James Gichuru Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'The Other Room Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d21236043-r1037079625-The_Other_Room_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Amazing Experience!', 'Muraguri and Mercy W. provided amazing service, the food was amazing and we had a lovely night. 10/10 definitely coming back again!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1222, 'Fab U', '154 James Gichuru Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'The Other Room Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d21236043-r1032818597-The_Other_Room_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Tasty lunch and amazing service!', 'Had lunch here whilst waiting for my flight. Brenda was amazing and the chicken sandwich was delicious. I definitely recommend!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1223, 'Sam K', '154 James Gichuru Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'The Other Room Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d21236043-r1031825870-The_Other_Room_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Hospitality without Compare', 'The warmest people coupled with food most comforting and some of the most exquisite coffee you‚Äôve ever had! Jocob & Brenda, ya‚Äôll are stars!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1224, 'OnAir09161500974', '154 James Gichuru Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'The Other Room Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d21236043-r1030491567-The_Other_Room_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Amazing', 'Wonderfully served by Lureata. Pleasant and very helpful lady. Went above and beyond to serve us and offer assistance where she saw fit. Excellent service.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(1225, 'Timm G', '154 James Gichuru Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'The Other Room Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d21236043-r1029724587-The_Other_Room_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Perfect place to relax', 'Food and service was amazing. Perfect place to relax and calm down after an exhausting trip. Thank you Ruth for serving us  üôèüèª', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
