(1251, 'Samuel N', 'Mpaka Rd Opposite Posta Westlands, Nairobi Kenya', 'Nairobi Street Kitchen', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23484428-r899284347-Nairobi_Street_Kitchen-Nairobi.html', 'Nairobi Street Kitchen guards are thieves!', 'Nairobi Street Kitchen guards are thugs. Was about to leave after parking was full. The front guard gave me parking upfront next next to the door, just near where the Uber drop off is. The guard stated the car is safe and will see each other when leaving.\n\nWhen was leaving, the guard was missing, first red flag. When started the car, got an alert there is sensor malfunction second red flag. On the high way on way home that\'s when noticed the passenger side side mirror, the mirror had been plucked out. Just outside Nairobi Street Kitchen with the guards just at the door! \n\nThose guards played me by insisting I park upfront then stole my mirror!', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
