(1253, 'Michelle N', 'Mpaka Rd Opposite Posta Westlands, Nairobi Kenya', 'Nairobi Street Kitchen', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23484428-r887868216-Nairobi_Street_Kitchen-Nairobi.html', 'Superb business event at NSK Rooftop Bar!', 'Held a business happy hour networking event at the NSK rooftop bar. Everything from the initial planning to the actual event was handled impeccably. The drinks, food, and service was superb. Thanks to captain of multitasking, Wanjiru Mukii and team for the seamless end to end coordination, execution, and overall great after work vibes!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1254, 'JM', 'Mpaka Rd Opposite Posta Westlands, Nairobi Kenya', 'Nairobi Street Kitchen', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23484428-r880449453-Nairobi_Street_Kitchen-Nairobi.html', 'Poor quality of food', 'I ordered a Korean chicken burger. Literally the smallest piece of chicken in the burger. What I got was all bread and some khimchi. Fries were average. \nNo point skimping on the meat of the customer has ordered a meat product.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\"]'),
(1255, 'Tish', 'Mpaka Rd Opposite Posta Westlands, Nairobi Kenya', 'Nairobi Street Kitchen', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23484428-r878370352-Nairobi_Street_Kitchen-Nairobi.html', 'Nice place to meet a group', 'Offers variety of foods, but most only average, although I hope this is improving (last year I had to mention on more than one occasion my concern for food handling and complain on food quality). While a small token of appreciation, a big vote goes to Si Senor (their corn is delicious). Still, a nice setting for getting together as a group. They sometimes have pop-ups, a few have been worth it, but mostly lately have been overpriced artisanal, which I think is better to buy at other venues with more variety. Glad they have a large parking lot adjacent now. ', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(1256, 'Patricia', 'Mpaka Rd Opposite Posta Westlands, Nairobi Kenya', 'Nairobi Street Kitchen', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23484428-r868366999-Nairobi_Street_Kitchen-Nairobi.html', 'Para todos los gustos', 'Excelente opci√≥n para ir a comer o tomar algo si est√°s en Nairobi. Divinamente decorado, el lugar es un est√≠mulo visual donde elegir√°s sentarte donde m√°s te guste. Son varios lugares en uno. Tendr√°s para elegir comida india, thai, mexicana, hamburguesas , pollo, helados, etc\nLa atenci√≥n es buena y el lugar seguro ya que hay seguridad al ingresar.\nNo es de los m√°s barato pero lo vale', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[]'),
(1257, 'William V', 'Mpaka Rd Opposite Posta Westlands, Nairobi Kenya', 'Nairobi Street Kitchen', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23484428-r866024812-Nairobi_Street_Kitchen-Nairobi.html', 'best dinner', 'Amazing customer service.\nI loved the food, dessert. Quite tasty.\nThe waiting time was less than 10 minutes for the drinks and starter.\n\nAmazing experience.I highly recommend the place.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1258, 'hcb81', 'Mpaka Rd Opposite Posta Westlands, Nairobi Kenya', 'Nairobi Street Kitchen', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23484428-r854400020-Nairobi_Street_Kitchen-Nairobi.html', 'Cool set up, great tacos', 'Loved this place. Such a variety of places to eat. We had great tacos and lovely cocktails. The decor is fab and it has a really cool, relaxed set up. We came in the day but I think it would be a great place to come for evening drinks. It‚Äôs also got some cute little shops to browse too.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1259, 'Clare W', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r1024488196-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Disappointed customer', 'I am a regular customer at Haru Sushi, but yesterday‚Äôs experience was extremely disappointing. I was there with a family member, waiting for friends to join us. Upstairs, only three tables were occupied, yet it took about 45 minutes before we were served.\n\nDuring that time, several white guests arrived and received immediate attention, even though we had arrived before them. When we finally managed to get the attention of a waiter‚Äîafter repeatedly calling out‚Äîwe asked about hot chocolate. He said he was new and would check, but he never came back. Instead, we kept seeing him serve the white guests at other tables while ignoring us.\n\nEventually, after more waiting and calling, another waiter came over. Only when we complained did they start paying attention to us. It left us wondering‚Äîdo we really have to complain to get basic service?\n\nThe manager was however very good and  welcomed us well, but the service after nah! \n\nIt‚Äôs sad to see fellow Kenyans treating other Kenyans this way. This was an unfortunate experience, and I will likely opt for takeaway in the future or dine at Sushi Soo in Kileleshwa, where the service is excellent and the food is amazing.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1260, 'annemarie v', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r981391923-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Terrible customer care and service!', 'Today I had a very bad experience service wise at Haru restaurant, which I vist very frequently ( 4-6 times a month). I was with 5 friends and I thought no one wants wine so I ordered a glass of the house wine. It turned out that 3 others wanted wine and we decided to take a botte of Vergelegen at 3600 ksh. I requested the waiter to take back my glass of inferieur house wine so I could enjoy the good wine. He refused, saying it has already been handed out etc, and that it would be a loss to Haru. I told him I understand and I know that but I am a very good customer and come here once a week and spend a lot of money. I told him \'consider it as a complimentary to a good customer and do with it what you want\'. He kept on arguing and arguing. Of course we ordered a more expensive bottle and I left the cheap house wine of 700 ksh untouched.\nWe had fun sitting and drinking and then that same waiter came asking if he could give us the bill since his shift was ending... however to us it seemed like we were being chased away, evidently his objective was to get his tip . He spoiled our nice conversation and we paid and we all left. Haru owners, I hope you read this review: You lost out on good customers because we won\'t be coming back unless you apologize and compensate us! Also you lost out on extra orders because we were still having fun and talking with each other. Lesson learnt hopefully: owner be there and don\'t leave your restaurant to staff who seem to have no authority and experience in customer service and are not interested in extra orders/upselling or customer retention. Hope to hear from you! Annemarie', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1261, 'Hode B', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r974358321-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Good food and attentive staff', 'The food was fresh. I loved the salad given as a starter. The staff were attentive and helpful. An overall good experience', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1262, 'Asya', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r971943925-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'cosy, sweetly decorated, super delicious Japanese restaurant', 'This cosy, sweetly decorated, super delicious Japanese restaurant is now my favourite place to eat in Nairobi. We have been there three times and we are never disappointed. The food is AMAZING! The service is great and the atmosphere is so comfortable. We LOVE, LOVE, LOVE Haru!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1263, 'garethd630', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r955519622-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Significant delays in being served and terrible customer service', 'Really disappointing lunchtime experience at Haru which is a restaurant we visit frequently. Our order took over two hours to arrive. Despite repeatedly asking what the issue was we were told that food was coming. Tables all around us were being served and some tables managed to arrive, order, eat, pay their bill and leave in the time we were waiting. Bearing in mind a number of elements were very easy and quick like noodles, fried rice etc it should not have taken anything like this to deliver this to the table. Eventually, after over two hours, Brian, who introduced himself as the manager, arrived at our table. When asked if he knew the order he said he didn\'t know what we were waiting on but that it would come soon. We\'d been told this repeatedly each time we\'d asked. Brian offered ice creams for the kids \'as compensation\' before the food had even arrived. Bearing in mind we spent 23,300 Kenyan shillings I\'d have thought they could do better. To add to the already poor experience unfortunately, Faith who had served us appeared to find the whole thing funny and laughed about it in front of us at the table. Totally unacceptable from both of them. Perhaps some customer service training might be undertaken for both Brian and Faith and a general look had into how orders are managed. ', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"delivery_takeout\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1264, 'Dania27', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r950648785-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Food poisoning', 'Had food poisoning because of the sushi‚Äôs I ordered, was vomiting the whole night, I texted Haru to let them know, but they didn‚Äôt seem to care. It was 7,000 ksh worth of sushi‚Äôs.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(1265, 'Ulrik Plenge', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r927071814-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Super overall madoplevelse ', 'Restauranten som ud over at v√¶re hyggeligt indrettet, har et serviceminded personale og en uds√∏gt sushi og sashimi menu. Det var en stor nydelse og ligger p√• en top 10 over bes√∏gte japanske restauranter. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1266, 'Pierra A', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r918764952-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Horrible horrible service ', 'Very terrible service. Went there for dinner and the waiters were hovering around the table eagerly waiting and pressuring us to finish eating quickly so that they clear the table. I honestly felt rushed and watched by around 7 waiters standing behind our table. One waiter in particular, Faith was very rude. She was so loud expressing how she couldn\'t wait for a group of guests to leave. The food is good, but the service yesterday night was utterly terrible . If you know you will rush guests to leave the restaurant, you\'d rather just say the kitchen is closed instead of hovering over the guests and clearing the table before even finishing the meal', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1267, 'Eyama E', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r895542388-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Real Japanese Goodness!', 'The Sushi they serve is delicious and always tasty! I have been there a couple of times and I am never disappointed! Their prawn tempura and crispy salmon roll is so delicious! Staff are also welcoming and attentive!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1268, 'adali2016', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r892126545-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Best E Africa Japanese?', 'We stayed at a hotel around the corner so thought, might as well try. Sushi might not be first on your mind when you think cuisine in Nairobi. We were very satisfied. Clearly, good service. There was a manager/owner type who was our guess Japanese, so it is authentic. Good sushi, tampura & ramen. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1269, 'Carol W', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r889029733-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Great Lunch', 'The food was fresh and delicious. The service was also great. I loved the chicken teriyaki and the maki rolls. The yakisoba however was a little too soggy for my liking. All in all, I would definitely recommend!', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1270, 'Clementine B', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r883113972-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Seriously reccomend', 'I really loved this restaurant. Well worth it.\n\nI would seriously recommend. We were a group of young 19 year olds and loved a change in cuisine. \n\nStaff are also very friendly.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1271, 'HK_Helen_Ma', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r877787667-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Professional chef with sincere service', 'Tried the Omakase, which the Chef served a good variety of delicious sushi with fresh raw fish and seafood. The roasted snapper fillet and tuna (young and adult) were especially good. The finish touch with a hot fish soup was also satisfying!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1272, 'Imani Wamai', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r876573840-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Good food. Terrible Service!! ', 'The food was good but the service was TERRIBLE. Either the staff are intentionally rude or poorly trained. NOT HAPPY AT ALL. ', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1273, 'Pierra A', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r863038887-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Amazing Sushi', 'Great ambiance and service every time I visit. We had an amazing waiter who made my birthday feel extra special.  I definitely give it 5 stars.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1274, 'Grease Monkey Taka', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r859910067-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Fake Sushi and Poor Service', 'This restaurant seems to have a pretty good reputation, but I found the service and food quality to be poor for the price.\nI would like everyone who gave 5-star and 4-star ratings to try eating genuine real Sushi, not looks like Sushi.\nI think the pricing at this restaurant can offer the real food.\nEven the soy sauce used is a sweet general-purpose product rather than a soy sauce that good for sushi. (Only the \"noren\" in the restaurant was Japanese soy sauce brand logo, but the soy sauce served is not a Japanese brand.)\n\nAs other reviews have pointed out, I don\'t think the service at this restaurant is worth the price.\nIn particular, the slow delivery of food is fatal, and the attitude of employees and managers are the worst unfortunately.\nAlso, in my experience, it seems to be true that the serving for fair-skinned people are fastest.\n\nThere are other Japanese restaurants, so it is recommended to compare and judge.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"delivery_takeout\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1275, 'nabeab', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r857623745-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Good but no edamames here!', 'Nice restaurant, everything we ordered was delicious and we enjoyed. They need a better selectio of wines by the glass though!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(1276, 'Upepo71', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r857561768-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'By far the consistent restaurant in Nairobi!', 'Its not glitzy and its not glam... but Haru delivers better than excellent food every time! Consistency is their secret and they never disappoint. Ambiance welcoming and charming, food delectable and the staff are extremely knowledgeable and make great recommendations. Don\'t hesitate to go!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1277, 'Mcnabb C', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r848148761-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'A good place but is loosing it\'s standards', 'I have been a regular of Haru since it opened, and i want to open up saying it is still a good restaruant, however:\n* They are frequently out of items (Tuna, Salmon, etc) which for a fish restaurant is a little odd. \n* They have added a new range of Sake which is good, but by the bottle is extreemly expensive, they need to adjust their mark up on this slightly\n* Service can be hit and miss, some of the waiters are very very efficent, friendly but some others are poorly trained, \n\nAll in all still gets a thumbs up but they need to spend a bit of time bringing themselves back to where they were four years ago. ', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1278, 'Manjeet', 'Karen Professional Centre Karen Road, Nairobi 24168 Kenya', 'Haru Japanese Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d4540736-r848143361-Haru_Japanese_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Awful customer service', 'Title says it all, won\'t bother going again, prefer Furasato any day!! Super slow, wrong orders given, no apology for late dishes given or even offering a discount for 45 minutes delay....', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(1279, 'Bu Rashed', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r711552162-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Nice place to go', 'A good place to enjoy your time and meet new friends in Nairobi. A good food variety to choose from.\nThey treat visitors very well and all staff are customer oriented.\nIt is a safe place and we really enjoyed it and will definitely go again next time we go to Nairobi...', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1280, '2910shezk', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r706306250-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Afternoon Lunches & a Fun night out', 'A totally different and enjoyable hangout! They have various food trucks and stations - my favorite being Mama Rock\'s and the Bistro. Been here several times.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(1281, 'Seaside26810470509', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r706265033-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Artistic Vibes', 'The place has a vintage kind of vibe going on. The music is great and the tiny food bars offer great food. Serious parking problems. Might need to park at Sarit.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]');
