(1282, 'WanderHopefully', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r703709384-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Good burgers and nice vibe', 'More an open air yard with a stage in one corner and surrounded by a selection of bars and food trucks. They have a couple of nice craft beers, the service is good and burgers excellent. What is not to like?', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1283, 'Tiffany c', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r684785159-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Fun Friday Party', 'We went to a fun Friday party there. It was packed and drinks were pricey but good. Only downside was that the DJ played sooooo much American music. (Although the crowd seemed to enjoy it.) Would have enjoyed more afrobeats!!! Definitely a fun place to dance though- if you don‚Äôt mind being shoved in the line to get in and shoved on the dancefloor too. But the crowd was fun otherwise. \n\nPs. Don‚Äôt eat shawama from the food truck though or you‚Äôll be visiting the toilet for sure. ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1284, 'Cynthia N', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r683618679-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Backyard yoga ', 'Had a tiring week?? Visit  backyard yoga at alchemist westlands and it will be worth your while, meet new people, get a feeling of yoga and some soothing music ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1285, 'cselempo', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r675691116-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Cool and fun clubhouse!!!', 'Definitely worth a visit next time!\nHowever, be warned as the place is cold at night.\nCome wearing warm clothes especially during the cold seasons.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1286, 'Hadeel Oz', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r674519915-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'A fun place to be', 'The open mics are very entertaining, service is great and the overall decor, music choices and variety of food makes this a must visit spot. Had a great time and will make it a regular spot.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1287, 'llansford', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r662241344-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Awesome, buzzing hub with tons of choices', 'We were at first confused trying to find the place--I didn\'t see any signage saying \"Alchemist,\" but did see some food trucks and signs for other bars, so we headed in. We had an awesome time and were completely surprised by how cool of a spot this was! It was an outdoor haven full of young people and honestly felt like our home in  Austin plopped down right in Nairobi: we came during a Pecha Kucha night about design, there were AMAZING food trucks, great outdoor seating and ambiance, a killer little shop, a sweet vinyl library, and of course, beverages galore. Pop in for some Tucker and a burger and you won\'t regret it! Compared to the prices back home and given the high quality of food and ambiance, this place was a steal. It\'s def a tad more expensive than some surrounding joints, but was totally worth it for the awesome noms, great event, and vibes.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1288, 'Tomas Bartas', 'Parklands Road Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'The Alchemist Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d10290440-r659585133-The_Alchemist_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Worth to jump in', 'We have jumped in for couole of drinks and it was fine. Good cocktails, nice and friendly staff. It was good time ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\"]'),
(1289, 'omokaro o', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r1037621265-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Nice place to chill with friends and loved once', 'The food is top notch‚Ä¶good customer service and a beautiful environment.nice place to be with friends and family.excellent', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1290, 'Japheth O', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r1037152130-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Best Seafood in Nairobi', 'Best sea food in Nairobi, served by Lucy she‚Äôs the best waitress made us feel at home and took good care of us‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1291, 'Kelley S', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r1028795850-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Amazing', 'Food was wonderful.  The presentation was  breathtaking.  Rose our server, was kind, considerate and so very attentive.  I highly recommend this place for a wonderful dinning experience.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1292, 'Barb M', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r1028364812-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Fabulous Seafood', 'Rose and Jan provided a wonderful dining experience. The food and presentation were amazing. higHly recommend enjoy!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1293, 'Gloria C', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r1026998433-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'A dance with passion', 'Chef Odhiambo is an alchemist. His smile is felt in the food he prepares. I absolutely recommend allowing him to surprise you. He is built to create!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1294, 'Jahrahn E', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r1021318814-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Chef Marco is Him but Galla made it special', 'Just know that the food, ambience and experience is 5 star at this place! Bring your appetite and a blanket for immediate rest afterwards! Top notch! 10 out of 10!!!!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1295, 'Brian W', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r1017832478-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent', 'Excellent service from Margaret.  We had great time tonight here for dinner and will definitely come back and also introduce this restaurant to my friends.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(1296, 'JD S', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r1017829506-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'A great family Dinner', 'We had Dinner with my family and everything was excellent. Thank you margaret. And the reception was also great from Samantha. We will definitely come back.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(1297, 'Kevin  M', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r1016810900-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Best food', 'Best seafood ever. Best service by vincent. Good quality music. Envitomeny is really nice. Food was fresh and reallt tasty', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1298, 'Moeen ud din', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r1013795357-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Nice Setting, Friendly Staff‚ÄîBut Food Disappoints', 'The restaurant has a great ambiance with comfortable seating and a pleasant environment. However, the live music was too loud, making it difficult to enjoy conversations. While the staff were friendly and welcoming, the food was disappointing‚Äîit was average at best, leaning toward below average.  \n\n**Suggestions for Improvement:**  \n- Adjust the live music volume to enhance the dining experience.  \n- Focus on improving food quality to match the lovely atmosphere and service.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1299, 'david k', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r1013114737-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant is a true gem in Nairobi! The food is incredibly tasty‚Äîfresh, flavorful, and beautifully pres', 'If you‚Äôre looking for a truly unforgettable dining experience in Nairobi, Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant is the place to be. From the moment you step in, you‚Äôre welcomed with warmth, elegance, and a refined coastal ambiance that sets the tone for a culinary journey like no other.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1300, 'Josep Maria M', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r1010481103-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Mawimbi experience', 'We had a delicious dinner. Our waiter tonny, gave us a wonderfull service with such a nice energy. We definetly recomend this restaurant. Seafood and desserts had a really high quality. \nASANTE SANA!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1301, 'Charles O', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r1008467093-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', '3 Star Review', 'I had high hopes for this seafood spot ‚Äî and while the flavors were good, the seafood itself was unfortunately overcooked and quite dry, which took away from the meal.\n\nThat said, the live music created a great atmosphere, and the hospitality from the staff was truly wonderful. They were warm, attentive, and made the experience more enjoyable despite the food not hitting the mark.\n\nWith a little more care in the kitchen, this place could easily become a favorite.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
