(1311, 'miguel p', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r791940361-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Very expensive,terrible waiter behavior..', 'Food was regular.. I asked for a cold beer and they bring a worm one.. and when I asked tge waiter said.. this is the one we have.\nThen we ask for a glass of white wine and was so little wine, not eve a 1/4 glass.. , when we claim about it he said.. if you  want more you can ask for a bottle‚Ä¶\nTerrible restaurant!!!', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1312, 'babiryieM', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r777044793-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Always a good time!', 'This was my first outing since COVID happened. Despite being closed for a while and having very little traffic, the staff welcomed us warmly and the service was top notch.\nThe food never disappoints. I\'ve been here several times and had a range of starters and mains and I am always content. Most recently I had the lobster risotto (Ugh, so creamy and dreamy) while my husband had the slow cooked (fall off the bone) beef short ribs. For dessert we split the chocolate pudding and ice cream.\n\nHighly recommend them. It is value for money, great friendly service and always a fantastic meal. Easily one of the top restaurants in Nairobi.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1313, 'Msafiri', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r768900376-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Terribly disappointed with quality of food', 'I visited this restaurant over the weekend and was really disappointed. They did not have most things in the menu. And he only food we could order was so tasteless - meet frozen was simply dipped into oil and presented as grilled with no marination at all - very chewy and poor quality.  The rissotto with lobster was such poor quality - much waste of money for such an expensive place. The restaurant should be honest to their customers that they do not have suppliers or not up to standard or the Covid effect - for such an expensive place that was a flop, yet first time in this restaurant. We reported to the waiter and all he could say is that \' I will inform the chef\' - no commitment at all!!!', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1314, 'Musalia', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r751297332-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Top Class Delicious Food!', 'Seven restaurant prepares some of the best seafood dishes in Nairobi. I particularly love their red/white snapper served with butternut and cream of spinach. Their hot lemon, ginger, and honey drink with a dash of cinnamon is tantalizingly refreshing.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
