(1316, 'TaurusTraveller-JM', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r746006934-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Did not Disappoint', 'The aesthetics of the restaurant was quite nice, has a few different seating areas.\n\nStaff was polite and attentive. The food was great, so good i went back the following night. \n\nThe Spicy Fish Soup was good, for Main dish: Salmon and Snapper were simply delectable.I highly recommend.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1317, 'Hugh F', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r740987898-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Masala crab to die for', 'Every time I visit Kenya I go to Seven.  This visit did not disappoint.  As we (9 in our party) couldn\'t decide what starters to have our waiter suggested bringing a mixture.  I can\'t remember what they all were but we cleaned the plates.  And then I had the masala crab . . . . . . . . .  I can honestly say that it is the best crab curry I have had anywhere, including Goa and Thailand.  And out of sheer greed I finished off with the Chocolate Brownie - the ones at Seven bring a whole new meaning to the word Brownie\n\nRoll on our next visit to Kenya.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
