(1327, 'Discover07181750483', '154 James Gichuru Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'The Other Room Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d21236043-r1017619604-The_Other_Room_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Lunch @ The Social House', 'Purity\nElizabeth\nChef Panda & Annibal\nJanet.\nAmazing guest experience from the above staff. The wild mushroom & butternut risotto was creamy and very tasty', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1328, 'Mbugua K', '154 James Gichuru Road, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'The Other Room Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d21236043-r1017619590-The_Other_Room_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Wines of South Africa at The Social House üç∑', 'I came to The Social House for a corporate event hosted at the house. It was a beautiful luncheon filled delicious food, lovely wone & great company.\n\nChef Annibal & Chef David aka Panda came up with a wonderful pairing with wines curated by the best sommelier around, Janet K!\n\nThe service and warm smiles by the hostesses Koki & Elizabeth made me feel right at home. From the moment I walked in to the moment I sat down, they were with me every step of the way.\n\nAnd the ever professional Purity was the best of them all. She was so attentive with her service and all my questions were addressed.\n\nHere\'s to more moments at The Social House üç∑ ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
