(1352, 'BabaZedi', 'Hurlingham Itersection of Lenana Rd. & Woodlands Rd, Nairobi Kenya', 'The Royal House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d17288207-r671106556-The_Royal_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Fine food', 'This is a new restaurant in Nairobi upmarket area of Hurligham. Fine food made in authentic Yemeni and Lebanese styles. Real food presented well and tasted good! I recommend. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1353, 'africanman_840', 'Hurlingham Itersection of Lenana Rd. & Woodlands Rd, Nairobi Kenya', 'The Royal House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d17288207-r665663030-The_Royal_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Decent Food and Friendly Service', 'I thought that service was fantastic. My waitress was so kind and helpful.The food was decent but not great,', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1354, 'scrubbybear', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r1000583556-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Superb service, superior food, sublime atmosphere!', 'What a great time! \n\nFirst of all I visited the restaurant in Nairobi, Kenya at the recommendation of a local who sometimes drives me and my sister around. I wanted seafood and this is where he took us. The atmosphere was lovely and tranquil with indoor/outdoor seating options. The indoor portion is intimately lighted and modern, exuding elegance and unpretentious style. The outdoor area features a small pool as its centerpiece, with lush tropical plants surrounding the tables. It‚Äôs beautiful. \n\nThe food was sublime!  Not only is the menu imaginative, the chef clearly knows the character of the palate as he chose seemingly unlikely pairings that were delicious together (plantain sushi?!)\nI ordered the snapper, which was lightly breaded and grilled to perfection. The dessert I chose was a mango cheesecake, which also did not disappoint. \n\nThe waitstaff was more than attentive, they were dedicated and clearly invested in providing the best experience possible for us. \n\nSimilar upscale restaurants have disappointed me greatly but this one is a keeper for sure. They have another location I intend to visit as well‚Äîthat‚Äôs how good they are.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1355, 'Ossi', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r999198221-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Good food, slow service', 'Visited Mawimbi for the second time because the first visit was so much fun.\n\nThe sea food was delicious again. I had some lobster.\n\nUnfortunately the service was very slow this time. At least our waitress apologized for it multiple times.\n\nWe still had a good time. Special thanks to the groovy band and soulful singers!', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\"]'),
(1356, 'Grace K', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r998372645-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Food and service review', 'Loved the food , ambience was served by a lovely lady , Maria Mutheu.\n Every food , drink and dessert she suggested was top tier. üíØ would be back again and again!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1357, 'Mwikali K', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r998372504-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Recommended', 'The seafood platter was amazing. Our server Mariah Mutheu gave us beautiful service and made good recommendations. üíØ would visit again.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1358, 'Stay62740285473', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r998370326-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Authentic feedback at Mawimbi Seafood Nairobi Ke.', 'This spot named Mawimbi Seafood is right next to Fairmont htl where I attend my daily gym facility.\n\nIn the beginning of 2025 during my journey of prayers and fasting I started visiting Mawimbi for a drink after workout.\n\nMaria had an invitating smile that made me purpose to walk in each Sunday and Thursday based on her great service and authentic trends of professionalism while serving.\n\nI would recommend Mawimbi each season.When out of town will miss this spot.Great service and ambience not forgetting the saxophone guy who spices the entire mood with authentic songs.I am blessed.\n\nThank you all.\nAgollah PhD...o', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1359, 'Millicent A', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r998262293-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'New client', '\"Mawimbi is the best seafood restaurant in Nairobi! Their ambience and service are on another level. They serve fresh food, and I was especially impressed by their live crabs‚Äîyou get to choose the size you want, and they prepare it for you. I‚Äôm so happy with that place! Their hostesses are also amazing; they make sure you‚Äôre well taken care of.\"', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1360, 'Pendo O', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r998260861-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Happy family', '\"I was at Mawimbi on Sunday for their seafood brunch, and I was not disappointed. We really enjoyed ourselves and will definitely go back. I was truly impressed.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1361, 'Mary W', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place, Nairobi Kenya', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r998246971-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'happy guest', '\"I was at Mawimbi on Friday, and I really loved their food and live band. From the reception to their service, I was truly impressed. I had high expectations based on my friends\' recommendations, and I wasn‚Äôt disappointed at all. I‚Äôm definitely willing to go there more often. I also fell in love with their ambience‚Äîit was simply amazing, beyond what I had imagined. Everyone should definitely give it a try!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]');
