(1393, 'Odys', 'Harry Thuku Rd Fairmont The Norfolk, Nairobi 00200 Kenya', 'TATU RESTAURANT', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1910873-r1034259724-TATU_RESTAURANT-Nairobi.html', 'Great food, wonderful service.', 'Our first night in Nairobi - staying at the Fairmont Norfolk. We met Joy and Tavim at the restaurant entrance.\nJoy engaged with us immediately, showed interest in our travels, gave us some great information on the restaurant and property, and brought us to a very nice table.\n\nTavin was our server and was extremely knowledge, not only about the restaurant, but so much more. He gave us great insight on our dinner options, wine suggestions, and general information on Kenya and out future travels.\n\nWe had a wonderful dinner. Everything was prepared properly. The only thing that was better than our food was service we received. Can\'t wait to come back.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1394, 'Zach A', 'Harry Thuku Rd Fairmont The Norfolk, Nairobi 00200 Kenya', 'TATU RESTAURANT', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1910873-r1034239707-TATU_RESTAURANT-Nairobi.html', 'Extraordinary service', 'Eunice made our evening so special. Extraordinary service. The eggplant lomo saltado somehow eclipsed the steak, which was also delicious.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(1395, 'Charles S', 'Harry Thuku Rd Fairmont The Norfolk, Nairobi 00200 Kenya', 'TATU RESTAURANT', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1910873-r1034209615-TATU_RESTAURANT-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent Service', 'I had an amazing lunch experience at Tatu Restaurant Nairobi. The fillet mignon was perfectly cooked ‚Äî tender, flavorful, and beautifully presented. Special thanks to Michael, who provided exceptional service throughout. He was attentive, professional, and made sure everything was just right. I‚Äôd highly recommend both the restaurant and Michael‚Äôs outstanding service to anyone looking for a top-notch dining/lunch  experience in Nairobi.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1396, 'Huma M', 'Harry Thuku Rd Fairmont The Norfolk, Nairobi 00200 Kenya', 'TATU RESTAURANT', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1910873-r1033116857-TATU_RESTAURANT-Nairobi.html', 'Experience Tatu - Fairmont The Norfolk', 'We had dinner at Tatu and the Chef is absolutely amazing! \nFrom starters to the main course, everything was crafted to perfection ‚Äî you can see and taste the attention to detail in every bite. They even didn‚Äôt hesitate to share a receipt to one of the dips!! \nKudos to the Chef and the team, especially to Tunda. She is a gem of a person and a fabulous host.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
