(1398, 'lauren n', 'Harry Thuku Rd Fairmont The Norfolk, Nairobi 00200 Kenya', 'TATU RESTAURANT', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1910873-r1032383563-TATU_RESTAURANT-Nairobi.html', 'An amazing experience', 'Absolutely amazing restaurant inside a gorgeous hotel. My fiance√© and I started our honeymoon here. During our dinner, we had amazing service from our waitress, Eunice - knowledgeable, funny, and friendly! The food was amazing, The atmosphere was lovely and, to top it all off, we were serenaded by the entire staff to celebrate! A truly memorable experience!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1399, 'Steven R', 'Harry Thuku Rd Fairmont The Norfolk, Nairobi 00200 Kenya', 'TATU RESTAURANT', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1910873-r1032235351-TATU_RESTAURANT-Nairobi.html', 'Amazing food and hospitality.', 'Amazing food ‚Ä¶. But most of all really amazing hospitality and staff. Nothing was too much trouble . It was our wedding anniversary and somehow a three piece trombone and trumpet band complete with singers arrived at our table to serenade us. Truly unforgettable experience all round.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1400, 'Ric v', 'Harry Thuku Rd Fairmont The Norfolk, Nairobi 00200 Kenya', 'TATU RESTAURANT', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1910873-r1031947275-TATU_RESTAURANT-Nairobi.html', 'Verrassend  goed', 'Restaurant bij hotel. Zeer goed eten.\nVooraf 2 gerechtjes van de kok. Met een soort chips met super heette sausjes ( heerlijk) wat er boven uitspringt is het vriendelijke personeel. Zeer kundig om wat te vertellen over het gerecht wat je besteld. Na de maaltijd de kokkin aan tafel.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[]'),
(1401, 'kelly0897', 'Harry Thuku Rd Fairmont The Norfolk, Nairobi 00200 Kenya', 'TATU RESTAURANT', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1910873-r1030713599-TATU_RESTAURANT-Nairobi.html', 'Fabulous experience', 'The food, ambiance and especially the service was phenomenal!  We had sea bass and the wet filet and both were amazing. I would highly recommend dining here when in Nairobi. If you have a chance, make sure to say hi to Joy and ask for Eunice to serve you. Both were so enchanting. We loved chatting with them and would love to return to see them.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
