(1404, 'Studdu77', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r1019370746-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'Good service, mediocre food', 'Really nice location with a really attentive service. Margaret was really helpful with our daughter\'s lactose intolerance. Only fall down was the main reason for the visit....the food...\nI was craving for ethiopian food , after long time, but it was blunt, zero taste. All the excitement for a spicy and zingy meal got disappointed......', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
