(1406, 'Meenal S', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r993893155-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'Bad service and incomplete order', 'Placed a take away order at 5pm, was asked to collect in 30 mins.  I reached at 6pm, only to be asked to wait another 30 mins as they had forgotten to prepare the salad.  \nVery annoying as they had no courtesy to even ask me for a drink, no-one bothered to come and make me comfortable.  \nThis requires to be noted and improved for future services.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"drinks\"]'),
(1407, 'btrivedy', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r954581010-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'Saava saava', 'The actual place is very nice and has a feel of fine dining however the food was just good. There was no wow different factor but was of decent portions. However what was really disappointing was the service. \nSeriously slow and just did not listen. Had to send one dish back twice!', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1408, 'Gladys N', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r920843798-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'Food ', 'I Dnt know what\'s happening to Asmara, their food once was the best, the tibs they dnt taste like tibs again and their pizza has no cheese and it\'s really thin like crepes, you need like 3 pcs to be full,it\'s like tacos with toppings ', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\"]'),
(1409, 'Rakhee J', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r919298913-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'Good', 'Nice cozy place. Service can get slow at times. Definitely need to wash their cutlery properly and need new sets else you\'ll eat in dirty plates and chipped ones too.\nFood is good.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
