(1411, 'marlin6957', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r862624243-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'Good food good service', 'The food is very good.  And the service is really friendly and efficient. \n\nThe restaurant is well lad out and has a bit of a cafe feel and a bit of a cosy family eatery place. Airy and well spaced out \n\nWe tried the pizza , chicken livers (spicy), goat meat and the chicken in the spicy sauce.  And Anjera of course.  \n\nThe spice levels were mediocre in the livers and the chicken but the condiment chillies made up for it.  The pizza was very good ! The goat meat was a bit chewy but tasty\n\nWould I go back? Yes. Do I recommend it? Yes.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1412, 'Jay S', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r842485761-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'Dinner', 'Service was exceptional. Their was something wrong with the kid\'s pasta, and they replaced it soo promptly and the chef and manager both apologised and it was genuine and real. The salad and chicken were amazing.!! Am going back for sure.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1413, 'Terrance R', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r842216808-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'Nice restaurant to eat at but they don‚Äôt take credit card payment. That‚Äôs unacceptable. Come on it‚Äôs June 2022.', 'Nice restaurant to eat at but they don‚Äôt take credit card payment. That‚Äôs unacceptable. Come on. It‚Äôs June 2022. Your establishment should be accepting credit card payment by now.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[]'),
(1414, 'ABDI M', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r837731176-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'Family dinner ', 'The food was good but no flexibility in terms of changing meal plan. The waiter insisted we take what is on the menu. Our request was non spicy meal but we were informed that can\'t be changed ', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1415, 'Jackson Mutisya', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r821441193-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'Asmara Tryst', 'First time dining @asmara. Was pleasantly surprised by the comfortable yet easy and chilled out ambience of the place. Being a Monday evening the place was nearly empty however service was slow with the waitress forgetting our orders twice!\n\nThe cocktails though not as strong (is this a weekday trick, management?) were well balanced. \n\nThe ambient music selection was good but kept switching from genre to genre after every 2 songs. This became irritating and unbearableat some point.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
