(1437, 'Thomas Z', 'Getathuru Garden Off Peponi Road, Westlands, Nairobi, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Amaica The Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3581892-r897862382-Amaica_The_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Super nice experience üëå', 'We went for a family lunch and had an amazing experience. Wonderful food, delightful staff and cozy atmosphere... highly recommended... we will definitely go back!!', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1438, 'nabayinda j', 'Getathuru Garden Off Peponi Road, Westlands, Nairobi, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Amaica The Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3581892-r893520884-Amaica_The_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'YUMMY, YUMMY FOOD üòç, SO IN LOVEüòç', 'Hi (enthusiastic wave üòÖ)\n\nNever had the opportunity to fly out of Uganda yet, a friend that did flew your chicken in rice dish for me and I must say that\'s some yummy you\'ve got thereüòãüòã\n\nI have thoroughly enjoyed myself üòç', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(1439, 'Minamiku', 'Getathuru Garden Off Peponi Road, Westlands, Nairobi, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Amaica The Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3581892-r873274276-Amaica_The_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Á¥îÁ≤ã„Å™„Ç¢„Éï„É™„Ç´„É≠„Éº„Ç´„É´„Éï„Éº„Éâ„ÅÆ„É¨„Çπ„Éà„É©„É≥', 'ÂÖ®ÂìÅ„Ç¢„Éï„É™„Ç´„ÄÅ„Ç±„Éã„Ç¢Âú∞ÂÖÉ„ÅÆÈÉ∑ÂúüÊñôÁêÜ„ÄÇ9 ÂìÅ„Åê„Çâ„ÅÑÂá∫„Å¶„Åç„Åü„ÅÆ„ÅßÈ£ü„Åπ„Åç„Çå„Å™„ÅÑÁä∂ÊÖã„Åß„Åó„Åü„Åå„ÄÅÈÉ∑ÂúüÊñôÁêÜ„ÇíÂ†™ËÉΩ„Åó„Åæ„Åó„Åü„ÄÇ„ÇÑ„ÅØ„ÇäÁÖÆËæº„Åø„ÅåÂ§ö„ÅÑ„Ç§„É°„Éº„Ç∏„Åß„Åô„ÄÇ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[]'),
(1440, 'Simon', 'Getathuru Garden Off Peponi Road, Westlands, Nairobi, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Amaica The Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3581892-r872025693-Amaica_The_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Tastless food, terrible service and complete rip off', 'The fantastic pictures and appeal of sampling traditional Kenyan cuisine fooled me into eating in this shoddy establishment when passing through Nairobi Airport..\n\nThe chicken was inedible - some was rubbery whilst the rest was brown and tough. It came in a sauce which appeared to be a sachet dissolved in boiling water and the rest of the meal was tastless.\n\nWhen the server mixed up my order there was no offer to make amends and she was completely unconcerned when hearing how awful the food was. \nI asked to speak to the manager but was referred to the chef who told me \'we\'ll work on it\'.\n\nIt is evident more money is spent on photoshop and touts selling the meals rather than the ingredients themselves. \n\nWithout doubt the worst meal I have had in Africa.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1441, 'hcb81', 'Getathuru Garden Off Peponi Road, Westlands, Nairobi, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Amaica The Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3581892-r859423655-Amaica_The_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Lovely experience', 'We ate here as a family and really enjoyed the opportunity to eat Kenyan food that was a little bit more interesting than the standard nyama choma. The food was really tasty and a little bit different. Really interesting choice on the menu. The staff were lovely too, really welcoming and friendly. A nice setting surrounded by lovely trees and very comfy, relaxed seating. Highly recommend.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1442, 'Meenah', 'Getathuru Garden Off Peponi Road, Westlands, Nairobi, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Amaica The Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3581892-r842640439-Amaica_The_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Exploring Kenyan food', 'While visiting Nairobi for the first time, i was very keen to try Kenyan food. We ordered a variety of things from Osubucco (beef bone soup), Rech Ngege (tilapia with a tomato sauce) and rabbit eshituyu. All of which were really good. Also got, Kelewele (plantain), Ugali and chapati as sides and they all tastes amazing. We also had the beef Samosa which was honestly the highlight of the meal, overall it was a great experience. \n\nAmbiance was nice and staff were also great', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1443, 'Sara H', 'Getathuru Garden Off Peponi Road, Westlands, Nairobi, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Amaica The Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3581892-r835860911-Amaica_The_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Fantastic restaurant!', 'Absolutely amazing! We did the Gourmet Safari Across Kenya and the food was delicious! The service was wonderful as well. We 100% recommend this restaurant if you visit Nairobi and want to try authentic Kenyan food.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1444, 'NEIL T', 'Othaya Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant Lavington', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23983934-r1011651042-Asmara_Restaurant_Lavington-Nairobi.html', 'Always great to come here', 'As ever, fantastic. Especially helpful is Mercy Emali. The food and drinks are always provided well and we are always looked after very well. Very pleasant surroundings', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1445, 'Inspire58425', 'Othaya Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant Lavington', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23983934-r987143251-Asmara_Restaurant_Lavington-Nairobi.html', '3 mistakes in a row', 'I agree with Kate\'s review, the restaurant is inconsistent. You can be lucky or have bad luck. I had bad luck today.\nMy lamb chops were well done (even burned) and not medium as requested. It was taken back, but big surprise : I got a new plate with only a small portion and half cooked potatoes. 2 mistakes in a row.\nI asked not to have to pay for this, but this was simply ignored, without any sorry or explanation. The third mistake.\nOnly when leaving, the chef cook and the \"manager\" came after me apologizing and wanted to pay back personally. Can you imagine ? I refused this. There is something really wrong with the way this restaurant is working.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1446, 'Expat Kate', 'Othaya Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant Lavington', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23983934-r976330730-Asmara_Restaurant_Lavington-Nairobi.html', 'Lunch was alright.', 'The food was alright. Been to this restaurant more than twice and there is no consistency in their cooking ( some days the food is outstanding and other days just average ).\n\nThe place is nice and clean. Can be quiet sometimes if not over packed. Service also depends on how busy the place is.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1447, 'Juliana Siapai', 'Othaya Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant Lavington', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23983934-r875450007-Asmara_Restaurant_Lavington-Nairobi.html', 'Beautiful Eating Place', 'Beautiful ambiance and Great taste of Habesha food. I enjoyed the outdoor gardens and no worries about where to park my car.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1448, 'Jonathan C.', 'Othaya Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant Lavington', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23983934-r869502712-Asmara_Restaurant_Lavington-Nairobi.html', 'asmara', 'The food here was not bad! I tried their sampler plate and got to have a taste of their different specialties. The staff are very welcoming and accommodating.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1449, 'Wairimu Y N', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r677336557-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', '45 minutes for tea', 'Visited this place at 3:30, only 2 tables occupied, asked for tea and 2 sausages. It took 45 min to arrive lukewarm!! Pathetic service', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1450, 'KENTTOURS', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r675913091-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'Nyama choma Den', 'Enjoyed their nyama choma and the mixed African songs too. Good customer services. Very efficient staff', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(1451, 'DXB_Traveller_2000', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r516355241-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'Mutura ...... a must have', 'We go for the mutura, a blood soaked offal sausage. Fantastic! \nFull of flavour, lots of meat and juicy fat.\nThe best sausage and the kids adore it\n\n', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(1452, 'mariahmbithe', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r454213492-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'disappointed during my graduation party', 'It was my graduation party and had paid 30k for 40 people only to get a shock that day....the food was enough for 20 people only. Afterwards I was given an extra 5 thousand receipt being told u paid less yet they had qoutes for me. The worst was when I was told to pay that cash because those were not the prices given to me. It was pathetic and i can\'t refer someone there. I felt like crying', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(1453, 'Blawan', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r450936874-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'Meeting, solo meeting', 'Sono stati qui numerose volte per partecipare ad alcuni meeting di lavoro. Le conference room cos√¨ come il ristorante sono un po\' datate. Il cibo √® di medio-buona qualit√†. Peccato che quando si prende il buffet si finisce col trovare tutto mischiato a met√† pranzo. I camerieri dovrebbero tenere sotto controllo i vassoi in cui sono esposti i cibi e forse la soluzione ottimale sarebbe che loro servissero.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[]'),
(1454, 'cyrus k', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r416725818-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'Lunch visit', 'I was driving along Mara road after church coz I was worship on Saturdays,then I spotted this restaurant,it reminded me of my college days when I wished to pop inn but I couldn\'t afford,to cut the story short we had lunch with my family.\nThe food was very delicious ,my kids love fish and my wife and I prefer chicken.both were prepared perfectly and brought on time not forgetting the gorgeously looking servers,i love their striped sweater.\nAfter all this lovely service and good people ,one thing really DISAPPOINTED, my younger boy who is 5 yrs  when almost finished his lunch,by bad lack vomited everything....... that\'s not a big deal,the catch is the two servers who were doing their job  perfectly DISAPPEARED.!!! My wife had  to look for water and serviette to clean the mess.DOVINE our waiter reappeared later and didn\'t even explain why he ran away,the lady DISAPPEARED for good.\nKind request just let the server to provide the material to help the customer whenever such an incident occurs again.\nThanks', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"portion_size\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(1455, 'Kimzi7', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r408398548-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'Good place for groups', 'Great for family settings, buddies and groups.. We got a room on the back so we didn\'t get the noise that comes from the disco and such.\n\nGreat meal. Though I\'d advise the kitchen team to try and select leaner cuts of nyama choma(roast meat)\n\nGreat staff overall friendly and responsive.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1456, 'godwinamalicha5', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r357721942-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'very professional', 'i loved every experience here. good staff, friendly management as well. made my stay in Nairobi very very comfortable', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1457, 'Chege G', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r293609140-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'Average', 'Typical nyama choma, fry, chemsha place with loud music and average service. Okay for buddies get together', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1458, 'Dave_Cowley_Road', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r291079800-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'A taste of Africa in Upperhill', 'Upperhill is an international zone in terms of food so if you are staying in Upperhill and want a taste of Africa, come here. The main thing is nyama choma, traditional Kenyan roast meat, best taken with ugali (cornmeal) and vegetables, oh, and beer. And don\'t expect a glass with that. They have other traditional Kenyan food as well. The food tastes really good. \n\nThis is clearly popular with local people. It is an open structure,  so lots of fresh air while you eat, but there is shelter from the rains.  You can see the meat hanging before cooking, so it should be fresh. They seem to have good music most of the time. There was a live band with families dancing. \n\nI really enjoyed my visit. This is a good, traditional place to eat, with an English menu but no nonsense.  We were the only wazungu (white folks) here, so don\'t come if you have a restricted comfort zone. But, If you are in Africa, you owe it to yourself to taste it.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1459, 'Riogi M', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r280143606-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'The nicest nyama choma joint in Upper Hill, Nairobi', 'Excellent meals, excellent service, excellent prices, excellent location, easily accessible etc are some of the words I can use to describe this out-of-the-world joint located just a few minutes away from the Nairobi CBD.\nIts easily accessible both by public and private means \nIts absolutely the best nyama choma (roast-meat) joint in Nairobi.\nBeen there more than 5 times and wouldn\'t mind a repeat and again and again.\nPrices are also friendly, tranquil place so no noise.\n\nWould recommend it to anyone', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1460, 'TravelThruFood', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r245378695-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'Less than average', 'This place has mediocre Kenyan food. Stewed chicken or wet fry chicken tasted like home made, skuma or greens were undercooked and bitter, beef stew and Ugali were nothing special. Motura tasted good, but made us sick (diarrhea). The chips/fries were old.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1461, 'Sanjay R', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r185289982-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'Rich', 'Rich in taste, rich in variety of cuisine. You get everything. I most like the exotic Kenyan dishes the served. New taste though, but was a nice experience.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1462, 'Arthur B', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r169551889-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'To be avoided', 'Visited this place on a Sunday afternoon with a couple of friends. Unless all other places are out of service, please reconsider. The service is terribly slow. The meat is tasty though but be careful with the chicken as they will bring you the previous day\'s fowl patted down with oil in an attempt to fool you into thinking that it is fresh off the grill.\n\nThey insist on pre-order payment. Perhaps in an attempt that you don\'t walk away after placing an order - something we really were thinking of doing owing to a 20-minute meal not being ready 90 minutes later. The place was quite empty, which made me wonder how they cope when the crowds come, if they ever do', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1463, 'Sadili Oval', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r161400993-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'Buffet Lunch Makes Sense', 'The buffet lunch served here on weekdays provides for a good meal for a working person who is in a hurry to rush back to work.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(1464, 'Kingorik', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r159881306-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'One man guitar', 'The most prominent description is the one man bands that entertains here, they have a good variety of both secular and gospel. Good meat too, but you must be patient. You have to take care of your valuables when here particularly in the evenings.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1465, 'tkay k', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r157272202-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'good food', 'Popular joint. Road blocked, rough and muddy. Has good nyama choma, very slow service and a waiter once left with my change. Location is okay and security also average.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\"]'),
