(1469, 'Annabel O', 'Kenyatta Avenue Westminster House, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe Westminster', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d19795523-r1034240207-Artcaffe_Westminster-Nairobi.html', '‚≠ê Exceptional Service and Perfect Food Experience', 'The service was absolutely 10/10! Hillary was incredibly fast, friendly, and attentive throughout. The food was pure perfection fresh, flavorful, and beautifully presented. Everything came out just right and on time. I was genuinely impressed by the overall experience and would highly recommend this place to anyone looking for great service and delicious food. I‚Äôll definitely be coming back ‚ù§Ô∏è', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\", \"delivery_takeout\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1470, 'Regina C', 'Kenyatta Avenue Westminster House, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe Westminster', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d19795523-r1012615613-Artcaffe_Westminster-Nairobi.html', 'Best restaurant to visit in nairobi cbd', 'Great service, nice background music and beautiful ambience. Not to mention drinks are amazing. Soo tasty, I enjoyed my stay.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1471, 'Yuriy B', 'Kenyatta Avenue Westminster House, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe Westminster', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d19795523-r1000921599-Artcaffe_Westminster-Nairobi.html', 'A Great Caf√© in a Historic Building', 'This is a great chain caf√© that always maintains high standards. The food is delicious, the atmosphere is pleasant, and there‚Äôs a good selection of pastries and drinks. The staff is professional and friendly, and the playlist is simply fantastic.\n\nThe caf√© is housed in a beautiful building that will soon turn a hundred years old. The main hall has a high, greenhouse-like translucent ceiling. The vintage feel is enhanced by soft lighting, lush green plants, and good music. At the center of the room is a bar with a wide selection of drinks.\n\nWestminster House is located right in the heart of Nairobi‚Äôs old town, making it a perfect spot for business meetings or a relaxing break after a stroll through the city center.\n\nI took shelter here from a downpour and met up with my favorite person. We enjoyed a great meal and had a wonderful time together.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1472, 'Tshiroh K', 'Kenyatta Avenue Westminster House, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe Westminster', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d19795523-r988407520-Artcaffe_Westminster-Nairobi.html', 'Customer service', 'Excellent services from Hamisi.\nHe is always  polite, kind and confident! He responds with no delays and his professionalism makes him stand out!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(1473, 'Hillary A', 'Kenyatta Avenue Westminster House, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe Westminster', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d19795523-r956344110-Artcaffe_Westminster-Nairobi.html', 'Racism', 'They are racist. Came and nobody bothered to attend to me, after I made a fuss someone did come and I made my order which was nothing complex and was told it\'ll take 15-20mins tops. I ended up waiting for 40mins and nothing but then a white couple came in they were promptly attended to and their order was sorted in about 20mins.when I raised the issue they basically played dumb, so I waited for them to go in the kitchen for my order them walked out without eating or playing when it finally came. They suck', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[]'),
(1474, 'Violet W', 'Kenyatta Avenue Westminster House, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe Westminster', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d19795523-r955937842-Artcaffe_Westminster-Nairobi.html', 'Visit at your own risk!', 'Horrible service. Poor service.\nThe food is very mediocre. Slow service.\nWaiters have bad attitude its like they are having a bad day!', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\"]'),
