(1510, 'David W', 'Harry Thuku Rd Fairmont The Norfolk, Nairobi 00200 Kenya', 'TATU RESTAURANT', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1910873-r1028705914-TATU_RESTAURANT-Nairobi.html', 'Worth the visit', 'While the service seemed like it was a little slow, it was actually perfectly paced. We had a large group and it was nice to all be served at the same time with the food still being hot. Speaking of the food, it was delicious! We really enjoyed our evening.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1511, 'Samantha J', 'Harry Thuku Rd Fairmont The Norfolk, Nairobi 00200 Kenya', 'TATU RESTAURANT', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1910873-r1028056200-TATU_RESTAURANT-Nairobi.html', 'Fantastic Experience', 'The food was outstanding, we had the signature tomahawk steak which was cooked beautifully. The service we could not speak highly enough of this, everyone gave excellent service and made our experience enjoyable and memorable, we came for a special occasion and they certainly made our trip special!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1512, 'Maria D', 'Harry Thuku Rd Fairmont The Norfolk, Nairobi 00200 Kenya', 'TATU RESTAURANT', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1910873-r1028053266-TATU_RESTAURANT-Nairobi.html', 'Extraordinary Culinary Experience!', 'From a warm welcome from Joy who escorted us from the lobby when we arrived, to Veronica, who shepherded us flawlessly through extraordinary culinary suggestions,\nTatu is a command visit for those who always consider fine food a must!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1513, 'Jessie Y', 'Harry Thuku Rd Fairmont The Norfolk, Nairobi 00200 Kenya', 'TATU RESTAURANT', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1910873-r1027714317-TATU_RESTAURANT-Nairobi.html', 'Great meal on our last night in Kenya', 'Veronica was amazing and every element of the meal was fresh, well seasoned, balanced, and paid respect to the ingredients.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(1514, 'MarbleNY199', 'Harry Thuku Rd Fairmont The Norfolk, Nairobi 00200 Kenya', 'TATU RESTAURANT', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1910873-r1027546071-TATU_RESTAURANT-Nairobi.html', 'Fine dining in Nairobi', 'Tatu is a wonderful restaurant with delicious aged steaks and seafood, in a beautiful ambiance and set within the historic Norfolk Hotel. Many thanks to Veronica for her excellent hospitality and service!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1515, 'C L', 'Harry Thuku Rd Fairmont The Norfolk, Nairobi 00200 Kenya', 'TATU RESTAURANT', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1910873-r1027039304-TATU_RESTAURANT-Nairobi.html', 'Wonderful honeymoon dinner experience', 'We celebrated our honeymoon here and had a wonderful time. We had the oyster tower which came with an amazing assortment of different sauces to choose from. We also had the tomahawk steak for the main - absolutely delicious!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(1516, 'patrick137h', 'Harry Thuku Rd Fairmont The Norfolk, Nairobi 00200 Kenya', 'TATU RESTAURANT', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1910873-r1026671742-TATU_RESTAURANT-Nairobi.html', 'Wonderful experience, showcasing culinary quality.', 'Went for the Chef‚Äôs table. Was very well done and Clifford and Victoria did an excellent job. The service is unbeatable and the food delicious. Maybe they can think about how to take it even to the next level. Great place, unique experience.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1517, 'Ajay G', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r1034965440-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent food in a humble surroundings.', 'Food was excellent- true to its description and really well prepared. Cumin chicken was juicy. Dalal and rest of the food was quite satisfying especially after a hectic business trip.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(1518, 'Jdafranca', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r1034016699-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Not to come back', 'Not indian food, it‚Äôs something else, the flavours are not there not even in the sauces!\nThe people is very nice and helpful', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1519, 'Nelly M', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r1012529627-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'keep up the standards', 'It had been a while since I last ate at Haandi, and I was pleasantly surprised to find good food, excellent service and superb ambience\nwe had nan bread and chicken masala\nit did not dissapoint', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1520, 'Dakshdeep Singh S', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r986531283-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Dinner at Handi', 'From outside you may not understand the legacy of this oldest Indian resturant in Nairobi.\n\nFood was spot on.\n\nThings to avoid here would be gajar ka halwa', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1521, 'Rajiv08', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r956166316-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Disaster', 'Visited with my friend as we heard a lot about the restaurant upon entering we ordered and waited for water for atleast 15 minutes. Ordered veg jalferezi daal feta wala and Indian breads. Veg jalfrezi was nothing but veg with added masala and little actually not even close to jalfrezi. Now daal derawala no spices no salt no taste. It was a total disappointment. When a manager in grey safari approached us on how the food was I actually told him it is bad and he asked what he can do for us on this I just said make good and authentic food he replied I will just be back but never returned so the service also collapsed. Would not recommend this and will never go back .', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1522, 'jabevan', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r931370239-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Great Family Restaurant', 'Took our family here and thought the experience was fantastic. The service was excellent and the food was absolutely delicious.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1523, 'philhelb', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r924017053-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Classic Indian dining in Nairobi', 'Great Indian dinner at Haandi.  I hadn\'t been back to this restaurant in over 20 years and I was thrilled to discover it was as good - or even better - than I remember.  Definitely recommend Haandi.  I\'ll be back. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1524, 'LuisVega2014', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r920564597-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Great fish', 'An absolutely genuine Indian restaurant with the most thoughtful Indian dishes. Make sure you try the fish in a banana leaf. Delicious and lovely. The open window to the kitchen makes the experience just an inch better. Their wine collection won‚Äôt impress you but you‚Äôll have a great time with the staff.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1525, 'Cathrine Elisab... F', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r919329352-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Not a night to remember', 'Medium food and cafeteria like ambience. If you are looking for the best Indian food, this is not the place. The lamb chops were nice. The rest were medium. The ice cream tasted artificial and must have been the cheapest ice cream they could find.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1526, 'Abdulkadir V', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r903390746-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Poor service', 'Very poor service by the waiters and the rude manager.. \n\nWaiters are confused and do not how to help the customers. \n\nI wouldn‚Äôt recommend people wasting their time and money on this Resturant as their service standards have really dropped..', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1527, 'Nen64', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r884374893-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'A  little  disappointing', 'Have always loved this restaurant. Persuaded my family and friends to go as had not been for quite a few years.\nThe service was very good and most of the food was Ok but not as tasty as I remembered. Although we ordered ‚Äúmedium hot‚Äù .. It was mild We were particularly disappointed with the papadums which were not ‚Äúfresh‚Äù and the gulabjamun weren‚Äôt anything special  either. Made into tiny sausage like shapes not the normal ball shape and they had been fried in oil which was not fresh. \n', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1528, 'Parachut', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r881819959-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Further deterioration', 'This place has really gone downhill. Prices have increased dramatically and now they double as a Chinese restaurant while they were very well known as the best Indian restaurant in Nairobi. The food is not always what you asked for. The wine is served very haphazard fashion. The tall light brown-skinned lady/waitress who stands at the door to usher people inside comes across as very arrogant and intimidating giving little room for customers to consider their own choice.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1529, 'matzeinleipzig', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r869478554-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Nice and easy', 'Haandi ist nicht ganz einfach zu finden, da es in der zweiten Etage eines Einkaufskomplexes liegt und nicht ausgeschildert wird. Das Restaurant ist dann aber im Gegensatz zur lauten Kreuzung angenehm ruhig und stilecht eingerichtet. Meine positiven Erlebnisse: Die Bedienung war sehr freundlich und auskunftsbereit, das Essen war z√ºgig da und der Preis ist in Ordnung, da eine Vorspeise und diverse So√üen inklusive sind. Etwas weniger gut fand ich, dass mir der Teller quasi gleich nachdem ich den letzten Bissen gegessen hatte abgenommen wurde und mein Mango-Lassi war seltsamerweise warm. Ich kann ansonsten einen Besuch aber nur empfehlen.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(1530, 'Mercy', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r861798971-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Disorganized lot', 'So online it says this restaurant opens at 11am. My family and I get there at 11:25am and are sat and told that the kitchen is not ready. So we sit and no one offers us a drink. My husband goes to ask if we can be served a drink at least as we wait for the kitchen to be ready. No one comes. I also go and ask and am told to wait they look for the bar man and still nobody shows up. And that ladies and gentlemen is how we left and went to spend our money elsewhere. Our six year old daughter was so disappointed just as we all were. We are most definitely never going back to any Haandis restaurant again.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"drinks\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1531, 'Akothe', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r857611324-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'lacklustre service', 'I hadn\'t been here in a while: the deco has been upgraded and contributes to a light airy feel while the service has suffered a nosedive. We felt absolutely neglected. The personnel seemed unenthusiastic and walked with their eyes averted from the guests so it was difficult to catch their eye when you needed anything. The menu is also more limited than I remember, but at least the quality of the food is still good.  Not too sure I will be visiting again given the number of Indian restaurants in Nairobi.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1532, 'Ms Irungu', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r853854495-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Nice ambience, service could be better', 'Warm ambience with good lighting. Service personnel could do better with training and dress code facilitated by management.\nChicken curry tasted lazy and basic with too much tomato paste flavoring, the garlic naan was okay', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1533, 'Raju', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r850846377-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Lack of proper service', 'Waiters not motivated or show any interest \n\n3 portions of meat arrive and one portion of vegetarian comes when the other meals are almost done \n\nChef didn‚Äôt cook it till much later (no point having a glass screen to show the cooking)\n\nNo manager available but chef comes and gives an excuse the platter wasn‚Äôt working \n\nJust a really bad ending to what could have been a good meal \n\nSort your customer care out', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1534, 'DGWanderer25', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r848222145-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Review for Westlands branch. Fantastic food and beer !', 'We went there twice during our trip. Most of the food options are good.\n\nBest: Dahi poori, vada pav, noodles, kulfi falooda and draught beer\n\nAvoid dahi vada\n\nService is good!\n\nMust try', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
