(1537, 'Reena C', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r1038099953-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'The best dining experience in Nairobi for Indo-Chinese', 'üá∞üá™ Taste of China Nairobi üá∞üá™ \n\nIf you love good food and excellent hospitality, then a visit to Nairobi‚Äôs famous Taste Of China should be top of the list! Run by Arty & Jits Lakhani and their son Kishan, we were treated like royalty. To be honest, every customer received the same treatment‚Ä¶..but we like to think we were special! \n\nFirstly, the decor of the restaurant is incredible. The sculptures of dragons üêâ on the walls are all created by a local artist and they look stunning. There are also statues of Buddha dotted around, plus lush greenery, which make the restaurant really welcoming and transports you to the Far East üá®üá≥. \n\nNow onto the food! The menu is vast and caters for all dietary requirements. And the portions are MASSIVE!! Zaiya had her favourite, Satay Chicken and Noodles üçú, whilst we enjoyed a variety of different dishes, ranging from Crispy Babycorn, Chilli Cashewnuts, Glazed Chicken Wings, Honey Chilli Chicken, Tempura Prawns üç§, Veggie Momos and the showstopper‚Ä¶. the flaming üî• chicken! Each dish was super tasty and cooked fresh to order. We just couldn‚Äôt stop eating! \n\nI highly recommend that you visit because the food and service and ambience is exceptional üíØ \n\nThank you Arty, Jits and Kishan for a memorable dining experience and will now have to make plans to visit Nairobi again soon just to eat there again!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1538, 'Duncan O', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r978805330-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Dinner', 'A really nice place, I highly recommend. The services there are super friendly and considerate. Props to Sir Henry Makhatse, he was so professional and responsive üíØ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1539, 'Martin C', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r967054796-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Still the very best', 'For years this has been by far the best Chinese restaurant in Nairobi. The quality of the food and the portions can\'t be matched. Brilliant service. Attentive owner. When in Nairobi do not miss the chance to eat here', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1540, 'Verah Odipo', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r923039998-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'The BEST chinese restaurant in Nairobi', 'Beautiful ambience with beautiful views! Food was so flavourful and the service is absolutely exceptional! I\'d go here everyday', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1541, 'Rumeet', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r900384725-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Awesome Taste of china.', 'Delicious food with a good friendly ambience.. knowledgeable staff who help with selecting the right dishes. Loved the crispy veg starters, stir fry and sauteed tofu.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1542, 'Lisa A', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r885975722-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Cozy Asian Dining', 'The best Tofu Satay in Nairobi ! Perfect for a cozy dinner. The owner of the restaurant is very considerate of the guest‚Äôs opinion on the food and adjusts it to your liking. The portions are also very worth it. Two  can share one dish and  be fairly full. Comfortable sitting and ambience. Lastly,I‚Äôd recommend specifying the amount of chili you can tolerate because it can be overwhelming .. \n', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1543, 'Maria', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r864609688-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Deeeeelicious and Taaaaaasty', 'Warm and friendly welcome by Daniel who organised the Saturday dinner reservation very well Asante Daniel üòé Secondly the ambience WOW its amazing and spacious Moving on to the food mmh mmmh mmmmh Excellent food choices on the menu literally mouth-watering from the starters to the main meal And our waiter Henry, served us with excellent customer service He went further to recommend a new dish Pancake with plum sauce rolled with carrot cucumber spring onion and this i must say was absolutely deelish Kudos TOC keep up your standards its definitely a place that one would make repeat visits Yes we will be back ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1544, 'Paul Kiriga', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r848946608-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Simply the best Chinese food Restaurant in Nairobi!', 'Their food is amazing and comes in considerable portions.\nThe staff is very professional and the restaurant has great ambience with a fantastic view of the city. \nLoved this place and will continue to visit!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1545, 'Ravinder S', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r847489142-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Family favourite', 'Always like coming here as you get looked after really well by the proprietor and the staff. Great flavours and love the Indo-Chinese cuisine. Portions are large so you always have a doggy bag to take home. Service was prompt. Nice location with lovely views of Westlands.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1546, 'Steve', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r846003286-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Tasty affordable chinese food', 'Best chinese food in Nairobi with a lot of variety. Their menu is vegetarian friendly and they offer a lot of food at an affordable price', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
