(1548, 'Frederic_Belgium', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r783157356-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Bonne cuisine asiatique', 'Le restaurant se trouve au douzi√®me √©tage, accessible via un ascenseur √† prendre dans le parking du b√¢timent.....\n\nPar contre, un fois dans le restaurant, bravo pour le respect des r√®gles d\'hygi√®ne.\n\nLe service est hyper rapide, la nourriture, servie en grande portion (m√™me seule donn√©e comme \"regular\") est tr√®s bonne.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(1549, 'makena mwirigi', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r761764597-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Takeaway experience', 'I\'ve always eaten at the restaurant until this past weekend I decided to order takeaway due to COVID. I called and the order was prepared promptly. Shock on me when I opened my packed lunch, first thing is that they now added carrots and broccoli on the \n1. Sweet n sour pork\n2. Chicken _____\nI was not impressed with the appearance. The there\'s the pork, it\'s the most sour dish I\'ve ever had... NOT SWEET AT ALL!  Had to recook it so it can be edible. The chicken was okay but the rice and noodles portions were also reduced. \nI can never order takeaway from them again.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\"]'),
(1550, 'Marlene G', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r750057147-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Follow my tips and you should get a very good value meal', 'Perhaps 4 is generous but generally the food was very good and served in large portions. Some tips - avoid the spare ribs unless you want to play hunt the meat ( the cost of these were deducted from the bill ). The crispy prawn starter was great. Ask for a good break between starters and main courses. And go steady on the main courses - 2 regular mains and one portion of noodles or rice would have been more than enough.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(1551, 'Rebs23', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r746139410-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Great food and great view of Nairobi ', 'Had delicious vegetarian and vegan food at this restaurant. The service was good and the menu was comprehensive. Can\'t wait to go again next time I am in the city. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1552, 'Shariffa Bholla', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r738932973-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Dinner', 'Ambience and service very good. Food tasty. Portions good. Plenty of parking. Would definitely go again.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1553, 'divyakumar92', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r736183472-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Amazing Chinese Cuisine', 'We were warmly welcomed into restaurant by the Manager. The waitress is excellent as she understood what we wanted, she even suggested to us what else we could have. The owner is very friendly as he came to our table to ask if we were okay. The service is excellent and the food is amazing with a great portion.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1554, 'Rizwan Mawji', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r729991520-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Chinese food speciality', 'We were greeted well and could select a table of our choice. The waitress was well trained and knew the menu off head she even suggested. Food did not take long to come. The food was amazingly delicious. Would certainly come back and recommend anyone for a real taste of Chinese cuisine.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
