(1558, 'Dennis Keya', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r125800501-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'Not for the feint hearted', 'You will have to turn down 1,000 other places before coming here. ', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[]'),
(1559, 'Evelyn N', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r124288924-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'Room for improvement.', 'I had lunch  asked if Matumbo was boiled b4 I ordered was told yes, but shocking it was unchewably hard,! The manager offered an alternative. Good. The bar sells mini bottles instead of tots  should be flexible I might not have capacity for a bottle! They have free WiFi which is G8, I can sit and work!', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(1560, 'Wangkin', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r122217052-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'Its cool great place for super bonding.', 'Ave been a regular customer from 2004 to now,but i can tell that thngs are not the same,recently on 22 dec, 2011.i went there with my friends for their popular nyama choma, and chicken,and it was very ok.only that they have unexplieced  new waiters who are slow and rude.the buchery staff are the most orgnized and clean and  they are ever busy as peoples like their meat.drinks and comfort is good except when it is raining you cant imagine the roofs leaking water to  the tables with foods and drinks.i had a complain and asked for a supervisor,but when he come icould not imagine the response i got,it was an issiue of missing items on the table,tomato,chilli souce and saviettes,the supervisor told us that  it was an issiue of the management and went away without carering,only later isaw a nyama guy passing ad asked for the items,he brought them within no time.its a good place,but improve.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1561, 'Rosebell - luxury travel consultant.', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r121915594-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'Family outing place', 'Upperhill springs is a favorite place with families though they need to improve their service the local delicacies here are great and I like the idea of cubicles for those who dont want mix with many people.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1562, 'eunicemutheu', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r91911791-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'Total Hell', 'I was there recently and i didnt enjoy anything at all.They are very slow in service,my car was broken in and my laptop was stolen and when i reported to the management Mr Nganga and patrick they told me that was at my own risk.i will never go back there ,same to you take risk.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"service\", \"speed_wait\"]'),
(1563, 'ellie052', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r89325014-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'good meat', 'They have well cooked meat, great live band but sloppy service', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1564, 'safarista', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r19460096-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'I was here on a Sunday afternoon and the place was packed with families out for some nyama choma and super-bonding...', 'I was here on a Sunday afternoon and the place was packed with families out for some nyama choma and super-bonding. Simple great meals. very reasonably-priced, energetic band (and patrons). All in all, a good place to unwind with family and friends.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1565, 'DonRicco', 'Mara Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Upperhill Springs', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1086260-r19350337-Upperhill_Springs-Nairobi.html', 'Ish Ish, but good night...', 'Ish Ish, but good night spot.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"location_access\"]'),
(1566, 'Stavros C', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r737056542-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'Nice ambiance, excellent service, well cooked food, recommended!', 'We were pleasantly surprised by the nice ambiance we encountered on both sides of the restaurant, you will see the pictures attached, The waitresses were very kind and looking forward to greeting the customers in a warm manner. Inside, the restaurant was well organized and you could easily find your way around.\nSince our friends had been here before, they took the liberty to suggest we eat Asmara Mix as main which though well cooked,  We also ordered as sides Peri-peri chicken liver was ok, the Asmara Garlic Mushrooms were quite good in taste.\nWe will definitely visit again this establishment to taste different dishes.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1567, 'Missy T', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r728193827-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'My Dining Experience', 'I have enjoyed dining at this restaurant for many years and have never been disappointed with any aspect of my experience. It\'s where I go to celebrate happiness.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"overall_experience\"]'),
(1568, 'IGOR J', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r725670613-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'Just visit to take a drink', 'Very nice place excellent aranged great coffe very kind stuff and ok prices for Nairobi. I will be there for my next visit to Nairobi for sure.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"location_access\"]'),
(1569, 'Prashant Bassi', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r722278325-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'Fantastic..for lack of a better word!!', 'Asmara was fantastic, from the friendly staff to the awesome food and drinks. The service was super, my wife doesn\'t eat beef or mutton and the staff spontaneously combined two different dishes and it was fantastic!\n\nThe food, ambiance, staff and overall cosiness..SIMPLY FANTASTIC!! Would definitely recommend a visit...', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1570, 'IGOR J', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r715158511-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'Just a drink', 'Very very nice and well kept place, service is excellent, highly recomended etiopiam coffe with unique way of preparing and serving', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1571, 'Dinesh Varma', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r706253869-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'Delicious Food', 'Being a vegetarian, we have little choices in any African Authoncity restaurant, but Asmara has a variety of foods suitable for vegetarians. Njera with vegetables was delicious. Just need little uplift for kids burger.\n\nWe will go again again to have more variety.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1572, 'SHILAN SHAH', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r694292846-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'Great Ethiopian', 'Although the service was slow, the mouthwatering food paid up for it. Excellent cozy ambiance, Friendly Staff,  I loved the fact that it had a wheelchair ramp. It has toddler toilets and a kids play area. We sat indoors as it was quite chilly but the font and back outside sitting area is quite big.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(1573, 'sheilacheyne', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r673406121-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'TERRIBLE SERVICE', 'The waitress was very casual. Clearly she did not care about any of the customers and the others seen very a like.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"service\"]'),
(1574, 'MexChilanga', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r667994068-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'Mediocre', 'Big fan of Ethiopian food so I was super excited to try this place. We went for our wedding anniversary and ordered a bottle of wine, which was lovely. Service was good and we decided to order our favourite Ethiopian vegetarian dish with injeera bread. I‚Äôve had this same dish all over the world and was extremely disappointed at Asmara. The potatoes and beets were raw - literally blanched, and every dish lacked flavour. ', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1575, 'Deadpan0', 'General Mathenge Lane, Nairobi Kenya', 'Asmara Restaurant, Westlands', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d6276115-r666324414-Asmara_Restaurant_Westlands-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent Ethiopian food', 'At first sight an Ethiopian-Italian combination restaurant seems a bit odd. However, considering that Ethiopia was under Italian occupation during WW2 it\'s not entirely surprising. \nWe were a group of 15 people with different dietary restrictions. The serving staff were great and coped well with the different demands. This is the first time I\'ve tried Ethiopian cuisine and it was a revelation. I had a red minced beef dish served with a type of steamed bread roll (anjera, I think it was called). All tasted beautiful. Washed down with Tusker of course! All in all, highly recommended!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1576, 'Nooosh7', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r1037864502-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'What a disgrace!', 'ArtCaff√©, what an utter disappointment.\n\nI celebrated my birthday last week at one of kenya‚Äôs well-known restaurants with 17 friends and colleagues who came bearing gifts‚Äîonly for the chocolate cake I had ordered and paid for two weeks in advance never to arrive. As a result, I could not serve cake, nor even blow a candle on my own birthday.\n\nTo make matters worse, it took five days and over ten messages, calls, and emails just to receive a refund‚Äîonly for your team to offer a so-called ‚Äúgesture‚Äù of a 1,500 KES voucher (‚âà $11).\n\nThis offer is an insult, not an apology. It trivializes the situation and shows a complete lack of accountability, professionalism, and respect for your customers.\n\nI have been a loyal customer for years‚Äîfrequenting your Village Market branches, ordering from you regularly, and even recommending your brand to friends and colleagues. After this experience, never again.\n\nThe disregard shown throughout this process is a disgrace. Customers deserve better, and I sincerely hope this serves as a wake-up call for your management to reconsider how you treat the people who keep your business running.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1577, 'haji h', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r1037486402-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'disrespectful waiters and unhygienic place..', 'worst coffeeshop in Westland mall... very disrespectful waiters and the cockroaches are running around.... if you\'re thinking about hearth don\'t go there....', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[]'),
(1578, 'Rhoda M', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r1032236277-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Service', 'The staff were so friendly from the moment we entered the restaurant till we left it really felt like home Faith Kioko was serving us I really appreciate her she made sure that we had everything üòä my friends and I were very happy', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1579, 'Parminder H', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r1020689628-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Steak at westgate', 'I had family members from overseas and we went for dinner to Artcaffe westgate mall. We ordered steak and without a doubt IT WAS THE WORST STEAK ever. One steak was just full of fat and despite being told we want medium rare, we got very rare instead. On the night the food was poor, the service was poor. Maybe we went on a bad day.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1580, 'Abood T', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r1009112354-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'So So', 'The place is really nice‚Ä¶ atmosphere is good and positive \n\nPrices were quite high for the food quality.. \n\nThat was the only disappointment.. food came very late‚Ä¶ and it wasn‚Äôt as nice as we expected from a nice place like that.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1581, 'Nimish Hadole', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r1008845861-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Artcaffe Nairobi: A Top Choice for Delicious Breakfast, Lunch, and Dinner with Exceptional Service', 'Artcaffe is one of those rare spots that perfectly blends quality, comfort, and style. Whether you‚Äôre stopping by for a quick breakfast, a leisurely lunch, or a satisfying dinner, this upmarket caf√© consistently delivers on all fronts. The menu offers a variety of delicious options, and everything is prepared with care and quality ingredients.\n\nFor pasta lovers, the Linguine Carbonara is a must-try creamy, flavorful, and perfectly balanced. The Roast Half Chicken is tender, juicy, and packed with delicious seasoning, while the Diavola Pizza hits the spot with its perfect crust and zesty toppings. The Hummus Bowl is fresh and light, yet incredibly satisfying, and the salads - ranging from light and refreshing to hearty - are always a great choice. If you\'re in the mood for something more indulgent, their burgers are truly a treat - juicy, flavorful, and made with top-notch ingredients.\n\nWhat really sets Artcaffe apart, though, is the impeccable service. The staff are friendly, attentive, and always ready to recommend something new if you‚Äôre unsure of what to order. The ambiance is modern and chic, with a relaxed vibe that makes it easy to unwind and enjoy your meal.\n\nWhether you‚Äôre grabbing a quick bite or settling in for a long, leisurely meal, Artcaffe never disappoints. It‚Äôs the kind of place where the food is consistently great, the service is exceptional, and the atmosphere makes you want to stay for hours. Highly recommended!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]');
