(1582, 'Nisi D', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r1002950537-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'It\'s not vegan or vegetarian!', 'I recently visited your restaurant and was extremely disappointed and concerned by our experience. Items on your menu were marked with a vegetarian \"V\" symbol, which led us to believe they were safe for consumption by vegetarians and those with dietary restrictions. However, we later learned that these items were fried in the same oil used for cooking fish and beef.\n\nMy son and I have allergies and were negatively affected by this cross-contamination. Moreover, our entire family is strictly vegetarian for personal and ethical reasons. Using the same oil for meat and vegetarian items defeats the purpose of labeling anything \"vegetarian\" and is deeply misleading ‚Äî not to mention potentially dangerous for people with allergies or dietary restrictions.\n\nI urge you to revisit your food preparation practices and menu labeling. The ‚ÄúV‚Äù symbol should universally imply that a dish is truly vegetarian, including being free from cross-contact with meat products.\n\nThis experience has shaken our trust, and we hope no one else has to go through a similar situation.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1583, 'Dr Glen', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r990815673-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Slowest barrista in Kenya - expect to wait an hr for a coffee - food just as slow', 'We stopped here on the way to the Mara for a quick coffee and something to eat. The stop ended up being well over an hour, coffee took over an hour to be served, which makes them the slowest coffee makers in Kenya. The meal took just as long and am pretty sure they manage to get 6 slices of bacon out of each original slice of bacon, as the bacon serves are pathetically small. If you\'re after something quick, don\'t bother with this place, no respect for the tourists time.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(1584, 'Tino C', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r990145500-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Attesa lunghissima per poter mangiare !', 'Esperienza molto deludente. Quasi 50 minuti per avere due samosa e una  margherita al basilico. Inaccettabile. Peccato, perch√© il locale - pulito, accogliente, √® uno dei miei preferiti a Nairobi. Il personale, che cambia in continuazione, √® gentile, ma un po‚Äô lento, ma certo molto meno della cucina, che √® lentissima. Inutile, comunque, ogni protesta. La manager √® quasi sembrata offesa per le mie rimostranze. Che peccato‚Ä¶', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"service\"]'),
(1585, 'Leah M', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r980618583-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Terrible customer service from both manager and waiter - Westgate Artcaffe', 'I am very disappointed to be writing this review as Artcaffe has been my cafe of choice in Nairobi, however my recent experience at the Artcaffe westgate was the worst service I have received in Nairobi in a while. The waiters and manager even worse all had a terrible attitude - simple things like cleaning the table for us to have a clean surface and correcting our coffee order was met with a lot of hostility. I am a very dedicated Artcaffe customer over the years so I hope management can fix this - mostly the staff professionalism and warmth is missing - and I would not recommend the westgate branch to others looking to experience the great Nairobian hospitality.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1586, 'Ossi', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r980615524-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Solid cafe / restaurant in the Westgate Mall', 'The food selection is wide. You have everything from all-day breakfast to sandwiches, burgers, salads and dessert cakes. Food was good and the staff were nice.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1587, 'Michelle S', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r974306241-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Great food and service at any time of the day', 'We were very pleased to come across this restaurant/cafe just around the corner from where we were staying in Nairobi. Valley Arcade is just one of the locations for this chain. The waitress was helpful, making good recommendations, and the meals came out in good time. When she heard that I am a big fan of breakfasts, she confirmed that the breakfast menu was available all day and suggested I try a Kenyan breakfast - the Nairobian. It was a great choice - a very tasty variation on the usual breakfast menus we are accustomed to being offered in so many parts of the world. My husband chose the Sicilian breakfast, which takes the form of a platter of all sorts of treats. The coffee was excellent too. This branch of Artcaff√© is located in a pleasant space in the centre of this complex of shops and offers so much.  A great bakery, a bar, meals of all sorts, plenty of tables in several different ‚Äúrooms‚Äù and food service. We will return!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1588, 'Salima N', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r974227231-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Noise', 'Upstairs westgate artcafe. Pls can you reduce the music level....so loud. Also very hot up here. Please . Make our experience better pls. This enables conversation to be clearly heard. Less head noise. Thx', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1589, 'KJain', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r960113111-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Art cafe is one of the best caf√©s in Nairobi!', 'Limited vegetarian options, despite that I love Art Cafe coz  the food is delicious. And I love the relaxed vibe. \nWe ordered tomato and basil soup, halloumi in teriyaki sauce with fried rice, spicy cheesy garlic bread, and the lemon mixed berry cake and everything was quite delicious.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1590, 'Hal72', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r959647983-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Must-stop while passing through', 'Stopped here twice while traveling between parks.  They had wonderful coffee/latte drinks and great pastries.  They also had very nice restroom facilities.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\"]'),
(1591, 'George', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r957798793-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'American commanders', 'Art Caffe Karen hub Brunch- This was like home away from home. The service was top notch and the food was spectacular. Very spacious layout and the backyard had the best scenery. Me and my friend were visiting the country once again and we were delighted at all times coming over to this amazing venue. Special mentions Shakira, Tracy and Anne made this venue a forever home and we truly enjoyed our time. Cannot wait to come back for food, drinks and great conversations. Would have given 20 stars if possible!!!! George & George aka commanders .', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1592, 'Salima N', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r957779397-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Crap coffee', 'Westgate mall ground floor. For a few months we have been complaining about quality of coffee...never strong enough , never hot. The waiter spilt the milk all over my table yesterday,  didnt apologise. Service slow. Am moving now to bistro upstairs....better coffee experience.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1593, 'Thomas K', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r957689233-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Great food', 'Was here 2 times, 1 time for breakfast and 1 time for dinner, both time was great. Excellent food, good vibe and very clean. Would love to go back.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1594, 'Daniella O', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r937433370-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Rude waitress and unprofessional staff', 'I went to Artcaffe two rivers brunch on Sunday‚Ä¶.pathetic service and a very rude waitress I can‚Äôt remember her name because she didn‚Äôt even have a name tag‚Ä¶\nI requested for 3 items on separate occasions after she told me what I had ordered for was sold out.\nTell me why this waitress  had the audacity to tell me ‚Äòsasa Kama hakuna unataka nifanye!‚Äôin her exact words..\n I report to their supervisor then the best he can do is call the waiter to apologize.\nShe goes ahead and tells me ‚ÄòI‚Äôm so sorry if I have wronged you‚Äô.\nFor her to tell me if she‚Äôs wronged me shows that she‚Äôs not even remorseful.\nI walked out and cancelled my order because honestly it was frustrating at the moment.\nTrain your staff!!!!', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"service\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
