(1602, 'A09871234', 'School Lane Westlands, Nairobi Kenya', 'Nargis Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3685476-r551717713-Nargis_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Aweful', 'What a horrible experience! Went there for lunch. Initially, wasn‚Äôt allowed to order what we wanted to eat as ‚Äòmanagement doesn‚Äôt allow it‚Äô even though its on their menu. They forced us to order other items which we reluctantly did. \n\nThen, whilst my friend was still having her drink, the manager sat a random man on our table! No explanations at all!!! Never been to a place where we have been forced to eat something we don‚Äôt want to and then forced to share a table without our consent! It was so uncomfortable as we were in middle of a conversation that a stranger was listening to!\n\nThere were plenty of empty tables available. What a disappointing experience. Never shall we go back', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1603, 'H S', 'School Lane Westlands, Nairobi Kenya', 'Nargis Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3685476-r551717364-Nargis_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Worst Customer Service', 'I went in with a friend for lunch and all we wanted was a plate of poussin chips with tandoori naan bread. We were told that we can\'t just order that and need to include paneer tikka. We refused the paneer tikka and instead reluctantly ordered an additional plate of chips. The waiter came twice to us, insisting we order paneer tikka. A restaurant can not do that; forcing your customer to order what they don\'t want. \n\nNext as I was finishing my drink and we were awaiting the bill, the worst thing for a restaurant to do to its customers happened. They made a waiting customer sit at our table, while I was clearly finishing my drink and the bill had not even been brought yet. He just sat at our table while me and my friend were gob smacked in mid conversation upon seeing a stranger at our table. They were empty tables inside! Why just sit at our table?\n\nI will never again got to this restaurant to be treated like this! This is the worst experience I have ever had in a restaurant or cafe,', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1604, 'asandhu_13', 'School Lane Westlands, Nairobi Kenya', 'Nargis Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d3685476-r548312623-Nargis_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Good food fairly priced ', 'Great place to get a good bite - the service is fast and the food very well marinated. I was at first a little unsure as to what to expect but was really impressed - my fav was the garlic chips and boneless tikka.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\"]'),
