(1611, 'B.R', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r784537834-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Standards dropping', 'For being one of the best authentic Northern Indian restaurants in Kenya, their standards are really dropping. Even if your ordering take away and not eating in, the food should still retain its quality.\nThe naan bread is overly dry hard and burnt most of the time.\nThe dal makini is sour and not palatable.\nThe lambchops even ordered medium have no spice or marination taste. Very bland.\nThe packaging may be fancy, but we pay for the food not the paper bags, and sadly food is disappointing. ', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
