(1614, 'Pastorino', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands, Westlands, Nairobi 00800 Kenya', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r752731524-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Best Indian Food', 'You‚Äôd never guess that such amazing food could be found in this place. It looks quite run down on the outside and being new to Nairobi, a bit shady. But with such great ratings and raves from people here, we just had to try. It‚Äôs my new found favourite place. The food is amazing. It is pricey but so worth it. Inside is a gem of a place with Indian decor, friendly and helpful staff. We enjoyed everything we tried. It‚Äôs such an delightful place, I would choose to go with company to share the experience.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
