(1616, 'Hershil S', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r696490746-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Terrible Food & Service ', 'This is a review on the new TOC at TRV, after 3 visits and similar experiences by other friends/family! The main course food takes 30-45 mins to arrive and the general service is slow. Food quality has gone down across the board and what makes it worse is the owner Jitesh seems ignorant of the lapses of his once vibrant restaurant. Complacency is not an excuse and this place is quite frankly not worth the price!!!', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
