(1619, 'party310', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r689028469-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Great Indo Chinese ', 'While visiting Nairobi to see family we had dinner at this place. The Chinese food in Kenya is the best. They cater for the Indian tastes. The portions are huge so it‚Äôs best when going with a big group. All good ranging from starters soups and mains are delicious. We couldn‚Äôt move after eating so much. They provide lots of special sauces along with the food which just adds to the experience. I would go back again and again when visiting Nairobi ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
