(1621, 'Kumar M', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r681734783-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Birthday party', 'We celebrated a party here and everything was excellent. The food here is superb and so is the service.\nThe spring rolls and the black bean chicken was the best I have tasted.\nDrinks are reasonably priced and there is a good view of the Nairobi skyline from the restaurant. Place is always busy so do book.\nA must for a repeat visit. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
