(1623, 'Subhash m', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r680424672-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'EXPERIENCE AND ENJOY DELICIOUS CHINESE FOOD WITH TOP CLASS SERVICE AT THE FAMOUS TASTE OF CHINA.', 'Taste of China which is situated on the 12th. Floor.Parkwest Office Suites,on 3rd. Parklands Avenue, Nairobi is known for its fine hospitality, top class service and quality food. The atmosohere is impressive with eyecatching crockery on the table. My family and I have been to this famous place couple of times and we always come home with wonderful dining experience. Being Vegetarians we really enjoy their Hot and Sour Soup,Okra/Vegatable Salt, Crispy Spring rolls,Dry Chilly Cashewnuts,Manchulian curry,Szechwan Vegetables, Chilly Garlic Noodles, Vegetable Fried rice and other tasty dishes.All go very well with freshly served sauces, chopped onions and chutneys. Try their lovely sweet dishes as well.My wife and I celebrated our 49th. Wedding Anniversary Heart Winning and Memorable Lunch recently at The Taste of China where one can also have a beautiful view of Nairobi and if you are lucky then you may be able to see the glimpse of the World Famous Mount Kenya. Taste of China\'s experienced and wonderful host Jitesh Lakhani and his friendly staff are always there to serve you to your joyful dining. Subhash Modi -             Former International Cricket Umpire', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1624, 'nutsynuts', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r675372006-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Weekly dinner', 'Amazing food, amazing ambience and very friendly staff. The portions are a good size and def value for money. Its the best indo chinese ive had!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1625, 'Sanjay T', '3rd Parklands Avenue 12th Floor, Parkwest Office Suites, Westlands, Nairobi 00100 Kenya', 'Taste of China Restaurant TOC', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1053829-r675064211-Taste_of_China_Restaurant_TOC-Nairobi.html', 'Mr', 'Excellent service, good selection, reasonable portion size, very tasty and reasonably priced and set in a great ambiance...', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1626, 'Directors PA', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r933693521-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'APPRECIATION', 'We were a group of 30 plus at the Art Caffe Naivasha on Thursday 21st December and what a great job done by the manager: Faith.¬†\n¬†\nThe staff did an excellent and efficient¬†job and we do appreciate.¬†\n\nThe place was clean, neat, tidy and very organized.¬† ¬†\n\nWe also remembered our good friend the Manager Mr. Philp who is now at the Masai Mara and used be the at the Art Caffe Aga Khan.¬†\n\nCongratulations for the excellent services.¬† ¬†Keep it up...', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1627, 'Sote C', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r933688097-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Lovely place, could have been better', 'Lovely ambience but the food could have been better. The chicken was cold, the pasta undercooked and the rosemary chips had no rosemary', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1628, 'you54', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r931141508-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Poor service incompetent kitchen', 'Have been dining at artcaffe for over a decade and had the worst experience ever during Christmas. Two things on the menu were incomplete. We asked for a toasted sandwich with melted cheese. Not only was the cheese not melted, the toast was cold. We sent it back to be warmed and it came back the same after 25 minutes. Never again! ', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1629, 'Salima N', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r931044897-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Very bad croissants quality. Price is high like london', 'Really bad croissants , tastes like bread bun not flaky croissants. Coffee is ok too. Service is slow', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\"]'),
(1630, 'Chicago A', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r925477983-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Please treat people equally ', 'Artcaffe Junction, wasn\'t dressed best,I don\'t know if that was a problem but I took and hour plus to get my order done.I felt discriminated since other people would walk in and were attended to real fast.I was buying fries to eat in my car,only to get there and find no cutlery.Maybe the services would be better If they start seeing smartly dressed and other people as equals,', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"speed_wait\"]'),
(1631, '555lindid', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r924593135-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Clients unwelcome', 'I got chased out of the coffee shop after spending 30 USD on coffee and coffee beans, but opting not to buy pastries and rather take the complimentary breakfast from the airline due to delayed flight...  and no, i didn\'t walk into a restaurant with another place\'s food. I\'m a little confused about what just happened there with the staff\'s outburst. And then the they went to sit and play on their phones. Very odd.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1632, 'Cath S', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r923009648-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Tables blocked by people using free wifi', 'I love this place but it\'s so frustrating that most of the tables are blocked by individuals on their laptops.  Art Caff√®. You are losing paying customers.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"location_access\"]'),
(1633, 'Roam11203130931', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r921438572-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'courses in salad dressings coming', 'Artcaffee westi please we all know that prices went up but if you serve salads please stick to your original level of quality. It doesn\'t mean that we now have to eat salads with a third rate dressing, sour as hell with cheap vinegar and oil. Increase your price and serve proper stuff. Ameeen', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"price_value\"]'),
(1634, 'Mary Emma Owiti', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r920811777-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Terrible Food', 'I went to Art Cafe Kamakis,i ordered for classic burger it was not well done, the beef was red and had a lot of oil, i informed the waiter, however when they brought back the food it was too greasy and blunt could not eat it, all i got for the bad food was apology. I‚Äôm definitely not doing Art Cafe any more this is actually the second time being served bad food in Art Cafe. Definitely i do not recommend.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1635, 'Bablu S', 'Westgate, Mwanzi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Artcaffe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1141042-r913659704-Artcaffe-Nairobi.html', 'Standards have dropped! Very Sad :(', 'It was Horrible, Garlic Prawns were smelly and bad tasting, returned.\nSkewer Chicken was cold and uncooked, returned.\nFish and Chips, fish was uncooked and funny tasting, returned!\nWont be going there again.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1636, 'al r', 'Shivachi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Maharaja', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7136362-r924890101-Maharaja-Nairobi.html', 'Mahadump', 'This is a  road side vender who is moved in to a garage space. Hygein is questionable. Food is ok at reasonable price. Owner shows of typical Indian rude attitude. Name is deceiving, it would be more appropriate to name it Mahadump. Just go to better places in nearby malls.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1637, 'Vinay F', 'Shivachi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Maharaja', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7136362-r890872491-Maharaja-Nairobi.html', 'Wonderful, authentic Indian food. ', 'Excellent Indian food, delicately spiced. Wonderful staff and reasonable prices. Much better than Handi. Owner is friendly and very hard working. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(1638, 'Jason', 'Shivachi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Maharaja', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7136362-r645307243-Maharaja-Nairobi.html', 'Good food at good price', 'This is a a budget friendly Indian vegeterian restaurant in Westlands. Food tastes good and they have lot of variety. They can invest on their cleanliness standards and ambience though.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1639, 'MIRZ007', 'Shivachi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Maharaja', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7136362-r593598312-Maharaja-Nairobi.html', 'CHEAP AND GOOD FOOD', 'Located in westlands near Mp Shah hospital this small restaurant serves good food at pretty reasonable prices. The ambiance is not as good as your average Indian restaurant but the large variety of dishes is quite enough to satisfy your taste buds. Hygiene at this place is questionable as that is the first impression you get when you see the place or the cutlery served.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1640, 'Stef', 'Shivachi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Maharaja', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7136362-r554899253-Maharaja-Nairobi.html', 'Indian Veg Food , Good Value for Money', 'Try the Indian Veg Thali on Sundays.    Curries, Dhal, Rice & Chapati.   Buffet meal at $5.  Good value for money.\n\nOther items are Veg snacks & mughlai style curries - Paneer Tawa, Veg Korma, Mushroom Curries...etc \n\nGood Value for Money.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1641, 'Bhattkishan9', 'Shivachi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Maharaja', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7136362-r534275856-Maharaja-Nairobi.html', 'Tasty food at an affordable price.', 'The food is good and affordable. There is a large variety of food from snacks to whole meals. I strongly recommend it.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1642, 'Mohanakrishnan', 'Shivachi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Maharaja', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7136362-r424578030-Maharaja-Nairobi.html', 'Little less price than saravana - but poor taste', 'Not clean - looks like road side high way dhaba in India - taste is very poor - if you have no other go to find indian veg. Food and you are very hungry it will fill up your lunch need ', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\"]'),
(1643, 'bhavnakassam', 'Shivachi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Maharaja', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7136362-r419443085-Maharaja-Nairobi.html', 'nice location and quick bite place - not very clean though.', 'Food is good but the place is not always clean enough for you to sit and enjoy the food there - so best is to do a take away ... thats what I do when I am in the area.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1644, 'Mayur N', 'Shivachi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Maharaja', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7136362-r361365117-Maharaja-Nairobi.html', 'A nice place to visit when you are broke', 'This place is like a cheap Indian restaurant the prices are cheapest in town and food is not bad i mean you get what you pay for. The waiters are not very conversant with the menu and place is a bit dirty but overall 5 people can eat for 2200/= in copatty you end up paying almost double.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1645, 'Shreeekant', 'Shivachi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Maharaja', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7136362-r356241667-Maharaja-Nairobi.html', 'Shreekant', 'Food is good ..Cheaper compare to other hotels..Mostly coz they own that Hotel building..STAFF NOT have any knowladge PLUS CleanNess Also Not that much Good Its seem to Look like KIOSK ...Not much good Not much Bad So so....No negative Comments...Its good For Middle class Family...Paneer iteam Good they make..One Problem is ther only NO GOOD MANAGEMENT okk', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(1646, 'moha m', 'Shivachi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Maharaja', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7136362-r348806129-Maharaja-Nairobi.html', 'Great Vegeterian Restaurant Great Value Great Service!!!', 'Cheapest Vegeterian restaurant and great food, serves all kinds of indian dishes and also pizza cheaper than any other restaurant in Nairobi. Best Place to enjoy good Indian vegeterian food.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1647, 'murtaza2003', 'Shivachi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Maharaja', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7136362-r258770567-Maharaja-Nairobi.html', 'Poor Poor Poor!!!!', 'Service is terribly, wait period for a simple snack is an eternity wait! customer care is horrible. Food is not as bad, but not good either, and the review of the food, is overcast by the shadow of the service. ', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1648, 'Sedie10', 'Shivachi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Maharaja', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7136362-r252056021-Maharaja-Nairobi.html', 'Delicious Indian vegetarain food', 'Although the restaurant is very small and very basic, it makes up in the food quality and service. A vegetarain haven of curried vegetables, lentils, rice and chapatis, you cannot go wrong dining here. The thalis are simply amazing and the owners are extremly friendly and obliging, they do go all out to please everyone. Will we be returning, most definitely yes!!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(1649, 'Maseline K', 'Shivachi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Maharaja', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7136362-r251055364-Maharaja-Nairobi.html', 'Vegetarian Surprise', 'This restaurant isn\'t big on ambience and feels a bit claustrophobic. However, it makes up for its shortcomings in good vegetarian cuisine at affordable prices for budget meal plans. They have quite a selection of dishes to choose from and even those of us who love ourselves some chicken and fish found good options in the menu. The food was appropriately flavoured for Indian food lovers and the portions were reasonable. The service was below par with the staff seemingly overwhelmed with our group of 15 & rushing us through the meal (they close early). In the end, the food was worth the experience.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1650, 'sanjaya58', 'Shivachi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Maharaja', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7136362-r235347909-Maharaja-Nairobi.html', 'indian veg food', 'it is a veg only restaurant,with main focus on Indian food. Indians visiting Nairobi find home food here. but the food quality is not top class. it is so so, fairly priced, and fills the gap.\n\nit is well located and easily reachable. the service is good.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(1651, 'jenlynn821', 'Shivachi Road, Nairobi Kenya', 'Maharaja', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d7136362-r233142482-Maharaja-Nairobi.html', 'So delicious!', 'I have to admit, I love meat, so when friends invited me to a vegetarian restaurant a few weeks ago, I was less than thrilled.  However, I was very pleasantly surprised.  This place is AMAZING!  It\'s a bit hole-in-the-wall-ish, but the food was SO good, and the prices were LOW!  I went back a few nights ago, and I\'m ready to go again! You won\'t go wrong with garlic chips, masala chips, chili paneer dry, or butter naan, just to name a few.  Opposite M.P. Shah Hospital in Parklands.  Try them out!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1652, 'Liz M', 'Gitanga Road Valley Arcade, Nairobi Kenya', 'Java House Valley Arcade', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13349918-r939693090-Java_House_Valley_Arcade-Nairobi.html', 'Great food, very poor service', 'The food is great at Java but the service is very wanting. The staff prioritize takeouts and make customers wait for at least 1 hour. We are regular customers and it‚Äôs unfortunate after regular complaints nothing has changed', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1653, 'jacobmar270', 'Gitanga Road Valley Arcade, Nairobi Kenya', 'Java House Valley Arcade', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13349918-r734284140-Java_House_Valley_Arcade-Nairobi.html', 'Decent option for Lunch', 'I\'m made to understand this is one off the older food & Coffee chains in Nairobi and it did not disappoint with the menu offering a good range of sandwiches & burgers.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1654, 'Stavros C', 'Gitanga Road Valley Arcade, Nairobi Kenya', 'Java House Valley Arcade', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13349918-r652965747-Java_House_Valley_Arcade-Nairobi.html', 'Top notch for dessert: sweets, coffee and savory!', 'We went after lunch and must admit were pleasantly surprised with how efficient the service was, how well prepared the sweets and coffee was; all in all, how descent was the whole atmosphere! Would recommend it and it is a must to visit!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1655, 'Phil c', 'Gitanga Road Valley Arcade, Nairobi Kenya', 'Java House Valley Arcade', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13349918-r634414315-Java_House_Valley_Arcade-Nairobi.html', 'Not the Java House I knew', 'Was excited back at Java House after a long time.  Gone are the waiters who used to be on stand by to sit clients,  it took us approximately 15 minutes to be noticed, no apologies offered, menus were placed on the table and we literally had to beg to be attended to. We took drinks and had to walk to the cashier to pay. I simply couldn\'t add up the lethargy in this particular branch given the positive experiences I have had in other Java\'s. I hope this was an isolated case', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1656, 'Shimnik', 'Gitanga Road Valley Arcade, Nairobi Kenya', 'Java House Valley Arcade', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13349918-r624773897-Java_House_Valley_Arcade-Nairobi.html', 'Great salads, tasty coffee', 'Java house is a restaurant chain and we actually had our lunch at Hava house Adams arcade. Caribbean chicken salad and crispy chicken breast salad were great! It was a big portion, fresh and tasty. Vanilla double coffee latte and usual double latte were pretty good. The Cafe offers sandwiches, soups, burgers, sweet and savory pastry, fresh juices, iced coffee and tea, etc. Wifi is free and strong signal. Credit cards are accepted.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"portion_size\"]');
INSERT INTO `restaurant_reviews` (`id`, `author_name`, `place_address`, `place_name`, `review_url`, `review_title`, `review_text`, `review_rating`, `location`, `created_at`, `predicted_sentiment`, `predicted_aspects`) VALUES
(1657, 'Andrew W', 'Gitanga Road Valley Arcade, Nairobi Kenya', 'Java House Valley Arcade', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13349918-r617205794-Java_House_Valley_Arcade-Nairobi.html', 'Good for a quick bite', 'Went in with the family for a late lunch Sunday. It was good. Service initially was a bit slow as I don\'t think someone noticed us coming in, but the manager saw us unattended and came quickly to take our orders. \nAfter that, the service was quick, and getting what we needed was easy. We had two small children and their kid\'s menu catered for their needs. They even had plastic takeaway cups for the little one who is prone to spilling stuff. The cups were quite sturdy and even with the constant tipping, nothing spilt.\nThe food was okay and quite filling. All in all, it was a good visit.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(1658, 'Mzungubabe', 'Gitanga Road Valley Arcade, Nairobi Kenya', 'Java House Valley Arcade', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13349918-r610399459-Java_House_Valley_Arcade-Nairobi.html', 'Pleasant outdoor space', 'This is one of the best branches of this coffee house chain. It\'s not too busy so you can always get a seat. There\'s also a playground next door so it\'s great for families with young kids.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1659, 'Akidiva K', 'Gitanga Road Valley Arcade, Nairobi Kenya', 'Java House Valley Arcade', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13349918-r552143926-Java_House_Valley_Arcade-Nairobi.html', 'Breakfasty', 'Went to this particular outlet of Java with a little bit of a biased opinion on what to expect.                                        The waiters didn‚Äôt keep us waiting before they took our orders given they had quite a busy morning.            The breakfast menu was comprehensive with a good variety of food on offer.                                      Given we had a young kid with us, the waiter brought along crayons and a coloring paper to keep the kid occupied. Was impressed by this.      It took around 10 minutes from making the order to getting served. Though one of the coffee orders was cold üòî.                                           May I say the coffee house is conveniently located near a supermarket, halaal butchery, a Samsung shop etc.                                 For those with young kids, there‚Äôs a small play area within the square.        The food was nice as was the service.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1660, 'Mark R', 'Pofu Road, Nairobi 00502 Kenya', 'Cultiva Farm Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d19292723-r1038189066-Cultiva_Farm_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Wouldn‚Äôt miss if visiting Nairobi.', 'Pizza from the wood burning stove was cooked perfectly.  Mixed cocktails with freshly squeezed juices were refreshing.  Awesome decor and vibe. Perfect place to eat after a 2 week safari.  It can challenge the best restaurants in California in terms of food quality, friendly service and great vibe.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1661, 'Jennifer C', 'Pofu Road, Nairobi 00502 Kenya', 'Cultiva Farm Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d19292723-r1031243274-Cultiva_Farm_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Fantastic menu, Fantastic food', 'The menu and ambience was excellent as was the customer service. When the food arrived it looked fantastic and tasted amazing. I ate more than I should have because it was so delicious. What a great place!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1662, 'mamma50', 'Pofu Road, Nairobi 00502 Kenya', 'Cultiva Farm Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d19292723-r1030190581-Cultiva_Farm_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'You will definitely enjoy your food here', 'Delicious food.  Well presented.  Great ambience.  A well spread out and huge place.  A must visit  when in  Nairobi.  Enjoyed our drinks and food.  The veg food is also tasty.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
