(1689, 'GlobeTrotting705923', 'Kenyatta Avenue & Kimathi Street, Nairobi Kenya', 'Thai Chi Restaurant - The Stanley Hotel', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1104866-r996749372-Thai_Chi_Restaurant_The_Stanley_Hotel-Nairobi.html', 'Fantastic dinner experience with the girls', 'Excellent experience. Ambience, service & food were all excellent.\nI applaud Brian Kabata for his excellent service. He is professional, extremely pleasant, knowledgeable about the menu and he gave the best recommendations on the meals and cocktails to sample. Great service through and through.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
