(1724, 'Pling-08', 'Silos Road Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Tamarind Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1214217-r1035962486-Tamarind_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'One of the best!', 'Amazing food and service. Oysters to start with and a Tamarind lobster cooked to perfection! But it would not have been a magic experience without the perfect service by Washington and Juma.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
