(1727, 'Simrit D', 'Silos Road Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Tamarind Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1214217-r1035245527-Tamarind_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Tamarind Vibes', 'Great food with great vibes. Juma went beyond above and beyond to ensure we had an incredible time. The service was Incredible', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1728, 'MT05', 'Silos Road Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Tamarind Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1214217-r1035121759-Tamarind_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great Ambience, Greater Food', '5/5\n\nThe food was tasty and well presented. The portions were as they advertised and explained when questioned. There was a live band that played and sang mellow and calming music.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1729, 'jackline m', 'Silos Road Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Tamarind Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1214217-r1034931942-Tamarind_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', '10/10 experience', 'Very beautiful views and ambience \nI was served my Mercy, I had a wonders experience \nFood 10/10\nAmbience 10/10\nService 10/10', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1730, 'Tony G', 'Silos Road Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Tamarind Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1214217-r1034846752-Tamarind_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Mesmerizibg', 'The food was scrumptious, and the staff very friendly & polite. We had a large group with different food orders & the staff delivered 100% without any mixup. Veronica (waitress) was absolutely amazing.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1731, 'Ritro E', 'Silos Road Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Tamarind Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1214217-r1034249186-Tamarind_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best food in town', 'Lovely staff as always - special thanks to Joyce who always beyond her call -. Best food in town and attention to details. Lovely live band during the weekend', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
