(1733, 'Atlucas', 'Silos Road Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Tamarind Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1214217-r1034066884-Tamarind_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best ever', 'The waiter was excellent. Service was exceptional. Food was superb and delicious. Always wanted to come here, met with our expectations. Well done Tamarind. Celebrated 40th wedding anniversary and birthday.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1734, 'Linda', 'Silos Road Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Tamarind Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1214217-r1033844475-Tamarind_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Perfetto', 'Servizio ottimo e cibo buono!!! Vista spettacolare su Mombasa‚Ä¶ ne vale sicuramente la pena! In due abbiamo speso 100‚Ç¨ con aperitivo, antipasto, secondo, vino e caff√®!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[]'),
(1735, 'Ellie M', 'Silos Road Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Tamarind Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1214217-r1033627075-Tamarind_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'An amazing culinary experience', 'My friends and I had a fantastic culinary experience at the Tamarind restaurant the past couple of days. The setting was beautiful, the food was exquisite and the staff were very friendly. I highly recommend the mamburi osyters for starters. We will definitely come back if ever in Mombasa again..', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1736, 'Sarah Purvis', 'Silos Road Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Tamarind Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1214217-r1033596613-Tamarind_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'OUTSTANDING FOOD & SERVICE!', 'Our experience at Tamarind was nothing short of exceptional - so good we went there again the following night. Dammah was very friendly and accommodating. Do book online before 4pm to ensure a table as Dammah processes the reservations after 4pm - we had not done this on first night and yet she still went above and beyond to set us up with a table.\n\nFood was full of flavour and deeply enjoyable. I recommend the seared tuna and the smoked butter prawns. My friends got oysters and were having literally food-gasms.\n\n10/10, would highly recommend.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
