(1766, 'Hassan', 'Kaunda Avenue Fidelity Insurance Building, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'MNKafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3902895-r962365822-MNKafe-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great spot to Enjoy Amazing Food.', 'If you\'re looking for a caf√© that stands out for its food and beverages, I highly recommend \"MNK cafe by the sea.\" This mesmerising sea-view cafe facing the Indian Ocean offers a delightful variety of specialty drinks that cater to all tastes, my favourite being the ‚ÄòVery Berry‚Äô mojito. Their menu features an array of delectable foods, and lots of choice all made with locally sourced ingredients. The cozy atmosphere, friendly staff, and attention to detail make MNK cafe a perfect place to relax, work, or catch up with friends.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1767, 'Miqdaad Walji', 'Kaunda Avenue Fidelity Insurance Building, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'MNKafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3902895-r961578745-MNKafe-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'A Go to place in Mombasa.', 'Excellent food, cozy atmosphere, and friendly staff. A must-visit for a delightful dining experience! Amazing views.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
