(1770, 'nilam a', 'Kaunda Avenue Fidelity Insurance Building, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'MNKafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3902895-r930094765-MNKafe-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Mnk in the city, Mombasa', 'Its a great cafe to visit.  Friendly service and food is great. We tried their peri peri  boneless chicken and wings. Great servings..comes with chips of your choice, naan and salaad.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1771, 'hannah w', 'Kaunda Avenue Fidelity Insurance Building, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'MNKafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3902895-r928813509-MNKafe-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Our waiters choice was the best', 'I had received a review from a friend about this place and had not visited it because of that but somehow my group ended up here on this Thursday night and let me just say I wish I had visited sooner.\n\nOur waitress I believe her name is Florence was the best, we asked for her opinion and she did not shy away. She gave us her recommendations for the best burgers and we were not disappointed at all. She offered great service to all 9 pf us and was very patient with us. \n\nI think the only thing I wish they would do is maybe cushon the seats outside for the sake of our behinds.\n\nOverall great food, great service.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1772, 'Amina S', 'Kaunda Avenue Fidelity Insurance Building, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'MNKafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3902895-r908347095-MNKafe-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Only go here if you want to be put to work', 'Terrible service. Never heard of a Resturant that‚Äôs asks the guests to write their own order. No room temperature water available. Waiter asks guests to pass the the food along the table. You will smell of food once u leave the Resturant no proper ventilation. No host to receive you at the entrance one has to find a table for themselves . Once you find a table you have to ask staff to clean the table and floor from previous guests.', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1773, 'Relax446656', 'Kaunda Avenue Fidelity Insurance Building, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'MNKafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3902895-r897604031-MNKafe-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Disappointing service', 'We have been to your cafe several times and we have always enjoyed .\n\nToday we invited our friends and we were very disappointed with the service. \n\nWe had ordered bbq and waited for half an hour to be served steaming hot but instead the bbq was very very cold.\n\nLater we ordered Arabian Sands and to our surprise it was served in a disposable glass. \n\nI did not expect this type of service from MN cafe .\n  \nMunira', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1774, 'Njoki K', 'Kaunda Avenue Fidelity Insurance Building, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'MNKafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3902895-r889892368-MNKafe-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Amazing food, good service, great ambience', 'Amazing place to eat lunch, the ambience is great, the food is quite honestly the best I had during my stay in Mombasa, and quite a good selection of desserts. Ask for Patience if you go there, her service is impeccable. Not only was she friendly and took care of us well, she suggested things to do around Mombasa that were actually fun. Five stars!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
