(1776, 'KJain', 'Kaunda Avenue Fidelity Insurance Building, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'MNKafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3902895-r882076922-MNKafe-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Loads of delicious options!', 'Quite a popular one in town. Loads of options to choose from. From burgers to sandwiches, from pancakes, crepes to waffles & other desserts, chai, coffee, Mexican fusion with Indian, lots of wedges and fries flavours, lots of mock-tails and shakes. Service fantastic, warm courteous. Food takes a little longer over weekends, but worth the wait. \nAnd yeah, the best waffles in town with some 20 options to choose from! Fab!!! \nWould love to visit again.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1777, 'Sarah Hawken', 'Kaunda Avenue Fidelity Insurance Building, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'MNKafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3902895-r871920381-MNKafe-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Superb', 'My husband and I came for lunch and ordered nachos, tacos and wedges as well as a mojito, cappuccino and soda. The food was delicious! The mojito flavours were perfectly balanced and the cappuccino was the best I‚Äôve had in all of Kenya. When my soda spilled, I was given a new one quickly and without an extra charge - superb service!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
