(1796, 'Cillian C', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r998209666-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'A Culinary Delight Awaits', 'Absolutely loved my experience! The food was bursting with flavor, and the ambiance was warm and inviting. Service was top-notch, making us feel right at home. Highly recommend for anyone craving authentic cuisine!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1797, 'Yogesh292024', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r967968925-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Excellent place to catch up with a quick lunch with quality of cuisine assured.', 'Shehnai Restaurant is strategically located in town-easier access, quality food and personalised service from the owners. In my experience, the standard of waiter service is excellent and to date have had no issues on the same. \n\nIt does not provide any alcohol but the mango lassi is highly recommended.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1798, 'F B', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r950299489-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Indian cuisine at it is very best', 'Shehnai is one of the unique restaurants that have stood the test of time. The family who run the establishment offer a classy, calm and romantic setting that offer a variety of sumptuous Indian dishes that make us come back for more.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1799, 'C√©line B', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r937455872-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Super leckere indischen K√ºche ', 'Wir hatten seid langem eines der besten indischen Speisen. (Nr 35 und 38)\nDie beiden Eigent√ºmer (vermutlich Vater und Sohn) waren beide sehr herzlich, gastfreundlich und man hat sich vollkommen wohl gef√ºhlt.\nEbenso unser Kellner Kahleb hat einen sehr guten und zuvorkommend Service gemacht.\nDie beiden Speisen sowie der \"Karotten\"-Nachtisch waren exzellent.\nKostenfrei gab es Papadam mit drei Dips als \"Pre-Starter\".\nIn Mombasa auf jedenfall einen Besuch wert!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(1800, 'Imran', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r881001099-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Average', 'Came here with friends whilst I was staying in Mombasa and had an average dinner to my disappointment.\nOrdered biriyani, mutton karahi, tandoori prawns, mutton kebabs, and some other dishes. All of the dishes were rather average, and we were all surprised given the reviews on TripAdvisor.\nI have to say the fresh passion juice and the service from\nThe x2 waiters was exceptional.', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1801, 'Anna B', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r872963463-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Excellent food and service', 'Very good Indian food and the service was excellent! The staff was very friendly, the dishes that they recommended was the best.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1802, 'Compass789384', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r870649309-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Overrated', 'The food came very fast and the staff is very attentive. But the dish I ordered was tasteless and overpriced. VAT comes on top, one should know that without reading the last detail in the menu ', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1803, 'Rub√©n E', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r862491199-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Excelente.', 'Buena atenci√≥n al cliente, comida rica y servicio r√°pido. No se puede pedir m√°s lejos de India. Buena suerte, me voy a Casablanca.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[]'),
(1804, 'Jason K', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r828216346-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Some of the best service in Mombasa', 'Restaurant is intimate.  Server is very caring and attentive.  Two gentlemen who seem like they might be the owners are also very warm and welcoming.  The service is well thought out.  All the food is delivered on a plate kept warm by a candle.  Very nice experience, would highly recommend.  ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]');
