(1805, 'CJ L', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r788842459-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Amazing food', 'Perhaps the best Indian food I have ever had. The mix of spices was masterful to say the least. I recommend emphatically ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1806, 'SST1964', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r788236051-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'well serviced Iftaar Dinner', 'We, me and my wife, had our Iftaar dinner last Saturday, May 01, 2021; amazing service; excellent menu, super food quality; yes it costs a bit more than average but every penny is worth it. We are so happy we connected with Mr. Adam there; an exceptional person who served us very well; even the owner visited us; the top notch item was their Prawn Biryani, super tasty. Love it. worth visiting again and again.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1807, 'Jen S', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r781012215-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Happy to join the positive reviews!', 'Happy to join in the positive reviews. My boyfriend and I had dinner here the other night on a stopover in Mombasa. The staff were very friendly and helped us with selecting some food, and what we got was very tasty. I had the palak paneer and he had a chicken curry dish. The manager (?) was also very helpful in identifying appropriate dishes for me as I‚Äôm also gluten intolerant, which was much appreciated.  Delicious food at a good price. If I‚Äôm back in the area, I‚Äôll definitely stop by again.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1808, 'Bhavika M', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r767248887-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Delicious!', 'We had a lovely evening meal here, I was craving some real indian food so hunted this place down as soon as awe arrived in Mombasa and it didn\'t dissappint!\n\nLovely staff and the food was perfect. They\'re only open until 7pm atm because of the curfew.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1809, 'DubaiChamp', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r749822928-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'GOOD INDIAN FOOD', 'I had a veg biryani and it was very tasty although the prices are pretty \'pricey\'. the split a/c mounted at a very high altitute from the ground level so, it wasn\'t effective, but they are nice to provide you with a pedestal fan near you. The Indian yoghurt drink Mango lassi was very good here. my colleague had chicken biryani and he said it was pretty tasty. Since the prices are a bit high, you will be greeted by the owner of the restaurant and also by the chef who would inquire about the quality of your food and taste. Indian style of marketing. Overall, it is worth going there for the taste of the food. ', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1810, 'Wander561211', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r749712338-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Excellent food. Amazing tandoori', 'Despite some bad reviews I decided to try it and it did NOT disappointed. Amazing tandoori fish and prawn curry. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1811, 'Peter A', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r749086441-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Compulsory Service charge', 'While the food was good, they put a \"compulsory\" service charge. This is very poor. \nWill not return as we were very dis', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(1812, 'William G', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r744349015-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Very fresh and quite flavorful.', 'Very fresh and quite flavorful. The naan was right out of the oven and the service / ambiance was memorable. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1813, 'Monica U', 'Likoni Mall Nyerere Avenue, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Blue Room Restaurant - Likoni Mall', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d33351558-r1023765471-Blue_Room_Restaurant_Likoni_Mall-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Awesome desserts', 'When my relatives come from overseas I always bring them here first. The variety on the menu means everyone is happy and the cakes and ice cream is a must. It‚Äôs easy to see why this is still one of Mombasa‚Äôs favourite dining spots.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1814, 'Pauline N', 'Likoni Mall Nyerere Avenue, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Blue Room Restaurant - Likoni Mall', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d33351558-r1023762617-Blue_Room_Restaurant_Likoni_Mall-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Delicious fresh pizza.', 'I was told to try Blue Room for pizza and I‚Äôm glad I listened. The crust is light but still chewy and the toppings taste fresh. Easily one of the top pizza places in Mombasa.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1815, 'Mildred L', 'Likoni Mall Nyerere Avenue, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Blue Room Restaurant - Likoni Mall', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d33351558-r1023759961-Blue_Room_Restaurant_Likoni_Mall-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best tea in Mombasa', 'I remember sitting here as a student, sharing plates of samosas and cups of tea with friends. Coming back now feels like no time has passed. This is one of those Mombasa institutions that never loses its charm', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\"]'),
(1816, 'Muasya M', 'Likoni Mall Nyerere Avenue, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Blue Room Restaurant - Likoni Mall', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d33351558-r1023751153-Blue_Room_Restaurant_Likoni_Mall-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Quick service and tasty food .', 'I stopped by before catching my bus and had tea with a meat pie. Quick service and tasty food made it a good choice. I‚Äôll remember this for my next evening tea in Mombasa.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\"]'),
(1817, 'Manal S', 'Likoni Mall Nyerere Avenue, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Blue Room Restaurant - Likoni Mall', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d33351558-r1021685422-Blue_Room_Restaurant_Likoni_Mall-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Wonderful experience', 'Went for breakfast with my husband at Likoni mall, we were served by Natalie... a very talented and kind lady... the food was veeeeery delicious, we enjoyed Just 4 laughs show while eating üòÖ, overall 10/10', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1818, 'Amina Kassim', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r1037947730-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Underwhelmed!!', 'I\'ve been here before and the experience was amazing.\nSo I was pretty excited to go again but was utterly disappointed by the service. Our waiter was very casual and too \"familiar\' Worst of all was me repeatedly asking about non alcoholic drinks, asked for a non-alcoholic wine yet he brought me a bottle of alcoholic wine. When asked his answer was that the alcoholic content was minimal! As someone who has never tasted alcohol,  to be forced to taste it was hellish! There was no remorse or attempt at service recovery. I was so upset, in hindsight, I shouldn\'t have had to pay for the wine or the food.\nThe ambience and food and proximity to my house are a win but I am not sure I would go back.', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1819, 'lidys m', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r1022715447-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best üßÄcake in town üòã', 'Very cosy space with delicious Italian cuisine. Mostly I loved the gelato and the cheesecake is the best I have had in a while.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1820, 'Emanuel B', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r998190250-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Delicious Italian with a Cozy Vibe', 'The atmosphere was warm and inviting, perfect for a cozy dinner. The pasta was cooked to perfection, and the sauce had a rich flavor. Service was friendly but a bit slow at times. Overall, a delightful experience worth a visit!', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1821, 'Cian Z', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r994317754-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Good Italian', 'It is a nice restaurant in Nyali with a nice feel. I went to the restaurant twice, and the food was good on both occasions however, on the first occasion, there were 4 of us dining, and our food came out at entirely different times, with myself having almost finished and my friend having not even received hers. But the staff were friendly enough, and it was reasonably priced.', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(1822, 'vsvk1', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r990419691-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Requires a visible manager all evening', 'Excellent service and very welcoming until the manager/ owner (?) left. The service then became poor. We were four and two  mains were served but we had to wait 10 minutes for the other two to be served despite asking several times. The fan above was so viscous the food was getting cold. Unable to enjoy our meal. No apology. Not great really. Have been before but not near the top of my list to revisit.', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1823, 'Victoria M', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r973543712-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Fantastic Italian restaurant in Nyali', 'This is hands down one of the best Italian restaurants I‚Äôve experienced in Kenya.\n\nFrom the moment we arrived, we were warmly welcomed by the staff and Roberto himself. The service was impeccable, the staff was attentive and well-informed about the menu items. Every recommendation they made was spot on and absolutely delicious.\n\nWe started with the pizza, which was simply divine. The fresh tomato sauce and top-quality ingredients really set it apart. The Wagyu sirloin was a highlight,rich and buttery, practically melting in your mouth. For the kids, we ordered chicken nuggets, and let‚Äôs just say they licked their plates clean!\n\nAnd then there was the dessert.. The cheesecake was out of this world! I honestly don‚Äôt have enough words to do it justice, it‚Äôs a must-try.\n\nThank you, Roberto and team, for making us feel so welcome and treating the kids with such care and class. We‚Äôll definitely be back!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1824, 'Mame', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r956074577-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Not so great', 'Second visit within a week. Safe and fair to say that everyone (wait staff and cashier) is rude and/or arrogant. The food is average. And the ambience is ok.', 2, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1825, 'Marco p', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r951666472-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Buono..ma non troppo ', 'Buon ristorante italiano a Mombasa, assaggiato un p√≥ di tutto!! Non il Top ma cmq nella media. Spaghetti allo scoglio molto dolce il sugo, grigliata troppo speziata con aglio come si usa mangiare qui.. la frittura di pesce niente di eccezionale..', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[]'),
(1826, 'ruqaiyahhusein53', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r951509052-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Bad waitering etiquette', 'Our order was mixed up and one of our orders had been completely forgotten, upon asking her why it was taking so long for one meal to come out our waitress said that it was a mix up with the kitchen, which later was found to be a lie as she slipped up and mentioned she\'d forgotten to place that particular order altogether. \n\nWe asked to see the manager or owner five times and each time our request was either denied or blocked, which is a show of very bad etiquette on the staffs side. \n\nYes the food was good but the service left much to be desired and I\'d definitely think multiple times before visiting the restaurant again for these reasons.', 2, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1827, 'Zaher', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r949295475-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'I cannot recommend anyone ', 'A restaurant I would never go back again...Over priced, unprofessional staff, food not as what we expected of....eg seafood pizza, contains Tuna and nothing else...total rip-off!!', 2, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(1828, 'Sergentone77', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r944706455-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Non consigliato', 'Pizza buona. Spaghetti ai frutti di mare scotti. Frittura riscaldata e rimandata in cucina. Tornata ai tavoli dopo 30 minuti, era passabile. Chiesto il conto, arriva al tavolo dopo aver sollecitato vari camerieri e l\'oste, dopo un\'ora e mezza. Non consigliato.', 2, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[]'),
(1829, 'Michele Maria R', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r911852244-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Sorpresa d\'Africa', 'Un pezzo d\'Italia vera in Terra d\'Africa. Accoglienza, sapori e casa. Per chi passa da quelle parti √® obbligatoria una fermata da Roberto e Renata.\nCibo gustoso e originale non influenzato da locali e personali variazioni ad un prezzo \"fair\".  Spero di tornarci un giorno. Un grazie a Roberto e Renata.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[]'),
(1830, 'Kjell F', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r908024029-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Trivelig sted', 'Trivelig og rolig sted.\nAlle fire i selskapet bestilte pizza, som b√•de var smakfull og god. Servicen var up√•klagelig og maten servert uten vesentlig ventetid. Dessertene smakte godt og det var solide porsjoner. Drinkene var ok, hverken mer eller mindre.\n\nTrivelig bes√∏k.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(1831, 'Michele Maria R', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r904331123-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Everything fine and tasty ', 'Thunderstruck by Roberto\'s restaurant and pizza. A really Taste of Italy in hospitality and cooking. \nBravi Roberto e Renata\n', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1832, 'Chrisinder', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r892587193-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Don‚Äôt take your customers for granted', 'Unwelcoming staff go alongside totally unkept gardens. Total lack of ambience in what could be a jewel in the midst of lacking competition. Good menu choice and pending what one chooses good quality at a price.', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1833, 'James B', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r887126283-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best Italian restaurant in Kenya', 'Best Italian I‚Äôve been to in Kenya staff are really friendly and the restaurant looks great. I had the crab cakes as a starter and a chicken pizza for main the food was lovely would definitely go back.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1834, 'KJain', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r884669809-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Fab Pastas & Pizzas !', 'Love the casual vibe of the place. Reminds me of Goa, India... of the casual shack vibes with dim lighting and cutely done up tables. \nThere\'s a lot of variety to choose from. Lots of pasta and pizza options.  The ravioli in Napolitana Sauce being my favorite by far.\nService is warm and courteous. ', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1835, 'Anna', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r882267685-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Outdated prices are used to draw in customers!', 'Be careful before you order as you don\'t know whether or not you are seeing the correct prices on their menu. It is dishonest and it could be a scheme to draw in customers with cheaper prices!\n\nI referred to the menu on their Facebook page (which I had used countless times before) and ordered my food for delivery. I was sent a Mpesa prompt to pay but realised the prices were expensive but I paid regardless. I referred back to their menu only to realise that I had been overcharged! Immediately, I called Robertos but their employee stated that the menu was out of date from 2017 (but it had been posted on their Facebook in March 2020 which did not make sense). There was no mention of any menu change on their Facebook and I was not refunded my money because the employee stated that once I paid, I accepted the price thus my money could not be returned.\n\nRegardless of whether or not it was an honest mistake, it has been days later and the outdated menu is still available on their Facebook.  This is surprising as they ensured me that they would talk to the managers about removing the menu.  Therefore, beware before ordering as you may be looking at an outdated menu and they will not refund you your money.', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(1836, 'Rozinnakauskas', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r872010105-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Amazing Place', 'I enjoyed visiting this place and their food is absolutely amazing. Their pasta is to die for and the pizza was amazing. Tasted as good as in Italy and we couldn\'t help going there for lunch every day. Can\'t wait to come back!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1837, 'dazzaref', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r866732689-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Roberto\'s has lost its mojo and magic', 'This was one of my favourite places to visit In Mombasa but something must have gone wrong. The ambience has changed indeed and for a Saturday evening it wasn\'t so busy. My starter mushroom bruschetta took almost 20 mins to arrive it was very bland and tastless. \n\nI had pizza which was OK I asked them to pack the last four slices it was packed in a white paper bag on top of each other???\n\nThe highlight was the dessert the Berry cheesecake these are always consistent. \n\nAll and all disappointing Roberto\'s has lost its majo I don\'t know why which is disappointing ', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1838, 'abduli06', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r1034090585-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'barka, mombasa meeting point', 'Good food always. The tea mahamri and viazi always delicious. Breakfast  sometimes you have to wait for fresh mahamri.  ( sells out fast)', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"speed_wait\"]'),
(1839, 'Irene S', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r947984574-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Do visit Barka please!', 'Amazing and affordable food! Best shawarma i have had in a while. The beef pilau was a large quantity and you get to serve yourself the salad!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(1840, 'Joy Brenda M', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r940984615-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Good food', 'Delicious food. Always. I can‚Äôt fly out of Mombasa without a stop over. Highly recommended \n\nThe ambience could do with a touch up but the coastal feel is also nice', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1841, 'Amar', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r875068473-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Good hotel', 'Best hotel in the world good experience I will never forget this hotel it is nice and lovely customer service is very nice', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1842, 'Zachary K', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r857935803-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best Biriyani', 'A wonderful restaurant tucked in a peaceful cool environment of Mji Wa Kale(Old town) in Mombasa. Every visit is always more  pleasant than the previous and their meals especially biryani seems to get more tastier every time. No wonder it is President Uhuru Kenyatta\'s best lunch haunt while in Mombasa. Pay Barka a visit and you\'ll always go back.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1843, 'slofty', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r835663503-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best Shawarma and Chicken Thika', 'We usaly pick  their Shawamar and the Chicken Tikka from Barka, the Shawarma are the best in Town and the Thika has also a great flavour... don\'t miss a visit...', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(1844, 'Joy Brenda M', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r809189069-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Swahili food fix stop', 'This is my swahili food fix stop.  Whatever your palate wants that is swahili cuisine, you will find.  The portions are generous, be ready to doggy bag for sure.  Its best to do self service, since all the food is on display, and you can \"eat with your eyes\" before making your order.\n\nThere\'s almost no service, their aim is to feed you I guess, and on that they deliver handsomely.  My mouth waters as I recall the chicken pilau and the mutton biriyani we had.  Open from really early, its great for a breakfast and is open till fairly late so we have done dinner there too.  Home cooked feeling.  Love it.', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(1845, 'MUNYAU', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r800281388-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Good Food, Average Ambience and Service', 'The food is good, though there\'s not much variety. For lunch, there\'s chapati, beans, mutton and chicken biryani, pilau and fried/stewed seafish. Their prices are very fair but this translates to average service and ambience.', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1846, 'Nthenya C', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r800071272-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Not too good, not too bad', 'Whenever I\'m in Mombasa, I try to make it a point to eat at Barka. The food is excellent! \nHowever, sometimes the wiat staff in nice, friendly and attentive. At other times the service is terrible.\nMost important, however, especially in these days of COVID and all sorts of other ailments, the Barka management must do something drastic about the hygene and cleanliness. This is very controlable; please take heed.', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1847, 'B H', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r781449560-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Exactly what it says on the tin ', 'This is good quality swahili food at a great price and with great service. The queues of cars picking up takeaway are a testament to the place\'s popularity. The biryani was great in particular. Welcoming staff too. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1848, 'Beverly Wakio', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r746515637-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best shawarma', 'Awesome shawarmas. BoooooombüëåCity star‚Äôs doen come close! Am yet to try their Biryani but I‚Äôll do that pretty soon. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(1849, 'Adesina_AA', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r735582484-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Poor Hygiene - lost my appetite; nauseating environment', 'Came across this restaurant by accident - we were looking for Island Dishes - we followed the map and it took us to this street, but we found that Island Dishes was actually back from where we came (Fort Jesus). Since we were tired and hungry, we walked into this restaurant after seeing it was one of the restaurants on tripadvisor serving local food - this gave us some confidence as the area outside looks a bit dodgy and dirty. It was absolute chaos - although it was not completely packed; the waiters seemed occupied with everything but serving us. We had to ask around as to where to sit and how to order (you have to place your order with some cashier in a corner before you sit) and after doing so, and sitting for a while, no one came to bring the order or even wipe the table. We left after seeing how the waiters were handling the dirty dishes; the area was just unhygienic and nauseating. The locals don\'t seem to mind and seem accustomed to the rudeness and lack of customer service; which may explain some of the management\'s don\'t care attitude. To be honest, coming from holiday in Tanzania, it\'s a rude shock to see the complete difference in mannerisms and approach by people in the two countries - from service staff in restaurants etc. even in the local restaurants. Tanzanians seem to be more hospitable and good natured while Kenyans are simply not - this is informed by a few interactions in the few days I\'ve been here, and my experience in this restaurant is just one among them.\nOne other thing, we relied on tripadvisor to inform our decision to go to this restaurant, but later we found many many more reviews on google, which affirmed our negative experience - so my take away is to consult multiple forums for better perspective before visiting some places.', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1850, 'edda d', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r729675643-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Daily Breakfast stop', 'Their breakfast offerings are delicious, vast and value for money. \nAll things coasterian matai, chapati, mahamri, beef samosa, viazi ya nazi, bhajias, maini, viazi ya rojo and many more\n\nDon‚Äôt forget to try the sauces on the table with your meal. Add an extra zing in your mouth. \n', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\"]'),
(1851, 'LongRoadUp', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r723184190-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great Biryani', 'Simple and tasty biryani and pilau. Chicken or goat meat. Great value and quick and efficient service. Thoroughly recommend.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1852, 'pirranD', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r714312924-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Tasty lunch! My kind of place', 'This place is a bit chaotic, grubby, and odd, but the food (Biryanis/curries) is served quickly, is very tasty, and is great value. No fuss, no faff, just great tasty food. Obvioulsy not a place for a special occasion, but for a filling and yummy lunch, this place is great - recommended.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1853, 'Ahmad I', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r702553291-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Poor service', 'After having paid and waited for almost an hour for food we only got half our order and to make matters worse guys who ordered later were served before us. We had to be refunded for food we dint get.', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\"]'),
(1854, 'DrSMD40', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r700751989-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Amazing experience', 'It was an amazing experience. Great food, excellent portion and very helpful staff. Totally recommend!', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1855, 'JaneNjuguna', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r652534419-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Authentic dishes - Mombasa town', 'Barka restaurant is located in Mombasa Island town. It is a simple local restaurant that serves coastal dishes. I had missed swahili food and went there for a chicken biryani meal. It is not a fork and knife place. Actually, the rice, chicken and biryani gravy meal is mostly eaten by hand. I also took their tamarind juice that was somehow too sugary and had very little tamarind.Their chicken biryani was good. ', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1856, 'gabriella g', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r647231594-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Ottimo cibo', 'Ambiente informale gestione semplice famigliare  i piatti sono un po‚Äô i classici della cucina africana con mescolanze di spezie India e ed arabe   Io ci torno spesso e non mi ha mai deluso', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[]'),
(1857, 'Ken Otis', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r645774391-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Amazing food priced well', 'Everything from the samosas, to the chicken biryani and the lamb curry was amazing and at under $10, all worth it. Honorable mention to the Tamarind juice. A hidden foodies jewel in the old town!! A must visit culinary treat.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\"]'),
(1858, 'Nilam A', 'Kaunda Avenue Fidelity Insurance Building, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'MNKafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3902895-r798681282-MNKafe-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Eve coffee', 'Had an amazing pistachio tart. Absolutely absolutely out of this world. Excellent service . Love the waffle too.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1859, 'That Dude', 'Kaunda Avenue Fidelity Insurance Building, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'MNKafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3902895-r781900974-MNKafe-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'WOW!!!!! ITS WONDERFUL !', 'WOW!!!!! ITS WONDERFUL  all the food there is wonderful and perfect, i once went there for a friends birthday and it was spectacular. All the wraps and burgers are perfect. And the waffles are immaculate. My favorite thing to order is either a Miami burger with chicken tenders and a chocolate milkshake, or the American barbecue also with a chocolate milkshake. It is my favorite place to eat from and I LOVE the food.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1860, 'Jian', 'Kaunda Avenue Fidelity Insurance Building, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'MNKafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3902895-r781060754-MNKafe-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Good food.. could be better if the owner had a better attitude!', 'I went there on the weekend, enjoyed my Chicken Bbq ... ( something new they have started) i tried to ask for a little changes to my order  but the owner totaly refused to accomodate my preference, insisted i have it as is!!', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\"]'),
(1861, 'kini_94', 'Kaunda Avenue Fidelity Insurance Building, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'MNKafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3902895-r776732731-MNKafe-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best breakfast in Mombasa ', 'Best breakfasts in Mombasa. Good environment, good food with a wide variety, good customer service too. Keep it up guys. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1862, 'Kumar Morjaria', 'Kaunda Avenue Fidelity Insurance Building, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'MNKafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3902895-r774617678-MNKafe-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Awesome waffles and grilled sandwiches', 'We were taken to this establishment by our host for lunch. We were welcomed politely and full Covid safety procedures were followed.\nWe had the bombay fries and an aubergine grilled sandwich which was full of flavour. Next came the waffles drenched in Belgian chocolate and the other one had ice cream on them. Both pancakes were\nvery good. A nice selection of coffee and shakes are on offer here. Burger selection is also good. We enjoyed our lunch here and was a nice experience. Keep up the good work. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1863, 'Sabra I', 'Kaunda Avenue Fidelity Insurance Building, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'MNKafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3902895-r767575640-MNKafe-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'No decency whatsoever to even apologise!', 'I visited this establishment a few days ago.the 2waiters that served our table were not the politest to begin with.\nMy spicy potato wrap order was served with a very off smell. \nTrying to get attention on that was a v upsetting experience not to mention even after reviewing this establishment on Google map regarding that incident,the owner mohamed has the audacity to call me a liar on my review of how the situation was handled.\nHow dare you insult a customer who settled her bill in full and belittling her experience that I only wanted a replacement for my order cz it was too spicy.\nYou served me smelly food,I have every right to tell you my experience and how poorly you handled the issue at hand.\nAn apology would have sufficed but to add salt to injury,you call me a liar!!!???\nYou are inthe wrong industry my friend if you take criticism and hurl it back to a customer like im out to get you or defame your business.\nI call it as how it is.\nSmelly food that was served to me,waiters were not so keen to raise it with the management and you the owner who is very quick to name call a customer a liar. \n\nI hope no customer crosses your path to be called that again. Very unprofessional and rude.', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1864, 'Zahra P', 'Kaunda Avenue Fidelity Insurance Building, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'MNKafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3902895-r740907743-MNKafe-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Amazing Food and Dessert', 'Went with some friends..the peri chicken wrap and the chicken burger was very tasty and just perfect. The Chocolate Haven Waffle is to die for...it is definitely a place with a very relaxed ambience that one would enjoy.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1865, 'ZIANA H', 'Kaunda Avenue Fidelity Insurance Building, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'MNKafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3902895-r740207909-MNKafe-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best burgers and wraps as well as dessert', 'You can‚Äôt go wrong with the food here,\nBest of the burgers you have eaten especially the Miami burger üëå.\nWraps the chicken one ‚òùÔ∏è.\n\nDessert the pancakes ü•û are the best.\n\nRate it üíØ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
