(1867, 'muzz', 'Kaunda Avenue Fidelity Insurance Building, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'MNKafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3902895-r739961155-MNKafe-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'A must visit place!', 'Incredibly gorgeous set up, with amazing desserts and dinning options!\nThorough enjoy with each visit, be it friends or family gatherings. Don\'t miss out!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"menu_variety\"]'),
