(1870, 'Stanley A', 'Silos Road Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Tamarind Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1214217-r1033108317-Tamarind_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Home away from - tamarind village', 'It\'s a nice place  and a good working environment, easily accessible with a very supportive staff both housekeeping and at the restaurants.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1871, 'Felix K', 'Silos Road Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Tamarind Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1214217-r1033103690-Tamarind_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Tamarind Dhow - An experience of a life time', 'Tamarind is home amazing staff excellent customer service right from the guard at the gate,the reception team, housekeeping and off course the food is amazing very taste well presented and consistent', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1872, 'Sweets S', 'Silos Road Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Tamarind Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1214217-r1032995380-Tamarind_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Absolutely excellent service by Mr. Kyalo & lovely food too!', 'Excellent customer service by Mr. Kyalo. Extremely friendly & super efficient. Keep it up Kyalo! You made our anniversary evening that much brighter. Food was amazing, very appetising & fulfilling. Really enjoyed our evening & beautiful experience at Tamarind. Keep it up entire Tamarind team. üëè Ashok Pattni.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1873, 'Michelle D', 'Silos Road Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Tamarind Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1214217-r1032972041-Tamarind_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best Customer Service in Mombasa!', 'Excellent location to the restaurant and our seating was perfect as well as the atmosphere!  The food has always been the best as long as I have been visiting Mombasa for the last 36 years.  The waitress/waiter staff has always been professional inside and out and they gave nothing but a ‚Äú10‚Äù service!  The food has huge servings for the money and I will always return as long as the service remains the same! P.S. My waiter was Mwambi and he had the best attitude and great conversation with my husband and I. We complimented the restaurant in many ways and he complimented in return his training is what makes the difference. Best luck to always serving great customer service satisfaction and great food!! Sincerely,\n\nMichelle Davis-Mohammed', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1874, 'Sandra R', 'Silos Road Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Tamarind Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1214217-r1032936969-Tamarind_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', '‚ù§Ô∏è', 'Mercy the Waitress  just perfect  üëå service \nThank you Mercy good job and keep it up.\nGood ambience as well too.\nNext time I will definitely visit.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1875, 'S T', 'Silos Road Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Tamarind Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1214217-r1032867301-Tamarind_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Excellent service and ambiance. Always a pleasure', 'We celebrated our anniversary dinner on the lawn & it was an amazing experience.\nThe team who helped setup were incredible and went above and beyond our expectations.\nPrudence and Elizabeth did an excellent job. Our hostess Damaris and server bonface did a wonderful job during our dinner.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1876, 'Wendy H', 'Silos Road Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Tamarind Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1214217-r1032561351-Tamarind_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Five stars shine brightly', 'Stunning setting, aesthetically pleasing, food was gastronomic, the staff were warm, welcoming & provided excellent service.\nOur favourite dish was the squid ink seafood linguine but all of our choices were absolutely delicious.\nThis was a recommendation and we have absolutely loved our evening of wining and dining.\nThankyou for our wonderful experience.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1877, 'Sandra S', 'Silos Road Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Tamarind Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1214217-r1032561237-Tamarind_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Flavour explosion', 'A flavour explosion. We really enjoyed the wonderful surroundings, and Kingdom‚Äôs excellent service. Highly recommend.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1878, 'Peter C', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r729637366-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'A BIG disappointment.  Not worth the trip there.', 'So much for fresh, mouth busting flavours.  I had their ‚Äòsignature shrimp dish‚Äô. The shrimp was clearly previously frozen,quite rubbery and tasteless. The sauce was so blended I could not identify the spices.  The watermelon juice was watered down as were the chutneys.  \nTrip advisor recommended this in 2017.  I think it is time to re-evaluate.', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1879, 'Nikunj P', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r727666213-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Lunch', 'Excellent beyond par!\nCustomised to taste...loved it\nSuper home delivery... hot n fresh.\nThe great hot taste', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"delivery_takeout\"]');
