(1880, 'Shamash V', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r725117455-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Excellent Consistent Service with Quality and Tasty Food!', 'For the past 3 months, have been ordering. Mehboob, Adam and Team never fail to disappoint!\n\nTheir service is spot on! The food is scrumptious,  delicious and finger lickin!\nThe quality of the food never deviates and is consistent!\n\nTheir after sales service support is great! They call for feedback which is unheard of!\n\nKeep it up and this is highly recommended for all! \n\nDefinitely not a miss!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1881, 'Mohamed V', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r725113497-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Excellent, Outstanding Service with Sumptuous Dishes!', 'We had a business luncheon for 12 people and everything from the services of Mehboob and staff to the food was extremely well laid out. Management went out of their way to ensure we were taken care of!\n\nThe food from the starters to the dessert was tasty and delicious. \n\nThis place is highly recommended! Do not miss!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1882, 'ckiarie2002ke', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r716255270-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Overrated', 'Went there for dinner. We were welcomed warmly and shown a table. It was empty but for one other table which was occupied by one couple. We ordered for lamb which was a huge disappointment. The naan was not different from  chapati. I think there chef has no clue what people expect of Indian food. For us it was a disappointing experience. It is also non-alcoholic so good to know this before you plan to eat there if you like a glass of wine with your dinner. ', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1883, 'mohamed b', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r706284129-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'trip down memory lane', 'This place is ideal for a quick \'dry\' business lunch because of its location. there aren\'t that many indian restaurants on the island. \nThe food is generally ok. We had several items on the menu however the prawn coconut gravy struck me as very good with tandoori naan. Generally the prices are on the higher side. \nThe restaurant is on 2 levels and if you require privacy, it is ideal to make a reservation for the upper level. \nThe place looks dated and definitely needs an update. The host is very charming and service is generally fine. ', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1884, 'Gina M', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r704674238-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Most amazing food and service ', 'This food is so tasty and flavoursome; one of the best Indian meals I have ever had (and we have thousands in the UK!) \n\nThe service was also absolutely amazing. Would definitely recommend as being the best food in town! ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1885, 'TONAMOMBASA', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r704394862-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Real Indian food', 'Excellent  service , food and atmosphere \nA must to try their prawns , corn in coconut as well their fish ... all are delicious', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1886, 'sabreGh', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r701525410-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Pers√∂nlicher Service', 'Wir waren leider etwas zu fr√ºh vor Ort, sind dann etwas \" um den Block \"gelaufen, was in dem Umfeld nicht wirklich Spa√ü macht, und waren dann um 19.00 die zun√§chst einzigen G√§ste, was nicht wirklich sch√∂n ist. Also lieber gegen 8 kommen !!\nUns hat die pers√∂nliche Beratung bez√ºglich des Essens sehr gut gefallen, auch der Service des Wasser-Reichens vor und nach dem Essen.\nDas Essen war gut aber nicht au√üergew√∂hnlich', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(1887, 'Alpesh30', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa, Kenya P.o Box 81676, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r696372728-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Lovely food and very good service.', 'the service here is very good and the food is very nice. one of the best indian restaurants in Mombasa.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1888, 'Claire R', 'Nkrumah Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Blue Room Restaurant - Nkrumah Rd', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d33357030-r1027098277-Blue_Room_Restaurant_Nkrumah_Rd-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Scrumptious avocado on toast.', 'I judge breakfast spots by their coffee and Blue Room delivers every time.Pair it with their avocado on toast and you\'ve got the best breakfast in Mombasa hands down.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\"]'),
(1889, 'hyder n', 'Nkrumah Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Blue Room Restaurant - Nkrumah Rd', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d33357030-r1027094434-Blue_Room_Restaurant_Nkrumah_Rd-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Delicious chicken gyro', 'I tried a chicken gyro for the first time here and it was amazing. The bread was soft, the chicken was juicy and the sauce tied it all together.This is now my top pick for gyros in Mombasa', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1890, 'ELIZABETH K', 'Nkrumah Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Blue Room Restaurant - Nkrumah Rd', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d33357030-r1023383915-Blue_Room_Restaurant_Nkrumah_Rd-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best biryani  in mombasa!!', 'I love trying local favourites when I travel and the biryani here was exceptional. The vegetable version was hearty and full of flavour. It‚Äôs a must-visit if you‚Äôre looking for biryani in Mombasa.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(1891, 'Tarlochan K', 'Nkrumah Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Blue Room Restaurant - Nkrumah Rd', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d33357030-r1022681351-Blue_Room_Restaurant_Nkrumah_Rd-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'On Point!', 'My all time favorite buffalo chicken pita served at Blueroom Nkurumah just hit the spot. This one is a must try. Excellent service by Rashid! I‚Äôll be sure to comeback for the new menu options', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1892, 'Jan-Luca T', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r1035353214-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Highly recommended!', 'Rozina‚Äôs is just like online dating: Don‚Äôt go after the first impression! It might look a little suspicious from the outside (ok, the inside reminds me of a typical german pub of the 80s), but man, that food and the cocktails were GREAT! We had meaty and vegetarian meals - and both were the epitome of taste, freshness, quality and spiciness. All with a fair price.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1893, 'Khadija M. Awadh', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r1004467413-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Rozina restaurant, Ratna square, Nyali', 'We popped in for a casual dinner as a team. Best services, great food I have had in the near past. They easily accommodated our numbers. Finger licking great food. I was definitely impressed. To the great staff - keep up with the good service. I will in shaa Allah be back', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1894, 'Anisha K', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r934573213-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Extremely Dissapointing! Ridiculous Service, High Prices, and Pathetic Food! Please avoid!', 'This is probably the worst restaurant i have been to in Mombasa. The service was pathetic, food took more than an hour and half to come with no explanation whatsoever. The staff was overwhelmed and confused because of the crowd. Some of our orders were messed up. One main course came with the wrong side, and one main course was completely even forgotten. The food was pathetic. The chicken tikka looked stale, and the presentation was very poor. Most importantly the prices are exhorbitant for a barbeque restaurant in Mombasa. The chicken tikka comes with no sides, and salad is actually countable and extremely low in portion, it is shocking to see.  We had to order a plate of salad to compensate.  We gave it a try and this is the worst experience so far.  Never again, you can even compare to other barbeque places and you will get value for money!', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1895, 'Jason K', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r815963669-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best service in Kenya', 'I think Mombasa has the best food in Kenya.  The one thing that can be a but frustrating for a forienger is how slow and unattentive the service is.  These guys are amazing, hands down, not even close, best service of any restaurant ive been to in Kenya.  On par with my expectations of a 5 star restaurant in western europe and the Americas.  ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\"]'),
(1896, 'Shayan R', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r791149782-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Delicious food', 'Food was delicious. I was told by a friend who lived in Mombasa to check out their keema chapati because that is a Mombasa specialty. So delicious. We also had the pepper wings on his recommendation which were delicious. We topped it off with a lamb biryani which was so good. Excellent food that we had.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1897, 'SST1964', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r788394383-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Value for money', 'Eating at Rozina is always a very good experience; excellent service accompanied with good tasty food. Last night (May 9, 2021) we had our Iftaar Dinner at Rozina and we were thrilled to have those scrumptious items (bhajias, pakoras, cutlets, fruit salad, amazing chutneys etc). We then ordered our prawn biryani and man, you better come here more often. Well done, Rozina', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1898, 'Byron78', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r772114542-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Superb', 'Got into Msa late after a 15 hr drive and with limited time before the curfew,drove in here.\nThe service was quick and attentive ,exactly what we needed.The barbeque platter of mixed grilled meats was quite superb,hot,tasty and fresh tasting,the nans were just right.The menu has seafood and other continental food too.\nReturned here with larger groups each time and the service and food was just as superb.Pleasant find indeed.\nGo try ,one will definitely have a great time.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1899, 'CFEIII', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r744984128-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'The place for seafood', 'Got a recommendation from our Tuk Tuk driver for this place, Clean neat, great seafood.  We had lobster and a seafood platter, the lobster was huge, the platter was small,  delicious!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1900, 'EscapadeSeeker', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r736486648-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Awesome sea food', 'We had a tantantalizing sea food platter especially because of the heat of spices that I love. Very warm and attentive staff. I loved that they kept checking on us as we dined. The price is a bit on the higher side than most restaurants providing sea food but probably because of the location.  The manager was particularly pleasant. I know I\'ll be back', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1901, 'edda d', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r729674970-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Lunch with friend', 'I got in before they opened and I was welcomed like I had made a reservation. My waiter was knowledgeable of the menu and answered all my questions on ingredients and made recommendations. \nI had poussin chips and grilled red snapper. Was delicious. Definitely will be back', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1902, 'Arti230', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r727151091-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best Barbecue Restaurant', 'Nothing beats Rozinas clean fresh foods. I ordered paneer tika naan & a glass of passion juice. Very well portioned. The chunks of paneer was well marinated and just melted in the mouth. Tha naan well cooked soft & buttered. The sauces are delicious, each with its unique flavours served with yummy chips.\nService was courteous by polite staff. Best Barbecue Restaurant in Mombasa. A must try!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\"]'),
(1903, 'Rustam Talsam', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r687536804-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'DELICIOUS FOOD ', 'Visit the place with my friends.The food was delicious and the place was ambience and looks good.\n\nThe services was good overall one disadvantage is you have to a bit loaded as the food way expensive.\n\nBut worth it :)', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1904, 'Sam B', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r684343447-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Delicious Samosas', 'We were here for lunch. Driver of our hotel brought us here after we asked for an Indian restaurant.\n\nWe had prawns curry, some rice and samosas. The samosas are small, but delicious. We ordered a second helping of those after tasting them.\n\nWe will be returning back to this restaurant to try more dishes. We loved the food.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(1905, 'Pascalechat', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r681885403-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'le Rozina grill restaurant', 'Il ne faut pas oublier que nous sommes au Kenya  ...;en Afrique !!\nC\'est notre guide Joseph qui nous a emmen√© dans cet √©tablissement pour y dejeuner apr√®s une visite de la ville de Mombasa\nLe restaurant est s√©curis√© par un portail surveill√© par un gardien!!\nL‚Äôaccueil est chaleureux et nous avons √©t√© tr√®s bien accueilli m√™me si nous avons eu un peu de mal a nous faire comprendre car nous parlons peu anglais  \nNous avions tr√®s chaud et le patron de l\'√©tablissement a mis en route les ventilateurs\nNous avons pris des boissons rafra√Æchissantes des bouteilles d\'eau  et des burgers accompagn√© de frites \npour cinq personnes nous avons pay√© une 50 d\'euros  ce qui me semble correct \nl‚Äô√©tablissement est vaste et propre !!\nje recommande cet √©tablissement qui reste tr√®s simple mais convenable !!!et n\'oublions pas nous sommes a Mombasa', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[]'),
(1906, 'Reviews-by-MT', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r673067267-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Good Food Overall ', 'We visited this restaurant with a large group of friends. There were many options for both vegetarians and non-vegetarians . Being a vegetarian, I enjoyed their Pizza, Crispy Bhajias and Paneer. The ambiance is bit dull. The service was good. \n\nThere is a lot of scope for improvements. Wish they brighten it up with modern seating and improve the ambience on the whole.  \n\n', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1907, 'sudref', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r653754532-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Bien manger, endroit propre', 'Une adresse pour manger correctement et sans √™tre malade. En effet au Kenya, il est tr-√®s facile d\'√™tre malade avec la nourriture, ici pas de risque les Europ√©ens y mange tr√®s bien ... Une grande salle climatis√©e, un bon accueil et de l\'attention.\nUn bon repas, simple mais bon. Nous avons appr√©ci√© de trouver un restaurant comme celui l√† o√π nous ne nous sommes pas pos√©s de questions sur la qualit√© de la nourriture.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[]'),
(1908, 'Gabriella C', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r647401789-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'The food is just unreal!! ü§©', 'Absolutely amazing food! Very simple place, nothing fancy, but exactly the spot for you to visit if you want the best seafood in town! On top of it, the service is quick!!! When you visit Kenya, you will know how rare quick places are :) staff were very nice. I ordered the garlic prawns, and literally gonna go back to Mombasa just for that!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1909, 'Anneke412', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r638771411-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Tijdens stadstour een lunch genomen', 'Heerlijke lunch. Soep vooraf was heerlijk. Kip was heerlijk en het vlees met pepersaus was super! Heerlijke koele ruimte. Aardige bediening .', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[]'),
(1910, 'Kamran M', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r616646500-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Quite nice', 'My first visit to Rosina last week and it was quite a please try surprise. Try the akbari kabab with Poussin chips. Absolutely brilliant!!!', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[]'),
(1911, 'Swabra M', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r610771451-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Quick Lunch on City Tour', 'I always walk in Rozina restaurant with my friends while on business tours, and they have never disappointed me despite my lack of prior booking.\nDrinks are excellently cool in this coastal town\'s hot weather, and the waiters amazing.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1912, 'Alex Matimu', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r643248716-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great Meals', 'Conveniently located within the town, the restaurant have great and affordable meals. Have a wide range of Swahili and  Arabic meals. Good place for both eat in and take away. Enjoyed their Shawarma and tamarind juices. Most people use hands though cutlery is provided on request. Early breakfast a big challenge though.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1913, 'shabbirtaherali d', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r638083805-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Breakfast Take away', 'The food is excellent but the breakfast timings are very poor\nIt says it is open from 6.00am but when i went to buy my take away breakfast at 7.00am the waiters were still cleaning the place and told me food not  yet ready\nThe next day the same thing happened \nI was very dissapointed as i need my beakfast by 7.00am to enable me to go to work in time\nIf they dont improve on the timings they will lose customers as i have already decided to look for alternative place for my breakfast', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1914, 'Adel A', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r566114219-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Amazing biryani', 'Love there biryani.\nI like my food worm, but it wasn\'t\nStill loved it, worth the money.\nLocal atmosphere\n', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1915, 'knjenga9', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r560997173-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Place has really changed', 'We all know the food is delicious etc so I‚Äôll come to the pointe right now.\nI didn‚Äôt like the military take by the owner always at the door sassing everyone that leaves. I mean even if people leave with out paying or the employees stealing you don‚Äôt have to make it obvious. We paid for the bill on our way out, the Askari at the door confirmed it was paid and the lady owner nodded to let us pass. I mean what is that????', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"price_value\"]'),
(1916, 'Peter M', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r545185434-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best chicken biryani in Mombasa; great place for a family meal', 'We went to Barka on three separate occasions. Loved the chicken biryani, the various potato options and the \"ndizi za kiume\" (sweet bananas in sauce). Children enjoyed the chips and shawarma. \nLots of locals were in the restaurant on all the occassion; the presence of Mombasa women was, to us, evidence about the authenticity of the food.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1917, 'Gabrielle W', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r528303162-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Phenomenal food', 'The food is remarkable. We shared everything on the menu, but the stand out by far was the chicken biryani. That sauce is to die for!\n\nThe only downside is the fluorescent lights which give the place an overbearing interior.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1918, 'Clarabel S', 'Makadara Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Barka Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12423843-r516331297-Barka_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Take away', 'Unlike many folks who totally speak highly of the place, I beg to differ. Food isn\'t so good and there\'s something off about the restaurant. ', 2, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
