(1923, 'Esteemed Travel', 'Haile Selassie Road Digo Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Blue Room Restaurant - Haile Selassie Rd', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2723620-r877279119-Blue_Room_Restaurant_Haile_Selassie_Rd-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Good milkshake', 'Very clean, nice and ambient setting with a great casual atmosphere. \n\nThe staff are kind and attentive, and will help with local knowledge too.\n\nThe food is great, reasonably priced and the milkshakes are to die for. \n\nParking is a bit of a problem, so Tuk Tuk or driver, or walking is recommended.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
