(1925, 'Nabil A', 'Haile Selassie Road Digo Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Blue Room Restaurant - Haile Selassie Rd', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2723620-r837599713-Blue_Room_Restaurant_Haile_Selassie_Rd-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Terrific food, service and ambience.', 'Went to the Blue Room in Likoni Mall. Frankly it excelled on all accounts - from the quality of the wide ranging dishes (including biryanis, kebabs and burgers) to the responsive and family-accommodating service. Surprised us. Greatly recommend.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1926, 'Sukesha D', 'Haile Selassie Road Digo Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Blue Room Restaurant - Haile Selassie Rd', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2723620-r823187681-Blue_Room_Restaurant_Haile_Selassie_Rd-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Excellent  pit-stop', 'Blue room restaurant ... is an iconic restaurant of mombasa established aeons ago. As kids in the 960\'s we have seen this cafe thrive to this day in  2021 too.\nTheir new branch in Likoni is a modern cafe with subtle ambiance and a great place to pop over for pre or post shipping snack or bite.... also a good place to network with friends.\nWith the medical lab in the vicinity  it\'s an ideal cafe to go for pre and post blood test.\nGood staff and good variety of food for the vegetarian community.\n. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1927, 'Stephanie shantel', 'Haile Selassie Road Digo Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Blue Room Restaurant - Haile Selassie Rd', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2723620-r807431024-Blue_Room_Restaurant_Haile_Selassie_Rd-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Very serene,neat,clean and pocket friendly', 'As a chef I would say this is one of the best restaurants in mombasa, because the food is served neatly,with good service ..I like how friendly the staff are and the kitchen is super clean.i had to take a peak(oops!);)..but all in all I\'d still go here everyday', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1928, 'Steve N', 'Haile Selassie Road Digo Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Blue Room Restaurant - Haile Selassie Rd', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2723620-r790291703-Blue_Room_Restaurant_Haile_Selassie_Rd-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Awesome!!', 'Clean! Very clean!! \nExcellent service! \nDelicious samosas! \nDelicious crispy Bhajia! \nFreshly squeezed, sweet tangerine juice! \nSimply WOW!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
