(1932, 'Gogs', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r865225964-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Definitely worth a visit', 'Joyce the waitress was very attentive. Food was fresh and hot and very good. Healthy portion size so we overordered üòÇ we will return', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1933, 'Avadh K', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r862492182-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Average', 'Very disappointed, Rissoto was overcooked and the carpaccio was bland the ruccola covered the entire plate. No truffle in the truffle rissoto', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1934, 'ssalaah', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r842985850-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Standards have dropped drastically at Roberto‚Äôs', 'I ordered the spaghetti scoglio which was basically supposed to be spaghetti seafood, what was served was a lot of fish unlike what was used to be served, looks like they are cost cutting at the expense of quality, standards have dropped to an extent their pizza crust is hard and unbeatable though the toppings okay. A bad experience.', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1935, 'Shamina J', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r838917610-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Dissappointed', 'I write this review with a very heavy heart. I went to Robertos for dinner yesterday evening 17/5/22 after having had lunch there some time ago. I was with family who were reluctant to go to an italian restaurant but I assured them the food was excellent. So two of us ordered different prawn dishes which were on the menu. Mine were pili pili prawns. These came as a poor amateur cooks version of prawn curry. I was served this with fries!. Very disappointed I requested the very excellent waiter to bring me some bread to eat with the watery curry. He obliged very pleasantly. for that I am thankful. My partner ordered another prawn dish which also came as a watery curry, this time with a sweetish taste. He did not bother to eat it and just ate the Fried potatoes which accompanied the prawns. Mind you he had requested for roast potatoes and he does know the difference between roast and fried potatoes. We had also ordered a Pizza which was ok not brilliant as well as ossobucco which again came as a curry with mixed vegetables! All in all very very disappointing . I think the chef was in a CURRY mood. But nope I will not go to Robertos again.', 2, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1936, 'Cate N', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r827047877-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Alot to be desired. ', 'I asked for a Penny Alfredo. The quantity that was brought to my table was a BIG joke!!!!! For 1450/=!!!!! I had to tell our waiter that it was unacceptable. The plate was taken back and returned with an increased portion. I believe that this shouldn\'t happen. I always remember Roberto\'s fondly and that specific meal. However this time, they have definitely lost a customer. It will be a while before I set foot here again. Their service standard also leaves alot to be desired ', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(1937, 'Lawrence W', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r819130081-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'The Place for Good Food & Conversations', 'This place offer an ideal environment for family or friends to meet for good Italian Cuisine. The open environment gives a nice ambience for relaxed conversations. The staff are friendly and the quality of the food is top notch.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1938, 'Federico', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r814024439-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Valido', 'Ristorante autenticamente italiano, dispone anche di uno shop di prodotto accanto. Il menu\' e\' valido ed il servizio eccellente, ovviamente il tutto ha un costo diciamo in linea con i prezzi dei ristoranti italiani', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"menu_variety\"]'),
(1939, 'Diana O', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r808507961-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'The best Italian pizza in the North Coast!', 'I relocated in Kenya a few month ago and I was looking for a good pizzeria in the Mombasa area. I was told that Roberto\'s could be the right spot. Now I can confirm that the pizza is on a very high level of quality: the crust is crunchy, the tomato sauce genuine,  the topping delicious. I was literally felt I could be eating in Italy during the meal. Make sure you book because it was packed!', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1940, 'Mahira A', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r804396741-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Food Heaven Aug 2021', 'We visited this place twice in a goup 5 (each time) and it was top notch. The ambiance, food and service was excellent. Had the dynamite shrimps, prawns cocktail, pizza and ravioli. All were amazing and ended it al with the Royale Tiramisu. Keep up the great standard and cannot recommend this place enough!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1941, 'Svetlana P', 'Links Road Opposite Premiere Hospital, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Roberto\'s Italian Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d10920334-r799875617-Roberto_s_Italian_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Lunch and Dinner', 'The Best restaurant in town. Good food and owner is very funny and entertaining. Wife is the most of polite woman I ever met. When people called him racist. It\'s not TRUE. Some  Asian would come and order 1 pizza and 1 big coke for 10 people. And he will serve. But, when they asked one of scoop of ice cream and 10 spoons , he\'ll served it too. But , when they asked 10 small plates for the 2 scoops of ice cream... sorry.  He has right to refuse.  I was the witness . \nSo, better to try it yourself .\nBTW, his selection of Deli and wine is incredible. \n\nBono appetite', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(1942, 'John K', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r944542814-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Precious Pizzas', 'Excellent, luscious, scrumptious, perfect, very good and prompt service..  we loved it! Fantastic, we will be back....', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"speed_wait\"]'),
(1943, 'slofty', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r835663214-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Amzing Pizza', 'we had different Pizzas and everyone was very happy on the standard of their Pizza.\nI had a Pizza Fungi, it was like from a other world, to die for... sooo tasty... \n\nAny time for Pizza , great choices', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1944, 'Connector443139', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r805612615-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Poor Service Recovery', 'We have ordered many times and would normally receive exactly what we order. Unfortunately the few times they get the order wrong, they get defensive and refuse to accept that they got the order wrong. What sets good customer service apart from mediocre customer service is how problems are resolved, and they are certainly lacking on that aspect. It always leaves a bitter taste when you are certain of what you ordered yet they claim that you are wrong! \n\nGood pizzas but very poor in handling their mistakes!', 2, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1945, 'Daniel M', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r788759607-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great food, great service', 'The food is great and the service is very friendly. They have a great vegetarian menu and a wonderful outdoor dining experience.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1946, 'Faizaan F', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r781912211-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Service is what makes this place special', 'I have been eating pizza from Milios for a very long time. Their customer service is really what sets them apart. They serve really good pizza but also care about their customers. They value feedback and are always trying to improve. They are a part of our culture and what makes Kizingo special. I am proud to be a Milios customer', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(1947, 'Shouryadripta S', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r781911293-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Enchanting', 'Spectacular varieties.Amazing pizzas. Fast deliveries.Favourable Prices. Is there anything else one needs?', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"speed_wait\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(1948, 'That Dude', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r781901123-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Wow, i love the pizza ', 'Wow, i love the pizza from here. It is always nice and fresh. I normally get the pizza delivered at home but it isn‚Äôt so hot, however when i order it at school, it comes STEAMING it is so good when it is nice and hot. It is also very accessible, they deliver the pizza nicely, the restaurant is in an accessible area and the pizzas are all halal. ', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1949, 'cummingscarolyn', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r768137176-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best pizza in Mombasa', 'This pizza is truly excellent with nice thin crust, just like I prefer.  I liked the steak and mushroom the best, but also enjoyed the chicken and mushroom.  The delivery service was quick and the pizzas were still nice and warm.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1950, 'Lisa', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r745937042-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Super Service', 'Sehr leckere Pizza mit d√ºnnem, knusprigem Boden.\nIch habe die Pizza zum Mitnehmen √ºber Whatsapp bestellt (da ich leider nicht telefonieren kann) und es hat alles wunderbar geklappt! \nIch komme gerne wieder.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(1951, 'ACE1979UK', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r733895798-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Perfect!!!', 'Beautiful pizza and fresh juices all served extremely fast.\nStaff were all very welcoming.\nWill definitely be going back again soon!!!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\"]'),
(1952, 'Sonia Madrid', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r725147092-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Lo mejor de Mombasa', 'Milio es encantador y hace unas pizzas en horno de le√±a que no tienen nada que envidiarle al mejor italiano. Mi √∫nica pega, no tienen cerveza ni caf√©. Milio se ofreci√≥ a llevarnos con su coche a una cafeter√≠a cercana, donde hab√≠a postres y caf√© para llorar de gusto. Mil gracias.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[]'),
(1953, 'CAROL', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r725146759-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'El mejor sitio de Mombasa', 'Creo que es el mejor sitio para comer una pizza, buen√≠simas, el due√±o s√∫per amable y tiene una terraza muy c√≥moda para soportar el calor de la ciudad, lo recomiendo 100%', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(1954, 'The Ricci\'s', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r722611024-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'interesting variations on the pizza theme', 'went there after reading very positive reviews and wasn\'t disappointed. courteous and fast service, nice wood fire pizza, not much in the italian tradition but very interesting nevertheless. surely recommended if you are into spicy an original flavours.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1955, 'Marika de Fijter', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r717998573-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Super lekker', 'Snel, keurige bediening erg lekkere pizzas, gebakken in mooie houtoven. Eigenaar spreekt zeer goed Engels en heerlijke fruitsappen', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[]'),
