(1957, 'Husain J', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r700399213-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best Pizza in Mombasa', 'They most certainly have the best pizza‚Äôs in Mombasa. Most certainly recommend it to anyone craving pizzas! They serve thin crusts which is the best part. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1958, 'Edward Munene', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r690858672-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Amazingly Tasty Pizza', '6 different pizzas, a team of 12 staff and none of the pizza was off or not tasty. We all enjoyed and loved it. Millios Pizza makes real, delicious Italian Pizza.\n\nThe staff were friendly, welcoming and served us with a smile. I will definitely be back.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1959, 'Wanjiku Ndungu', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r690854698-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Welcoming,friendly and accomodating', 'I had a group of 13 people and needed a meal and with one phone call I was quickly sorted. wonderful customer service and great tasting pizzas !', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1960, 'Z23ra', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r682766548-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great pizzas', 'Delicious pizzas! Great addition in Mombasa. They deliver and very good service offered. This is a very welcome restaurant in Mombasa Town. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(1961, 'Munazzam A', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r662183950-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best Pizza In Mombasa', 'The tastiest pizza I have had in Mombasa and keep on going for more. Warm and welcoming. Amazing staff and amazing pizzas!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1962, 'mahmoodkanji', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r603787306-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Couples Dinner', 'Very comfortable and serene environment for couples, family and a group. food is unbeatable and fantastic taste. Keep it Up.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(1963, 'Martin P', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r588742415-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'good place', 'good service, good food (Indian or international).  Not expensive.  Good parking (but restricted on market day but that adds flavour to the experience). Well worth a visit ', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1964, 'vivekrajdev81', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r572662477-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Good roast meat ', 'We normally get take away from here.\n\nWe ordered the chicken Tikka, paneer Tikka some masala fries.\n\nThe delivery was prompt. \n\nFood was excellent \n\nThe pepper sauce is too good make sure you get an extra large tub. ', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"speed_wait\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(1965, 'Zatur', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r570555775-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Excellent Briyani, Chicken Tikka and Chapatti', 'We ordered dinner 2 times from this restaurant. Both nights the meals were amazingly delicious. We have chicken briyani, chapatti stuffed mutton, chicken tikka and margarita pizza. The delivery was fast and all food properly packed and still very warm when it arrived. Price was also good. ', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(1966, 'Uzutin', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r566473141-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Tasty food and friendly service', 'The staff was helpful giving suggestions to us when asked. We ordered paneer tikka and mutton masala with naan breads. Everything was really tasty and the portions were big enough. The food came relatively fast. \n\nAfter all that chewy meat in other restaurants the mutton here was so soft! \n\nPrices were around 1000sh/portion.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(1967, 'Chirag L', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r557305263-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Quality, Quantity & Warm service', 'This historic restruant brand has been in Mombasa for ages and still has that nostalgic feel to it. The food is decently priced, quantity and quality is good. The service is personal and the owners and waiters are attentive enough to needs of diners. I would recommend any of their chips, paneer tikka and egg or paneer chapattis. Its a good place to meet people without being hassled for the table. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1968, 'Moodi', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r551722606-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Cher pour ce que c est', '\nRestaurant qui sert nourriture indienne.\nNous avons √©t√© manger √† midi. Restaurant vide et trop chaud. Nous demandons la climatisation qui nous ait refus√©.\nLe prix des plats est tr√®s cher pour le pays. Les burger ne sont pas servi avec des frites, c est en plus.\nLe tout revient √† un menu ( dans un fast-food  connu) prix suisse.\nBiryani n √©tait pas tr√®s bon au niveau des saveurs. Bof bof le tout', 2, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1969, 'Sukesha D', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r530184818-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'HOME STYLE EATERY', 'Tasty food, something you make at home with a flourish.  Simple seating layout, PATRONS are frequently the ones who are used to the place having specific wants and needs which the chef is aware.  OWNERS are always keen to cater to your personal taste.  GRILLS AND barbeque items are favoured.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1970, 'bwanamdevu', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r527079277-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Nothing exceptional! Average at best.', 'We were taken to Rozina\'s by relatives whilst staying in Mombasa who assured us that it was a very good restaurant. My hopes were high even though everything was pretty unassuming - a very low-key exterior with simple tables inside and a laminated double sided menu to show what was on offer with the list of dishes being extensive! Still, the staff were very welcoming and I was open to be surprised by the standard of fare chosen. Unfortunately it was not exceptional in any way, being very average on the whole.\n\nThe three ladies in our party ordered a large mixed grill to share together with fish fingers which are more like fish kebabs. I ordered the Malaysian chicken whilst the other male in our group had the chicken with garlic sauce. The dishes did not take long at all to appear - never a good sign in my experience - and so we all tucked in. \n\nThe two chicken dishes were remarkably similar in appearance, small pieces of chopped up meat in a heavy sauce. My Malaysian chicken was like nothing that I had eaten in Malaysia earlier in the year with a flavour that was very hard to describe - not unpleasant just unidentifiable! The consistency was also very thick and stodgy, usually a sign of too much thickener being used. The texture of the chicken pieces suggested that they were precooked. The garlic sauce chicken was evidently OK but was also very thick. The mixed grill produced mixed results with the kebabs quite reasonable but the small lamb chop pieces being very overcooked, tough and dry. The fish fingers were surprisingly decent considering the standard of the rest of the food. \n\nOverall decidedly average. Perhaps other items from the menu might produce better tasting dishes but I certainly won\'t be pressing our relatives for a return here!', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(1971, 'JEFFREY P', 'Nyali Road Ratna Square Nyali, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Rozina Nyali', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3574067-r522515080-Rozina_Nyali-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'GOOD  COASTAL MENU', 'This  establishment  provides  quality  authentic  coastal  fare  at  reasonable  prices &  with  excellent  service.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
