(1975, 'musesmailji', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r651069221-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'real pizza after a long time', 'This homely place beats all those high end places in the quality of their pizzas. The crispy based was still soft after it had became cold and you could easily bite.\nGENEROUS use of fresh ingredients. Both our order of the Mushroom and Nyama Choma pizzas were excellent.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1976, 'FerTarran', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r646826451-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Nice ambience and good pizza', 'Good pizza and excellent and fast service. The waiter and the owner were very nice. The tables are disposed in a garden with trees all around. It is a bit away from the city center but we only needed 10-15 minutes to walk there from Fort Jesus. And they still have free WiFi.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1977, 'Mike P', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road, Mombasa 80100 Kenya', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r642220471-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great pizza', 'Best pizza we\'ve eaten in a long time. Great base, fresh toppings, unique flavours, good, swift & personal service. Highly recommended.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
