(1982, 'maureen m', 'Eldoret-Malaba Rd Rupa‚Äôs Mall, Eldoret Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d12981993-r876585093-Java_House-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Sometimes, they don\'t even try', 'Customer care is good but the food, at times they just don\'t even try. Why is the pancake charred? Why not give quality as advertised?', 2, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1983, 'Allan S', 'Eldoret-Malaba Rd Rupa‚Äôs Mall, Eldoret Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d12981993-r831428263-Java_House-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'I love Java House', 'I travel through Eldoret often and when I do, I always stop for a meal at the Java House in Eldoret. It is located on the ground level of the Rupa Mall, which is a great place to go shopping, visit the Safaricom office, or buy groceries.  There is both indoor and outdoor seating and even a play area for kids. Java House is not only a great place to go for coffee, but also for breakfast, lunch, or dinner. The staff are consistently very friendly and it seems I always have to buy a Java House coffee mug or Moka Pot before I leave to give as a gift to someone. ', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(1984, 'Kim DeWitt', 'Eldoret-Malaba Rd Rupa‚Äôs Mall, Eldoret Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d12981993-r776474989-Java_House-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Excellent Service', 'We have eaten at MANY Java Houses in Kenya and this one had excellent service and the food was awesome - the turn around from our order to it in front of us blew all the other Java\'s away.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(1985, 'kingsburgguy', 'Eldoret-Malaba Rd Rupa‚Äôs Mall, Eldoret Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d12981993-r709447034-Java_House-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Craving American food', 'Java House is a great place to get good coffee, food, and use the free WiFi.  The prices are good and the food is plentiful.  Great milkshakes and burgers. The banana nut pancakes are delicious. Service can be slow but I like being able to linger. The Rupa mall is an oasis in Eldoret.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1986, 'Barbara K.', 'Eldoret-Malaba Rd Rupa‚Äôs Mall, Eldoret Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d12981993-r703325875-Java_House-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great for a stop over with family', 'Visited the restaurant for breakfast with my family on a road trip\nThe service and food was ok\nBut the moment to remember is the relaxation the kids had at the play area. It was amazing,well maintained kids play area indoor at Java. The rupas mall, where it\'s located is well stocked too.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1987, 'kingsburgguy', 'Eldoret-Malaba Rd Rupa‚Äôs Mall, Eldoret Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d12981993-r695940331-Java_House-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good food ', 'Java house is nice and spacious with patio dining and a children‚Äôs play area. Food was good and portions are large. Loves the burgers, pork chops and wraps.  The milk shakes are large and delicious. Prices were about $11 per person for lunch.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(1988, 'Byron78', 'Eldoret-Malaba Rd Rupa‚Äôs Mall, Eldoret Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d12981993-r683103960-Java_House-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Java expands to the county', 'Located in the new Rupa mall with a Chandarana,KFC and other stores.Ample secure parking.Can get busy.Pleasant sitting in and out,bright airy atmosphere with privacy a factor as tables are set apart.Decent service and food,hard to fault a new opening.Friendly service.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1989, 'harunani k', 'Eldoret-Malaba Rd Rupa‚Äôs Mall, Eldoret Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d12981993-r675769591-Java_House-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Expensive yet not palatable', 'I had their chiken quarsedillo before finding out it is not halal.i wasnt impresed at all-it was stinking and tasted disgusting.sumthing was stale in that.i love their salted caramel shake.rest of menu is simple,limited quantity and expensive.i still dont understand why thers alot of hype for java.ambience is good though', 2, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(1990, 'nyagoti', 'Eldoret-Malaba Rd Rupa‚Äôs Mall, Eldoret Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d12981993-r657849437-Java_House-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Coffee date', 'Java is the best coffee place in Eldoret. It provides a wide range of beverage. I had caramel macchiato and chicken samosa. The samosa was very dry and not fresh. The next morning I had a stomach upset which was very disappointing. ', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"location_access\"]'),
(1991, 'EKamaara', 'Eldoret-Malaba Rd Rupa‚Äôs Mall, Eldoret Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d12981993-r650012936-Java_House-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'convenient and spacious', 'If you are looking for a convenient place to eat with ample parking and kid\'s play station near your dining place, Java House is the place to be. ', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"location_access\"]'),
(1992, 'Tim F', 'Eldoret-Malaba Rd Rupa‚Äôs Mall, Eldoret Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d12981993-r638874540-Java_House-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Not as good as Nairobi ', 'I visited the Java House in Eldoret twice this month. I was disappointed both times. On my first visit they got my coffee order wrong. It was so busy that I was not able to get it corrected. On my second visit I ordered a cheeseburger that was so over cooked it was crunchy. I wonder if the Java House enterprise is growing faster than management can provide training and quality control. The volume of business is not going to provide any incentive to improve the service or product. \n\nThe Java House at the Nairobi airport is still excellent. ', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
