(2165, 'Ratimo Aduke', 'Safina Plaza, Ronald Ngala St, Eldoret, Kenya', 'Jisty Foods Eldoret, Safina plaza', 'https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUR1eHU2eFB3EAE!2m1!1s0x0:0x736b5dc95ce93598!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgIDuxu6xPw%7CCgsI1-2urAYQ2LKoAQ%7C?hl=en', '', 'This is the hidden affordable foods place in town! Just discovered it through Google Maps. It\'s inside Safina Plaza first floor next to MKU. Been here countless times. Each time I am in town I love passing by this place. The place is so relaxed and hidden away from the busy streets of town. Very minimalist tables and chairs and a relaxed environment. This is not a fine dining place. Just a no frills high quality eatery. You can meet a friend, have a meeting or even just work on your laptop etc. The staff are very relaxed and friendly. You don\'t feel rushed. They have all kinds of food from homey chapati and beans to fast food like chips and chicken.  You wanna try the pilau for only 100Ksh or try the peas and chapati. So well cooked and delicious! If you feeling hungry in town and need a place of peace and quiet head here!', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
