(2238, 'Julia', 'Tom Mboya Road Milimani, Kisumu Kenya', 'Ujima Food Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d27165327-r938063051-Ujima_Food_Garden-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Delicious food and a beautiful garden', 'I discovered the restaurant by chance when I was looking for a place for lunch in Milimani. I was surprised by the serenity of the place. There is a daily menu with an excellent selection of dishes, including vegetarian options. I had a delicious Indian vegetable curry with chapati. I was told that the restaurant also serves as a training facility for disadvantaged young people, which I think is wonderful.\nI can definitely recommend this place.', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(2239, 'james n', 'Tom Mboya Road Milimani, Kisumu Kenya', 'Ujima Food Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d27165327-r937019431-Ujima_Food_Garden-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'True definition of fine dinning.', 'Awesome ambience, true spirit of how good food should look in a plate, We had butternut soup for a starter and it was heavenly, the chicken with sesame seed was my choice, the plate was just colorful a true testimony of heathy clean food. The service was perfect knowing its from the foundation beneficiaries. What a better way to support an organization doing impactful programs to change the lives of the society than dinning with them.\n\nIts defiantly a place to be for meals and drinks if you are looking to unwind your day with peace, good food, a good cup of coffee or a glass of wine while in Kisumu.\n\nThis defiantly needs another come back.', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(2240, 'Monika K', 'Tom Mboya Road Milimani, Kisumu Kenya', 'Ujima Food Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d27165327-r937015309-Ujima_Food_Garden-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Beautiful restaurant, excellent food', 'A unique restaurant: A lovingly designed garden restaurant. Excellent food, beautifully presented and very friendly staff. The fact that it is a training venue for Ujima foundation also makes you feel good.  A real highlight in Kisumu!', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(2241, 'Anke', 'Tom Mboya Road Milimani, Kisumu Kenya', 'Ujima Food Garden', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d27165327-r936970731-Ujima_Food_Garden-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Excellent Food in a nice garden restaurant', 'We went there for a business lunch and had very good food. We ordered tilapia fillet in coconut sauce and vegetarian quesadillas. Both dishes were very tasty and nicely decorated. The service was warm and welcoming and we loved the peaceful atmosphere in the garden. It¬¥s an ideal place for a business meeting or for work and should be fine for families as well. Wifi was good and music not too loud. The place was opening only one week ago. We learned that it is a training restaurant for hospitality students. We will definitely come back.', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(2242, 'Leticia L', 'Achieng\' Oneko Rd, Kisumu 00505 Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d14009169-r1004616952-Java_House-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Nice, but can be better.', 'The place is nice, with a wide range of options. Service is more on the slow range, but waiters are polite. An air conditioner would also come in handy.', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\"]'),
(2243, 'Henk v', 'Achieng\' Oneko Rd, Kisumu 00505 Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d14009169-r924181711-Java_House-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', '\'Coffeehouse\',  Can be better!', 'Java is a nice place. Both the branch in Kisumu West Mall as the one in United Mall provide good food and nice services. But there is one complaint that I need to make. The coffee is terrible. Whether you ask for an Americana or a Macchiato, you will always get an instant coffee. Instant coffee with too much powder. When you ask about it, the gentle  waiters will first deny, then admit and then they bring some real coffee, but then it will take ages. It is obviously not a habit to make real coffee. What a shame for a company that likes to portrays itself as the ‚Äúcoffeehouse‚Äù. Please, you can do better!', 3, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(2244, 'wayne d', 'Achieng\' Oneko Rd, Kisumu 00505 Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d14009169-r882381789-Java_House-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Java House, a staple of food and coffee while in Kenya.', 'Everyone that has been to Kenya, knows about Java House. Not only do they have fantastic coffee, Kenya AA, Espresso, Yirgacheffe, and Rwandan coffee available either ground or whole bean, their food is great.\nI would recommend the California garden salad with spicy chicken and avocado. As a side dish the fruit salad with yogurt, honey and almonds is exquisite! These are my 2 plates that I order nearly every time I visit a Java House.\nIf you order 2 bags of coffee with your meal, you get a free cup of fresh coffee to go! Just one more reason to visit them.\nThe Java House that is in the mall attached to the Acacia hotel is my favorite, but there a  few of them in Kisumu, as well as Nairobi.', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(2245, 'K. O', 'Achieng\' Oneko Rd, Kisumu 00505 Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d14009169-r748096339-Java_House-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Good service ', 'Very good service and good food can\'t complain. My daughter dropped her fork but we didn\'t expect to get a new set but we got a pleasant surprise. The second it happend She got a new set. ', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(2246, 'Mary', 'Achieng\' Oneko Rd, Kisumu 00505 Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d14009169-r736114961-Java_House-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Food and ice cream.', 'While in Kenya, we ate there twice.  The ice cream was to die for.  We were a team of 10 on a medical mission and one of the participants kept wanting to return.', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(2247, 'Toto Joy :-)', 'Achieng\' Oneko Rd, Kisumu 00505 Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d14009169-r691303806-Java_House-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Best Cafe in Kisumu, great for meetings', 'Always a sanctuary space when the business of Kisumu gets up your head. Excellent service and great food in a calm space. Totally recommended', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(2248, 'Bunnio', 'Achieng\' Oneko Rd, Kisumu 00505 Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d14009169-r675947365-Java_House-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Helpful staff.', ' Offered to reheat coffee! Also offered to delay food while one of the group popped out to a nearby shop.', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\"]'),
(2249, 'Paul C', 'Achieng\' Oneko Rd, Kisumu 00505 Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d14009169-r648187691-Java_House-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Good location, very good food and service', 'Java house is very well located in the shopping mall with a fair amount of seating. \n\nThe selection of food and drink is very good and reasonably priced and was of a good quality.\n\nWe had steaks, grilled chicken and a burger, they were all prepared exactly as we had requested and were very tasty with good portion sizes.\n\nThe service was quick and efficient.\n\nWe will definitely visit again.', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(2250, 'Stephen Ouma', 'Achieng\' Oneko Rd, Kisumu 00505 Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d14009169-r637253209-Java_House-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Good place for coffee and business meetups', 'Java is a good place for business and coffee meet ups. It is also located next to Acacia Premier Hotel which is also a convinient amd prestigious hotel in Kisumu', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"location_access\"]'),
(2251, 'Annelot T', 'Achieng\' Oneko Rd, Kisumu 00505 Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d14009169-r618830285-Java_House-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Warme sinaasappelsap? Gekke gewoontes:maar prima plek', 'OK. Als je rondreist in Kenia vraagt de bediening bij alle soda\'s: \"warm or cold\". Ook bij het bestellen van een sinaasappelsap in Java House werd deze vraag gesteld. Normaal betekend warm \"niet gekoeld in de koelkast\". Toen ik mijn sinaasappelsap \'warm\' bestelde kreeg ik opgewarmde sinaasappelsap. Ik was er erg van in de war en vind het ook niet aan te raden :-)\nOok was er toen wij er waren een promotie. Bestel 1 hamburger, krijg er 2 Maar dat wordt niet vooraf gezegd. Zit je daar ineens met super veel eten. Erg raar. Maar het wordt keurig ingepakt om mee naar huis te nemen (ookal komt dat niet goed uit als je op reis bent :-))\n\nDe smaak van het eten en drinken is erg goed! ', 3, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(2252, 'Sylvester G', 'Achieng\' Oneko Rd, Kisumu 00505 Kenya', 'Java House', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d14009169-r606563132-Java_House-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Great Breakfast', 'I had breakfast at Java House at Westend Mall Kisumu. The place is small but very cosy. The staff are very courteous and efficient.\nThe breakfast was great and more so the coffee amazing.', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
