(2499, 'Harry G', 'Oginga Odinga Avenue, Nakuru 20100 Kenya', 'Taidy\'s', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d8012578-r786359145-Taidy_s-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'A pleasant surprise.', 'I had a brief lunch meeting, this venue was chosen by my contact and not me, I have to say that I was pleasantly surprised. Observing all covid counter measures and restrictions, we were sanitised and had our temperatures taken then shown to our table, the place was clean and well laid out. Our waiter, (Kevin) was a very polite and well mannered young man. Our lunch arrived in good time and was delicious. The prices are fair and i will certainly be viditing again.', 5, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
