(2501, 'Gerald', 'Oginga Odinga Avenue, Nakuru 20100 Kenya', 'Taidy\'s', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d8012578-r752218389-Taidy_s-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good customer service. Have your chicken at peace.', 'Found myself at the sports bar as I was waiting for my meal.\nThe interior decor\' is on top, good ambience. Cool smooth music, not full blast. Good customer service: fast, waiter take their time to take you through the menu. \nThere is a restaurant (ground floor) where you can relax with a friend/Family and a sports bar on 1st floor where you can hang out with friends and have conversation especially on weekdays, listen to cool music or play pool.', 5, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
