(2509, 'Tony C', 'Oginga Odinga Avenue, Nakuru 20100 Kenya', 'Taidy\'s', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d8012578-r679054475-Taidy_s-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Nakuru has officially joined the list of cool towns in Kenya', 'Nakuru has always had its fair share of visitors to the National Park, it‚Äôs served by many ‚Äúok‚Äù hotels, some even claiming 5stars (but just their own opinion).\nFinally Nakuru town has a truly stylish and cool hotel; the exterior styling has had tongues wagging for quite sometime, and it‚Äôs soft opening this week did not disappoint. Cafe, restaurant, sports bar and terrace grace the lower floors; stylish rooms with large flat screen smart TV‚Äôs, sumptuous furnishings and cool palette grace the middle floors. The rooftop is left for the swimming pool, complete with glass panels to see all the way down to the terrace on the ground floor; there is also a rooftop bar with seating and the spectacular vista of the National Park. Taidys Suites coolly places Nakuru on the style map of Kenya.', 5, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"events_entertainment\"]'),
