(2713, 'ginabA3889OI', 'Oginga Odinga Ave, Nakuru, Kenya', 'Eagle Palace Hotel, Nakuru', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d7706079-r1033933426?m=68573&staydates=2025_11_23_2025_11_24&uguests=1_2_0&supdv=desktop&supuc=US&supul=en', '', 'The rooms are good, breakfast is awesome with various options and staff are friendly. Overall good experience and I would visit again.', 0, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(2714, 'Caroline V', 'Oginga Odinga Ave, Nakuru, Kenya', 'Eagle Palace Hotel, Nakuru', 'https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WRlowSkJUMVpVZEVwVlpGRTFVVXRVWkVvNVUzYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x1ad054387b9aefa2!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmVFZ0JBT1ZUdEpVZFE1UUtUZEo5U3c%7C0ctVjTLpi2K%7C?hl=en', '', 'We stayed at this hotel during our third day of safari, as it\'s very well located, just minutes from Lake Nakuru. It\'s a comfortable and well-maintained hotel, ideal for resting after a long day of hiking.\nThe rooms are spacious and clean, with comfortable beds and a large, modern bathroom. The staff was very friendly and helpful, always ready to help with a smile, which made the stay even more welcoming and enjoyable.\nBreakfast was very good, with a variety of local and international options: fresh fruit, eggs made to order, bread, cereal, and juices. Everything was well presented, and the service was prompt and attentive.\nAt times, the Wi-Fi can be a bit unstable, and depending on the room, you can hear some noise from the street or nearby establishments, but it\'s nothing bothersome. There\'s a bar/club on the corner, although the noise wasn\'t loud and stopped before 11:00 PM, so we were able to rest well.\nOverall, a very good option in Nakuru, with excellent service, a good location, and spacious rooms. Perfect for those stopping off on safari or visiting Lake Nakuru National Park', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-09 12:44:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
