(2887, 'VampyreNectar', 'Langata Rd', 'The Carnivore Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d809397-r1037574606-The_Carnivore_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'The name of this restaurant says it all', 'This restaurant is not for people whom don‚Äôt enjoy adventure in their meals!! I think I had every type of legal meat there was to have in Kenya. I would advise you to paste yourself, as they stuff you before you even get to the main course. The service is impeccable. Everyone is super friendly. My server, Rodgers, was extremely attentive and explained everything at least twice to me because it was too much to take in all at once lol. \n\nIf you are in Kenya, this is a stop you have to make there is indoor dining and outdoor dining and the place is absolutely beautiful. This was a perfect last dining experience after my nine days safari experience.\n\nThank you again Carnivore for going above and beyond beyond!!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-10 18:49:11', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
