(2919, 'Gem E', 'Langata Rd', 'The Carnivore Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d809397-r1036151384-The_Carnivore_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Disappointing Experience at The Carnivore', 'I was really looking forward to my visit to The Carnivore, but unfortunately, it fell short of expectations. While the atmosphere was lively and enjoyable, the meat quality was underwhelming and not as impressive as I had hoped.\n\nWhat surprised me most was the ‚Äúwelcome drink‚Äù offered on arrival ‚Äî it seemed complimentary, but we later discovered it was chargeable at $9 each, which felt like a hidden cost. A small thing, but it left a sour note at the end of the meal.\n\nOverall, it was an average experience that didn‚Äôt quite live up to the hype. Good ambience, but be aware of extra charges that aren‚Äôt made clear upfront.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-10 18:49:11', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
