(2922, 'Leah M', 'Limuru Rd Village Market, Opposite NCBA', 'BangBang Thai Kitchen', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26792367-r1036870831-BangBang_Thai_Kitchen-Nairobi.html', 'Amazing BangBang', 'We were welcomed with great smile by the hostess,(forgort her name with glasses)shown options of places to seat as it was an easy afternoon and we chose the outside cz of the ambiance. Our server was Cephas who guided us through the menu.We ordered the tom yam soup ,Devil sen khao ,Lamb curry and had to force a space for the mango and sticky rice dessert ,food portion\'s were alooot,but flavourful.Cocktails were slapping as well 10/10 experience.We were also taken thorough the story of BangBang himself,by the manager ,Jackson when he came to check on us,fascinating.We will be back', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-10 18:53:43', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
