(2939, 'Jerono O', 'Limuru Rd Village Market, Opposite NCBA', 'BangBang Thai Kitchen', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26792367-r1032202929-BangBang_Thai_Kitchen-Nairobi.html', 'Superb Menu, Exceptional Care', 'The menu was superb, and I especially enjoyed the story of Bangbang...he seemed to have lived five lives in one. The food was flavorful and delicious, and Susan took such great care of us that I almost forgot where I was. The service was excellent, and the dessert was unforgettable, the cheesecake was absolutely divine. A solid 10/10 experience. Don‚Äôt leave without trying the tamarind juice! \n\nSusan also gave us blankies when the rain started pouring - right at home here', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-10 18:53:43', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
