(2941, 'Mercy O', 'Limuru Rd Village Market, Opposite NCBA', 'BangBang Thai Kitchen', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26792367-r1032023835-BangBang_Thai_Kitchen-Nairobi.html', 'Consistency at its best!', 'I have be coming to BANG BANG for several months and I would say some few Reviews \nFirst is the quality of service from Cephas, he has been an amazing server since 2023, the chef Milan has been giving us the best dishes so far. \nThe wait time since the first time has been reliable and taken well care. \nI have been recommending to my friends and they love the place. \n\nShout out to the Manager Eric and Jackson for the well organized Team work \n\nBANG BANG has a special place in my heart.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-10 18:53:43', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(2942, 'Amon K', 'Limuru Rd Village Market, Opposite NCBA', 'BangBang Thai Kitchen', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26792367-r1031811376-BangBang_Thai_Kitchen-Nairobi.html', 'Birthday celebration', 'It was my wife\'s birthday and couldn\'t think of anywhere else to take her but Bang Bang. They didn\'t disappoint us - Anthony Karanja went extra mile in serving us. Had two little ones and he made our experience unforgettable - he planned and surprised my wife with a lovely cheese cake and joyful songs.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-10 18:53:43', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
