(2971, 'Alfred O', 'Peponi Road Kwetu Nairobi, Curio Collection by Hilton', 'Upepo', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27497618-r1038488454-Upepo-Nairobi.html', 'AMAZING DINNER', 'I had an amazing dinner experience at Upepo !! The food was absolutely delicious ,full of rich flavours and beautifully presented,shout out to Chef Ashley,Ian and Benson. The atmosphere was cozy and relaxing, perfect for an evening out.\nA special shout out to Trevor for serving me with such friendliness and professionalism. He made great recommendations and made sure everything was perfect through out my meal. His warm personality really added to the experience .\nHighly recommend this place .', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-10 18:58:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(2972, 'Tru?', 'Peponi Road Kwetu Nairobi, Curio Collection by Hilton', 'Upepo', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27497618-r1015757803-Upepo-Nairobi.html', 'Upepo Mtamu', 'Lovely spot with the warmest chic interiors and vibe I‚Äôve experienced in a while. Love the food curation (literally presented as art) - I‚Äôd advise as a group of friends to get a number of the platters so you can have a bit of everything. THE BEST MARGARITA (yet ü§≠) in Nairobi.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-10 18:58:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
