(2974, 'FuriusStyles', 'Peponi Road Kwetu Nairobi, Curio Collection by Hilton', 'Upepo', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27497618-r1037481816-Upepo-Nairobi.html', 'Absolutely Perfect Evening at Upepo', 'We were staying at Kwetu Nairobi and decided to have dinner at Upepo ‚Äî and it turned out to be one of the highlights of our trip. We brought our two boys along, and the team was so welcoming and accommodating, which made the evening even more special.\n\nThe atmosphere was warm and elegant, with a great breeze and beautiful lighting that made it feel both relaxed and refined. We ordered the chicken satay, nasi goreng, salmon, and the Upepo dessert platter ‚Äî every dish was perfectly prepared and full of flavor.\n\nThe service was excellent throughout, attentive but never overbearing. It‚Äôs rare to find a restaurant that balances sophistication with genuine hospitality and family-friendliness this well. We‚Äôll definitely be coming back the next time we‚Äôre in Nairobi.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-10 18:58:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
