(2976, 'Scott B', 'Peponi Road Kwetu Nairobi, Curio Collection by Hilton', 'Upepo', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27497618-r1037138505-Upepo-Nairobi.html', 'Our five star experience at Upepo', 'We are a family of four, Upepo made an allowance for us to dine with them as there was an event in the restaurant downstairs so we are unable to go there. Usually Upepo is adults only. So we was particularly grateful for their exception. Kevin was our waiter and he was absolutely amazing. He gave us great recommendations for food and drinks, he was extremely helpful and hospitable to all of our needs. He made a great experience that much better! Thank you to Kevin and all the staff at Upepo!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-10 18:58:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
