(3255, 'Armand', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r692251466-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Amazing', 'The food is amazing, very delicious....The service is the best, warm welcome from the owner. \nThe hospitality is on top...and the food does take long to come.\nIt is affordable and located right in the city center in Mombasa and there is a good ambiance.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:28:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(3256, 'yachtmasterjohn', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r689538346-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'No alcohol ', 'I just arrived in the city after 12 hours traveling and found my way to this restaurant guided by the great reviews. \n\nI‚Äôm giving it a great review because it looks excellent and the previous reviews are excellent. \n\nBut I think restaurants should make it very clear whether they do or don‚Äôt serve alcohol. This one doesn‚Äôt. \n\nI like a beer at the end of a long day and a glass of wine with my dinner. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:28:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3257, 'Jimmykinsx2050', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r687524447-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Pleasantly surprised by this gem of a restaurant', 'Located downtown Mombasa, i had read a few reviews of Shehnai restaurant in Mombasa.Was happy i popped in,the service was perfect and the food was excellent.\nIt is the best Indian restaurant i have ever sampled in terms of food quality in Mombasa.\nThe owner was equally friendly as well checking on me if all was ok.\nKudos!', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:28:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3258, 'Said T', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r665928509-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best Indian food in mombasa', 'Amazing taste of the food ,finger licking . Fresh and exellent service. \n\nThe manager /director exceptional service by him \n\nTreats all like royalties .\n\nThe Tulsa.  ,birianis . Kulfi ,tandoori nun etc .well prepared and presentable. 5√ó√ó√ó service', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:28:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(3259, 'VIRENDRANAGORI', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r659536342-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Authentic Mughalai Cuisine', 'in the heart of Mombasa Island, one of the oldest restaurant and still going strong due to its unmatched standards.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:28:15', 'positive', '[]'),
(3260, 'Olivier M', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r654217973-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Way too spicy and really overpriced', 'I went to Shehnai last night driven by all the really good reviews I read. It seemed like a very expensive place (especially by Kenyan standards, since prices exclude all taxes so you need to add an additional 30%) but I love Indian food and went there for a treat. \nI ordered a butter chicken, sheek kebab, rice, water and a chocolate milkshake. I paid 2950 shillings ($30) for it. \nWhen asked I answered that I wanted my food medium spiced (I was offered 3 choices mild / medium spicy / spicy).\nBefore I got my food the owners checked on me twice which was nice. They did not come back once I had been served. \nWhen the food arrived it was not possible for me to eat the kebab as it was way too spicy and I love spicy food but this way beyond nice. Butter chicken was ok but still way too hot. \nI had to leave most of the meat and ate only the rice. My waiter asked me why, I told him it was way to hot and that only prompted a laugh from him. \nWhen I left mist of my food the owner didn\'t come to check what had happened yet by this time I was the sole customer left in the restaurant (there was only another family when I arrived). \nAnd it was really expensive compared to other restaurants (the rice itself once included the taxes was over $5).\nI regretted eating there and felt that this restaurant did not live up at all to its reviews.  ', 2, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:28:15', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3261, 'Mayur N', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r651959088-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Lovely ambiance', 'Despite having visited Mombasa on several occasions this was the first time we went to Shehnai for lunch. I was amazed by the entire set up. There were Indian musical instruments put up on the walls and the colour themes were goods. \n\nThe owner Mr Mehboob will always make sure he visits all the tables to ensure the client is fully satisfied with the food and service.\n\nWe had a curry with Nan the taste was okay but the presentation, Service and ambiance made the moment.\n\nOverall a nice place and worth visiting', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:28:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3262, 'Omatilla', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r633470591-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Gastvrij', 'Altijd weer een hoogtepunt wanneer we in Mombasa zijn.\nHeerlijk eten en erg gastvrij. Hier weten ze nog wat service is je voelt je als gast echt speciaal', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:28:15', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(3263, 'Salim K', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r628334489-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'WOW is the right word for Shehnai Restaurant', 'Great Customer service, great people, tastey food..lods of choicesto choose from..I will come by again and again and again and again..Keep feeding us and Thank you!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:28:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(3264, 'Aditya B', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r626830406-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Seafarer\'s review ', 'Guys if you are looking for some indian cuisine option in mombasa then Shahnai us a must go place!!!', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:28:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3265, 'Alex B', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r622756943-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great Indian dinner in Mombasa', 'All the meals that I‚Äôve taken - paneer as a starter, dal and prawns curry - were much tasty and delicious. \nI will definitely come to study its menu in more details. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:28:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3266, 'Michael G', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r612900058-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Lunchtime visit', 'I was in the mood for Indian cuisine in Mombasa and Shehnai was recommended to me by locals.\nThe poppadum to start was delicious and soft!\nI had the paneer starter, peppered chicken with butter naan, and kulfi for dessert. All excellent.\nTo cap it all off the service was some of the best I have had in a while.\nRecommended \n\n', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:28:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3267, 'Umnada', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r609954516-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Worth a visit', 'We were a big group and was well received. The place is a little dark and gloomy, the decor very poorly done .\nFood was nice and spicy but cold when dishes should have been served hot.\nWaiters very knowledgeable and helpful.\n ', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:28:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]');
