(3270, 'Hannah M', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r593911438-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Amazing service', 'I went there with my dad for dinner and we really enjoyed our time. The service is amazing. The food is wonderful and the ambience is just great. If you have a birthday, they have this amazing tradition where the waiters bring the cake while singing and drumming. Brilliant!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:28:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(3271, 'tjthefoodie', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r584705004-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Hidden gem in Mombasa town', 'I\'ve been to this restaurant countless times both for business and personally and its always a great experience! The owners are very involved and really make the effort to make the meal as pleasurable as possible. The staff are very friendly and well trained- super efficient and attentive. \nAs for the food itself- authentic and excellent- consistently. The portion sizes are generous so groups are better ;) They also cater to children well.\nI absolutely love this place and would say its a must do while in Mombasa :)', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:28:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3272, 'Joanne N', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r580887085-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Birthday dinner', 'We enjoyed every moment of it. Great service.The Food was awesome . Everything was just perfect üëå üëå', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:28:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(3273, 'Mohammed Hersi', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r577557262-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great As Always', 'Felt like having a nice indian meal with my brother and niece and I found myself at my usual Mombasa place Shenai. Sad thing is that the founder Zul Haruani passed on a few months ago and we truly miss him. His able nephew Mehboob was at hand with his team who gave us the special Shehnai feel that we have been accustomed to over the years. For those of you who are worried rest assured that late Zuly ( May Allah Grant Him Jannatul Firdous left behind a very able dedicated team.\n\nLooking forward forward to our next visit and dont forget to try their special home made passion juice, Prawns Tikka and of course the mutton Biriani', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:28:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3274, 'KLM1914', 'Nyerere Road, Mombasa', 'Shehnai Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d2002413-r573768343-Shehnai_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great group lunch', 'Excellent lunch.  Out tour group Asaray arranged lunch here for our group of 8.  It was amazing.  Some of the best Indian food I\'ve ever had.  Would definitely recommend and would go back.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:28:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3275, 'Miles M', 'Danka Plaza Links Road Nyali Next to Odds & Ends', 'Cool Beans Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d25944019-r1038455642-Cool_Beans_Cafe-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great food, drinks and service!', 'Really enjoyed Cool Beans. At first thought it was just a coffee shop, but it is much more. We ordered wings and drinks that were amazing. Especially the BBQ wings and strawberry daiquiris. Our server Nancy was very kind and friendly. Would definitely visit again.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:35:19', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\"]'),
