(3457, 'JetSky88', 'Malindi Road', 'Yul\'s Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d911572-r873347958-Yul_s_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Excellent ambience, good drinks and food. What else would we need?', 'This was our best dining experience in Mombasa, if not Kenya to date. We loved the ambience of this place, busy but not overly so. Our waiter was excellent and he was so charming and helpful. Big thumbs up for the service and the food preparation time. Everyone loved the food they ordered, the chicken tikka was juicy, tender and succulent. The salads were delicious. The desserts were yammi. Definitely we will visit again.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:48:02', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3458, 'Jenna M', 'Malindi Road', 'Yul\'s Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d911572-r870502788-Yul_s_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Blatant racism', 'Went with a friend and we notice a table that\'s just being vacated. We ask the staff to sit there since there\'s a shade and this woman tells us that the table is reserved and shows us to another table that didn\'t have a shade. Barely three minutes later, some Arab women show up and they are told to sit wherever they want, including the table that they just told us was reserved. They sit and are given the menu. Later the staff come to us to give the menu, which she had conveniently forgotten to give us before she served the Arabs. We ask her why she treated us that way and she replies, \"you know how Arabs are.\" Dumb internalised racism! Never visit if you\'re Black.', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:48:02', 'negative', '[\"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3459, 'Prudence', 'Malindi Road', 'Yul\'s Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d911572-r869688410-Yul_s_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best experience', 'I visited the restaurant on a thursday 24th nov and i was received warmly. My entire service was done by Veronica (trainee). She was amazing. She advised on the meal to take which was really tasty. The place is beautiful and its a nice place to chill and relax. Looking forward to visit again soon.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:48:02', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3460, 'Anna w', 'Malindi Road', 'Yul\'s Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d911572-r868211132-Yul_s_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Besuch bei Juls', 'Wir waren gestern mite der Familie da, 6 Personen. Wir wollten mal das gut bewertetes Eis probieren. Es war noch besser, wir waren alle total begeistert. Mein Schwiegervater hatte das M√°laga Eis bestellt. Die eingetr√§nkte Rosinen in Rum waren der Hammer. Die Becher mit Obst und Eis waren riesig. Anbei ein paar Bilder.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:48:02', 'positive', '[]'),
(3461, 'Mario Ap', 'Malindi Road', 'Yul\'s Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d911572-r865917226-Yul_s_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', '3 veces en 3 d√≠as', 'Muy buen restaurante en la orilla de Bamburi Beach en Mombasa. Fuimos 3 veces y en todas muy contentos. Personal muy agradable, muchas mesas pero espacioso, m√∫sica chill out de fondo. El primer d√≠a nos tomamos una pizza y unas gambitas rebozadas, por la noche tomamos unos solomillos de ternera con salsa de pimienta y pur√© de patata muy bueno. Lo acompa√±amos con vino Purebred de sud√°frica y fue un agradable acierto. Los lunes cierran el restaurante por descanso del personal. A los dos d√≠as volvimos a comer ya que los precioso de otros restaurantes de la zona son desorbitados, y nos comimos una langosta con salsa de queso y champi√±ones y un pescado (red snapper) con salsa de tomate y coco. Los apperol de aperitivo muy ricos. Buen√≠sima relaci√≥n calidad precio en Mombasa.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:48:02', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(3462, 'knad_11', 'Malindi Road', 'Yul\'s Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d911572-r864758701-Yul_s_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Used to be Good!', 'A nice view of the beach however food is not up to par very cold food being served and the rates are quite high. \n\nStaff were friendly and very fast with serving however they need to add more employees as it may take a while after you place an order for any further assistance. \n\nNeed to add PDQ/Credit/Debit card machines its 2022 everyone uses plastic money for payments no one walks around with cash only WEIRD place that still accepts cash only. \n\nRoom for improvement by the mangement.', 2, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:48:02', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
