(3464, 'hitendra g', 'Malindi Road', 'Yul\'s Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d911572-r837345021-Yul_s_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Family lunch', 'Yuls is the best place for all the veggie food options be it lunch or dinner. Extremely warm welcome on arrival , most courteous members of the team to serve you, wide range of veg fast foods and snacks .  Very well presented, very tasty veg foods and the whole place was jus packed out. That shows how popular and the people love Yuls for their foods on offer. Nice venue right next to the beach.\n\nHighly recommend Yuls when in bamburi beach area. You won‚Äôt regret it. \n\nMy whole family just can‚Äôt stop talking about Yuls and the veggie foods they served us. \n\nTry it out , it‚Äôs an amazing experience. Hats off to the whole team who run the show at Yuls. \n\nThank you all at Yuls.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-10 19:48:02', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
