(3474, 'Victoria', 'Club Road Gilanis Supermarket Building', 'Gilani\'s', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d8012579-r767843936-Gilani_s-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'They are practicing social distancing', 'My first experience was pleasant. Their were only 4 families inside dining,remind you it\'s very spacious. The food was fresh and good. I ordered chicken sandwich\"nice portion of meat\" of course french fries and vanilla shake were all good.I sat a little to squeeze room in for dessert they only had 1 kind of cake. I just wish they had brownies with ice cream,fresh baked cookies,1cheesecake or something. The atmosphere is quiet,very relaxed they had the tv on the news,not to loud not to low. Perfect place to eat in privacy', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:52:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
