(3477, 'Rakhi M', 'Club Road Gilanis Supermarket Building', 'Gilani\'s', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d8012579-r731014412-Gilani_s-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'enjoyed every dish we ordered', 'we did a jumia food order & enjoyed every dish we had ordered. the chicken biryani, noodles, pizza were all very tasty. if i am in nakuru i will definitely eat here again.', 5, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:52:51', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(3478, 'Omar B', 'Club Road Gilanis Supermarket Building', 'Gilani\'s', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d8012579-r720797445-Gilani_s-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'If you want Indian Cuisine in Nakuru, this is the place.', 'It\'s located in the centre of Nakuru Town, being part of an old family establishment, ubiquitous in that part of town.\nIt has an old-style interior decor. \n\nThe service was satisfactory, took the servers about 5 minutes to attend to us. The waiting time was about 15-20 minutes for our orders. \nThe food was quite spicy and tasty at the same time, and I definitely needed a cool drink, to down it, but hey! That\'s part of the appeal.\n\n To sum it up, if you\'re looking for a great taste of Indian food, this is the place.\n\n', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:52:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3479, 'Prinal Shah', 'Club Road Gilanis Supermarket Building', 'Gilani\'s', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d8012579-r715731430-Gilani_s-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Tasty food ', 'The food at Gilanis has picked up a notch. Having been there a number of times now in the past few months. I have been impressed with the taste of Indian food and it‚Äôs consistency. A slight aspect to work on is the speed of delivery, otherwise great job. ', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:52:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"speed_wait\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(3480, 'yachtmasterjohn', 'Club Road Gilanis Supermarket Building', 'Gilani\'s', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d8012579-r697508358-Gilani_s-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Excellent Indian food ', 'Most of the really good food in Kenya is Indian. This place is is highly rated because it‚Äôs serving excellent Indian dishes with good service. If I lived here this would be one of my regulars. ', 5, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:52:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3481, 'Dinesh S', 'Club Road Gilanis Supermarket Building', 'Gilani\'s', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d8012579-r670052459-Gilani_s-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Interesting new bar \"The Penalty Box\"', 'After renovations, the place seems to be much better. Food quality is also good.\nChris a long serving waiter seems well versed with what\'s on the menu and the specialities of the house. A pocket friendly place.', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:52:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3482, 'RealMissDee', 'Club Road Gilanis Supermarket Building', 'Gilani\'s', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d8012579-r657725883-Gilani_s-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Love butter chicken? Go to Gilanis. ', 'We last went to Gilani‚Äôs a year ago and at the time did not try their butter chicken until recently. \n\nAs a person who loves Indian food and has therefore tried lots of butter chicken from various restaurants- the one from Gilanis is the best I have tried. It is rich with complex flavours. Recommend having it with their spicy nan. \n\nRegarding the restaurant- it is a basic clean restaurant- nothing fancy.  If you find yourself in Nakuru town  - stop by. ', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:52:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3483, 'Bill W', 'Club Road Gilanis Supermarket Building', 'Gilani\'s', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d8012579-r649091827-Gilani_s-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Best Naan Ever !! ', 'Our driver recommended this restaurant and we were not disappointed.\nDespite a quite unattractive entrance,we were welcomed by knowledgeable,friendly and helpful staff.\nAnd the restaurant serves alcohol \nNo drink is as good as a cold beer with a good curry.\nWe got some advice on choosing our dishes,taking one of the specials each,which white rice and naan,butter and hot turbo for me.\nI really enjoyed my main dish but the naan was the best I have ever eaten,including on trips to India and Sri Lanka \nAbsolutely superb \nWe paid a return visit during our short stay in Nakuru and were equally delighted.\nTo Westerners the decor is a bit old fashioned,and the restaurant is unusually adjacent to a food court,but I strongly recommend for the quality and value of the food and the excellent customer service ', 5, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:52:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3484, 'David M', 'Club Road Gilanis Supermarket Building', 'Gilani\'s', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d8012579-r646578085-Gilani_s-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'TRUELY DELICIOUS DELICACIES', 'Bought a big Pizza for KES 1000 on friday 21st Dec last year and was supprised to find a same size free pizza. I though this offer is exclusive to the Terific Tuesdays but not anymoreeee. ', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:52:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(3485, 'Lily101', 'Club Road Gilanis Supermarket Building', 'Gilani\'s', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d8012579-r643088744-Gilani_s-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'It only gets better!', 'For the past 5 years, its been my family\'s random dinners joint. The food has been consistently great! They offer meals on √Äl a carte, my fave being the chicken in a basket.  The staff is very friendly and prompt and the atmosphere is just cool.', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:52:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(3486, 'wayne y', 'Club Road Gilanis Supermarket Building', 'Gilani\'s', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d8012579-r621884748-Gilani_s-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great food! Nice Atmosphere!', 'We ate in the restaurant area, not in the cafe.  The setting is nice.  The food was delicious with reasonable prices.  All of us ate Indian dishes with Naan.  The service was pretty good, though the waiter had missed one of the orders because it was a multiple of the same menu item.   ', 5, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:52:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3487, 'mbuguarimui', 'Club Road Gilanis Supermarket Building', 'Gilani\'s', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d8012579-r618963492-Gilani_s-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Lunch', 'Great fresh meals, friendly staff. Julius, for many years now makes us feel at home everytime we have gone to Gilanis', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:52:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]');
