(3488, 'Susanne J', 'Club Road Gilanis Supermarket Building', 'Gilani\'s', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d8012579-r597344895-Gilani_s-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'god indisk restauranet', 'god service, hvor de gerne vil tilberede maden, hvis man √∏nsker √¶ndring til en ret.\nMaden kom ok hurtigt (ift. den normale gennemsnitlige ventetid i Kenya).\n\nAlt i alt en rigtig god oplevelse, med store portioner og utrolig fair priser p√• de forskellige retter.', 5, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:52:51', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(3489, 'Jabs', 'Club Road Gilanis Supermarket Building', 'Gilani\'s', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d8012579-r567289976-Gilani_s-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'A place for All...', 'Had lunch at the Indian Restaurant here, free salad served - eat as much as you want, the food was good, the vegetable fried rice was superb and so was the sweet corn chicken soup. However the waiter messed up my order and brought me chicken instead. It‚Äôs probably one of the best places in Nakuru. They also have a snack place for quick bites. ', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:52:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3490, 'Zoe B', 'Club Road Gilanis Supermarket Building', 'Gilani\'s', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d8012579-r565608509-Gilani_s-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Excellent Curry', 'Went to Gilani\'s twice in a week and both times were excellent. Complimentary bread, good selection of wester, indian, and chinese food. I had vegetable curry and paratha and it was delicious. Good value, good service. No complaints.', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:52:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
