(3523, 'Africkson Safaris', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r863667197-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'The Merica Hotel: A Surprisingly Comfortable Stay in Nakuru', 'The Merica Hotel restaurant in Nakuru is a great place to enjoy a delicious meal. The service is excellent and the food is top-notch. The restaurant has a wide variety of menu items to choose from, so there is something for everyone. The Merica Hotel restaurant is a great place to eat, drink and be merry.\n\nThe ambiance of the restaurant is perfect for a night out with friends or a romantic dinner for two. The staff is very attentive and always ready to help with anything you need. The food is cooked to perfection and the portions are generous. The prices are very reasonable, especially for the quality of food and service you receive.\n\nI would highly recommend the Merica Hotel restaurant to anyone looking for a great dining experience in Nakuru.', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
