(3525, 'Muralee K', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r842806374-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Dinner Time', 'We had corporate dinner recently at merica hotel restaurant and had wonderful time.  Chef David Wanyonyi helped me to plan in advance and took all our endless requests to make menu to uit our needs. Thank you and looking forward to see you all soon.', 5, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"menu_variety\"]'),
(3526, 'Evans A', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r842153149-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Business conference', 'I honestly  would recommend this restaurant/ hotel based on:\n\nThey are diverse- they served a variety of soups (all of which were professionally prepared by quality chefs, including but not limited to Chef David). When you have David around, you don\'t need a menu. He is exceptionally skilled at what he does. His courtesy is unrivaled, and he is also friendly. He works as a nutritionist. When you see him, please give him a shout because he will always drop everything and serve you right.\n\nI will aways pass by and have my meals here when around and having great conversations around food and dieting.', 5, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3527, 'Rose N', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r811870258-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Food was average but the price was high', 'I had Fish with ugali, my husband had pizza, the fish tasted as if it had been fried earlier and just warmed up in the tomato sauce, also when the bill came we found out that they were trying to scam us, they had put a different price than what we had seen on the menu, so we asked for the menu and sure enough the price on the bill was different.', 2, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
