(3540, 'mbuguarimui', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r618971923-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Business', 'Great location in the cbd, top notch security, prefessional staff. Very ideal for business and pleasure. Gym and swimming enthusiasts are catered for here', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3541, 'Wairimu M', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r611640928-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Dull', 'Their buffet breakfast was dull and cold.The rooms definitely need a revamp.Their bathroom was a no no .they have a very warm reception setting but let that not fool you because the rooms are not the best.', 2, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'negative', '[\"atmosphere\"]'),
(3542, 'DonDon', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r556614078-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Noise all Night', 'Located in the middle of town Merica is an easy choice, the parking is a challenge but a guard will at most times guide you to a street parking, the hotel it self is busy with various activities the staff though friendly and few and this leads to security issues with personal  items removed form your room ( stolen ) the other activities when I was there included an all night cacophony from a dance floor! All in all I would not recommend it at all.\n', 2, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'negative', '[\"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3543, 'Nilda M', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r555343557-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'DELICIOUS FOOD', 'I had the opportunity to eat breakfast and dinners at this restaurant and found the food to be fresh, good quality, deliciously prepared and a great variety to choose from.  ', 5, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
