(3546, 'Hans Lind', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r541041071-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Very good breakfast and dinner - twice', 'I am impressed by the chefs capacity. One does not have to wait long time for the food - and what is served is very good. Especially the Chicken Special  - which i had 2 evenings in a row - was very good. But all my colleagues were also very happy with their plates.', 5, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3547, 'Gachau', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r535345260-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Rather a pale shadow of old self. ', 'After a long hiatus I chose Merica Hotel as the chick place to treat a family gathering with kids. Quite courteous staff, tight and friendly security and ambience. \nHowever, it was rather deserted (as early as 8pm on a Saturday, no music or entertainment for kids....I walked out in search of an alternative..which I found barely 200m next door. ', 1, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3548, 'tkariri', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r519587793-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Always glad to be Back', 'Been going to Merica for the last couple of years on both business and personal family trips. The rooms are very spacious which is always welcome, their breakfast is great with a large variety you must try their broth beef broth for breakfast. Great service all round the hotel. Wonderful, friendly front office willing to extend repeat visitor discount. The bar on the first floor is a good place to spend the evening. The swimming pool location not ideal for adults (too exposed) but okay for the young ones. The room would do with more ambiance   especially the lighting scheme, it\'s too bright with no mood lighting, the bathrooms need some upgrade but overall great, centrally located hotel. You have to pack in the street but hotel provides ample security', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"events_entertainment\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3549, 'vZylWillie', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r512544535-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Wide spread to choose from', 'Meals were good from the buffet for breakfast and supper. A la cart not at the standard as experienced before. Over-all not a bad experience.', 3, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"overall_experience\"]'),
(3550, 'samsonnyangau', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r490030035-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Situated in Nakuru Town centre, with humble parking.Inside,a swimming pool and sited  people  round it all enjoying.', 'A good place to stop and rewind.Very hospitable and the food is taste.Many people on their way to other tourist places like Lake Nakuru,Menengai Crater, Lord Egerton Castle stop here for food.\n\n', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3551, 'Rajeev712', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r484289866-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'My Stay at Merica Hotel', 'Dear Friends,\n\nI stayed in the hotel for 7 days and it was a very confertable stay.\n\nA fully eqquiped hotel with free break fast, use of swimming pool and free Wifi made the things even better.\n\nA centrally located hotel, banks, malls, casino market all are in around the hotel.\n\nGood food and helping & courtious behavier of the staff will make the stay very nice.\n\nAll credit cards including Amex are accepted here.\n\nRegrads\n\nRajeev', 5, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3552, 'Rita G', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r467912435-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'An evening with friends', 'We were six people and eat on the terrace. Everyone had something different from the others. And all of us liked it. Two had an indian menue which was too spicy. But they asked for a yogurt and get a lassi. Then the meal was fine. On the first evening my friends eat without me. They had a buffet and all of them were enthusiastic about it.', 5, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3553, 'Elizabeth Wangari', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r460292828-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Seminar', 'Upon an invitation by a CSO on Health and reproductive rights, i was privileged to eat and drink at Merica Nakuru.. they have a wide selection of food and drinks including ten and four O\'clock teas. Good conference halls', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3554, 'Nyambariga', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r458593216-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'GREAT SERVICE FROM A GREAT TEAM', 'We received a 5* services as we celebrated a birthday for my Fianc√©. \nThanks to Mr.Martin who arranged for  everything and Pastry chef Grace for the amazing white forest cake.\nAs Martin was leaving for the day He gave hand over to Lucy who mobilized a large team for singing. \nThat was outstanding and well appreciated. \nManase I cant forget the great service you gave to us and I cant thank you enough, I recommend you for being attentive and always smiling. \nI cant forget to mention Job from Concierge. \nI promise to come back again just for the great service and delicious food.\nPass my Sincere Regards to Martin, Lucy, Grace and Manase.', 5, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3555, 'evalynek2015', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r458175763-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'ok,....', 'after our wedding, my husband and i together with the family went there for the drinks in the evening.... it was good... but he food is ok, not that special..', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\"]'),
(3556, 'Alex N', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r452522225-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Timely Service', 'The service is very timely and the pastries are fresh. If you want some coffee, try out this place as they have wonderful cakes to go with it. The place is also quiet, clean and easily accessible. ', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3557, 'DCHT', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r445016277-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Utile pour une halte', 'H√¥tel situ√© au centre de Nakuru, d√©coration vieillotte mais globalement plut√¥t bien entretenue\nChambre correcte sans plus avec confort minimum, les pi√®ces d\'eau m√©riteraient une r√©novation en profondeur\nRepas et petit d√©jeuner banals et peu vari√©s mais corrects \nH√¥tel qui convient pour une halte ponctuelle lors d\'un d√©placement', 3, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[]'),
(3558, 'Kairu Isaac', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r428628746-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Best lunch Restaurant in Nakuru', 'Reception was amazing. Tasty food . Great Value for money. The staff is equally friendly and humble.', 5, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
