(3561, 'tlock25', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r418009269-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good quality Mid-level food', 'Good quality Mid-level food served buffet style or ala-carte. Local dishes and Western food available', 3, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3562, 'Gioko A', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r411265341-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great Breakfasst', 'A great place to have breakfast in the morning. a variet of choice and also on demand request. What a place to be.', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"location_access\"]'),
(3563, 'Andrew Lawrence C', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r405209055-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Friendly service, fine cuisine options', 'Nice place to eat: by the pool or in the comfortable restaurant. Large menu, a separate Indian menu even, but when we ordered (8PM on a Thursday night) there were not many options available - which seemed surprising for a hotel of such caliber. The buffet looked amazing (though pricey at 1750KSH), and you got the feeling that the servers realllly wanted you to order that. Ordered the rack of lamb and it was not there. Was very happy however with the grilled snapper - the best meal I\'ve had in Kenya yet. Cooked perfectly, great mustard reduction sauce thing (I\'m not a foodie), priced at 900KSH. My friend did order her biryani without cilantro - it came filled with cilantro. Ruined her meal.', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3564, 'JC E', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r379807508-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good central hotel with good service', 'I am a regular traveller to the town and this is one of the best hotels in Nakuru.\nThe hotel is centrally located for easy access. The staff is friendly and the service good.\nThere is a nice swimming pool and bar area to relax.\nThe rooms are clean and beds comfortable.', 3, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3565, 'willy c', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r379537461-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'where i was treated like a terro', 'this is the place where i was treated like am a  by security even they left with my phone be carefuly', 1, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'negative', '[\"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3566, 'Runar Andreas K', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r378940674-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'My favorite restaurant in Nakuru', 'Been there many times. First time nachspiel after my wedding in August 2013, and since then nearly one time every second week while living in Nakuru. They serve from buffet or by big menu. Usually have most on the menu. Prices is more than average, but not expensive. You can also get served from restaurant while you are seated by the swimmingpool. They also have a nice pizza menu in addition to local and international dishes. The pool is fantastic, and when eating food from the restaurant there, you have a very nice time.', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(3567, 'jomanwa', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r376733616-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Cool atmosphere.  Quite spacious.  Quick service.', 'They have excellent pizzas, ice cream served together with variety of fruits, delicious chicken wings, tasty and delicious chicken in the basket.  ', 4, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3568, 'Freda232015', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r372459878-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Food is poor', 'Limited choices - food ordered were not available, no vegan options and not willing to change/substitute items. Others in the party decided to eat elsewhere', 3, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3569, 'akinyiss', 'Kenyatta Avenue', 'Merica Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1015946-d2416748-r367051574-Merica_Hotel_Restaurant-Nakuru_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good customer service and good food', 'The place is on the Main Street so easily accessible. The customer service is good and the food above average. Some of the food on offer may not be served depending on availability. However; because I am used to that, making a different choice is not difficult. The staff are friendly and helpful without being too much in one\'s space. \nThe hotel has inside, outside and poolside sitting. They also have a decent gym which is not crowded before 4pm. \nDefinitely worth a try!', 3, 'Nakuru', '2025-11-10 19:57:19', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3570, 'NorthStar37006017012', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r1030274430-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Best  restaurant in East Africa!!', 'The food was simply stunning. The flavors are so robust.All for a very reasonable price.I recommend the butter chicken with cheese naan along with pousson chips.You will be amazed.I have traveled around Africa and I can Confidently say this is the best restaurant in East Africa.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3571, 'ntsven', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r978083072-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good food and service is nice', 'I was looking for good indian and spicy food after a very long day of travel. The service is good. Food is very tasty. The food was prepared exactly like i wanted. Keep it up.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(3572, 'Tanvir Singh Sabharwal', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r840052736-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Go to for a quick Indian meal in Eldoret', 'Sunjeel is one of the oldest establishments in Eldoret that has been offering Indian meals at a reasonable price and the flavors have also been constant. \nYou should try their Cheese Naan with Pousine Chips! You can thank me later', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\"]'),
(3573, 'viqq', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r837162431-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Indian Cuisine üëèüèæüëåüèΩ', 'I\'ve gone to Sunjeel numerous times and I am convinced this is the best Indian restaurant in Kenya! Not in Eldoret but in Kenya!! Tried ordering the Kadai chicken from a restaurant in Nairobi and it was nothing close to it! Haven\'t been to Eldoret in a long time but this is the first place I\'ll go as soon as I\'m there. Hands down the best Indian restaurant! ', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3574, 'Kiama2013', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r824835523-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great place. Good food. Excellent staff.', 'I visited via the reviews I saw on TripAdvisor. I was not disappointed. Back in Eldoret after a couple of years, my familiarity with good spots was pretty low. I picked this one out and dragged some folks along. Great food, excellent staff and very generous portions. I highly recommend for a single or group visit. Thanks.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3575, 'Byron78', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r774614366-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Indian food.', 'Back in Eldoret after a few years and visiting this restaurant was a delight.\nGood service,great portions and exquisite tasting food in the middle of the cbs ,ideal.Only major issue is finding parking ,otherwise it is an ideal stop for indian food.\nGo try.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3576, 'Digsy Dave', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r773296333-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Amazing Family meal', 'One of the best Meals I had in eldo. Any Aussies head to this joint the Indian food as as good as home. Lollipop chicken is next level!!! Top notch. Will be back.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(3577, 'bidan m', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r769180281-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Awesome', 'I liked the food, no spice was overwhelming the other one, professional work!\n\nKudos! Keep up the good work', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(3578, 'cgore13', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r749504518-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Very good food.', 'Food and service was excellent. Very good recommendations from the server. Atmosphere and decor are old, but charming.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(3579, 'sdmmb', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r748449960-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Very good quality Indian food.', 'Very good quality Indian food.  Meat dishes, vegetarian dishes and nans were all excellent.  Service good also. ', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
