(3581, 'Julie M', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r725647690-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Excellent Food in a Nice Atmosphere', 'Sunjeel makes great Indian food. It is a great choice for both take out and eating in. I especially like eating in since the dining room is cozy and has a nice atmosphere. The staff are always courteous. I especially like the paneer.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(3582, 'Jon Kyle', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r708873429-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'BEST Indian food', 'I was in Eldoret for business and tried Sunjeel taking a recommendation from TripAdvisor. 10/10. It was amazing. The place may not have the best setting or decor but we were blown away by the service and fabulously portioned food. I cannot wait to go back!', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3583, 'yachtmasterjohn', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r697506622-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'So good I went back the next day. ', 'Super service, excellent authentic Indian food, a great menu. The only complaint is that the portions are too big. One main course would easily feed two or maybe 3 people. On both nights we asked for take away boxes to give to the street kids outside. They‚Äôre the best fed kids in Kenya. I loved it. ', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(3584, 'Byron78', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r683135880-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Asian restaurant and bar', 'Down one of the main streets in Eldoret .Parking is a major issue.Front reception has varied types of seating.Good service.Food has maintained is quality and taste,the drumstick is legendary here.There are two rear bars for quieter times.\nGood restaurant if in the main cbd of eldoret.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(3585, 'twistoliver', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r681753437-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Game day', 'It\'s a good place to watch the game and delicious food is always ready to be served.I highly recommend a visit for any one who hasn\'t been to the place ', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3586, 'hawwa26', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r678892040-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Eat out', 'Best mughlai in eldoret...very yum food. You will never go wrong with the food. Have always enjoyed the food whenever I have been there. ', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(3587, 'Bency', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r673888961-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Indian restaurant', 'Its an old and famous restaurant in Eldoret town, we like the chicken drum stick, fish fry and veg rice . it a very good restaurant serving  Indian food in the small town.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(3588, 'harunani k', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r668630376-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Tasty food', 'Iv been to sunjeels quite a few times and their tawa chiken has never disapointed.other chiken meals are good too.juices are fresh and yummy.service is slow esp on weeknds and public holidays.only disadvantage is parking and ventilation.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3589, 'Portosky', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r664965730-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'One of the best ', 'Good food and great service. The nan is excellent and also the butter chicken. The place needs good air conditioning since it is always hot. ', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3590, 'nyagoti', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r652395372-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good food ', 'I went to sunjeel with my mum.. The food was enough to fit 3 people, I\'ve never been soo full. The Naan and butter chicken were awesome but the vegetable rice didn\'t taste fresh.we also had passion juice which was so good. I would recommend it especially for families', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
