(3596, 'Kelvincheskimzion', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r636876850-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Best Vegeterian Restaurant in Town', 'It happened that my family vacational trip in the Fast growing green Eldoret Town were not only be spent on my Sirikwa Hotel at the outskirts of the town after our days touring the Nandi County. So I came across this restaurant I had read a few positive reviews in TripAdvisor and we decided to give them a shot for two lunches we happened to be within Eldoret center, you guys are great in all services for restaurants their class only tht we felt the urge of an extra packing would be a nicer idea.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
