(3598, 'Kieran Tours T', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r611031189-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'excellent Indian cuiisine', 'great food with a bar to finish off the day. It is a nice place to do business and leisure too..... can be a little bit congested towards the weekend', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3599, 'gordita33', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r603146971-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Tasty &  Yammyyyy', 'Had family lunch there last Sunday. Place was full to maximum capacity which is always a a good sign. We had rice and dhal with cheese naan and of course mango lassie. Food very tasty, bread freshly baked & drinks served on big tall glasses lasted till we finished lunch. \nPrice wise is good,  location although is right in busy Kenyatta Rd we overlooked it & had to walk the road twice. Called restaurant & helpful manager came out to wave to us. Perhaps because they were running a full house, it took quite a while to get our food. ', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(3600, 'lutfi i', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r597369621-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'best indian restaurant in eldoret', 'went with friends for a get together dinner,the staff personnel are amazing and really helpful,plus they know what they serving,unlike most indian restaurants i\'ve been to.\nthe food was damn amazing,highly recommend their prawns gravy with naans.\nmissed my 1star, because of the hotel setting,it has an inside bar,just across the kitchen area,plus the bar entrance is just the same main door as the restaurant, if unlucky might find a staggering gentleman about to fall on your plate', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3601, 'EKamaara', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r588775197-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Excellent Indian Food', 'I had the best Indian Meal in a long time. It was a three course meal served by friendly and resourceful waiters. One advised me on what to eat for dessert and it was yummy!', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(3602, 'Sarah K', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r571208581-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Wonderful! ', 'We visited this restaurant on Easter Monday for lunch. The ambiance was wonderful, the food was delicious, highly recommended. I can especially recommend the butter chicken!', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3603, 'Simon O', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r564174816-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'best of indian in africa', 'lunch consisting of 3 course menu. visited with two friends and had indian salads and papadum for starters. enjoyed meal of ginger chicken with nans and finished off with sweet lasi. atmosphere good with background indian ballads for total homely feel.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3604, 'jairuskoki', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r553197954-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'a sumptuous dinner', 'the meals are Indian and warm. very enticing  and spice. the meal comes in courses. the waiters are very alert and ready for service', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(3605, 'timokip', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r551926958-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Impressed', 'Good atmosphere, within the town but quiet contained with the closed doors. Ample for conversation. Great service from the knowledgeable staff. Delicious food in generous portions. The food is fresh and may take a bit longer than you would expect.\n\nNairobi prices might be a surprise though.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(3606, 'Victor K', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r550164604-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Delicious', 'The restaurant is situated right at the heart of eldoret town. It is the best in town for indian cuisine. I usually come here with friends at least once every fortnight. Their butter chicken is heavenly delicious, for only $6. \nthe staff are very welcoming and friendly. \nenjoy dining with soft indian music on the background. The inside of the restaurant has been designed with an indian touch. You can have a table for two or a round table for 10.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3607, 'Janfrans van der Eerden', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r543762743-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Heerlijk diner', 'Het restaurant dat ik voor de derde maal in 5 jaar bezocht was moeilijk te vinden want van buitenaf niet zichtbaar. Maar het eten was uitstekend.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[]'),
(3608, 'cleophaswanyonyi', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r540459104-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good Indian cuisine joint', 'This is a beautifully set joint for Indian cuisine in Eldoret town. The service is friendly and welcoming.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(3609, 'Lucy', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r535143200-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Best in town! ', 'This evening we had diner at Sunjeel Food Palace, it is our third time this week. The food in this Palace is delicious. We dined at the round table and in the centre of this table there is a turntable. Ones company can use this table to elegantly share dishes. One course of food (like only starters or main-dishes) with maybe some naan is more than enough to satisfy. The host can recommend a lot of nice dishes if you find it hard to choose them yourself. We will visit this restaurant again.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3610, 'rejoicing', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r515558453-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Absolutely superb!', 'I discovered this wonderful place a couple of years ago and have eaten here many, many times! I come with friends or family and even alone. It\'s quiet, the food (both Indian and Chinese) is delicious, and the servers are top-notch! There\'s also a large, beautiful aquarium for your enjoyment. Highly recommend you give it a try, especially the garlic naan!', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3611, 'maldomino', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r509432062-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Delicious', 'The butter chicken and the naan bread were awesome. Service was great, friendly and accommodating. Visited this place two times in one week.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3612, 'Kim K', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r504640641-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good meal in Eldoret', 'The ambiance and space size could discourage you but this place had nice meals. Especially the Indian cuisine. A very wide choice and fairly well done. The wine selection is rather limited. ', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(3613, 'Dan Kuto', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r499647366-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Sunjeel ', 'The place is superb.. But the bar area  is very hot  ..needs  Aircondtioning..also  WIFI  should be connected. ', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3614, 'Kblessing254', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r471588102-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Excellent induan cuisine', 'If you need a restaurant with excellent food, try Sunjeel. Quality of service supercedes the prices. Anyone can fit in because it has family restaurant side, bar section and a smoking area. Make sure you secure a table near the aquarium.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3615, 'Eric K', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r470317913-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Best foods in town', 'Best place ti dine n wine loved the cuisine frm local to international dishes, staff well informed. Loved the prawns', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3616, 'tenetsi', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r465090511-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Best place in Eldoret', 'I had a lunch there as I wanted to get out from Starbucks hotel and restaurant and eat anything else. I was very positively surprised about this unimpressive restaurant by outside and indoor decor as the food was amazing. Real Indian deal, quality guaranteed and very tasty.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(3617, 'Swaleh A', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r462533778-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Swaleh Albeity ', 'The food is delicious is at the center of eldoret n the price is reasonable u can also get sea foods ', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\"]'),
(3618, 'jairuskoki', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r460898134-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'celebrating mood', 'my wife offered me a surprise dinner after my masters graduation from Moi University. she took me and my two children to sunjeel restaurant. it offers Asian food, an assortment of delicious food offered in several courses.  from starters to the main meal we ate a lot of asian food. my liking was their spiced chicken and backed chapati. this experience to me was is unforgettable and it helped us bond as a family. i had a wonderful evening out after the hustle of graduation. try it out', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3619, 'WeldonWK', 'Kenyatta St', 'Sunjeel Food Palace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3854188-r456837530-Sunjeel_Food_Palace-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Best choice in Eldoret', 'The food here is legitimately good. It wouldn\'t be in my top 5 Indian restaurants ever, not by a long shot. But certainly in top 5 Indian restaurants in Kenya, and it is heads and shoulders above every other place in Eldoret.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3620, 'Ganeev M', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r915469144-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Worst experience', 'Only thing goo was the view and we had to pay for it. The food was absolutely foul. Complained to manager and he said his son can eat it. No sorry no apology.  Meat was like a rock and chicken was so hard couldn\'t even swallow it. Never going back', 1, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(3621, 'Michael T', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r893515956-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Go for the sunset and stay for a great meal', 'Kerio View is the best place in the county for a nice meal- the lodge is outstanding and the service is excellent. I highly recommend it.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3622, 'Arnold K', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r886285771-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Wahalaüòä', 'It was nice and fantastic place to hike\nIt is the best place to hangout with your family, friends or even with your love of your life (Habibi‚ô•Ô∏è)üòå\nAlso it\'s a silent place and it gat nice fresh air', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3623, 'AamirSK', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r794063310-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Wonderful view', 'We were fortunate to have reached kerio view, weather permitting.\nThis place is known for one thing and that is the spectacular views! \nThe elevation is breathtaking! Standing on the cliff surely requires some serious balls of steel!\nPerfect place for a photoshoot, the views stand out.\nThe Resturant also has a great view while you enjoy your meals.\nThey also have huts where you can have privacy when you go in a large group or for a stay!\nThe food was excellent, we had ordered a variety of different items and all was well served and good portions too.\nDefinitely should be in your bucket list for places to visit in Kenya! Never a dull or boring moment..can visit over and over again!', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3624, 'Tanvir Singh Sabharwal', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r782287723-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'A magical place in the Heart of the Rift Valley!', 'Kerio view point hotel is a personal favourite spot and never fails to disappoint. \nThe spot offers uninterrupted views of the Kerio Valley while you sip on your hot tea or relax and have a meal. \nThe lodge offers accommodation and has extra options for a group bbq as well which you must order in advance. \nThe view at night is unbelievable! You literally are under a billion star hotel and have the best view of the sky above you! They say seeing is believing so this is one spot you cannot miss on a trip to Iten or Eldoret! \n\n', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3625, 'Byron78', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r774618370-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Old lady of the Valley', 'Perched on a hilltop in Iten in an area popular with the runners,this place has a unique charm with a glass front looking out over the Kerio Valley.\nGreen spaces everywhere add to the serenity of the place ,the rooms and cottages all face the valley and the view with the twinkling lights in the night sky is breathtaking.The run way for the paragliders still exists .\nService is touch and go but pleasant and friendly.\nLovely place to relax and while away a day.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3626, 'GLORIAH N', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r729003682-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'The best', 'I loved the way the hotel was designed, the perfect wide glass view and mountains slopes trees and the nature in general. \nWhat I enjoyed the most was their chicken, especially the salad made with cucumber. The best have ever tasted so far.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(3627, 'Makaya D', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r723912951-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Magnificent', 'An amiable and friendly service place with nice scinery. Good affordable food and accommodation. Try the place', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3628, 'Jarlath M', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r701461597-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'KERIO view Hotel', 'What a beautiful facility.  Great rooms fully equipped as in European standards.  Wonderful restaurant with terrific staff all overseen by an ever vigilant owner JP who is so nice.  Id recommend it to all.  And of course all this is capped by a great great spectacular view of the escarpment and rift valley. Wow.  ', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3629, 'Bency', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r673889690-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'View point and Food', 'Its a place to be in, there is a restaurant, View point, Para Gliding, accommodation at the resort. we can enjoy this place. the entry fee can be redeemed agents the restaurant bill as we give them the pass from gate , they have very good quality food African and  other category including pizza, toasts, etc     ', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3630, 'harunani k', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r668066816-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Average satisfaction', 'Nyc place for family outing and relaxation.taste of meals depends on what dish you buy.the spageti we had was of poor quality but coconut rice and steak was tasty.the mzungu owner hates kids esp if ur kids are jumping around.service is slow but you can keep urself busy admiring the amazing scenery.', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3631, 'Minesh S', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r667767742-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'the most fabulous views but so-so on veg food and service could be better.excellent breakfast though', 'The view is to die for from almost any table in the restaurant.\nThe non veg food is good and breakfast comes with freshly squeezed juice and is very good.the challenge is with the veg food- very limited choice and not done too well.\nthe service is friendly but not very professional', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\"]'),
(3632, 'Dan Kuto', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r652124859-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'The Great Rift view', 'I did visit kerio view and I must admit that the view of the Great rift valley was great..\nThe service is good and the staff are Very friendly.. would recommend to anyone visiting Iten', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3633, 'Dismas K', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r647513551-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Marvelous and Exciting', 'the first thing that captured my attention was the beauty of the place. It\'s breathtaking. You will be pleased by the quality of customer services being offered.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3634, 'sydneyannem', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r646233126-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Feels like a ski lodge', 'I can\'t speak much to the food as we only ordered soup and sandwiches. Those were nice, but probably not a good indication of the quality of the rest of the menu.\n Honestly, the quality of the food would not matter anyway, this place would still be worth visiting. \nThe view is breathtaking.\n There are colobus monkeys playing on the grounds. The lodge is quaint and looks like a Swiss chalet perched in the alps until you turn around and realize that you are actually on the edge of the Great Rift Valley. There are people paragliding from the premises. There are people training for marathons all around. We \"hiked\" (we have two kids in tow, so we will call it a hike, though it was more of a stroll) over to the as yet unfinished stadium. On the way, there were runners passing us right and left, but one woman was running up and down the hill for training, and we are half-convinced that she may or may not be an olympic gold medalist. At any rate, we would love to go back and stay a night in the lodge and try the nyama choma in one of the huts that overlooks the valley.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3635, 'Kelvincheskimzion', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r636879413-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Another beautiful experience in Nandi', 'I couldn\'t have missed this in the schedule while planning for my ever-waited first time family trip to Eldoret. We spent one night here and the experience was great. Their food being the best served from within restaurants in the North Rift. We loved your quick service and professional ever smilling customer service personnel. Anyone planning a family vacation, this is a must stop location. I promise you\'ll like it.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3636, 'MatildaRose78', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r632514649-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'A True Gem', 'I must say I wasn\'t sure of this place when a friend recommended. But I admit I was blown away by the beauty and incredible vistas that is Kerio Valley. The rooms were rustic but immaculate with a touch of modernity. The ambience gives off a peaceful vibe that is a welcome break from the hustle and bustle. The staff were friendly and there are lots of activities to partake. Will definitely visit again.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3637, 'dancheptot', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r631623080-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'A view point to the rift valley escapement', 'more of a campsite,that gives you an opportunity to view the rift valley escapement and relax as you enjoy fresh air from the valley', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"atmosphere\"]'),
(3638, 'doktorib', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r630898614-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Spectacular view', 'Very nice premises with spectacular view over Rift Valley. Restaurant itself airy and with and ambiance suitable for its location\n\nFood is decent but plain and unimaginative. Best was a pot of goatmeat.', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3639, 'Phil c', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r622006876-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'The best view in the valley', 'I have visited Kerio View a dozen times and each visit is like a new experience. The manager and his staff are always courteous and welcoming. The views are breathtaking and sitting on the deck can be addictive. The restaurant is excellent although the table and seat covers makes it look artificial and untidy. The natural wood blended well with the out door mood in the restaurant. The fireplace is a must especially during the cold days.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3640, 'WSaula', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r621450476-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'An awesome place to visit for day out with friends!', 'I had pleasant moments with friends in this awesome place! The food is great, the environment is quite relaxing with spectacular view of Kerio Valley. The staff are very hospitable, very friendly. We had a really nice working holiday!', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3641, 'Char J', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r618870426-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Amazing view and buffet meal', 'The view of the Rift Valley is stunning!  There are trails to walk a short distance along the ridge and look into the villages in the valley.  Amazing flowers on the grounds- poinsettia TREEs, all kinds of lovely flowers and interesting birds.  The buffet at the lodge was amazing, too. Nice ice cream (and ALL stayed healthy after the meal). Nice beer and coffee with warm milk If you like.   Enjoyed the veggie pizza!   Fabulous outing with great, friendly service, clean washrooms, lovely food and breath catching view!  I highly recommend!', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3642, 'saham_bajaber', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r603346677-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Nice view and food', 'We had a good time at kerio view wih sight of kerio valley infront coupled with good food from the restaurant. Recommend it anytime.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3643, 'Sergoit2016', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r567215402-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great place with the world\'s best view', 'Terrific high class bar and restaurant. Amazing view of kerio valley. Beautiful grounds and building interiors. Real gem for all', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3644, 'AnT_8793', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r559585397-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Nice place for a good dinner', 'We had a good all-you-can-eat dinner. Place worth recommending, we paid in US dollars. Everything was OK - meat, potatoes, vegetables and the views down the valley -excellent.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]');
