(3645, 'Jay J', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r549625037-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Lovely view but slow service', 'Lovely view but service, though friendly, was quite slow and the food quality didn\'t merit the wait. Nice spot though for having a leisurely breakfast if you have some reading to do or work to catch up on', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3646, 'k0wyl', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r526471851-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'great', 'great food i enjoyed the meals, especially the breakfast . and the view especially the way the weather kept changing...', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3647, 'Neema A', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r513794524-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Serene', 'Beautiful views of the valleys the view is brethetaking.  If ur lucky the clouds could literally pass amoung to you while u r there n u literally feel the moisture and experience the reduced visibility until they pass. You pay to enter the place but it doesn\'t go To waste you can use the tickets as money at the restaurant and redeem it while buying food. The food takes forever to be prepared I guess because it\'s being freshly made. Food is quite good and with very good portions, the prices aren\'t bad either. There\'s cottages to stay in overnight if u are Coming from far. Can\'t comment on the rooms as I haven\'t had a look at them.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3648, 'Roopi B', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r510403373-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'AMAZING AMBIENCE', 'Kerio view has a beautiful view of the valley. It is so soothing and relaxing. A place to go and unwind the stress from the busy town or city life. It is just a beautiful experience to see the sunrise.', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3649, 'EKamaara', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r510347667-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great Getwaway', 'This is a  beautiful and quiet place to be. Great environment. Excellent food. It is located in  High Attitude area with about 90% of Kenya\'s athletic champions  living within a radius of 50km. If you choose an early or late evening jog, you could be lucky to meet with the champions and their pacers training. You could pace behind them and feel like a champ.\nIf you don\'t care for these, three are many other sports to enjoy!', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3650, 'maldomino', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r509432765-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great food, great views!', 'Breathtaking views, and wonderful food. This is a must visit anytime I\'m in Kenya. From the occasional monkey sightings in the trees, to incredible views of an ever-changing landscape!\nLarge portions, and good food! Ask the chef to make the mustard beef stroganoff.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(3651, 'Mary O', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r468294593-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Beauty in depth', 'My friend invited me to hang out after their cycling race. This place is quite a distance from the road but so worth it since i\'s tranquil on a level unknown.\nMost residents are athletes but it\'s incorporated nature, vintage and elegance. I thought I was getting a raw deal but this blew my mind, the prices are so pocket friendly n the food is AMAZING to the last bite. \nOh n there\'s paragliding when the winds are great which is almost every time. \nTHUMBS UP KERIO VIEW.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3652, 'Terry M', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r418747544-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'This Place is Special', 'My wife and I are sitting having lunch at the Kerio View as I write this. To call this a magical place would be to undersell its charms. First, the view is stunning. You sit on an escarpment and look down into the Rift Valley. Colobus Monkeys and an abundance of birds dot the landscape.\n\nWe had a private cottage which was comfortable and quiet. The beer was cold and the food bountiful. Do know that everything is made to order when you come. The wait for the food can be a bit long because it is not precooked. \n\nFrom the Kerio View you are less than a mile from the famous Kaminy running track as well as the Iten town center. The people are friendly and gracious and the staff of the hotel are wonderful. For us this is a can\'t miss spot which we will return to.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3653, 'WeldonWK', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r371334349-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Don\'t bother with the food', 'The view is amazing. That\'s why it\'s called Kerio View. But the food is just tolerable and way overpriced for what you get. Order some drinks and enjoy the view, walk around and get pictures from every angle. But don\'t bother with the food.', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3654, 'Anne S', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r348674247-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Stunning views, OK food', 'The views from the restaurant and patio area were breathtaking and worth the visit. The service was slow but pretty normal for East Africa and the food was fine.', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3655, 'Pascal K', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r343507327-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Un standard satisfaisant, attention √† l\'attente.', 'Le restaurant offre une vue sur la vall√©e du Rift. Il est ouvert en Mezzanine, orient√© Ouest.\nLa salle du restaurent est inond√©e de lumi√®re.\nLa terrasse offre plusieurs tables et hutte √† barbecue.\nLe service est de bonne facture, m√™me si le personnel ne se montra pas toujours pr√©sent.\nLe buffet est vari√© m√™me sur une semaine, et les salades semblent √™tre lav√©es √† l\'eau en bouteille.\nL\'attente √† midi pour les plats command√©s depuis la carte est tr√®s longue, alors que les plat de la semaine (plats du jours) sont cuits plus rapidement.\nLa viande est de qualit√© comparativement √† d\'autres restaurants d\'Afrique.\nLa bi√®re est √† 2.5‚Ç¨ alors que le Coca est factur√© 90 cts.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(3656, 'owen t', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r326329355-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Fantastic View-Food is okay', 'What a view!!! This place is set in one of the most amazing spots in the world. Wow, we went on a very clear day and you could see across the valley so clearly. Food is okay, service is slow. We were there for 2.5 hours and part of that time was waiting on the food. The butternut squash soup is great and the special of the day was pizza or pork tenderloin. My group had both and enjoyed it. One of the members got mixed grill and it was charcoal, so make sure to pass on that unless you enjoy burnt meat/ash.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3657, 'Peter P', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r322696702-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Shame it was dark. The view could have offered a distraction to the wait. ', 'We booked for a group of 14 so large numbers were expected, however from ordering to the arrival of first food three long hours passed. \n\nWhen the food arrived we expected piles of tantalising, rare fillet steak however we were instead treated to steak that had clearly been cooked for the full three hour wait. The accompanying side dishes either never turned up or were stone cold.\n\n', 1, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(3658, 'Pascal M', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r294982367-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Tolles Essen super Aussicht', 'Das Kerio View ist auf √ºber 2500m√ºM gelegen neben der Sport Academie. Ein genialer Ausblick √ºber das Rift Valley lohnen die Anfahrt. Von Eldored Stadt ca. 1std. Essen, Service, Ambience sind sehr gut. Preise ab 7-12 euro pro Menu. Hat Spielplatz, Aussichtsrerasse und H√ºpfburg f√ºr Kinder. Europ√§ische Hausleitung. Ist auch ein Hotel. Empfehlenswerter Ausflug!', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(3659, 'Angela O', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r168876773-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'A MUST stop!', 'A perfect lunch stop or stay overnight - either way, this is worth the drive to Iten when visiting Eldoret or other areas in the region.  We stopped for lunch on a day trip form Eldoret.  We placed our orders and then toured the High Altitude Runners Training Facility which got us back at Kerio View right on time!  The food was delicious and very traditional, although there was enough of a western spin (European owners and mgmt.) that something will appeal to just about any taste.  As other reviewers have stated, this is not a stop when you\'re short on time.  The service was very good, but like many places in Kenya, this is too beautiful to rush through and as long as you take that attitude, it\'s all good.  Ordering, leaving and then returning was a great idea.  Afterwards, leave time to wander the beautiful grounds with fabulous plants and fun sculptures.  A great place to walk off the wonderful lunch...or just sit, relax, and take in the gorgeous views across the Kerio Valley.  \n\nWe did not spend the night in the hotel, but may schedule that for our next trip since I\'m assured, and believe, the view changes throughout the day and evening.  The midday June weather leaves the view a little hazy, but as the sun sets, and the colors change...I can\'t wait to see it.  Also, on a clear morning, I hear you can see Mt. Kenya in the distance.  Beautiful.\n\nFor the food, there were eight of us in our party and I believe we ordered six different items from the menu including some of the daily specials (a sizzling fillet steak and spiced fish fillet) and everyone was pleased.  I got the spiced fish fillet special, a pan fried Nile perch marinated with ginger, chilies and lemon juice.  For the included side dish, you had a choice of Mexican rice,  parsley potatoes or butternut chapatti.  I chose the parsley potatoes.  Wonderful!  This was all for just 600 KSH (~$5.00 US).  I even sprang for a side of the butternut chapatti, but I thought it was not as good as other chapatti I had in the region although others in our party loved it.  The highlight was dessert!  Chocolate cake, ice cream and other delicious treats were a hit since this was not an indulgence we had the opportunity for during the previous two weeks in smaller, less developed villages of Western Kenya.\n\nThe only negative...since they don\'t like people just wandering around for free (and I understand that) our driver had a difficult time convincing the gate guards that we were really going to eat.  They wanted to charge for entrance which would be refunded when you produced your receipt.  Our experienced driver stood his ground and it all worked out, but it might be nice to work out a new system.  Started our visit on a bit of a negative note...but this is Kenya!', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"delivery_takeout\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3660, 'maldomino', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r167618288-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'View and service makes up for any lacking in fare', 'Incredibly breathtaking view from our dinner table and the grounds. My second visit, but first for those in my group. Definitely a highlight. Staff were very accommodating, food fare was fine, and like all things in Kenya, nothing moved swiftly. At times that\'s exactly what is needed though.', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3661, 'Byron78', 'Kerio View Road', 'Kerio View', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d2416916-r141647448-Kerio_View-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great', 'Took friends for the views and the location and ended up having dinner and drinks.The view never ceases to amaze either walking down towards the hotel or sitting upstairs in the dining section.As dusk falls and lights appear in the valley the atmosphere changes as does the environment as the fire is lit downstairs.A cozy place with delicious soups and foods to keep you warmed up.Service was a tad slow but nothing to complain about.A lovely evening enjoyed enormously by all.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:04:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3662, 'John R', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r893202138-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great meal with family ', 'The place is located in Elgon view estate in Eldoret, such an elegant place to have nice meals with family and friends. It is a nice place to be, or is a nice place to chill and have fun ', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3663, 'harunani k', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r854726559-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Average ', 'Nice ambience,open area for kids to roam around,banda\'s are clean and accommodative.food is average but small quantity.the good thing is you get 5 chapatis with every stew you order.prices are average too.', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(3664, 'Colleen J', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r833816639-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'The name is no longer Mamma Mias. Its Kwa Bupe', 'This restaurant is our favorite place to eat in Eldoret. Quite area with beautiful trees and outside small pavilions for groups. The bar tender Tony make the best Dawas on earth and the waitstaff treats you like family (Joanna, Eve and Frankie) We ate there almost every night. The Indian food is delicious. I miss it already.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(3665, 'Tanvir Singh Sabharwal', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r782288893-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Open space and overall good atmosphere with indoor and outdoor seating', 'Mamma Mias was once the go to place in Eldoret when it was just opened. The hotel has since changed hands and is not at its best, they can do much better! \nTheir pizzas are well known and the food in general is good. \nThey could do with a change in the atmosphere by spending some time on redoing the decor and redesigning it, there is huge potential here. \nTheir menu also has local cuisine which is prepared properly and tastes good!\nOrder their Samaki Wa Kupaka (Whole Fish) with Ugali and try it for yourself.', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3666, 'Bency', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r673886437-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Evening pizza at Mamma mias', 'We went late in the evening had dinner plans, we had gone for pizza. we enjoyed the food it was delicious. ', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"speed_wait\"]'),
(3667, 'nyagoti', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r652395906-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Cosy afternoon ', 'We went to mama Mia for the pizza.. It was delicious,the best place for pizza in Eldoret. However when we went in there was absolutely no one in the hotel to welcome us and direct us. It looked a bit deserted. The food was delicious. They should add a little more variety for the pizza especially. ', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3668, 'Dan Kuto', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r652126511-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'mamma mias', 'Mamma mias is a great place to visit while in Eldoret..I took my friends there and they were excited about the Koroga..( it\'s an idea whereby customers Cook their own food..)\nGive it a try', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3669, 'Georgie P', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r637732031-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'MM', 'Nice outdoor pub. Gets cold in the evening. Carry a warm jacket or sweater. Plenty of parking space .', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3670, 'Chella2018', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r637381130-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good Indian cuisine. Slow, and could use a face-lift and life injected back.', 'I treat myself to a booth every so often. It has grounds for small families and teams to enjoy a well-cooked Indian meal together in green space as well as a cozy indoors. Make sure you have a lot to do as the dishes take really long to come out, but this also means, great conversation and time to share. They offer Pizza delivery, but I would suggest you pick it up yourself as ours was rock cold when it arrived.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(3671, 'simongoveyausuk', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r624132118-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Very nice Indian food', 'Nice food and a pleasant garden setting. Out door furniture looks a little tired though. Staff are  friendly and attentive.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(3672, 'Char J', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r618842437-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Tastes great but we got sick', 'We got pizza that tasted great; however, 2 hours later our whole group was very sick.  Seems like it was momma mias.  We are North Americans so maybe more sensitive than others, but I recommend using caution.', 2, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3673, 'Joshbrex', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r600646450-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Not great ', 'Visited on a Sunday ordered 2 dishes and had a good 1.5-2 hour wait for the food. \n\nWhen the food came it didn‚Äôt come together so one dish was finished before the other arrived. \n\nI ordered a biriani and have no idea what I was served but it was like a rice in tomato chicken soup. \n\nFound the price on the high side. ', 2, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"price_value\"]'),
(3674, 'James S', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r572759909-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Nice place to eat', 'A large menu with many different offerings. We had different types of curry, which was very good. This restaurant has been here a long time. Its pretty much a landmark in Eldoret.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"menu_variety\"]'),
(3675, 'Grytsje K', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r541880384-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Fine restaurant', 'Ate a wonderful dinner. The service is good, and the italian food was well-prepared and very tasty. Would recommend this to anyone.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3676, 'Lucy', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r534886361-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Still waiting for the lassi', 'This evening we had diner at Mamma Mias. Mamma Mias is claimed to be an Indian restaurant with Italian specialties. We ordered pizzas, ravioli and some Indian dishes. The portion size of the ravioli was minimal, not nearly enough to satisfy one stomach. The pizzas were nicely sized, but the taste was doughy. The Indian food was good in taste but we\'ve had better for the same price in a different Indian that restaurant. Some of the people of our company never received their drink after many times of requesting them. Next time we will go somewhere else. ', 2, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(3677, 'maldomino', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r509433332-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good food, comfortable environment', 'I\'ve been here on several occasions, the pizzas are OK, but the stroganoff, salads, and naan bread are some of my favorites.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(3678, 'Jimenairobito', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r477034386-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Indian and continental food', 'Mamma Mia is a good option if you want to have indian or contiental food. It is correct. It is located in a big compound with garden. ', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(3679, 'Swaleh A', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r463840859-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Mt', 'Nice place but isolated I won\'t recommend for a Muslims cause at first I myself I didn\'t know that they are cooking pork but the good was good', 2, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3680, 'Anne N', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r462890166-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Dinner', 'Visited with a friend and enjoyed their tasty indian food. I loved their chicken which was very well done. Would definitely visit again.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(3681, 'Global35', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r453526761-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good food, good service, bit dark!', 'Came with a colleague and we had a big selection of italian food. We had the cheese filled dough balls (v good!) and the fried eggplant (also good). The pizzas were a little bland, next time we\'ll go for Indian as they also serve. Also the place is a little dark inside, needs more light...service very good though and friendly.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(3682, 'Deepak B', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r453287179-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', '\" Good Food\"', 'A good Place for Fast Food, Lunch and Dinner..Indian food is very good and a very friendly staff. Pizzas are also available . nice atmosphere if you are sitting in the Garden. ', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3683, 'shabbir m', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r448528530-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great food', 'It is a very big area wish they could utilise the ground and make spacious sitting space as when it gets many customers the place becomes very noisy and stuffy \nThey have ample space for a better sitting arrangement', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3684, 'Smith C', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r436264681-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'No comments', 'Disappointing service, very rustic public and over hyped. This is surely not a family type place so avoid if you have kids', 1, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'negative', '[\"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3685, 'Halbe K', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r411844446-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'prima restaurant', 'Elke keer wanneer ik in Eldoret ben probeer ik hier een heerlijke pizza te eten. Maar ze hebben meer dan alleen pizza. Voor mij een plek om terug te komen.\n', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(3686, 'Daniel G', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r380118361-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good food, Kama kawaida', 'Mamma mia\'s never dissapoints. good food, great ambience and personal service. food is a lot so there is value for money. Kudos to Augustine, he sorts me out all the time.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(3687, 'Sylvia M', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r375035546-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Large menu.....but good food!', 'Im always sceptical when I visit a restaurant that offers several different cuisine however I was pleasantly surprised. The restaurant offers Indian(pizza), continental and swahili dishes and all dishes were very tasty! Service is above average. Parking - in plenty.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(3688, 'christinek658', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r367427384-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great meals!', 'Really enjoyed dinner with family at Mamma Mia.  It is located in Elgon View in a quiet surrounding.  Although the set-up of the restaurant is quite basic, the food is really good and tasty and there\'s plenty to choose from the menu.  If you love Indian dishes, this is the place to eat.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3689, 'kissmycalves', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r360060372-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Fine food', 'We went here as a big group as part of a film crew. We ordered ahead and the food took quite quick once we got there. I had a burger while others had pizza, pasta and seafood. My burger was quite greasy but rather tasty and the pizza was pretty good. Like most places in Kenya the service was exceedingly friendly.', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\"]'),
(3690, 'ChivasG', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r339593098-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good ambience, average food and slow service ', 'The restaurant has nice ambience. The menu has a wide range of options including Indian, Italian, pizzas etc. The quality of the food is average. The service is very slow. The prices are reasonable. ', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3691, 'Mayur N', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r338332644-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Delicious Food', 'I have been to this place like four times,The atmosphere is very homely, it was actually a house that was turned in to a restaurant, They have a large variety to choose from, and their food is very tasty, fresh and served hot. It is quite popular for Italian dishes, service is also good. A must try place when in eldoret', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3692, 'Sander H', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r323562702-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Well made food, good service', 'Was there a few weeks ago with some friends and have to say the service was pretty good, if a bit too much for my personal liking (but we seemed to be pretty much alone in the restaurant that evening) , the ambiance was ok (we were seated inside due to bad weather) and the one thing that really shined was the food, whch was delicious and plenty, while it did take a way for 4 persons (1 hour).\nOverall, do recommend, but do not expect too much of it.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3693, 'anis k', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r305232613-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Very good food...', 'Very good food, really authentic indian and Mughlai, should try their starters like delicious indian restaurants ', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(3694, 'Bboyo333', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r285238600-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good Food - Terrible Service', 'I am a local resident who loves Indian food. The food at Mama Mia\'s is good BUT the service is awful. On several occasions I have had to wait for just over 15 minutes for a waiter to attend to me. The order then takes much longer. Must improve their service. Anyone can make good food but not everyone will offer good service.', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(3695, 'JR M', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r284904105-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good food, very nice ambience', 'Mama Mia has very good food, nice people, and a pretty setting.  We have eaten here several times and it is always good.  We usually order multiple Indian dishes.  This is Indian with a Kenyan twist, and always high quality.  The meat is good, not fatty or tough like some other places.  It is relatively close to Moi Hospital and some of the upscale neighborhoods.  Definitely a place to try.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3696, 'NishithC', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r282028829-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'An Indian Restaurant in Eldoret', 'If you crave for Indian food, Mamma Mia is  the destination in Eldoret. It was very close to the hotel where we were staying. The food preparations were good, though they took quite a long in preparing them.', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3697, 'Ajay S', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r265171819-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Impressive and enjoyable', 'The ambience is great thoroughly enjoyed dinner and service despite a full house. If you have a palate for  fish,the coriander (Dania)  fish with some hot roti is really tasty. Chocolate mousse for desert is great. Restaurant is exceptionally clean and the staff were very courteous and friendly . Ajay Shah eldoret.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(3698, 'ManishMax', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r250040730-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Nice food and fantastic service', 'They have a good variety of cousin esp nice North Indian dishes. Good for friends and family. The ambience could be improved ', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3699, 'MatthijsdDulk', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r240531191-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Worth coming back', 'Good chicken tikkaa, exellent pizza! We sat outside during the night, next time around we\'ll definately pop in. ', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(3700, 'EKamaara', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r239309928-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'The best Pizza in town', 'Fresh food! That  is what I associate Mama Mia with.  and their pizza is the best in town. And they deliver - in time! ', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(3701, 'Naureen K', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r228814961-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Absolutely the most amazing restaurant in eldoret!', 'We had a lovely day out for lunch at Mamma Mias in Eldoret. There is a lovely garden, a waterhole bar and by far, the tastiest and most reliable Indian and continental food in Eldoret! It is quaint and family run. The owners are wonderful and the atmosphere boasts a great energy! Would definitely recommend a meal here! üíõüëçüëçüëç you wont go wrong!', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3702, 'Willy C', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r226295150-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'plush with out door scenery', 'Nice place to go with the family it has great scenery and good grounds for eating out doors. The Indian cuisine is splendid and the services are good not forgetting the reasonable prices for drinks.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3703, 'Kakkad_Vipul', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r221167021-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Nice Garden restaurant.', 'Very good food.... small portions though...:(.. well stocked bar and great menu. Will definitely go again', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(3704, 'Paul414', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r212992918-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Awesome place for outdoor and dinner', 'I liked the set up. Outdoor versus the indoor makes it a cool choice to decide.Secondly the ambiance is mature and less crowded.\ni do recommend their pizzas not forgetting friendly people who works there.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3705, 'Peter W', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r210541515-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Very quite restaurant', 'In fact that time the food was not well prepared and really too much cooking oil spoiled the taste. Otherwise the service is friendly and the environment has been left natural.', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(3706, 'rswooding', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r207788996-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Reliable and Tasty Indian Food', 'I use this restaurant often when in Eldoret - becuase it is popular with friends and colleagues, and the Indian food is very good. Whilst the menu is wide and covers Indian, Chinese and other options, I always go for the Indian options - their Chicken Vindaloo is great, the stuffed Aloo Paratha spot on and the chef does wonders with vegetable curries too. \nDecor is basic, and service takes a bit of time - but the wait is worth it', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3707, 'PGtraveller', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r196980375-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Consistently Good', 'Have been visiting this restaurant almost fortnightly for the past 18 months. The service is always friendly and attentive and the food consistently good. I am not sure whether, as one reviewer stated, that its the best Indian food between Mombasa and Kampala (remember there are some extremely good, if very pricey Indian restaurants in Nairobi) but it certainly is one of the best value meals in Kenya and certainly probably the best food in Eldoret. the great advantage is consistency - the Indian food is extremely consistent and good size portions mean you can probably share a curry and rice + a nan or two with a partner. makes it even better value. \n\nThe non-Indian dishes are interesting with some nice fish dishes and chicken dishes and the pizzas are possibly the best in Eldoret too.\n\nCertainly a restaurant i shall continue to visit.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(3708, 'Asghar_khan', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r154234698-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Nice Homely atmosphere', 'Has a nice atmosphere the food is good, and staff friendly.. There is self cooking which is nice. Chicken Kiev good.', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(3709, 'Jake L', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r150981253-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'An Oasis in the desert...', 'Seriously good Indian food in a town with miserable dining options.  Plus they take Visa!  I\'ve eaten here twice but will be sure to come again any time I\'m passing through Eldoret.  It\'s seriously the best Indian food I\'ve had between Kampala and Mombasa.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3710, 'Byron78', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r147288778-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Gem in Eldoret.', 'Offers mixed menu,of continental,indian and some italian dishes.Good quality of service and the food generally is tasty if not totally authentic.Cost wise,its probably the most expensive in Eldoret,about 1000/- a head min.There is a main dinning section as well as an area at the back with an outdoor bar ,pool tables and screens for sports.Setting is in a residential neighbourhood and its set like a house.Has delivery now as well.Hosts the odd house music party in eldoret when the hoi polloi descend to show they belong and state \'do you know who i am\'.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"delivery_takeout\", \"events_entertainment\"]'),
(3711, 'beejmcc', 'Rumogi St.', 'Mamma Mias Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3604436-r146856538-Mamma_Mias_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Mamma Mia\'s in Eldoret', 'I lived in Eldoret for 6 months and Mamma Mia\'s was the only restaurant within walking distance.  It serves Indian dishes as well as pizzas.  The restaurant is clean and the service is good.  The outside bar behind the restaurant provides a relaxing environment.  Food can be ordered in the bar area as well.  Take out is available.  The average price for a meal is 500 Kenyan shillings ($6).  Very reasonable.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:08:51', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3712, 'MikalA', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r999499184-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Best Chapati wraps', 'My friend and partner was visiting Eldoret for the first time and we needed a place to eat before we got to our next destination.\nWe have previously had not very good experience with places located inside a mall but this one was surprisingly good.\nThe food is good especially the wraps and quite filling; he is not really a fan of chapati but this one  he wouldn\'t really mind.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3713, 'Andrew', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r911749689-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Disappointingly poor', 'Had to wait 15-20 mins for drinks after ordering, vegetable spring rolls were replaced by meat samosas and fish was undercooked - so we would have been ill if we\'d eaten it. Very disappointing.', 1, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\"]'),
(3714, 'harunani k', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r850999152-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Nice place ', 'Nice ambience nice food.i love their shepherd pie and lasagna.pizzas good too.its also reasonable.their Shirleys temple is amazing too.keep it up', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(3715, 'Pete O', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r785476167-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great place to enjoy a relaxing music, good food, a drink or two and a chat', 'I always love The Well Irish Pub. The staff are super friendly, service is exemplary and the ambience is unmatched in Eldoret. Always enjoy a good game of rugby and motogp since they\'re always accessible at The Well.\n\nI\'d like to suggest, that one bar be made a rugby bar. The bar on the left, the one with the signed lions jersey. It has one TV, and that\'s all us rugby lovers need. Currently, we\'re scattered, some on one counter, others way in the bar trying to watch from behind or trying to get the staff to put the game on in a closer TV screen.\n\nSetting this up means one screen can serve up to 15 people, condensed in one area, not distracting the rest of the pub. Rugby isn\'t a popular sport, we know, the least you can do and you\'ve always done is give us a screen or two to watch the game. One area and one screen dedicated to showing rugby matches even when they coincide with football games.\n\nCheers, and I hope you consider this. ', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"events_entertainment\"]'),
(3716, 'Tanvir Singh Sabharwal', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r782287901-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great vibes, good place to hang out but below average food!', 'The atmosphere of the place is definitely worth commenting on, the bar is popular for those who drink and the outside sitting area is pleasant with a nice breeze and good views of Eldoret Town. \nThe food menu is however abit of a let down, they do have many items on the menu but are unable to deliver on the quality. \nThe meat is overcooked and the food is very bland, not too sure if it was fresh or not! \nI do recommend this place if you are out to meet with someone or want some alone time but not for a meal. \nThe design and the set up is definitely worth commenting on! Well done! ', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3717, 'marikowaithaka', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r732053051-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Dinner', 'Sports bar environment with decent food that was overdone but tasty. Enjoyed the butter fries. The filet mignon did not really live upto the moniker.\nI\'d go back.\nFriendly service too.', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3718, 'Real squad', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r727508445-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Missed an experience', 'Went there thrice and I realised the food they cook if you don\'t know how it\'s cooked they omit some ingredients when I asked they told me Kenyans won\'t take it but I\'m Kenyan I want the experience make it as it should be......we go out to eat/try new foods because of the experience', 1, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3719, 'Matthias V', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r718888436-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Zu empfehlen ', 'Das Essen schmeckte gut und die Portionen waren reichlich. Die Auswahl ist recht gro√ü... √ºber italienisch etc...', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[]');
