(3720, 'Jarlath M', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r701463289-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Eldoret Well irish Pub', 'What a beautiful irish Pub with terrific cuisine and service on 2 levels. Great staffand service.  But the fits and finishes in the pub are second to none.  Enjoy. And check out those photos ..... ', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(3721, 'Joe C', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r701170066-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Amazing', 'Went to the rupa location..  Excellent Craft beer...  Good food..  Good ambience...  First class service', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3722, 'Steph', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r698973635-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Hidden Dime in Eldoret', 'Hands down one of my favorite places in Eldoret.. The one at Saito has a really cool vibe with the whisky barrels for tables and the sarcastic wall art. The male bartender is really nice.. Like super nice. Alafu their pizza je??!! You\'ll die. Walai Tena. Thin crust super delicious.. The one at Rupa is even better. Interior decor dayuuuum!! Then the balcony where you can go smoke. I\'m in love with the green couches and their Buffalo wings!!!!! Best wings I\'ve ever tasted. I would also recommend the porkchops, fried rice and chicken curry. Best thing of all is its not as expensive as people think. I mean you can get fries from Ksh 200..', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3723, 'yachtmasterjohn', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r697507561-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Smart bar', 'I‚Äôm Irish & this place is not ü§£ however it‚Äôs smart, clean, with bar stools around the circular bar and comfy sofas throughout. The service is excellent, there is live music occasionally and lots of TVs to follow the sport. The only negative would be for the food, the fish & chips I ordered had undoubtedly been cooked earlier in the evening and reheated for me. ', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3724, 'Ken M', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r685423097-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'The place to be', 'This is the place to be whenever you\n are in Eldoret town, good food and not to forget the service with best hospitality. Keep it up', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3725, 'George M', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r683424315-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great Chill Spot.', 'Great place to watch sports and drink some exclusive beers not available in other bars and restaurant. Their whiskey collection is also good.  Two thumbs up', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3726, 'Solomon T', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r682919337-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'The Well Irish Pub place to be!!üëå', 'Blissful place to be! This is where we got nothing but merry.Services are top notch!! They got us coming back whenever we‚Äôre in Eldoret.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3727, 'harunani k', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r679368891-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Kip it up', 'Nyc ambience,friendly staff.food is v.good too.love ur shepherd pie and mocktails.sofas are comfortable too.thumbs up.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(3728, 'Nickson Z', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r654433898-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good service and Ambience', 'spectacular. went to a good lunch but turned out a quick meeting with the able team at the facility. :) .', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"speed_wait\"]'),
(3729, 'Chris I', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r653202193-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good service, excellent food...', 'Clean and very helpful staff, Loved it, Need to work on time though\nOtherwise everything was great, loved the experience ', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"delivery_takeout\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3730, 'Jerry Y', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r648345733-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Counter Charging Ports', '‚ÄúHi, great service and all, but a complain, on why we don\'t have the counter charging systems. I have raised the same with the Manager in charge, but he seems to ignore my pleas. The charging ports on the counter, would be a great plus for you guys.‚Äù', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(3731, 'Collins Kirwa', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r640758116-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'great food, slow services', 'great fod, a large selection of local and international beers, I loved the pork ribs, also the chicken wings glazed with honey, great ambience too. but the waiters??? a tortoise can do better than them,', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3732, 'WSaula', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r639201662-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great place to spend time with peeps!', 'I visited this pub twice in the month of October 2018. Great dishes and enjoyable drinks too. The ambiance is nice & the staff are hospitable too. A great pub I must say!', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(3733, 'Tim F', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r638164179-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Not very Irish', 'The music was loud popular, nothing with a Celtic sounds. Food was fair, my ‚Äúmedium‚Äù T-bone was charred to the point of barely edible. Won‚Äôt be going back. ', 2, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(3734, 'Georgie P', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r637732231-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Irish Pub @ Rupa Mall', 'The food quality changes during different visits. One time excellent meal, next visit not so nice a meal! Nice pub and good stock variety. Staff are friendly. Ambiance is very good. ', 2, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(3735, 'dancheptot', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r631622406-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good ambience,food and service', 'A nice place to relax and have fun.Recommended for sporting activities and socializing.\nThe ambience,Food and service is exemplary good.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3736, 'nyagoti', 'Cheruiyot Street Saito Centre 1st Floor', 'The Well Irish Pub & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d3675400-r622334727-The_Well_Irish_Pub_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Last visit', 'The service was OK but the waiter tried to con us on the amount we were meant to pay. He added a dish that we didn\'t eat. He only brought a total bill. When he realized we had noticed the bill was not accurate is when he brought back the rest of the bill with our change', 1, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-10 20:12:54', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
