(3816, 'wamaitha m', 'Jomo Kenyatta Highway Acacia Premier Hotel, West End Mall Next To The Central Bank Of Kenya', 'Acacia', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d8537654-r775546784-Acacia-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Ms.', 'I found a much improved hotel, the following areas\n1. Swimming restaurant - very quick and beautiful presented food as we wanted\n2. Bar was great as well, we kept asking for hot water and dawa, great service \n3. The best was the rooms. Loved the small petit four in the rooms super surprise I think I needed sugar. \n\nConcierge and reception area, quick and bills presented very well. \nThank you so much', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-10 20:24:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(3817, 'ROSE A', 'Jomo Kenyatta Highway Acacia Premier Hotel, West End Mall Next To The Central Bank Of Kenya', 'Acacia', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d8537654-r770729164-Acacia-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Bed and breakfast', 'The hotel room was superb,For your dates consider this as the best in town.I loved how we were treated.The food was delicious too.I will come back again and again.', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-10 20:24:37', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(3818, 'Great Horizon Trails', 'Jomo Kenyatta Highway Acacia Premier Hotel, West End Mall Next To The Central Bank Of Kenya', 'Acacia', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d8537654-r768731792-Acacia-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Excellent staff, excellent amenities and great food', 'located within Kisumu City, Overlooking Lake Victoria, this refined lakeside hotel only a few minutes drive from both the Kenya Wildlife Impala Park and Lwang\'ni Beach. with excellent staff, excellent amenities and great food it an ideal accommodation for both business and leisure travellers.', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-10 20:24:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3819, 'Fekuchand', 'Jomo Kenyatta Highway Acacia Premier Hotel, West End Mall Next To The Central Bank Of Kenya', 'Acacia', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d8537654-r730925435-Acacia-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Lovely view, very ordinary food.', 'The view is lovely, henceforth I will visit this beautiful poolside venue for drinks only, been here many times, the food is disappointing, the worst is whatever\'s served as Goa curry, the pizzas are like premade bakery pizzas, chicken wings are uninspiring, lamb chops aren\'t bad probably the best in town considering other restaurants where I have eaten lamb chops. \nA Hotel like Acacia must realize that fancy decoration can make the dish look good but the proof of the pudding is in its eating. ', 3, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-10 20:24:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(3820, 'Wanja Ngiri', 'Jomo Kenyatta Highway Acacia Premier Hotel, West End Mall Next To The Central Bank Of Kenya', 'Acacia', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d8537654-r695131378-Acacia-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Exquisite!', 'I had a wonderful time at the Acacia Premier hotel restaurant. From the attentive and polite guards, waiters and waitresses to the amazing food which you could tell that a lot of thought, expertise and time had gone into, i wouldn\'t even blink when it comes to another visit when i;m in Kisumu. I simply just loved it!', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-10 20:24:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(3821, 'Jacqueline J', 'Jomo Kenyatta Highway Acacia Premier Hotel, West End Mall Next To The Central Bank Of Kenya', 'Acacia', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d8537654-r693635131-Acacia-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Good Food, Great Hospitality!', 'We went for our anniversary lunch and the F&B manager saw to it that we were well attended to. For the starter we had chicken wings with barbeque sauce and they were finger licking good. For the mains we would have preferred the Mutton Rogan Josh and the Tandoori Chicken but unfortunately the clay oven was not working. I liked that our waiter James was proactive in telling us all the dishes that were unavailable due to the lack of the clay oven. \n\nWe settled on the Angus Beef Burger and the Mutton Biryani. The Angus Beef Burger was juicy and flavourful and the Mutton Biryani was spicy and the biryani flavours were spot on. We had ordered the dessert platter but we were too full so I can\'t remember all the four mini-dessert but there was a coconut cake and a marble cake with a strawberry jelly and ganache. To crown it all the team surprised us with a cake to celebrate our anniversary. Very memorable lunch that was! The only thing that I would improve is the variety on the menu. We felt it was a bit limiting. But yes Acacia is every bit the home of African Hospitality.', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-10 20:24:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3822, 'alexmbotela', 'Jomo Kenyatta Highway Acacia Premier Hotel, West End Mall Next To The Central Bank Of Kenya', 'Acacia', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d8537654-r691920867-Acacia-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Acacia... The Place to be in Kisumu City...', 'I\'ve always loved Acacia and i wouldn\'t hesitate to recommend Acacia to anybody. The place is just Awesome...', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-10 20:24:37', 'positive', '[\"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(3823, '_shivona_tavares', 'Jomo Kenyatta Highway Acacia Premier Hotel, West End Mall Next To The Central Bank Of Kenya', 'Acacia', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d8537654-r683925491-Acacia-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Excellent snacks by the poolside', 'We tried the fish that Kisumu is famous for on one day and it was great.  The next two days we had an assortment of snacks and they were all delicious', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-10 20:24:37', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(3824, 'alexmwanginjagi', 'Jomo Kenyatta Highway Acacia Premier Hotel, West End Mall Next To The Central Bank Of Kenya', 'Acacia', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d8537654-r672586596-Acacia-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Will visit again', 'It is an awesome place to be, I loved the food, the restaurant, the view from my room window and the accommodation service. Sadly I was so busy with work so I spent very little time enjoying everything and especially my bed (had only 3 hours to sleep). I hope the service improves though especially at the reception and conferencing. Nevertheless, thanks to Emmah Oduol for saving the day', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-10 20:24:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
