(3845, 'Stephanie S', 'Jomo Kenyatta Highway Acacia Premier Hotel, West End Mall Next To The Central Bank Of Kenya', 'Acacia', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d8537654-r454771463-Acacia-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Nice view, super slow service (Bonita vista, servicio muy lento)', 'The view from the rooftop is really nice, you can see Lake Victoria. However it took them more than one hour to bring our food.\nThe plates are very big, a lot of food and nice, but not the best. \n____\nLa vista desde la terraza es preciosa, se puede ver el Lago Victoria bastante bien. Sin embargo les tom√≥ m√°s de una hora traer nuestra comida.\nLos platos son grandes, muchas comida pero sin duda  no lo mejor que he probado.', 3, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-10 20:24:38', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
