(4012, 'Vacation26798653145', 'Junction of Kionange & Biashara Streets and The Village Market CJ\'s Building', 'CJ\'s Koinange', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d14008730-r1020960892-CJ_s_Koinange-Nairobi.html', 'Great Food & Customer Service', 'First of all, they are very generous with the food amounts. My friend and I ate to our fill and the food was very sweet. Our breakfast date was epic. Also, I applaud Beatrice Muthoni for the awesome and warm customer service. We really enjoyed every bit of our experience.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:43:57', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4013, 'Maria C', 'Junction of Kionange & Biashara Streets and The Village Market CJ\'s Building', 'CJ\'s Koinange', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d14008730-r1020544481-CJ_s_Koinange-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent. I will recommend as many people as possible', 'I am Kenyan but living abroad, when I came to Kenya in 2023 I took my mom to cjs and we both loved it, the food portions and taste stood out, I made sure to come back a number of times. So yesterday was my dad‚Äôs birthday and I knew I had to bring my parents there (in my absentia) they both loved the food so much and the warm welcome they received from the stuff. I appreaciate it, specifically , Fatna who handles everything, her kindness, patience and quick response to making everything smooth and a success. I love love cjs and can‚Äôt wait to visit many more times. Many thanks from Colleta üòä', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:43:57', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
