(4018, 'Henry K', 'Junction of Kionange & Biashara Streets and The Village Market CJ\'s Building', 'CJ\'s Koinange', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d14008730-r1010141197-CJ_s_Koinange-Nairobi.html', 'Best chicken bowl in town', 'Great food, even better service! I ordered a dish and didn‚Äôt pay attention to lettuce which I‚Äôm allergic too, but the manager Abhishek kindly remade it for me. They didn‚Äôt have to, but they did and that speaks volumes about their dedication. Highly recommend!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:43:57', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4019, 'richj65', 'Junction of Kionange & Biashara Streets and The Village Market CJ\'s Building', 'CJ\'s Koinange', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d14008730-r1009219962-CJ_s_Koinange-Nairobi.html', 'Top notch pizza ', 'On a rainy day, I did not want to go far from the hotel. So I stopped by and glad I did. I  had the chicken and pineapple pizza, and from the cheese to the crust, it was delicious. The price was budget friendly considering the size of the pizza. You should try it. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:43:57', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(4020, 'euni l', 'Junction of Kionange & Biashara Streets and The Village Market CJ\'s Building', 'CJ\'s Koinange', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d14008730-r1008388911-CJ_s_Koinange-Nairobi.html', 'Unforgettable Dinner in Nairobi.', 'On our last day of the trip. We decided to try some local dish in the restourant. Every service they offer was great. We ordersome cotails and dinner. I do recommend the CJ\'s rstourant.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:43:57', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
