(4061, 'Mads Bo F', 'Dagoretti Road Opposite The Hub Karen. Approx 200m from Karen Roundabout', 'Tin Roof Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5561344-r922995305-Tin_Roof_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'The Tin Roof food disaster', 'I agree with some of the other reviews that the ambiance is fantastic, with some nice shops around, a fantastic nail Spa, but the food-is very vey bad, we had some Halloumi wraps with absolutely no taste, by human hair inside, I had a ciabatta beef sandwich, i got a panini with uneatable meet and a few leafs of rocket salad, what a boring sandwich, their drinks however are very good.\nIf you want to eat ther go to the ‚ÄúMama Rocks‚Äù burger container, that is very good burgers,  ', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:46:18', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
