(4070, 'Laurel B', 'Dagoretti Road Opposite The Hub Karen. Approx 200m from Karen Roundabout', 'Tin Roof Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5561344-r840339796-Tin_Roof_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'We Ate at Two Tin Roof Locations', 'We ate at this location and their second location near our hotel off Langata Road. I really liked their healthy salads--and would have rated them higher, but only gave it an average rating because  my husband did not enjoy his hamburger. Even after sending it back to be cooked longer--it was still pink. The other time, he didn\'t order a hamburger. ', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:46:18', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
