(4073, 'tmcmoore', 'Dagoretti Road Opposite The Hub Karen. Approx 200m from Karen Roundabout', 'Tin Roof Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5561344-r820957500-Tin_Roof_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Delicious and great for vegetarians!', 'I had the haloumi chappati wrap and it was absolutely amazing. The whole place smelled wonderful and the staff was great. We were seated near the kitchen and everything that wafted out of there I wanted to eat. Very cute porch to eat on and some nice shops to explore as well.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:46:18', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4074, 'Ouitamata', 'Dagoretti Road Opposite The Hub Karen. Approx 200m from Karen Roundabout', 'Tin Roof Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5561344-r804831964-Tin_Roof_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Meh. Equals throwing money into a wasted bin', 'Had high hopes for this one.. but the dry fish taco and even drier sweet potato quickly put that to rest. The taco had a tiny serving of fish mixed in with weird cucumber cubes, a smattering of sour cream and garnished with  hard unyeilding lime. Actually the only good thing about this meal was the ketchup, because with that you get what you pay for.\nI was seated next to the kitchen where the workers could as well have been at a loud market event. Whats with all the loud talking?! I have a feeling the owner of this establishment either does remote management or couldn\'t care less about what is going on here. Such a waste! Suffice to say won\'t be going back there again', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:46:18', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(4075, 'Mzungubabe', 'Dagoretti Road Opposite The Hub Karen. Approx 200m from Karen Roundabout', 'Tin Roof Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5561344-r784640963-Tin_Roof_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Relaxed outdoor ambience', 'I was here for the first time to meet a friend for coffee. I decided to try out the breakfast menu and it was good - large portion and reasonably priced.  I will be back to try out the lunch next time!', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:46:18', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
