(4323, 'SAMUEL MWANGI M', 'Plot No. 05, Westlands Road Crossroads Plaza', 'Barbeque Nation', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26226468-r1029336018-Barbeque_Nation-Nairobi.html', 'I love this restaurant', 'We discovered the Restaurant a few months ago while looking for a place to have dinner with my wife. The welcome , service, food and the ever jovial Manager who takes time to talk to the each and every guest has made us go back there over and over as a couple and also with our children. We were there on Friday evening and the food was amazing as always and we will keep coming back. Shout out to Emily who takes care of us and recommends something new every time we visit. See you soon', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:58:13', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4324, 'L0lal0la', 'Plot No. 05, Westlands Road Crossroads Plaza', 'Barbeque Nation', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26226468-r1027834151-Barbeque_Nation-Nairobi.html', 'Tasty Indian food', 'Flavorful Indian dishes, served a la carte or through buffet option. Good value for money,  attentive service and some special treats coming from the chef. I found the quality really good, with each dish bringing a distinct taste, which is not always the case. Good variety of vegetarian options. Cocktails and mocktails also available.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:58:13', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
