(4328, 'Imran H', 'Plot No. 05, Westlands Road Crossroads Plaza', 'Barbeque Nation', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26226468-r1024040548-Barbeque_Nation-Nairobi.html', 'Great dining experience', 'My family and I enjoyed a variety of different meats and desserts. Our favourites were the chozer chicken, fish, and the cake desserts. Our waitress Venus served us with kindness and respect, always smiling. The owner of the restaurant was also very cordial and kind and kept checking to see if we were okay. I would recommend everyone to visit if they are in the Westlands area.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:58:13', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
