(4330, 'Janet C', 'Plot No. 05, Westlands Road Crossroads Plaza', 'Barbeque Nation', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26226468-r1019057176-Barbeque_Nation-Nairobi.html', 'Wonderful food and service', 'During our visit to Nairobi we enjoyed a delicious lunch at Barbeque Nation. Great selection of salads. Meats were all superb and desserts were yummy. Service was fantastic.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:58:13', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4331, 'Benga S', 'Plot No. 05, Westlands Road Crossroads Plaza', 'Barbeque Nation', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26226468-r1012447908-Barbeque_Nation-Nairobi.html', 'Delicious food, soulful service', 'Mom and I had a wonderful meal here; the Indian-African fusion was absolutely delicious. We were served by Emily, who was warm and attentive, and the manager was just as lovely.\n\nHe shared a beautiful reminder with us: ‚ÄúJoy and peace are what‚Äôs most important in life.‚Äù I dare add: love, too. üòâ\n\nA truly heartwarming experience, both on the plate and in the atmosphere. Highly recommend!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:58:13', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
