(4333, 'changalwa f', 'Plot No. 05, Westlands Road Crossroads Plaza', 'Barbeque Nation', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26226468-r1012441654-Barbeque_Nation-Nairobi.html', '10/10 Experience!', 'I was there for dinner and had a wonderful experience. The food was absolutely delicious,full of flavor and perfectly prepared. I was also served by a lovely lady called Venus who was kind, attentive, and made sure everything was just right. Her warm and professional service really stood out. Thank you for making the evening so enjoyable!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:58:13', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
