(4336, 'Misheck M', 'Plot No. 05, Westlands Road Crossroads Plaza', 'Barbeque Nation', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26226468-r1006174045-Barbeque_Nation-Nairobi.html', 'Food and service', 'The food and experience was wonderful.  Venus\' service and demeanor was excellent. The music on the background was lovely too.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:58:13', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4337, 'Tahlia O', 'Plot No. 05, Westlands Road Crossroads Plaza', 'Barbeque Nation', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26226468-r1002209320-Barbeque_Nation-Nairobi.html', 'Great food and experience', 'Buffet and starters were amazing. flavors were great. the lime mojito threw me off because of the artificial mint flavoring. otherwise great experience and great service.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:58:13', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
