(4339, 'veriko b', 'Plot No. 05, Westlands Road Crossroads Plaza', 'Barbeque Nation', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26226468-r1002173474-Barbeque_Nation-Nairobi.html', 'Great Indian Cousin', 'Delicious appetizers and main courses. Fish curry, fish fingers and Chicken biryani was our most favorite. The owner kept in checking on us. He gave us complimentary dessert. Overall great experience. Thank you', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:58:13', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
