(4341, 'ALVIN W', 'Plot No. 05, Westlands Road Crossroads Plaza', 'Barbeque Nation', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26226468-r1001288160-Barbeque_Nation-Nairobi.html', 'AMAZING INTIMATE EXPERIENCE', 'The Restaurant is amazing with a chilled ambience.  Venus was amazing and served us really well.  Would highly recommend', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:58:13', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4342, 'Ayako', 'Plot No. 05, Westlands Road Crossroads Plaza', 'Barbeque Nation', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26226468-r1000240162-Barbeque_Nation-Nairobi.html', 'Great Food, Drinks & Vibes!', 'Barbeque Nation (BN) was amazing! The service was excellent, especially Venus, who guided us to order just enough to share. The portions were generous, we were full and even had leftovers to carry home.\n\nThe cocktails were fantastic, with generous pours, and happy hour made them even better. The manager stopped by to chat, sharing how BN has restaurants worldwide, which was a nice touch.\n\nOh, and don‚Äôt forget a mirror selfie in the ladies‚Äô restroom, it‚Äôs beautiful! Hahaha. Definitely a spot worth visiting!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:58:13', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4343, 'Drusilla O', 'Plot No. 05, Westlands Road Crossroads Plaza', 'Barbeque Nation', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26226468-r999797823-Barbeque_Nation-Nairobi.html', 'Great customer service', 'A great restaurant experience with mouthwatering chicken variety. I especially enjoyed chicken biryani. Venus was my highlight. She was great from the onset,   friendly, patient, warm and made sure we had unforgettable experience. She made it special for me. \n\nHelga you were amazing üëè too, great service, ensuring we were comfortable.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:58:13', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4344, 'Gloria W', 'Plot No. 05, Westlands Road Crossroads Plaza', 'Barbeque Nation', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26226468-r999797428-Barbeque_Nation-Nairobi.html', 'Venus Rockss', 'Venus is sent from heaven. Her customer service is exemplary. It was our first time here and she was so gracious with showing us the process. She was funny and happy a quirky comment which made the experience so much more. She loves her job and you can see her heart.\n\nVikas is amazing. He walks around making sure we are all okay and it\'s beautiful to see.\n\nThe food is amazing. My favourite is of course their buttered nun. \n\nThank you Barbecue Nation', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:58:13', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4345, 'Thomas K', 'Plot No. 05, Westlands Road Crossroads Plaza', 'Barbeque Nation', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26226468-r998428402-Barbeque_Nation-Nairobi.html', 'A Heartfelt Culinary Experience ‚Äì More Than Just a Meal', 'We just had the pleasure of dining at this wonderful Indian restaurant, and it was truly something special. The food had that unmistakable feeling of being made with love ‚Äî rich in flavor, perfectly spiced, and clearly prepared with care and tradition.\n\nWhat made the experience even more memorable was the personal touch from the owner. He came to our table, shared stories about the dishes, let us taste some of his personal favorites, and gave us insight into their ingredients and origins. He also told us about his family\'s long history in Kenya, which added an extra layer of authenticity and warmth to the evening.\n\nThis was not just a meal ‚Äî it was a cultural and personal experience that we will remember for a long time. Highly recommended!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:58:13', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
