(4359, 'Shruti-Pramod', 'Plot No. 05, Westlands Road Crossroads Plaza', 'Barbeque Nation', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26226468-r987918443-Barbeque_Nation-Nairobi.html', 'Serves large indian tour groups', 'On Dec 24, 2024 ate lunch here.\n\nThis outlet plays Bollywood songs & is opposite the Soin arcade & is located in the ground floor of the Crossroads hotel.\n\nPayasam/kheer, naan, paneer, chole, rice, chicken, salad, chocolate cake & other pastries were available to us. \n\nIndian veg and non veg fare both are available here.\n\nThis outlet is run by an Indian origin Gujarati manager who said he was a 3rd generation immigrant.\n\nWhen asked the staff for WiFi password, they entered it directly into my mobile.\n\nThe local black attentive staff come around with meat on long skewers asking table by table if we need anything and plop it onto our plate.\n\nGood Indian food, service & ambience - would heartily recommend!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:58:13', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
