(4363, 'Mansha', 'Plot No. 05, Westlands Road Crossroads Plaza', 'Barbeque Nation', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26226468-r979303722-Barbeque_Nation-Nairobi.html', 'Best place to dine in Nairobi! Amazingly delicious food with great hospitality. ', 'Absolutely sumptuous food right from soups, salads and amazingly delicious starters!! Their veg dilruba, crispy corn, tandoori mushrooms, tandoori paneer, veg gilafi and hara bhara kebeb is to die for!! The main course leaves your taste buds tingling to an extent that your tummy is full but you crave for more! The biryani is equally delicious and to top up your overall food experience, you have a great selection of desserts. And that\'s not all, everyone\'s favorite ice cream is still to be enjoyed! üòã All in all, great value for money with endless options to explore. Perfect to make your day extra special with the food and hospitality. The staff is warm and makes you feel at home the moment you enter! We are quite regular here and plan on continuing our trend of \"no cooking Sundays\" üòÑ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:58:13', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4364, 'RI', 'Plot No. 05, Westlands Road Crossroads Plaza', 'Barbeque Nation', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26226468-r979037546-Barbeque_Nation-Nairobi.html', 'Food that feeds your soul.', 'Wow ü§© unbelievable.  \n\nIn all my travels I never found food this good and in an environment so friendly and well laid out.  \n\nVikas really has a love and a passion for what he is doing.   \n\nThis makes the experience amazing. The buffet takes you on a trip to India while keeping  you grounded in Kenya.  \n\nEvery food item is perfect.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:58:13', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4365, 'Resort14556472885', 'Plot No. 05, Westlands Road Crossroads Plaza', 'Barbeque Nation', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d26226468-r973609488-Barbeque_Nation-Nairobi.html', 'BEST BBQ in the world', 'First of all, if you are looking for the best barbeque in the world then this is the best place in the world, not only in food but also in ambiance and service. Last week, I wanted to get food like a wedding, the price should be reasonable and there should be a lot of things. If you have this thought in your mind too then this is the best place in the world. There are salads from all over the world, both veg and non veg options. A waiter will be dedicated to you and you will get tired but the food will not finish. As the name suggests all the items are tandoori so you will not feel heavy. I have gone there once and it has become my favourite place for the weekends. I have been out of India for 12 years, I have eaten food everywhere - Saudi, Bahrain, Dubai, Qatar, but the fun I got here, I have not had it anywhere else. all the best bbq nation.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:58:13', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
