(4415, 'Patrick O', 'Church Road Mimosa Lane', 'The Aviary', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27095013-r1001532084-The_Aviary-Nairobi.html', 'Evening out at Aviary Lounge Westlands', 'Aviary Bar and Lounge offers a sophisticated yet inviting escape from the ordinary nightlife experience. Tucked away in a sleek, modern setting, this venue effortlessly blends stylish decor with a warm ambiance. The lighting is soft and atmospheric, making it perfect for date nights or intimate catch-ups.\n\nThe cocktail menu is where Aviary truly shines. Each drink is crafted with a creative twist, using premium spirits and fresh ingredients. Whether you\'re into classics with a modern flair or experimental mixes, the bartenders here are masters of their craft. \n\nService is attentive without being intrusive. The staff is knowledgeable about the menu and always happy to recommend something based on your preferences.One specific staff stood out i guess his name was Charles..he made us feel very comfortable while explaining to us what they had for the day.\n\nMusic-wise, expect a smooth mix‚Äîlounge beats, soulful house, and the occasional live DJ set, all at a volume that still allows for good conversation.\n\nAviary isn‚Äôt just a bar‚Äîit‚Äôs an experience. Expect to pay a bit more than average, but for the quality and vibe, it‚Äôs worth every cent.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 17:59:48', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"events_entertainment\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
