(4480, 'Tedd O', 'Limuru Road The Village Market', 'Harvest Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15213862-r1030059259-Harvest_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Perfect Burger', 'The burger was cooked perfectly juicy, flavorful, and complemented by fresh toppings and a soft, well-toasted bun. The portion was generous without being overwhelming. What stood out even more was how well it paired with the glass of wine recommended by the Kiarie . The wine balanced the richness of the burger beautifully, enhancing the flavors rather than overpowering them.\n\nThe service was attentive and friendly, and the ambiance of the restaurant made the meal feel relaxed yet refined. Overall, it was a satisfying and memorable dining experience. I‚Äôd definitely recommend trying the burger and wine pairing if you‚Äôre staying here or even just passing through.!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 18:03:28', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4481, 'Mary G', 'Limuru Road The Village Market', 'Harvest Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15213862-r1030005441-Harvest_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Best Breakfast restaurant in Nairobi', 'I had a pleasant time at the restaurant, the ambience is just breathtaking, cool, calm, and gives a luxurious feel. Hannah Njau served me quite fast as soon as i took my seat , she came towards me and welcomed me with a homely smile, and made me feel comfortable and at home, away from home. The food is top notch, tasty, a wide variety to choose from, and caters for all people in terms of food preferences , vegan, or other kind. The location of the restaurant is just so convenient from the city centre or from any other route. Thankyou Harvest Restaurant', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 18:03:28', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(4482, 'Deep S', 'Limuru Road The Village Market', 'Harvest Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15213862-r1029999295-Harvest_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Amazing', 'Amazing service and amazing food, Dennis is one of the best waiters and so friendly please look for him when ur there and try the fish ceviche', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 18:03:28', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
