(4495, 'Melanie L', 'Peponi Road Nairobi', 'Meko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27497587-r1033765786-Meko-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent food and service, beautiful decor and setting', 'We were staying in the hotel (Kwetu Nairobi Hilton Curio) and so we had experience of both breakfasts and dinner. Food is very good quality, for both breakfast and dinner. The breakfast buffet is extensive and fresh, and there is a large a la carte menu as well. Our server Steve on the first morning was lovely and very attentive, as were the lovely ladies who made me ‚ÄúDawa‚Äù when I became sick with a bad cold (hot lemon, ginger, garlic and turmeric). Dinner was also excellent with a variety of options from western and European choices as well as some local dishes. My order on the first night wasn‚Äôt quite correct (missing a couple of key ingredients!) but this was quickly rectified by the manager, Grace. The decor is modern and cool, set next to a swish pool with beautiful sculptures. On the whole I recommend the restaurant.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 18:05:14', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4496, 'Judith K', 'Peponi Road Nairobi', 'Meko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27497587-r1033048416-Meko-Nairobi.html', 'Wonderful servers', 'Stayed at your hotel for our wedding anniversary on October 2, 2025. Beautiful facility with wonderful reception. Tasty food served at breakfast. Outstanding service by our servers Imelda and Susan. They made us feel special and helped to memorialize our wedding anniversary. Thank you for your exceptional service and I‚Äôll definitely be back next time we are in Kenya.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 18:05:14', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
