(4500, 'Amittai Muumbi', 'Peponi Road Nairobi', 'Meko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27497587-r1032392737-Meko-Nairobi.html', 'Top-Notch Experience ‚Äì The Ambiance, the Food, and Misita', 'I have always loved coming to this hotel for its calm ambiance, great food, and relaxing music. But this month, my experience has been taken to another level thanks to one of the hostesses, Misita.\n\nShe has such a warm presence and brings a wonderful vibe every time. Her service is exceptional‚Äîattentive, kind, and truly genuine. I now find myself looking forward to seeing her whenever I visit because she makes the experience that much better.\n\nThe hotel already had the right atmosphere, but Misita tops the list and is a big part of why I‚Äôll keep coming back. Excellent service like hers deserves to be recognized.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 18:05:14', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
