(4506, 'CeceHinga O', 'Peponi Road Nairobi', 'Meko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27497587-r1030677027-Meko-Nairobi.html', 'Spectacular/ emmaculate', 'Very good food and very good customer service \nWe were served by Raphael 10/10. He gave us a very well detailed explanation of the menu and helped us make a decision. The food was fresh and very tasty we will definitely be back', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 18:05:14', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
