(4508, 'Brian A', 'Peponi Road Nairobi', 'Meko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27497587-r1030370661-Meko-Nairobi.html', 'Ecstatic', 'Great experience. Jacinta was kind, overall lovely experience. DJ Ki ng Kev was Thee DJ. Main event. Can\'t wait to be back.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 18:05:14', 'positive', '[\"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4509, 'Terrence', 'Peponi Road Nairobi', 'Meko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27497587-r1030163557-Meko-Nairobi.html', 'Book Kwetu Nairobi now! You won‚Äôt regret it.', 'I had a pleasant stay at Kwetu Nairobi. Everyone was welcoming from the time that I arrived on the property. Moses and Susan were wonderful and glad I encounter them during the check in \n\nWhile staying there, I also had great welcoming interactions with Grace, Ananda and Misita at Meko. \n\nJohn and Sam at Upepo are the best bartenders. \nLucy was excellent at 1893 Brew Club. I tried my first expresso martini and it was great. Lucy gave great recommendations where to get the best kuku choma. \n\nI recommend this hotel for anyone traveling to Nairobi. It‚Äôs in a great location if you want to be away from the hustle and bustle but not too far that you can‚Äôt take a 3 minute uber ride to the action and malls. Theres also a DJ that comes on the weekends so it‚Äôs a lively experience at Upepo and Meko. \n\nI will stay here whenever I return.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 18:05:14', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4510, 'Dani W', 'Peponi Road Nairobi', 'Meko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27497587-r1030132287-Meko-Nairobi.html', 'Service', 'Great food and service from Steve and Yvette, very courteous! Beautiful spread with variety. Delicious halloumi and fruits and fresh juice', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 18:05:14', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4511, 'Samsam A', 'Peponi Road Nairobi', 'Meko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27497587-r1030086683-Meko-Nairobi.html', 'A Phenomenal Dining Experience', 'I  visited tonight this restaurant with my niece, and our experience was exceptional . Upon arrival, we were warmly greeted by Misita at the reception, whose smile immediately set a positive tone. The ambiance of the restaurant is undeniably great; it\'s stylish and well-maintained. However, the culinary experience didn\'t quite match the aesthetic. The food, unfortunately, was a bit disappointing, with an excess of oil and salt detracting from the overall taste. Despite this, the smart and good-looking setting certainly added to the dining experience. Overall, while the service and atmosphere were commendable.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 18:05:14', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4512, 'Monica N', 'Peponi Road Nairobi', 'Meko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27497587-r1029999359-Meko-Nairobi.html', 'Good service.', 'We loved the food and service too. \nMy family is happy and we will definitely be back again. \nThe ambiance and surroundings are good.\nKudos to Purity.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 18:05:14', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
