(4514, 'Chioma', 'Peponi Road Nairobi', 'Meko', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d27497587-r1029828013-Meko-Nairobi.html', 'Perfect service from Raphael and Purity', 'Raphael and Purity were fantastic. Their service was detailed and caring. We came for breakfast and were received with warmth. When we got chilly from the balcony we were easily moved to the table of our choice. Raphael and Purity truly went the extra mile when offering us options and taking care of us during our dining experience.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 18:05:14', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
