(4572, 'Fred S', '154 James Gichuru Road The Social House Nairobi', 'Copper The Urban Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d21138141-r1019821069-Copper_The_Urban_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Good food and service', 'George K took wonderful care of me.  I had the tenderloin which was yummy.  I also had a cosmo, which was delish! \n\nI was able to work at the bar table, which was nice since I was by myself.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 18:06:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\"]'),
