(4574, 'Dimitri F', '154 James Gichuru Road The Social House Nairobi', 'Copper The Urban Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d21138141-r1018941819-Copper_The_Urban_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'When you crave a good piece of meat', 'Chill, dark, intimate, beautiful cadre. I asked George K and Chef Anthony for recommendations and went for the sirloin steak with fries and a delicious lager beer. Can\'t go more classical than that, and it was perfect! The meat was juicy and delicious.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 18:06:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\"]');
