(4578, 'It\'s M', '154 James Gichuru Road The Social House Nairobi', 'Copper The Urban Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d21138141-r1017695192-Copper_The_Urban_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Service review', 'We had an excellent experience thanks to our waiteress Grace Wachamba. From the moment we arrived, she was attentive without being intrusive, knowledgeable about the menu, and offered great recommendations. Our food and drinks arrived promptly with ease and a smile. Her friendly demeanor and professionalism truly enhanced our dining experience. I would definitely return based on the quality of service alone.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 18:06:58', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
