(4635, 'davidalnwick', 'Shanzu, Serena Road Serena Beach Resort & Spa', 'The Jahazi Grill by Serena Beach', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d15887310-r884336832-The_Jahazi_Grill_by_Serena_Beach-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Probably the best upmarket seafood in Shanzu area, very fairly priced house wine', 'A much better experience than the last sea food restaurant that I posted a review of a few days ago in the same area.  Although there were also very few tables occupied, I ordered the \'days special\',  large prawns cooked in coconut and rice, and it was spot on.   Compared to the other place, it was clear from texture and taste that the prawns really were freshly caught, and had not sat in a big freezer for weeks or months (which I believe was the case in the other place I reviewed).  A bottle of very good house wine was served with a price maybe only 30% more than you would pay in a supermarket.   And the food came fast, no time wasted thawing out the prawns!  My only negative comments is that it was hard to make a booking, the phone number that shows up on Google, and maybe on Trip Advisor, gives a \'not in service\' response, had to phone the main Serena Hotel reception desk and wait to be put through.   Final bill came fast and was printed clearly, with clear instructions how to pay using mobile phone payment system, and it was only 70% of the final bill at the previous place in Shanzu that I reviewed.  ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:11:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4636, 'Tang', 'Shanzu, Serena Road Serena Beach Resort & Spa', 'The Jahazi Grill by Serena Beach', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d15887310-r876310302-The_Jahazi_Grill_by_Serena_Beach-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Grillades', 'Une d√©coration cosy et reposante , beaucoup de choix , ce sont des connaisseurs de grillades , cuissons excellentes pour chacun ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:11:05', 'positive', '[]'),
(4637, 'Wanderer Traveler', 'Shanzu, Serena Road Serena Beach Resort & Spa', 'The Jahazi Grill by Serena Beach', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d15887310-r836689458-The_Jahazi_Grill_by_Serena_Beach-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Fresh Seafood.', 'Fresh Fresh Fresh Seafood!!!! \n\nFrom the time we Sat down on our table to the time we walked out of the restaurant, The experience was Amazing. \n\nFrom the Staff to the Ambience was On Point. \n\nFood was Delicious ü§§ \n\nSeafood was Fresh , and that is the theme of the restaurant as well. \n\nSeafood restaurant primarily, but they do have limited options for people who are vegetarian and or want to try Chicken or Beef. \n\nBut if you do visit please try out Seafood, especially Chilly Crab Meat. \n\nWe are surely coming back for another dinner.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:11:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4638, 'KM', 'Shanzu, Serena Road Serena Beach Resort & Spa', 'The Jahazi Grill by Serena Beach', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d15887310-r826596071-The_Jahazi_Grill_by_Serena_Beach-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Fresh seafood, perfectly cooked', 'The food, service and location of the Jahazi Grill is just perfect. I went for the grilled prawns with piri piri sauce and rice with fresh veggies ‚Äì everything was so fresh and delicately flavoured with amazing spices. My hubby chose the seafood platter. It was huge and again amazing prepared. The different butters served with the bread were delicious too. I can\'t report on the desserts as we were too full to order one! The wait staff were friendly and their attention to detail was brilliant.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:11:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4639, 'VioAnne O', 'Shanzu, Serena Road Serena Beach Resort & Spa', 'The Jahazi Grill by Serena Beach', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d15887310-r820168247-The_Jahazi_Grill_by_Serena_Beach-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Must Try Seafood Temptations!', 'Hungry and craving seafood, this was our first stop within Serena Beach! OMG my palate was knocked out‚Ä¶salmon butter, garlic toast, amuse bouche, seafood chowder, seafood platter ‚Ä¶ no room left for dessert.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:11:05', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(4640, 'Lauren C', 'Shanzu, Serena Road Serena Beach Resort & Spa', 'The Jahazi Grill by Serena Beach', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d15887310-r819862547-The_Jahazi_Grill_by_Serena_Beach-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'FANTASTIC!', 'The food here was so delicious we took multiple photos of the BUTTER. Why was this butter better than other butter?!? It‚Äôs a mystery. \n\nWe went for a light lunch before scuba diving, and split the red snapper ‚ÄúSwahili style‚Äù and crab cakes. They also brought out basket of bread with two delicious butters and a salmon spread, garlic bread, and a fried shrimp. So much for light. \n\nThe food was DELICIOUS, and priced to match. The snapper was roughly $30 USD and and there were many more expensive items on the menu. We also went to the top-rated restaurant in Mombasa, Tamarind, and Jahazi blew Tamarind out of the water. \n\nThe ambiance was also lovely. Situated right on the beach in a boat-themed building. Staff were friendly and attentive. Overall our best culinary experience, by far, in the Mombasa area.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:11:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4641, 'Rolf W', 'Shanzu, Serena Road Serena Beach Resort & Spa', 'The Jahazi Grill by Serena Beach', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d15887310-r817336745-The_Jahazi_Grill_by_Serena_Beach-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Just fantastic', 'Place: top, seaside, viel oder the sea\nStaff: very frendly and helpful \nKirchen, Seafood of high quality, top\nEverytime again', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:11:05', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4642, 'Simeon Kisaka', 'Shanzu, Serena Road Serena Beach Resort & Spa', 'The Jahazi Grill by Serena Beach', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d15887310-r816156328-The_Jahazi_Grill_by_Serena_Beach-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'The best in sea food experience', 'I recently travelled to Serena Beach Resort & Spa and had a memorable experience at the Jahazi Grill. I always enjoy eating prawns and Jahazi Grill met my expectations. The food was super nice and I wish I had a longer stay.\n\nBesides the nice food, the staff here are the best in what they do.\n\nI would recommend this truly beautiful restaurant to anyone who wants to have a sea food experience', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:11:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
