(4667, 'Ninsiima M', 'Nyali road, Inside City Mall, Nyali', 'Cultura Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d27253415-r967943960-Cultura_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great food!', 'The food was excellent! The children enjoyed a fine dining experience in a calm and cool classy environment. Wonderful service as well. The desserts were exceptional - especially the coconut panacotta!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:12:43', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4668, 'KJain', 'Nyali road, Inside City Mall, Nyali', 'Cultura Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d27253415-r967671957-Cultura_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Lip smacking food !', 'We just dined in yesterday and I couldn‚Äôt wait to review. \nUndoubtedly, the best food I have eaten in Mombasa! Despite being vegetarians, whatever limited menu options were available, everything was on point. \nHalloumi puri with sweet chilli was such fusion to the perfection. \nThe Italian main course spinach & ricotta ravioli & cheese gnocchi in 3 cheese pesto sauce was lip smacking. \nAnd one of my most favourite desserts was available on the menu & was baked to perfection, with the perfect toffee sauce .. the sticky toffee pudding! \nThe decor is lovely. There‚Äôs both inside and outside seating. \nThe service was warm & courteous but the staff had no clue on wine recommendations or food reccos. Linda was serving us mostly & was attentive. \nHowever, when I asked for the cork for the wine bottle cz half the bottle was left, she took the wine bottle & got it wrapped in the paper bag, but the wine was much lesser (like 1/3rd). \n\nWe have dined at Cafesserie a million times as it‚Äôs the best cafe in town, usually they would get the paper bag and pack it in front of you. \n\nTo conclude, lip smacking food & lovely ambiance, and definitely recommend this place.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:12:43', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4669, 'nezquifriz', 'Nyali road, Inside City Mall, Nyali', 'Cultura Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d27253415-r963635899-Cultura_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', '√ânorme surprise √† Mombasa ', 'Nich√© au second √©tage d\'un centre commercial, un cadre agr√©able avec terrasse, bon go√ªt et soin. De tout petit et rare d√©tails quand au maintien du lieu comme neuf.\n\nUn service parfait √† la fois intentionn√© et intelligent. Une serveuse qui n\'a nul besoin de se renseigner pour apporter conseils et solutions. \nBravo pour l\'excellence. \n\nVenons-en au principal l\'assiette. D√©j√† cela d√©marre tr√®s fort pour les gastronomes, un pain au levain digne des meilleurs ouvriers de France accompagn√© par un beurre sal√© que ma grand m√®re bretonne n\'aurait pas reni√©. Ici au Kenya cette simplicit√© parfaitement ex√©cut√©e rel√®ve de l\'exceptionnel. \nLe menu propos√© est international, le voyage nous transporte en Italie ou en Tha√Ølande avec talent. Ceci pour un rapport qualit√© prix juste.\n\nC\'est pour ma part la note maximale que je donne √† compter et tr√®s tr√®s largement m√©rit√©e.\n\nBravo aux chef d\'orchestre de cet √©tablissement et au personnel.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:12:43', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4670, 'Amina Kassim', 'Nyali road, Inside City Mall, Nyali', 'Cultura Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d27253415-r953241136-Cultura_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'A Culinary Masterpiece: A Dining Experience to Remember', 'This is definitely one of my best restaurants!\nThe ambience, the class, the friendly staff...all wrapped together in a spectacular bow of elegance and sophistication. \nThe food is delectable, and the portions are so generous.\nMy waiter Nusra was an absolute delight.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:12:43', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4671, 'Omar J', 'Nyali road, Inside City Mall, Nyali', 'Cultura Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d27253415-r951320192-Cultura_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'On Vacation', 'I went on vacation with my family and tried the restaurant there for the first time. And everything was perfect. The staff were super nice, the food was delicious and the ambience was wonderful. I will definitely come back here on my next vacation. Greetings from Germany', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:12:43', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
