(4681, 'Angellaüòä', 'Nyali road, Inside City Mall, Nyali', 'Cultura Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d27253415-r948462321-Cultura_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Highly recommend!! Master cuisine!Excellent service! Great ambiance', 'First time visiting Kenya, and I‚Äôm glad my friend recommended cultura so I went ahead and put in a reservation. The service was attentive and professional without being overbearing. Throughout our trip, this was the best meal i had in Kenya. For my main, I had the red Thai curry with chicken I definitely recommend you‚Äôll love. For desert our waiter suggested that we try the sticky toffee pudding and with each spoonful you are greeted by a heavenly blend of sweetness. \nWill definitely visit again', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:12:43', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
