(4721, 'Stefania C', 'Nyali First Avenue Kedev Cottages Road', 'Poco Loco Bistro', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d24045564-r873084710-Poco_Loco_Bistro-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Cute bistro, delicious food', 'Quiet and cool place, with enjoyable music. \nPasta bolognese and pasta with octopus were good as well as pilau and coconut octopus rice, large portions of everything. You might wait a bit to get your food ready but it worth it. Staff extremely kind, prices very fair. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:14:26', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4722, 'Paul A', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r1029926675-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Callous, inhuman, indifferent establishment', 'We were walking at the beach and was a long way from our beachfront apartments. The tide was rising so we saw the restaurant sign and decided to crash there and ask to pass through to get to the road. We offered to buy some drinks and if need be place an order with a deposit for dinner later when we could come back with our kids who were still at the apartments. The manager said he had to make a call first and then said he was instructed not to serve us and we had to go back to the beach.\nWe did and got off at the next resort. These callous, unkind, inhumane and indifferent establishments should not be allowed to operate along our coast where our people are known be kind and hospitable. They are a pollution on our beautiful coast. I wouldn\'t trust their food after that.', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4723, 'Dominique', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r988047588-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'To discover', 'place to discover\nWe came on a Tuesday at noon.\nAn exceptional view of the Indian Ocean, fresh produce and quality wine.\nLobster/crab/shrimp platter 4950\nKsh\nSuper fresh grilled fish 1650 khs\nUltra clean toilets.\nGood value for money.\nImpeccable service,\nFree parking', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4724, 'Francis Swaray', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r972281458-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Tasty meal', 'We had such a wonderful experience at this seafood restaurant with a great view of the Indian ocean. Those giant crabs were well seasoned and quite tasty...wont forget them in a hurry. Great customer service....the owner, Roy has such a great sense  of humour. Will definitely visit again whenever am in Mombasa', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4725, 'wolfgangP', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r966832816-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Mittagessen nach Strandspaziergang', 'Essen war gut, Aussicht ist ein Wahnsinn. Immer ein Essen wert.\nPreislich leider etwas gehoben Preis pro Person muss man mit 2500 Schilling rechnen.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[]'),
(4726, 'Wolfgang R', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r938345555-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Unfreundliche Bedienung', 'Sehr unfreundliche Bedienung.  Vor allem der Oberkellner. Nicht zu empfehlen.  Nie wieder. Ich kann die guten Bewertungen gar nicht verstehen. ', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'negative', '[]'),
(4727, 'Peter', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r925685793-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'EXPENSIVE-THIRD CLASS AMBIENCE. GOOD VIEW', 'The portions do not match the prices. It was very expensive and crap food. A plate of fries was going for $6 Which was not normal. The sitting was also on plastic chairs which didnt match since it charges food like a high end fine dine restaurant WHICH WAS NOT THE CASE HERE. One thing for sure it had a good view but we can\'t eat the view so why charge us for it.', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(4728, 'Delhia C', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r884517453-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Langouste et vue tout au top', 'Vue superbe. Accueil super. Le repas tr√®s copieux.  La langouste grill√©e c est une tuerie . Je la recommande fortement. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[]'),
(4729, 'davidalnwick', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r883817703-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Tired old 1980‚Äôs restaurant with a big freexer', 'Setting beautiful , very few diners,, but we did visit on a Monday night. my family ordered seafood.  it took a long time to cone (considering only 3 tables occupied and  it looked like 8 cooks were in the kitchen),  food was edible, but i suspect once  frozen, and delay in serving was due to time needed to thaw out the sea food.   Such a pity!,  Mombasa sea food is great but probably not improved  by a month or two in a deep freeze, it could have been shipped to Nairobi or NY.  A high end high priced restaurant by the sea like this needs to inform diners transparently of where the seafood was caught, when it was caught, and whether it had been in the freezer and why ( probably necessary  for health reasons for Tuna for sashimi).  \n\nWorst  of all, when the bill was presented,  scribbled in barely legible handwriting (fine in the 1980‚Äôs but which high end restaurants  dont use good up to date software and a printer),  the printed form was from the 1980‚Äôs as well, an d paid no reference to the mobile money and payment revolution which  has changed so much in Kenya in the last Decade.  \n\nSadly, probably a dying little restaurant in a beautiful site that we will not see next year, unless they wake up to the reality of 2023 fast.', 2, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"portion_size\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(4730, 'JetSky88', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r872766674-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Beautiful setting but expected better food for that price', 'The setting of this place is amazing. Sitting in the breeze and having a gorgeous view is highly recommended. Watching the sunset from here is like a bliss. \nWe had high expectations on the food, based on the reviews here and the menu. Lobster, crab, prawns. But unfortunately they were all overcooked. It felt so because the texture of the meat was dry. \nThe prices being charged are of European levels, so for a pricey meal, we expected better food. \nAnd prepare to wait a long time for your food, although it seems to be the rule in many places in Kenya. \nPity as the location is unique.', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4731, 'Bayusuf N', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r871177769-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Premium Seafood and Views', 'Amazing seafood , best I‚Äôve ever had and wonderful service and views. Easily top restaurant around the city. Would really recommend over others.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4732, 'Brigid K', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r870967501-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Fantastic', 'I visited Sea Haven for a girl\'s lunch date and we had a great experience.  Very warm welcome, fast excellent service, menu has a very good selection and very pocket friendly, breathtaking ocean view and most importantly very yummy food. Will be back soon.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4733, 'H√•var', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r869842861-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'A delight for seafood lovers', 'A bit hidden, and off the beaten track, but an amazing discovery for any foodie or seafood lover.  Beautiful views of the beach and the sea from the top of a cliff. Elaborate and mouthwatering seafood menu (will need to come back many times to continue exploring!). Good service!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4734, 'TeriAllen2016', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r863548355-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Fantastic Restaurant with great food', 'Beautiful restaurant with delicious fresh Seafood, Steaks, Oriental Curries etc. and great wine. Truly enjoyed this romantic place with great view of the beach. Visited this restaurant several times when in Mombasa in Shanzu and will always go back.  My favorite is the seafood platter. The owners are very friendly, caring, attentions and enjoyable. \nI can‚Äôt wait go back to this lovely restaurant and get a good dose of fresh seafood and wonderful atmosphere from the Indian ocean sunset.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4735, 'jackykowa', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r855423918-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Terrible customer care at the gate!!!', 'I have visited this place before with a car. I got in swifly, with no check ups. Yesterday, we were on foot, we were profiled, asked alot of questions at the gate, the Manager was called and he asked what we wanted, we are still at the gate waiting. We replied we wanted to have lunch and after being handled like that, we preferred to leave.  SHAME ON YOU MANAGEMENT! ', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'negative', '[\"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4736, 'Claudia S', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r852597551-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Our favourite restaurant !', 'Hands down, the best seafood restaurant at the coast. They tick all the boxes for best food, best location, best service! Best kept secret at the coast ..', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
