(4738, 'Dione V', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r824448987-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Bad service', 'Poor customer service. Seemed to treat white people better than black folks. It‚Äôs just so unfortunate. Good views, good food but very poor customer service.', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(4739, '227Julie', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r815993436-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Really good seafood', 'Delicious seafood, excellent service, a great view and best of all a very calm romantic atmosphere. I had oysters to start then seafood platter. Very good value and very fresh.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4740, 'Jason K', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r815964380-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best food in Kenya', 'This is my favorite redtaurant in all of Kenya.  Run by a kenyan hudband and his german wife, both kind, intelligent enjoyable people to be around.  While that is nice, the food is still the star of the show.  My personal favorite is marinated shrimp in a giant, perfectly ripe, avocado.  For my entree I typically get a mix of seafood in a cheasy creamy sauce serve in a shell dish.   Everything Ive had here has been fantastic.  For context I have been to the top 10 restaurants on here and feel this is the best of all of them.  ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(4741, 'Severus S', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r801087102-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Lunch', 'Very expensive\n\nA plate of Fries Kshs 600/- üôà and that also you can count the fries by looking at them.', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\"]'),
(4742, 'bery p', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r794404522-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Place awesome but poor food overpriced', 'Ordered prawns with chipps,Exactly counted got 8 pcs small ones double portion for myself and girlfriend.Chipps as well few pcs.Bill 6000 KSchls,equivalent 60 USA $ couldnt believe when saw the bill.Except view everything is very very poor,would not recomend to noone definitelly.If quality I would not comment,know what is good restaurant but this one ones and never again,be aware', 2, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'negative', '[\"price_value\", \"portion_size\"]');
