(4743, 'Sean962', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r792465669-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Seafood with a view', 'Delicious seafood and a great view plus friendly service, what more could you ask for? Our family of four including a teenager and one younger stopped for lunch after visiting Mombasa. Ginger crab, prawns, and fish and chips were all very tasty. Sitting out in the breeze with a view of the ocean and Nyali was also lovely. Service was prompt and friendly and questions about the menu answered clearly. After lunch the owner came out to chat a bit and share some of the story of the restaurant. A great place for seafood, great service, I would definitely visit again!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4744, 'ray f', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r787104786-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'On the top of the rocks', 'Sticks out as a fantastic view across the beach high up all along the coastline to nyali from shazu roughly. The owner if still the owner is a very friendly guy that makes you or certainly me at the time very welcome for a nice lunch or evening meal. Funny guy as his humour I like and enjoyed our chats on all subjects from politics to kenyas past history . Very educational for me and sad also that this country was neglected years ago by many including UK.  Most Kenyans now are so nice and genuine people sure they need jobs and wages for themselves and family so I\'m sure like many businesses in Kenya these are really bad times for lack of tourists. Let\'s hope things return to Normality asp and another visit is possible to this nice beach top restaurant.  ', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4745, 'Faith', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r786308852-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Awesome Quiet environment with top notch food ', 'Awesome\nQuiet environment top notch service,Top notch food you won‚Äôt even regret really really amazing and we will definitely be back ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4746, 'dazzaref', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r785231094-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Another fantastic meal ', 'My favourite seafood restaurant in Mombasa never fails to disappoint another fantastic lunch\n \nHad the oysters to start and these were quite big which was a bonus. Followed by the seafood platter with potato salad always good. \n\nPrice was reasonable on a lovely sunny Mombasa day. Cant wait to get back ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\"]'),
(4747, 'director059', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r784116610-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best food best garlic toast', 'Random visit after church and indeed it was a no regret\n\nFresh seafood\nGarlic toast \nGreat view \nFriendly staff and owners \n\nPls try it out ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4748, 'Islam Elnagar', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r783431960-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Romantic dinner', 'We were welcomed in an amazing place with a beautiful sunset on the ocean , we enjoyed our dinner prepared with care and attention, fresh seafood , tasty grilled fish and don\'t forget to taste banana flamb√® !\nThe owners are very nice they enrich our stay with pleasent talks\nWe went 2 times in one week and planning to go back soon !!!\nI&S', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4749, 'mwanjiru1011', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r782559508-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Amazing sea food', 'If you want to enjoy the best of the best sea food in Kenya then this is the place to be.mouth watering cuisine .will definitely go back', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4750, 'Globe Trotter', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r781622662-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Didn‚Äôt get as far as ordering - disgusting ', 'Didn‚Äôt get as far as ordering . The very rude waiter refused to get us drinks before ordering food and demanded it was ordered together !   We were then Told we were not allowed to exit the restaurant through the entrance to get a taxi and had to hike down the cliff into the sea as the tide was coming in!  Never had such a rude service in any Restaurant! Avoid at all costs ', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4751, 'Maggie maina', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r777886977-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Incredible', 'The food was very nice. also the Entertainment guys were good including the Singer@ Thomas aka Bokasa the Sound was Fantastic. _', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
