(4756, 'HotspurUK', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r737982316-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Outstanding view, great food and decent service', 'Had dinner here a few evenings ago with a friend. It was my first time here although my friend had been there before a few times. She convinced me to go there for dinner.\nUpon entering you are graced with the most outstanding view of the lovely beach and the beautiful Indian Ocean. The waiters showed us to our table.\nOur food was amazing. My friend ordered the beef carpaccio and peppersteak while I ordered a prawn cocktail and fish & chips. The steak was so tasty that my friend did not even offer me a bite to taste!\nWashed down with white wine. Pure bliss.\nMy only complaint, if any, would be that the wine list is a bit limited. We wanted a dry red wine and the choice was not very extensive.\nWill definitely return and this time order a peppersteak all for myself!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4757, 'Zaher', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r736549598-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'New Year\'s Eve', 'A Must for those who can afford a decent meal not too expensive,  but value for money, it\'s Haven on Earth', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\"]'),
(4758, 'shp_12', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r735595071-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Worth every penny!', 'A calm clean, serene restaurant on a cliff with beautiful view of the sea and great food. Excellent customer care too. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4759, 'Sp√•nga Johan', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r735477002-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Fantastic food with an amazing', 'Fantastic food with an amazing view\nThey took us in despite having a huge wedding reception. A nice table by the balustrade overlooking the Indian Ocean. And the seafood was exquisite. \n', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4760, 'Alpesh30', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r735305589-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Good food..', 'One of the best place for seafood in msa..good service and a nice spot for sundowner..definitely worth a try when in msa.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4761, 'Noel P', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r735144419-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Equally gorgeous food and views!', 'We decided to visit after checking out some positive trip advisor reviews and boy was it worth it! The restaurant is a hidden gem which overlooks the beachfront. Upon arrival the three of us we were shown to a table with an outstanding view of the coastline which made the dining experience both iconic and idyllic. Seafood is the name of the game here and the various starters did not disappoint. The deep fried prawns were especially delicious. The main courses were also well presented and tasty. Waiters were professional, kind and attentive. The restaurant owners even came out to chat with us. There is direct access to the beach if you fancy a nice after dinner stroll.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4762, 'irishwolfhound673', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r729614246-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Wonderful!!', 'Wonderful like always.Everything is perfekt,the vue,the food and the service.THE place to go if you are in Mombasa.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4763, 'Caroline Mwende', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r729001801-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Sure Return!', 'A total gem, definitely coming back soon. Beautiful ambience, picturesque views of the sea as the sun sets. Very cute and cosy. Enjoyed the food, excellent service and the host and staff were very friendly and helpful.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4764, 'Jacquim88', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r720985038-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Fantastic Seafood, Wonderful Service', 'My husband and I went here for dinner, and it was well worth the drive (just a bit north of the main Nyali area).  We had the prawn and avocado appetizer, snapper, and Garlic Prawns, which were all magnificent‚Äîperfectly cooked and the sauces were all delicious, too. Our only regret was that we arrived after sunset, but it was still lovely to hear the sounds and feel the breeze of the ocean. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4765, 'Jerome K', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r716596780-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Delicious seafood with amazing view!', 'Definitely a very good address in Mombasa: Very warm welcome, delicious prawns and wonderful view. I will come back.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4766, 'SamN001', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r700523207-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great View', 'A hidden gem with a beautiful view overlooking the beach with a spectacular view of the ocean. If you love sea food, this is a place worth a visit. The staff are friendly and professional and the food is very good. Roy, the owner is always engaging, willing to share his time.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4767, 'romanholiday28', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r699506826-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'What a view!', 'Was looking for a decent seafood place after a disappointing experience at the previously impeccable Tamarind. Sea Haven, duly delivered. Offering a view that cannot be described, the setting was cosy and the service personal. The Fresh oysters and grilled oysters were very good, The coquille was to die for. Our Mombasa prawns were very good but the accompanying sauce just didn\'t work. Would definitely return!', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4768, 'dazzaref', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r691331466-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Truly spectacularly good view and the best seafood Ive had ', 'I have visited here a few times and the tranquility of the place is beyond words. The staff are very attentive and professional and just sit in the background . I had oysters to start maybe slightly small but delicious. For my main course I had the seafood platter with the potato salad just truly truly delicious.the prawns the crab and the lobster were truly divine. If you are in Mombasa you need to visit and experience this beautiful restaurant ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4769, 'Paul S Bacote', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r690440016-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'No Words To Fully Desribe', 'We can not go to Mombasa and not visit Sea Haven...\nBest food, best manager/owner... \n\nIf you love sea food that comes with everything excellent, then here you have it!!!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(4770, 'Gianina T', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r688078918-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Delicious food and very welcoming staff ', 'The taste of the food ü§§ is just as per your dreams when you expect to have a seafood platter after long time.\nThe peanuts ... I am still thinking about the taste ü§§and the garlic bread as well very yummy.\nThe owners are very welcoming and friendly.\nThe place is very clean with a beautiful view.\n\nThank you for your service!!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4771, 'Thiongo', 'Shanzu-Mombasa Malindi Road, Shanzu', 'Sea Haven Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g1183067-d2465613-r685807367-Sea_Haven_Restaurant-Shanzu_Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great crab', 'They had a great whole crab hammer and all!!! It tasted really great and was a quiet night with great service all round ', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:18:08', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4772, 'Parasaks', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r577195815-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best wood fired pizzas in town', 'Nice location to get takeaway pizzas. They only deliver in the vicinity of town as their policy is if it ain‚Äôt going to reach your place hit it ain‚Äôt worth delivering it. I agree. \n\nThey have about 6-7 tables where you can sit and eat in. Recommended time to go for an early dinner 6:30 pm to 7pm after a round of mama Ngina drive (lighthouse). \n\nOne point of caution. Ensure that you are wearing long trousers and long sleeve shirt or Apply some insect repellent to avoid getting bitten by mosquitoes as the sitting arrangement is in the open which adds to the charm of MOMBASA raha style! The management does try to rid the place of mosquitoes by setting up neem leaves jikos. Kudos for that. \n\nI recommend ordering 2 pizzas at a time for a family of 4 so that you enjoy them whilst they are hot. \n\nThis is the only Restuarant that offers fresh mushrooms pizzas in the whole of Mombasa! Even the other famous Italian restaurants do not bother to go to that length of detail! You have to be a foodie to appreciate that. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:19:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4773, 'Ariane Z', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r577136040-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Delicious meal and warm welcome', 'This place is simple, welcoming and delicious. The pizzas are crusty and tasty, and the service is super fast - it took less than 10mn. The chef and owner Milio was very  welcoming and gave us all the directions we needed to discover Mombasa. \nI highly recommend.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:19:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4774, 'Katharina E', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r571506422-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Amazing place ', 'Such a great and comfortable place to eat an amazing pizza in a nice area. The chef Milio made the stay more comfortable than the environment already did. \nHappy to be here. :)', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:19:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4775, 'TashE123', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r570386614-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best pizza in Mombasa if not in kenya', 'Delicious wood fired pizza. Excellent service.. pizza came with 10 mins of ordering. Highly recommend this place', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:19:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4776, 'Lalindra D', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r564788113-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Good Pizza', 'Have tried their pizza a couple of times. The pizza is thin crust and delicious. Their service is very good, even their home delivery is very fast. If you are in a hurry and in Kizingo, you must try the pizza.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:19:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(4777, 'Junainabbas', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r563481868-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Excellent pizza', 'Its just the best pizza üçïwith a nice, cosy seating . The natural grass and trees give it an amazing atmosphere to eat in. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:19:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4778, 'FatemaMohammed1', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r559808980-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Millios', 'I swear the most delicious pizza i ever had in mombasa was at millios i had chickenperiperi it had loads goey bubbly cheese with rich tasty tangy reddish orangish sauce wid loads of spicy delicious boneless chicken pieces üòç waaah and there goes a soft hot lip smacking hand toasted crispy crust mmmmhhhh it was soooo yummy Ma sha Allah #myalltimefav #neverdisappointed you shld try it too im 100% sure u wont be disappointed either i promise', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:19:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4779, 'Salmasheikh', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r556812937-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best pizza ', 'Hands down the best pizza in Mombasa, service delivery is excellent and efficient. Highly recommend to all pizza lovers!!! Even if you aren‚Äôt, guaranteed you‚Äôll be hooked with their tasty pizzas.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:19:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"delivery_takeout\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4780, 'DanSonko', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r555854894-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Pizzas that touch the Soul! Literally!', 'What can I say.....\nIf you are not careful, you can miss it on Day 1.\nOnce you venture in, you will wish you discovered it earlier!\nSituated in the heart of Kizingo and with a wonderful \"Home\" setting....Milio\'s Pizza has an awesome location with an ambience that is very relaxing.\nThe staff are warm and welcoming.\n\nLet me get to the best part, the Pizzas!\nOMG the Pizzas!!!\nYou can literally taste every single ingredient that is in the Pizza. The layering and serving is perfect. The presentation is sublime and when you take that bite.....oooh that bite!\n\nYou have got to try it to understand where Im coming from!\n\n....oh....the price? \nGood things are definitely expensive.....but Milio\'s Pizza is an exception to the rule!\nGood Pizzas at affordable prices!\n\nOk....enough, this feels more like a Promo/Ad rather than a review! Hehehehehe!\n\nEnjoy!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:19:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4781, 'Karugi', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r554738626-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Hidden Gem', 'Was driving by, saw Milio\'s, decided to check it out. I was not disappointed. Decided to go a 2nd time, see if they were consistent and tell you what? I was still not disappointed!\nMilios has excellent authentic brick oven fired thin crust pizza, the location is so peaceful and the service OUTSTANDING!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:19:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4782, 'Alessandro T', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r554253916-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Delicious and Fresh', 'Milio\'s Pizza is simply delicious and fresh. It\'s the best pizza in Kenya! I order pizza or eat there at least every 2 weeks. My siblings order weekly for their school days. There is more than just pizza at Milio\'s. There is a lovely friendly atmosphere. The owner Milio himself is there and chats with you while you wait. The staff ask you how you are. It\'s really nice. It means this is there passion and I salute that. When I go somewhere to eat I wanna feel welcome and like at home. And at Milio\'s I do. It\'s no coincidence that Milio is right next to the Pranic Healing Centre. If your in Mombasa whether living or on holidays trust me, you will want a pizza from Milio\'s. It\'s like being in Italy for the first time! ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:19:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4783, 'Azhar M', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r554231588-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Asghar Hussein', 'Just brilliant..best woodfired thincrust pizzas ever ..very polite staff..superb pizzas...excellent garden atmosphere ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:19:37', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4784, 'Rozmin B', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r554200869-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Pizzas done Right!', 'Amazing pizzas every time. Have tried the whole menu and love it every time..  Good seating for whole family and very reliable delivery. Keep It Up!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:19:37', 'positive', '[\"speed_wait\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(4785, 'Hinjal P', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r554156555-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great food!!!', 'Yummy pizzas and great service ....the food quality is on point .. amazing owner always has a smile on his face. PR skills well maintained. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:19:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(4786, 'sameera s', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r554072297-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'PIZZALICIOUS!', 'I\'ve had alot of  pizzas at alot of places,but nothing comes close to Milios Pizza in Mombasa. Courteous staff,a very friendly owner/manager and to top it off Amazing Pizzas! The peri peri is definitely my favourite! Will definitely be back again and again!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:19:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4787, 'Sukesha D', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r553102359-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'MAGNIFICENT MILIOS', 'Mostly a takeaway centre, though does have minimal seating arrangements.  Fantastic thin base pizzas which have remained consistent over a period of time, some punjabi food too available on menu, however pizzas remain the all time favourite.  i would suggest they should start a selection of various kinds of chips, that will add value to their menus and increase sales, as in kenya, chips is a condiment, and not a side dish - plain/masala/poussin/pepper/cheese chips etc.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:19:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4788, 'Tariqa', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r546997201-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best pizza in town', 'You don\'t need to drive so far when milios pizza is around the corner in Kizingo. Warm reception, hearty smiles and great tasty pizzas üçï. We have never been disappointed.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:19:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4789, 'AnmaqM', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r541490971-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Pizza Specialists', 'This must be one of the best new places in Kenya for eating pizza. Nice clean and quiet garden area. Proprietor Aamil is very friendly and welcoming. Did point out to him that the meal needs to be rounded off with a good dessert offering e.g. quality Italian ice cream. I think he\'s going to work on it!', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:19:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4790, 'SamN001', 'Tritton Avenue Off David Kayanda Road', 'Milios Pizza Mombasa', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d12609369-r526694014-Milios_Pizza_Mombasa-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Tasty Pizza', 'I have been here on two occasions and had pizza on both. Milios makes great wood fired tasty pizza, if you can find the place!\nIt\'s rather hidden.', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:19:37', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4791, 'Curious55195721592', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r1038644902-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Mies', 'Lieferservice ist unm√∂glich. Ich war vor Ort habe 10 Minuten mit der Managerin gesprochen, weil bei meiner letzten Lieferung die H√§lfte gefehlt hat. Dann etwas zum Mitnehmen bestellt. Wieder die H√§lfte nicht da. Angerufen und beschwert, die Dame wusste gar nicht wovon ich spreche. Sie sagt in der K√ºche bescheid. Danke f√ºr nichts. Wenn der Besitzer nicht vor Ort ist, tanzen die M√§use auf den Tischen', 2, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[]'),
(4792, 'Bernhard', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r1005750552-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Netter Abend mit gutem Essen und Live Musik.', 'Uriges Lokal mit Live Musik. Gemischtes Publikum mit vielen Expats und Touristen. Wir wurden von Rudi, dem Besitzer herzlich empfangen. Die Tische waren teilweise sehr schlecht beleuchtet. Das Essen hat l√§nger gedauert,wohl weil die H√ºtte voll war. Aber geschmacklich gab es nichts auszusetzen. Die Portionen waren sehr gross und die Preise absolut angemessen.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[]'),
(4793, 'SEB06000', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r921960264-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Good atmosphere ', 'Great place in a tropical atmosphere. Staff is friendly. Two screens with sport. A walking distance from the major resorts nearby.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4794, 'Sharon and Simen', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r899426056-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Hidden gem', 'This bar and restaurant has a huge international menu. Everything I have tried has been of the best quality. I would recommend the wienersnitchel. German owned. Also a great place to chill by the bar and chat. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4795, 'Martin C', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r889295076-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Schweizer K√ºche, √ºberraschend gut und Fassbier. Bundesliga live dazu', 'Es gibt neben franz√∂sischen und italienischen und indischen auch Schweizer K√ºche, √ºberraschend gute R√∂sti und einen speziellen Wurstsalat und Fassbier. Leider nur zwei Weine aus der RSA. Bundesliga live dazu sogar heute.  Gemixtes Publikum , alt und jung, wei√ü und schwarz.  Gerne wieder', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[]'),
(4796, 'Federico', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r789064962-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Wonderful', 'Fast service, good food with a lot of option in the menu, price not expensive. Plus live music for the dinner, and a pool table. Also wifi is free inside', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4797, 'Weltenbummler', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r784142348-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Die Mischung machts....!', 'Irgendwie eine lustige Mischung aus Wirtshaus/Biergarten, Bar und Musikkneipe.\nDementsprechend das Publikum. Viele Expats, Stammg√§ste. ‚ÄûZebrap√§rchen‚Äú Und auch schon mal Damen an der Bar, die nach einem Muzungu Ausschau halten. \nWem nach heimatlichen Gerichten gel√ºstet: Die R√∂stis sind wunderbar. \nAn den Abenden mit Musik sollte man vorher reservieren. ', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[]'),
(4798, 'Globe Trotter', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r781090089-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Super surprised with the quality', 'Super surprised with the quality of food this bar is serving ! \nI had a Thai curry, the wife went for the local beef Choma . Both cooked to perfection ‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è\nGreat style , great atmosphere ! ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4799, 'ryanc3', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r780977205-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'lively bar', 'this bar is owned by a german, the place is lively with music and live bands,very large choice of drinks ,beers and spirits.also there is a good menu for food , while visiting this place .it was always full,so go visit for yourselves.\n', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4800, 'Michael P', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r750812728-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Rustikales Ambiente und gutes Essen', 'Wir waren mit Freunden dort essen. Rustikales entspanntes Ambiente. Ich hatte die Seafood Platte...die war sehr gut....\nWir w√ºrden wiederkommen', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[]'),
(4801, 'Alec White', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r743137544-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Fantastic food', 'I visit the safari inn every time  I am in Kenya love it there there and all the staff are welcoming to all.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(4802, 'HotspurUK', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r739133473-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'A hidden gem in Shanzu', 'Came here for an impromptu lunch with a friend. It was her decision to come to this place. I was a little aprehensive as I do not frequent such establishments, unlike my friend. But boy was I wrong. \nThe setting is all under a huge makuti roof, generous seating availability with a large bar in the centre.\nThe waitress took our drinks order. She did not even frown when my friend ordered an ice cold Tusker Lite even though the morning hours had barely passed.\nFor starters we ordered a tomato mozarella salad which I made sure we shared. It was delicious.\nWe are normally far more adventurous and order different meals on our various outings but on this rare occassion we both ordered meatballs with pan fried potatoes. Again it was very delicious and tasty.\nWill definitely come here again but next time we\'ll be more daring and order different meals to spice it up a bit!!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(4803, 'PROFESSOR ENGLAND', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r729929566-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Professor UK', 'Outstanding for ambience staff food drinks prices and Music\nI have been staying in Shanzu for 14 years sometimes for many months and visit Saf Inn 3 /4 times per week for a drink ,meals good company and the music \nWHY GO ANYWHERE ELSE', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4804, 'Ndutts In Boots', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r728413957-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Chilled out + affordable drinks', 'Very chilled out spot. Loved the fish & chicken too. Service is prompt. The owner is usually around & might pop in to check up on you. They also have a live band üòäüòäüòä  drinks are  also well priced. Loved it ‚ù§', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4805, 'Whitney', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r722663626-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Good lobster ', 'The place itself has a very chill vibe and can be eaten at for lunch or dinner! The lobster is delicious and definitely a must try! ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4806, 'W K', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r698464545-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Einfach mal probiert', 'Waren mit der ganzen Familie zum Abendessen da. Aber gleich vorweg: muss nicht sein! Bedienung nicht so flott, Essen geht so, Getr√§nke wie √ºberall, Ambiente Ballermann m√§√üig. Publikum: √§ltere Wazungu, j√ºngere Einheimische \'Damen\'. \nDas Essen ist einfache, afrikanische und europ√§ische K√ºche ohne dem Aahh effekt. Alles in allem gebe ich 4 von 10 m√∂glichen Punkten. Selbst die Livemusik Do/Fr ergibt keine h√∂here Bewertung. Also mal hingehn ist in Ordnung, aber jeden Abend dort essen muss nicht. ', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[]'),
(4807, 'Lugtenpe', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r662218295-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Goede keuken', 'Wij bezoeken de Safari Inn ieder jaar tijdens ons bezoek aan Kenia. Het is altijd een welkome afwisseling van de alledaagse sleur (niets doen op het strand). Deze keer voor lunch alleen maar ‚Äúsnacks‚Äù genomen. Knoflookbrood, calamaris, samosas en knapperige patat. Het was weer goed...volgende keer weer!', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[]'),
(4808, 'RRudi', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r655646256-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Gute K√ºche tolle Atmosph√§re', 'Hatten einen wunderbaren Abend unter Freunden mit hervorragendem Lobster, gut zubereitet mit absolviert fairen Preisen. Werde mit Sicherheit wiederkommen.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[]'),
(4809, 'edward p', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r648497650-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Lobster', 'went to restuarant had a great lobster dinner at very good price,drinks at very reasonable prices,the owner Rudy welcomes you,and the service is top rate,I have been to more up market restaurants in the Mombasa area but this compares better than most,For value for money give it a try.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4810, 'Sada K', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r612306281-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best nyama choma and fries this side of the Coast!', 'This is literally the best place I\'ve had fries and nyama choma while at the Coast and I must say I was pleasantly surprised. If you have been to the coast then you know that getting fries worthy of your palette is a daunting task, and if you are a nyama choma fan then you know the struggles of getting meat that\'s either not fresh, not tender, that took ages to get to you, or that didn\'t have any flavor. Well the good news here is that the food was so amazing I literally asked my family to not get me cake for my birthday because I would much rather be treated to an \'all-you-can-eat\' spree here lol. \nAnd the service is also really great with friendly and honest staff, as well as the food taking half an hour tops to get to you.\nThere is a live band (which starts playing at 2000 HRS) on Tuesdays and Fridays, with different bands performing on each day. We went on a Tuesday because the Tuesday band is my mum\'s favorite and the music was quite delightful! The place is kid friendly too and even the band plays a combination of old school and new school music.\nOverall, great food, great location, great band, and I am definitely going back a couple of times to try everything else on the menu!', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4811, '792lbert', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r595826907-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Leider hat es kein Animation oder Unterhaltung in diese Hotel also immer Raus und mit Taxis', 'Ja eine Top Hotel und eine Super Anlage f√ºr Familien Preis / Leistung sehr gut, kan es  weiterempf√§hlen', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[]'),
(4812, 'BRUNO G', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r594797705-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Happy Birthday Party at Safari Inn', 'Unique Place in Shanzu only a few km outside Mombasa.\nSimple but always fresh good food. Fondue Chinoise is a Bomb.\nPlenty of meat, huge variation of home made dips and of course never miss a Roesti.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4813, 'Kevin M. D', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r591085934-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great bar food!', 'A visit to Mombasa is never complete without stopping in at Safari Inn! The bar is usually hopping with delightfully beautiful clients, the bartenders are friendly and efficient, and the prices are good. The menu is limited but everything will fill your belly to help you soak up the alcohol you\'re about to drink! Live music on Tuesday nights....good place to watch sports (i.e. World Cup, Premier League, etc)', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4814, 'Franz G', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r580624687-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Speziell f√ºr europ√§ische Besucher', 'Essen, speziell das Pfeffersteak ganz hervorragend, ebenso die Filetspiesse, dazu Livemusik 2x die Woche und Do 20% Rabatt auf alles - der Besitzer (Rudi) versteht sein Gesch√§ft.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[]'),
(4815, 'maddinX', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r574895677-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Einfach toll', 'Ich war schon ein paar mal dort. Essen toll, Stimmung toll, Ambiente toll. Insbesondere an den Abenden mit Life-Musik sollte man mal hingehen. Nach dem Dinner mit den Girls flirten und auch mal das H√ºftbein schwingen das hat was. R√ºdi, der Schweizer Besitzer, hat den Laden im Griff. Er begr√º√üt auch gerne die G√§ste mit Handschlag und ist auch f√ºr ein kurzes Schw√§tzchen zu haben. Ein paar mehr lokale Speisen w√§re vieleicht nicht schlecht... ansonsten Top. Man f√ºhlt sich wohl.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[]'),
(4816, 'knjenga9', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r572685032-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Dinner at Safari ', 'It‚Äôs been close to 8years since I was last here!!! \nI had pan fried potatoes and spare honey glazed ribs. Tusker cider. Amaaaaaing!!!\nAlthough the furniture and ambience is still the same, I honestly didn‚Äôt mind. Great memories!!\nVery helpful and friendly staff this side of Shanzu. I‚Äôd recommend it anytime ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]');
