(4818, 'tuskerboy', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r572093940-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Good service and ambience ', 'We went here on a Sunday afternoon it wasn\'t particularly busy. We all chose the pepper steak - which was delicious  and the table service was excellent. It is a good place to people watch and enjoy the ice cold drinks while you do. Prices are very reasonable so in all we would highly recommend.!!', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4819, 'OEUxx', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r563219747-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Bier vom Fass und gutes Essen ...', 'Wo gibt es am Serena Beach Bier vom Fass? Wahrscheinlich nur im Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant. Es handelt sich um ein eher einfaches, landestypisch offen gestaltetes Lokal. Dieses geh√∂rt einem Schweizer > was auch Auswirkungen auf die Speisenkarte hat. Mein sehr gutes Pfeffersteak mit R√∂sti kostete 890 KSH = ca. 7,50 ‚Ç¨uro. Gratis-Wifi. Zum \"Safari Inn\" geh√∂rt offenbar auch ein daneben gelegener Massagesaloon ...', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"location_access\"]'),
