(4835, 'Reto_Kreyol', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r447741004-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Good swiss food', 'The restaurant is good frequented by locals and foreigners. We hadgodron bleu and piccata milanese. It was very very good and i liked the cool athmosphere. We will come again to eat fondue chinase a discretion for only 1200 ksh. But you have to reserve a day in advance. In the evening there was a live band and people dancing', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"atmosphere\"]'),
(4836, 'Lugtenpe', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r439959659-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Safari Inn ... ieder jaar weer goed', 'Wij verblijven ieder jaar een paar weken in een nabijgelegen hotel. Dan is de Safari Inn altijd weer een leuk uitje. Lekker buiten zitten, een praatje met \"de locals\". Het bier is ijskoud, lekker! Het eten is goed (wij hadden grote garnalen, en halve kip)...wij gaan de volgende keer weer naar de Safari Inn.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[]'),
(4837, 'Mmm_72_70', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r438686834-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Music - Food - Drink ', 'Premise\n\nHas a nice authentic feel. Large bar area in the middle of the premise. Locals and visitors.\nParking at the front.\n\nFood\n\nGood Food, hot and well cooked. Very good value. Range of meats and seaford.\n\nService \n\nProfessional, polite\n\nMusic\n\nAttended on a friday, I think Tues is another evening when they have live music. Maybe a couple of other evenings also. Good local bands with classic european music and African.\n\nOwner\n\nRudi (I think) welcomed us with a handshake, and welcomed us. Clearly does this to guests. Nice touch.\n\nA nice locals and visitor bar/restaurant.\n\nOpposite the Serena Hotel.\n\n', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
