(4839, 'Dani D', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r430071330-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great food at great price, clean, friendly', 'Loved eating her. Owned by a chef, the menu is a mix of local fresh fish meals, Kenyan dishes, German and Thai food. Any choice is a good choice. Live-music by small local band Tuesday and Friday evening, great atmosphere, not a rowdy disco but just a great place to finish your day. Meals available all day, Thursday 20% discount at the time of this writing, October 2016. A hidden gem, loved by all who go (and come back, again and again!)', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(4840, 'Anneke H', 'Shanzu Tourist Road Mombasa Opposite Mombasa Continental Resort', 'Safari Inn Bar & Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d1167454-r383900390-Safari_Inn_Bar_Restaurant-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Nice place and good food', 'The food, the music and good service.... Perfect spot for a nice evening out. Local music and mix of tourists and local. I\"ll be back!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:21:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4841, 'Khadija M. Awadh', 'Nyerere Avenue Ralli House, Opposite Shell Petrol Station', 'Qaffee Point', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d16739335-r1029594560-Qaffee_Point-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Ladies lunch at Qafee point restaurant.', 'We had a ladies lunch to celebrate a few birthdays at the restaurant. Wonderful service. The set up in the basement is just as beautiful as the other levels of the restaurant. Great food options, tasty and great portions. \nThank you for having us.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:23:30', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4842, 'richj65', 'Nyerere Avenue Ralli House, Opposite Shell Petrol Station', 'Qaffee Point', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d16739335-r1010882803-Qaffee_Point-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'A place to find an authentic meal ', 'The restaurant is somewhat small, so choose your time wisely. The food is tasty with large servings and the staff is polite. My meal was delectable. There are many options on the menu. ', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:23:30', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(4843, 'irene g', 'Nyerere Avenue Ralli House, Opposite Shell Petrol Station', 'Qaffee Point', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d16739335-r1005352763-Qaffee_Point-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Wrapping up our time in Mombasa', 'After a weeklong retreat and Safari, our group had a few hours in between the end of the retreat and the time our flight.  We chose this place and the group of 11 were all thrilled.   Food was delicious. Service was beyond accommodating.  So so happy.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:23:30', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4844, 'jannikajahn', 'Nyerere Avenue Ralli House, Opposite Shell Petrol Station', 'Qaffee Point', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d16739335-r988858420-Qaffee_Point-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Guter Spot f√ºr den t√§glichen Kaffe zum Mittag', 'Das Caf√© liegt sehr zentral und ist gem√ºtlich. \nDer Cappuccino mit Kamelmilch war wirklich gut und die Chocolate Tarte sehr lecker. \nPreisleistiungsverh√§ltnis top.\nService war sehr schnell und freundlich. \nSie achten auch auf die Sauberkeit', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:23:30', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(4845, 'Hans E', 'Nyerere Avenue Ralli House, Opposite Shell Petrol Station', 'Qaffee Point', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d16739335-r987740091-Qaffee_Point-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Delicious breakfast - fair price', 'Good food and drinks for a fair price, esp. Coffee and friendly waitresses. Can recommend the middle east breakfast. Interior comfortable with air conditioning.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:23:30', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
