(4863, 'Kishen R', 'Nyerere Avenue Ralli House, Opposite Shell Petrol Station', 'Qaffee Point', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d16739335-r708893428-Qaffee_Point-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Super Satisfied ', 'From interior To the way the desserts look on display,  everything is amazing...  Doesn\'t feel like you\'re in town... I had a cheese Egg burger with fries and boy was that meal filling!  Aesthetic way of placing the meal on a plate...  Super satisfied...  After I finished with dinner, I couldn\'t get my eyes off that kitkat cake!  Oh man it was so good!  However I advise, when buying it, don\'t think with your stomach..  Think with your head :p I thought with my stomach and once I reached half way eating the cake,  my mouth was super sweet!  So I had to take a break.. I guess I\'ve said enough! ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:23:30', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"portion_size\"]'),
