(4891, 'ckiarie2002ke', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r716248496-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Overated', 'We had heard that food was very good at Tapas. We were disappointed by the quality of food we got. It was mostly empty and seems to be overstaffed as there were waiters everywhere. Service was prompt. Waiter was polite and confident-speaking but her advise was mostly lies as whatever she recommended as being the best food at Tapas was really terrible. The food is  not worth the price here.', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:15', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4892, 'borayabonnie', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r698946610-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great', 'Tapas has a kind of old school likes playing old school music awesome sitting arrangement and aficourse a side to smoke away your thoughts.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:15', 'positive', '[\"atmosphere\"]'),
(4893, 'Mercy Victoria', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r693560523-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', '#Octoberescapades', 'Good Music coupled by wonderful customer service from everyone.\nI enjoyed the cocktails and chicken wings\n', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4894, 'MinKrasi', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r687917288-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great ambience! Food quality can be improved!', 'What a lovely place. The music was lovely and the staff friendly. However unfortunately the food we had was way below what we expected. I had the drumsticks and my friend had steak - and he couldnt eat it because of the taste of the steak. This can be improved! Other than that we enjoyed ourselves', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
