(4896, 'ELLY NYAIM O', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r666335699-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Evening and night out', 'Graeatly laid out modern lounge. Great mix of music. Excellent service. Located in close proximity to many amenities. Certainly a place to visit again', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:15', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4897, 'Edwardmartins', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r659112203-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Cold beers, good music, nice ambiance', 'Very nice club to hang out solo or with the boys.. Good music nice crowd great vibes. The staff were very friendly and efficient. Slight annoyance if you are too close to the smoking zone.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:15', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4898, 'Gav D', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r629815603-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Guys nite out ', 'Visited the pub late on a Friday night \nPlace was packed \nDecor is üëç.   Nice cold drinks \nGood atmosphere \nThis is a party place \nRecommend ', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:15', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]');
