(4899, 'antoine572', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r626396151-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Rubbish Joint Nowadays.', 'It\'s a rubbish spot with boring seating & poorly positioned televisions. Would have been alright...but then you realize the staff are deceptive, try to take advantage of you once the night has gone on, then have rude security men backing them up.\n\nJust honestly go to the place next door and pay their entrance fee. Much more organised and honest (and client-oriented). Forget this egotistic bar.', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:15', 'negative', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4900, 'Fwawesh', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r625306587-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Night out ', 'Drinks and music was awesome and the ambience is great.made me feel like I was in Nairobi night life.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:15', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4901, 'Whitney S', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r620665894-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Nice services', 'I enjoyed the services there. It\'s a wonderful place the cocktails are really good. Had fun and I\'m looking forward to my next visit there soon and hope it\'ll get more better...', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'positive', '[\"location_access\"]'),
(4902, 'gee182018', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r620506514-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Rude waitress and extreme impunity', 'Rude waitress called Lucy. My friend double paid a bill and when we tried to sort it out she completely decided to be uncooperative claiming I‚Äôm disturbing her. It took the intervention of one of the supervisor called Richard and another humble waitress to sort the issue. I imagine she was targeting the excess amount. I‚Äôd request all to be alert on such character. The rest seemed ok but that particular waitress had an air, snobbish and rude, even in the supervisors presence. Impunity of that level ensures that we are at the rude waitresses mercy. I hope management deals. This happened on Friday around 1 am , Friday 28th September 2018 incase you want to verify with your cctvs.', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'negative', '[\"service\", \"price_value\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(4903, 'alexNairobi', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r614714247-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Am not coming back ', 'Visited this place ...first the music is soo old school ...service is okay ...drinks are overly unnecessarily priced compared to other clubs with way much better ambience and crowd  ..unbelievable..when you visit here first ask beforehand for the price...am not impressed at all with this place ...my experience was soo off ...', 2, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4904, 'nicholas m', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r614714064-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Ridiculously expensive and overated', 'They dont charge entrance fee but be ready to pay for that in the drinks,drinks 4 times the retail price and rude waitresses,see attached photos,price charged vs offer on local retail shop', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'negative', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(4905, 'Renay_KE', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r611870606-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great Ambience', 'Tapas has a wide selection of food and drinks served by attentive staff. There is an outside sitting area, ideal for groups of people. The facility is also clean and well maintained. The music selection is varied and well suited for a mature crowd out to have a good time. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4906, 'Emmanuel M', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r608838235-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Still the best and of good class and service !', 'Went there for evening out and have some little entertainment just for myself. I love the service and the ambience was so good! This place is the best in Mombasa. Keep up the quality.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4907, 'Cynthia A', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r586467494-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Awesome', 'This is the place to hung out whenever you are in Mombasa. Great location, really good music, a lively crowd, delicious food. My favorite thing is their amazing cocktails. Until next time Tapas...', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4908, 'Scurarie', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r574841764-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'A Nice Club', 'A nice club to hangout and perhaps dance with friends. Although it does get very crowded and the food is average it has a great ambience and nice drinks especially the cocktails', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4909, 'Trushar P', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r573097088-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'A must visit in Mombasa', 'Great drinks, with an endless amount of cocktails and premium spirits to taste. Terrific music, with a fun and friendly crowd partying into the early hours of the morning. To top it off, fantastic food for lunch and dinner. A must visit when in Mombasa.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4910, 'luizamortimer', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r563528622-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Ambiente muito gostoso', 'As bebidas s√£o geralmente mais geladas do que no resto dos lugares e o ambiente √© bom. √â bem uma baladinha mesmo, musica alta e gente dan√ßando.Recomendo. Fique atento ao n√≠vel de pimenta nos pratos!', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'positive', '[]'),
(4911, 'geyMBUHG', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r558829215-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Cozy environment', 'Great pub with a nice open area given the location. The ambience is made to sooth and relax an overworked mind', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'positive', '[\"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4912, 'christian o', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r555622107-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Night out', 'Super joint enjoyed it every time i have visited. The drinks list has some of the craziest names. Music and location are great and prices pretty fair. There is no dance floor but you will enjoy', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4913, 'Ruth W', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r555421742-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'One of the best outings in Nyali', 'I loved the ambiance was lovely and it was adjacent to another club at the mall. They have variety of cocktails and they are mixed well. You should visit when in Nyali', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4914, 'TonyMugoBiz', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r550382985-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Service staff are kings... customers come 2nd', 'As is usual the memo on customer being king is yet to come to mombasa and to tapas.\n\nI have just been kept waiting for 40 minutes for a drink i had paid for and now can\'t find. \n\nSo apart from that i paid 9000 for a drink i only used a quarter for which they have misplaced.\n\n4 different service staff have come and none of them is yet to admit their disorganization or even offer an apology.\n\nWell i had been warned and refused to listen to my friends regarding the aloofness of the management and ownership.\n\nSo i have checked in to the place next door where all my friends go to.\n\n', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'negative', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4915, 'simply s', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r547204030-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best outing', 'Tapas cielo mombasa is the best lounge in mombasa,it has the most delicious array of international cuisine, the best liquor, most amazing hookah, and the ambiance is relaxing and clean not to forget beautiful...with the most friendly stuff .and flexible djs who will keep you dancing all night...however if you want a great group evening book in advance..next time i visit Kenya i will definitely go back to tapas', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4916, 'SasenJP', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r547130693-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Harde muziek en eten niet geweldig', '3e maal hier gegeten, deze keer buiten op terras zodat muziek iets minder hard is. Eten wederom niet goed, vlees erg taai en de garnalen hadden een vreemde smaak.', 2, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'positive', '[]'),
(4917, 'OneG K', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r547007710-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Cozy lounge/Club', 'I loved the ambiance and music and the dj was on point.Well spaced and clean toilets,bartenders were also on point when it came to cocktails', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'positive', '[\"atmosphere\"]'),
(4918, 'Sukesha D', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r532270483-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'TEMPTING TAPAS', 'A boistrous Pub, designed on the lines of an English Pub, with an african touch and with more space outdoors.  Good Loud music and filled with patrons of all shapes and sizes and of all ages.  Famed for their meats, a few vegetarian dishes are available.  Drinks and spirit range is very good with lot of choice.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4919, 'Maureen M', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r529464460-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'very good place and liked by many people', 'Very beautiful,good music and variety of cocktails. The service is quite good and fast. The environment is quite good and security is okay', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4920, 'Nyobu', 'Nyali Centre, Links Road Nyali', 'Tapas Gold', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d7002905-r524128557-Tapas_Gold-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Bar none the best bar on the north coast ', 'Having visited several spots on the North Coast, I am convinced that Tapas Cielo is a cut above the rest. The following reasons apply: mature crowd, good music, air con, good food. Highly recommended.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:25:16', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4921, 'Khadija M. Awadh', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r1029593914-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Sarova by weekend.', 'Great experience as always. It was nice to be back. We had a family lunch over the weekend, we received excellent service at the Lido restaurant, the kids were well taken care of by the Ozone kids club supervisors', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4922, 'Nguyen Hop', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r1012562364-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'A place to enjoy and celebrate joyful moments', 'I love the food, service and atmosphere here. The food is good, I can enjoy the food with good gin tonic and the sea breeze. It‚Äôs so beautiful place. The staff, especially the girl named Angela is so attentive and taking good care of us during the dinner. Will come back Mombasa and will stay in Sarova and have meals at Lido. \nP/S: I wish the seafood menu would have more options, especially the seafood of Mombasa', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4923, 'HINA W', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r952344611-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Lovely atmosphere!', 'This is the open air seaside restaurant. Here the resort offers grilled dishes. Seafood is their speciality. The staff is very courteous. The food though is nothing special. It was totally bland.  Though the eatery has a serene, romantic, classy atmosphere. The sound of the sea waves, the light from the candles and the gentle breeze from the sea create a lovely ambiance.', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4924, 'Dorah549', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r934904110-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Delicious meal', 'I am not a fan of 5* restaurants. Whenever I stay a 5* star I always eat in stand alone restaurants nearby but this day we were  exhausted and short on time so we decided to eat at Lido. Jimmy was very welcoming and patient, he gave a few recommendations and in the end we were happy with the food. The food didn\'t take long and it was very delicious and fresh. We enjoyed it so much.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\", \"delivery_takeout\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4925, 'TonyL5178', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r848878908-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'A fantastic bar and restaurant with excellent staff', 'We stayed at Sarova Whitesands and used the Lido everyday.  It has great views over the Indian Ocean, great food, a great selection of drinks and excellent entertainment from local musicians.  The warm welcome, friendliness, and excellent service from the staff made our stay in Kenya truly memorable. \n Special thanks to Jimi, Sylvia, and Julia who were fantastic.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4926, 'Tracey S', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r838963970-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Birthday Dinner', 'We celebrated our friend\'s 50th birthday at Lido. The atmosphere is beautiful with seating oceanside. The food was fresh and delicious. The staff made our celebration one we will never forget. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
