(4932, 'David E', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r560588654-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Just us', 'This restaurant had a really nice atmosphere and ambiance about it. We where the only ones in the restaurant but I think that was because of the time of year. It wasn‚Äôt the tourist season. I thought the food was nice but a little bit over priced. The staff are extremely well mannered and always on hand if you need anything ', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
