(4934, 'Ecate87', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r538764308-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Dinner on the beach', 'Amazing service, we got 3 free starters while waiting for the main courses. We were all very happy about the food, my friend got a lobster, I got some delicious asian noodles and a green oriental salad. It was chilly outside but the location is wind safe.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
