(4936, 'Philip1327', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r537294681-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Tr√®s agr√©able surprise', 'Tres agreable diner dans un joli petit restaurant avec vue sur la plage. Nous y avons savour√© des crevettes g√©antes apport√©es sur un brasero . Produits de qualit√©, le  service est attentionn√© , petits amuses bouches gratuits , vin correct,  ce restaurant est une tres belle surprise. Bravo !', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(4937, 'Maxxwell7777', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r523439129-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best grilled fish', 'Very nice ambience. Enjoyed fantastic dinner near the beach and very friendly waiters. This is the best seafood restaurant i have been to.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4938, 'Micke S', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r458448973-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Simple outside and pricey food...', 'Do not let the simple outside deceive you! The menu include crab, lobster and platters, almost no fish. Seafood is almost as expensive as at the famous Tamarind! All prices are exclusive of all taxes (same story with all restaurants and bars at the hotel).\nThe food is good though but without the luxorious ambience of the Tamarind.', 3, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4939, 'Heathermwt', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r451793608-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great food and view!', 'This is one of our favorite places to eat, sit and relax! While staying at Whitesands, it was our lunch stop each day. The food was amazing! My husband always has the grilled lobster, which is the best he\'s ever had, and my son had the three grilled giant shrimp. These were huge! I loved the cajun chicken sandwich and my other son loved the cheeseburgers. While eating, it is wonderful to sit there and enjoy the beautiful breeze that comes in with the tide. We love to watch the people and goings on that happen on the beach as well. We are back in the states now, where it is cold and snowy, and I can\'t help but think about that wonderful little seafood grill.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(4940, 'Rory James DOYLE', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r437295697-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Seafood on the beach', 'Seafood restaurant on the beach. Part of Sarova Whitesands Hotel. Good service and good food. Good for business or a special occasion.', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(4941, 'Madame_Trey', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r428999870-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'To die for!', 'We were in Mombasa for a concert recently and we spent the afternoon lazing by the pool. Normally, every trip to Mombasa involves a mandatory stop at Tamarind, but laziness got the best of us.  We ordered 2 seafood platters from Lido and my jaw dropped at the delicious array of delicacies. Prawns, crab, lobster, accompanied by the world\'s best garlic butter. \n\nA chilled bottle of wine (or dawa) and salty crispy fries is the only other necessity you need. Harrison is the friendliest waiter in the world, full of jokes and super efficient.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\"]'),
(4942, 'Stavros C', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r335460976-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Fresh and well cooked sea food!', 'We thoroughly enjoyed the Rock Oysters, King Fish, Swahili Prwan Curry, and Mixed seafood salad. The beer was not cold so we had to order a bucket of ice. The service was very good but expected as we were surprisingly enough the only table in the restaurant. Major drawback was the surrounding noise due to the large screen television and neighboring karaoke night... Would recommend the restaurant to fish lovers!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4943, 'Ahmed M', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r332729025-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Lovely', 'Fantastic staff and yummmy foood...every thing was perfect... You wont regret every single penny you spend it here.. Kuddos', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(4944, 'the-hospitality-expertKE', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r282268945-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'The staff at the Lido restaurant make it a lovely experience on it\'s own. With the Food as well, it\'s a win-win.', 'The Sea food here is amazing. The ocean breeze adds to the ambience and helps with setting the mood. Most of the restaurant is dimly lit which makes it just the right place for a romantic beachfront dinner. With warm and attentive staff, it\'s an amazing place to set aside for a dinner in Mombasa.  ', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4945, 'MercieMyra1', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r282059574-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'great service', 'a great place for a romantic dinner ,great seafood second to Tamarind.\ncarry your credit card,the prices are average,service great and yes,the amazing White sands hotel rooms.Philip,keep it up.\nmiss Hersi though,but the staff still hold the same high customer service always,truly a home away from home a smile on your face and your wallet empty.good ambiance,plus the nearby bar!', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4946, 'paola p', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r254536262-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'SOLAMENTE RIDICOLI!!!!!', 'Ho scelto questo locale solo come ristorante ma purtroppo mi sono reso conto troppo tardi che in effetti non lo era afftto!!! Infatti le foto ingannano perch√© si tratta in realt√† del ristorante dell\'hotel Bamburi Beach. Non √®  stato possibile ordinare nulla ma solo scegliere le pietanze al buffet. La qualit√† era pessima ma la cosa piu assurda √® stata che non ci avevano detto che era tutto finito!!!! Erano solo le 2130!!!..risultato √® che abbiamo mangiato dei pezzi di pollo secchi e qualche verdura ormai fredda. Non andateci assolutamente perch√© lo staff non √®  stato neppure gentile infatti hanno iniziato a riordinare tutto mentre noi magiavamo....altamente sconsigliato cibo pessimo e servizio scadente...', 1, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'negative', '[\"service\"]'),
(4947, 'mombao77', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r253133155-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great holiday place world class costumer service please to visit.', 'Best of best in mombasa enjoyed myself there am looking forward visit again great Fox great place you gonna enjoy .', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"location_access\"]'),
(4948, 'bijou1985', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r240500633-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great restaurant!', 'I ve found this restaurant here at trip advisor and desided to eat here. I never regreted. Food was amazing. I have a plate of sea food. It was great! Fresh! Tasty! Before that they gave me free starters: different breads with sauces. Mostly i liked the basil with lime! It was so delicious! Have also to say couple words about service! It was very very nice. Lady, who was serving was very friendly, smilling and polite! I enjoyed my time in Lido restaurant! And definitely will recommend it to anyone! And of course next time, when will be in Mombasa will be back! Thank you! :-)', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4949, 'Azam S', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r230888776-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best Sea Food I\'ve had', 'Sea food platter is a must! The burgers are also a good choice to indulge on. Prices for meals are pretty decent. ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(4950, 'Cathy-Ngina', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r210873367-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Beautiful*', 'My boyfriend and I went for dinner at whitesands, First, it was a setup by the beach and was done amazingly beautiful and romantic. I commend Olivia for a job well done. The food was delicious and the amazing and professional service from Philip made the evening even more memorable. A big thank you to the two staff.  Will definitely be back again.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4951, 'Idris Adamjee', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r205470225-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'A wonderful experience', 'My wife and I could not decide where to for our wedding anniversary dinner. As we were driving I decide to go in to Whitesands. The Receptiom staff recommended Lido Grill and we definately not disappointed.\n\nWell set restaurant area with friendly staff. We were served by Eunice who was an amazing host all evening. It started raining at 1 point but Eunice was quick into action to move our food away and set up a nice cosy corner table for us.\n\nEverything about the food was excellent. My wife being a seafood fan had no words to describe. \n\nPricing is a bit on the higher side but worth while if you are looking for a change in eating out in Mombasa.\n\nKudos to Sarova and Lido for giving us a wonderful evening!!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4952, 'Linda I', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r200664854-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'A meal fit for the king', 'We had dinner at Lido last month, and the only way to describe it is \"The best meal I have had in my life\" & \"Service for royalty\" The chef made excellent dishes, while the two waiters who served us, Phillip & Kennedy treated us with out-of-the-world hospitality. \n\nOur heavenly meal started with salads: the shrimps cocktail & the calamari fritters. Next came the \"shot\" to cleanse our palate and stimulate our appetite. This shot was mint & cucumber. Third was the dips which were tamarind: sweet dip, chillies oil: hot dip & the savory dip, which was peanuts & coriander. Not to forget the bread of the day and the sundried tomatoes & herbed butter. \n\nThen there was the ampuse bounche which was the smoked salmon, cherry tomato & gherkins. The main courses were flavorful seafood platter: lobster, prawns, crab, calamari & kingfish. My friend & the spring chicken.\n\nAnd of course the dessert! A lovely, crispy fruit platter of apples & sweet melon & vanilla ice cream.\n\nLido also had a fine selection of wines & Kennedy recommended just the right one for us: Nederburg Cuv√©e brut, & so we wined & dined like true royalty.\n\nLido gave me the best dining experience in my life, we were totally spoiled for real. The price could be a bit on the higher side, but worth every penny!\n\nPlease do not forget to order a wine of your taste, the waiters are very knowledgeable and will recommend the right one to compliment your meal selection. \n\nI definitely recommend this little gem right by the ocean. It will not fail you. I have had first class experience!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4953, 'waterwaysGY', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r193691765-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best meal of our holiday!', 'We dined here twice for evening meals. Over the two meals my partner and i tried different dishes and was delighted with all of them. The setting is perfect as its right on top of the beach. All the staff at the lido sea food grill were very friendly and efficient, particularly Eunice, Humphrey and Phillip. Our second meal was made extra special by having a duo playing live music plus we had Phillip as our waitor who was truly exceptional with his enthusiasm, passion and general quality of service.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4954, 'Nairobi_ciku', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r186137159-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Lovely dining experience', 'I had lunch at Lido every day during my stay & i loved it. The food was always lovely accompanied by great service from Phillip. The outdoor setting is beautiful & the view was lovely. I\'ll definitely be back for more during my next visit', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4955, 'westwoodboy', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r184687895-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Over rated and over priced', 'I live 10 minutes away from Whitesands and have eaten at the Buffet restaurant on several occasions. i have read the reviews for the Lido sea Food Grill and as my partner and I had a special occasion to celebrate I decided to try it. The place I ate at bears no resemblance to the reviews on here.\nOn the good side I will agree that the setting is very good and the service provided by Phillip (the waiter) was excellent.\nThe down side was the quality of the meal and the price we were charged for it.\nMy partner ordered French Onion Soup which we had to return as it had more salt in than Onions - it was changed and the replacement one was slightly better. What is it with kenyan Chefs and salt - do they realise that if they put too little salt in you can add more - once they have put too much the dish becomes inedible as you can\'t take it out. \nMy starter a crab \'Timbale\' was average and not worth the 1000ksh cost (with Taxes).\nWe ordered Seafood Platter each as a main course and at over 4000ksh each (with Taxes) was basically extortionate vis a vis the quality.\nThe Lobster was miniscule and overcooked - the Crabs Claws were overcooked - the Kingfish Steak was overcooked, dried up and very small. The King Prawns were fine.\nI have eaten Seafood Platter at many Restaurants on the coast and this was by fat the worst in terms of value and quality. Maybe the Food and Beverage Manager should look at Tamarind or Monsoons - their quality and value put Whitesands to shame.\nThe desserts were not a lot better - over 1000ksh (with Taxes) for something very average.\nAnybody who complains about Tamarind prices should go here - they would never complain again.\nI feel that alot of the previous reviews were written by guests at the hotel who had not eaten at outside Restaurants and had something to compare with.\nOverall the quality of the meal was very poor and was exceptionally poor value for money and t was the sort I would expect from a small local Cafe a fifth of the price.', 2, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4956, 'howie100', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r179781913-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Number 1 restaurant and number 1 waitor Philip!!!', 'We ate lunch everyday here during our visit to the Whitesands, the fresh bread followed by the catch of the day is awesome!!! Our waitor Philip was Very, very, very GOOD!! He is number one waitor in Mombassa!!!!!!!!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(4957, 'car973', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r178728437-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Fish Lovers\' Heaven', 'Absolutely superb seafood platter and Philip was the perfect host. The shrimp cocktail is a meal on its own! Try it, you\'ll love it', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\"]'),
(4958, 'Natalie R', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r177928453-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Amazing', 'The service was exceptional! Our friend, server and waiter Philip made the night feel truly special. The food is amazing and, as you would expect from being next to the sea, absolutely fresh! What cannot be understated though was exceptional service, provided by Philip throughout, which tended to our every desire and made the night truly unforgettable.\n\nThank you Philip.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:48', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(4959, 'darrenmcfa', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r177675936-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Fantastic, a real gem', 'Currently enjoying my third visit in a row to lido. The quality of food here surpasses many top uk restaurants. Not only is the quality of food fantastic but the atmosphere is the best I have witnessed anywhere. The aervice is attentive from the onset and throughout. special thanks to philip the waiter sent down from the God\'s. He offered a very special and intimate service making both my wife and I very comfortable. \nFantastic place a must whilst in mombasa', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:48', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4960, 'Ivan V', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r173908759-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Fantastic, fantastic, fantastic!', 'The food was fantastic, the atmosphere was fantastic and the service.......fantastic!\nWe were made to feel at home and as it was our honeymoon we were made to feel even more special! Prince Philip was especially charming!!! \n\nBIG SMILES all round.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:48', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4961, 'Emma J', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r172811359-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Excellent food.', 'Food here was excellent fresh fish and a range of different breads and dips made and differed daily , credit to the chef . \nBeatiful location overlooking the sea made even better by the live singers. \nService by Philip was excellent very fast an helpful. \nDefinatly worth a visit . ', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:48', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4962, 'Stuart_Thomas1980', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r172394998-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Just Excellent Food', 'The food at Sarova was excellent but Lido Seafood Grill was awesome for food and service. Ate here several times and each time the food was not \"all inclusive\" but 5 star dining! \nSpecial thank you to Phillip for that extra special service that made our nights in Lido that extra special', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:48', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(4963, 'CiaoOliver', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r170651654-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Ein perfektes Dinner', 'Wir waren im \"Sarova White Sands\" Hotel in den Flitterwochen. In dem Hotel befindet sich das\n\nRestaurant. Eigentlich wollten wir beim ersten Besuch nur ein Steak und eine Suppe. Das diese \n\nBestellung in ein hervorragendes Abenddinner mit \"5\" G√§ngen endete (Snacks, Drinks, ...) wussten \n\nwir da noch nicht. Die Gerichte sind sehr fein dekoriert und geschmacklich beste Ware. Ich hatte \n\ndas Steak (medium). Vom optischen war es ein Vorzeigeprodukt wie im Lehrbuch. Geschmacklich \n\nist dieses Steak spitze gewesen. Dies kann ich jedem weiter empfehlen. Der Service ist genauso wie \n\ndas Steak gewesen. Wir waren √∂fters im Lokal und egal ob unter Tags, oder am Abend: Freundlich, \n\nzuvorkommend und auf die W√ºnsche eingehend!\n\nEine Herzlichkeit an Person ist Olivia. Wir haben sie dort als Kellnerin kennen gelernt und als \n\nFreundin verabschiedet!\n\nWenn es nicht 6.000km von uns entfernt w√§re, w√ºrden wir gerne immer wieder dort hinschauen.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:48', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4964, 'Karen R', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r168007535-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Best place for Indian Ocean Seafood!', 'I had one of the most rememberable dinners of my life last night next to the beach at Lido Seafood Grill. The Seafood Platter was scrumptious with lobster, giant prawns, grilled calamari, fish, and crab claws. The grilled parrot fish was outstanding and an unexpected treat. As we waited for everything to be prepared fresh, Phillip, our server, attentively waited our needs and continuously brought out tidbits and bread to keep our anxious appetite under control. If you are visiting Mombasa, don\'t miss this wonderful dining experience!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:48', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4965, 'Arthur M', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r167043950-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Excellent ambaince, Excellent food', 'Got to eat at the restaurant during my last trip to Mombasa and it was one of the highlights of the trip. \n\nThe view of the Indian ocean from the restaurant just sets you in the mood for a great time coupled with the excellent service from the staff. \n\nOrdered the Seafood platter which compromised of Grilled Lobster,King Prawns, King fish,calamari and Crab claws, which were all fresh from the sea and tasting like heaven.\n\nI can not recommend enough this restaurant to anyone looking to have seafood while in Mombasa', 4, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:48', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4966, 'SoCalJoy', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r166846314-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Lobster at Lido', 'After scuba diving the marine reserve & seeing the size of what Kenyan lobsters could look like, I was pleasantly surprised to see that lobster was being offered on the lunch menu at the Lido :)  My server, Olivia, informed me that I was still a bit early to order lunch (I think it was right around noon) but if I were interested in the lobster, she would be more then happy to get a beverage started for me while she put the order in.  They offered a broiled & thermidor preparation.  I chose broiled.  (Btw - They officially open at 12:30 PM. ) The OUTSTANDING beach view along with chilled carrot juice kept me entertained & next to giddy in anticipation of my Kenyan crustacean.\n\nWhen Olivia came with my order, the chef did NOT disappoint & the wait was COMPLETELY worth it!!!!   The lobster was grilled to PERFECTION, served in it\'s shell with a bowl of butter garlic on the side.  Accompanying this colorful dish was some fresh vegetables & a generous portion of mashed potatoes....Absolutely DELECTABLE!!!  Every bite was like a SYMPHONY.  I savored EVERY single bite.  To finish this Sarova Whitesands luncheon off, a trio of vanilla, strawberry & pistachio ice-cream was presented in a tall glass.  This was without a doubt the BEST lobster I have had ALL year!!!!  My compliments to Olivia & the chefs at Lido . . . Asante sana!!!!', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:48', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4967, 'Gemma R', 'Bamburi Beach', 'Lido Sea Food Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294210-d3369602-r165426100-Lido_Sea_Food_Grill-Mombasa_Coast_Province.html', 'Great setting, great food', 'We ate at this restaurant several times during our stay at the Whitesands hotel. Each time the service from the staff was exceptional. The restaurant itself looks out onto the ocean and has a unique ambience with live musicians playing on some occasions. Each course is well presented and there are always some little extras which make it such a pleasant experience. \n\nWe tried several things off the menu but our favourite item was the fillet steak which was big, tasty and delicious and also cooked to order. \n\nOverall we would recommend everyone trying the restaurant as we highly recommend it.', 5, 'Mombasa', '2025-11-24 18:35:48', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4968, 'harunani k', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r985786033-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Best Chinese food', 'Best Chinese restaurant in Kenya and may be the world too.we ordered hot and sour chicken soup,golden fried prawns,veg fried rice and beef sizzler.every dish was amazing.my kids love this restaurant and eat well here.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4969, 'KPCSRC', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r877493180-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Our favorite restaurant in Eldoret', 'We are from the US and this is our favorite Chinese Restaurant anywhere. It never disappoints. Our favorites are spring rolls and hot cashews as starters and then sizzling beef and sesame chicken for mains. Never had anything we didn‚Äôt like.\n\nThe location and entrance is a little intimidating if you are not familiar with the restaurant. Don‚Äôt let that stop you from going there.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4970, 'Tanvir Singh Sabharwal', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r780198261-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'The finest Chinese food Experience in East Africa!', 'I have been a loyal patron of Siam for many many years now and I can confirm that the quality and taste of the food is always constant and the service is always on point. \nMr Yu. and his Mrs. run the restaurant like a family business and not a commercial kitchen. \nFeel free to ask them for recommendations on what to eat, you shall not be disappointed. \nThey Chilli Garlic Prawns are the best in the country so ask for these!\nThey will always serve fresh food and will refuse to serve a dish that is not. \nIts very difficult to find such honest restaurants with a big heart.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]');
