(4971, 'harunani k', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r675767770-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Thumbs up', 'One of best chinese restaurants in kenya.soups are awesome.rest of the dishes are good too.a restaurant not to miss out for chinese food lovers', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:55', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(4972, 'Bency', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r673888517-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Chines at Eldoret', 'We went for a dinner , we wanted a change so choose to go a chines restaurant. it a small place but we get very nice chines food. we loved the beef sizzlers and white veg fried-rice.  ', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:55', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(4973, 'Portosky', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r664966599-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'The best Chinese restaurant in Eldoret ', 'Fresh food, and friendly owner but could do with a little renovation, the place is plain tho the sizzling pork is very good also the fried vegetable rice and the chicken wings. ', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:55', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4974, 'Jan-Erik N', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r614649635-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good food hard to find', 'Siam Restaurant in Eldoret is not easy to find. It is tucked away on the first floor of a quite run down commercial building in central Eldoret. Luckily they have a person with a yellow SIAM banderol standing at the sidewalk who can show you how to find the restaurant. The restaurant could do with some renovation. However menu is typical for a Chinese restaurant and the food tastes good. Nothing extraordinary, but good. If you crave to eat Chinese food and you find yourself in Eldoret, I believe you will be satisfied despite the difficulty to find the place and the somewhat rundown environment. ', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:55', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4975, 'Byron78', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r515111228-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Oasis in small town Eldoret.', 'Located upstairs in a building just opposite Zion mall which is convenient for parking.Went on a Sunday and it was packed out the weekend before elections.Found a table and orders were taken quickly.Has tom yum as a starter and it was filling and flavourful.Our mains of beef and green pepper and shredded pork came quickly too considering how busy they were.Great tasting food and fair prices.Place could do with some updating and more lighting on the stairs going down.An old establishment that keeps doing things well in small town Eldoret.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:55', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(4976, 'maldomino', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r509431653-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Awesome', 'I always look forward to eating here when traveling to Eldoret. The food is very Chinese, and it is very accurate! Sizzling beef and the Kung Pao chicken is very good.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:55', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(4977, 'Swaleh A', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r463839294-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Mr', 'Avery nice place to visit. Very delicious Chinese food n at reasonable prize st the center of eldoret near Zion mall ', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:55', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4978, 'TravelerCentralFLA', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r458705553-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Decent Chinese Food', 'We visited Siam while in Eldoret.  The menu was quite extensive and included shrimp, chicken, pork, and beef.  The Chinese tea was quite good.  The spring rolls were good with plenty of meat.  The only dish we tried that we did not care for was the sesame chicken.  The plum sauce was too sweet.  The other food was very good.  The ingredients seemed to be of a good quality and the seasonings were good.\nThe restaurant was a little dingy, but it did not seem dirty.  It was busy while we were there.  I would return.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:55', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(4979, 'Silong', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r410027814-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'relaxed exotic for eldoret level', 'The food is nothing like what you find in any other restaurant in Eldoret. \nThey always have everything on the menu...they serve everything with vinegar and onion salad which is amazing, (according to me, my brother thinks its weird. )\nI love the shrimp or chicken dishes, I\'ve never tried the pork or beef options, they have more things going on as well. \nVegans would be pleasantly accommodated too. \nThe food presentation is always amusing...little stands and candles and simmering hot plates.....sometimes huge bowls.\nAll food is prepared on order, always fresh.\nThe tables are always dressed but the linen needs an upgrade yesterday....they always give hot towels and plenty of drinking water, condiments and their fresh juice is decent. \nThey have strict operating hours so make sure to go between 9:am and 11:30 am then next session is 3pm and 11pm\nThey can host meals for up to 12 people upon reservations. the staff are friendly and swift. \nThey have oriental style decor and you would not miss to see an aquarium with funny looking/CUTE fish. Finish dining and say xiexie to owner....they will always smile back.\nif you want a quiet lunch and dont want to get out of town, definitely the place to go.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:55', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(4980, 'juzernurbhai', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r403568470-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Excellent Chinese Food', 'Best Chinese Restaurant. No one can be compared to him. Quality has been maintained for years and years. Keep it up Mr. Yu. ', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:55', 'positive', '[]'),
(4981, 'Martin Tairo', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r402738458-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Surprise', 'I did not expect to find a Chinese restaurant in Eldoret. But here I was having my fried rice and chicken and pork, perfectly done. One of those places you must visit to have lunch while in Eldoret.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:55', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(4982, 'Roopi B', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r355978519-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good Food', 'Eldoret has only this Chinese restaurant. And the food is quite good. Their services are good as well and the owner - Mr Yu ( a very friendly person ) is always around for a personal welcome.', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:55', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(4983, 'Kananu M', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r346596785-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Indian Food ', 'I went here for dinner when visiting Eldoret. Food and drinks service was slow. \n\nThis was compensated for in the price being reasonable for the huge portions served. ', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:55', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\"]'),
(4984, 'WSaula', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r339814102-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Always lovely', 'I visit this place frequently for meals. They have the best food in town, hospitable staff! True value for money! The best Chinese cuisines in Eldoret. Awesome!!', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:55', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4985, 'Asghar_khan', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r332654136-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Always been  a favourite', 'Always been a favourite, the food is excellent, with the ambience chinese. The service is commendable.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:55', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(4986, 'DeanJM', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r331460706-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Really good food & service.', 'Siam\'s always a winner. Every. Single. Time. I commend them for setting & keeping the high standards they do. Eating here is always a pleasure. \n\nTheir portions are generous. One dish is easily shared between 2 or 3 people. So you could order several different dishes & everyone at the table gets a decent serving. \n\nThe waiters are friendly & attentive. Mr. Yu (the owner) comes out to your table with a smile to ask you how the food was, & thanks you as you leave. Nice touch. \n\nThe prices are fair & very good value for money. There\'s a good range on the menu too in terms of choice. My personal favourites are the chilli prawns & the ginger-garlic fish. Both dishes are generously portioned (the fish dish is a whole tilapia) & perfectly seasoned.\n\nDefinitely 5 stars! :)', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:55', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(4987, 'BarakaFarm', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r325016756-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Chinese Food ', 'The best place to have dinner in Eldoret for over 15 years. Well prepared, delicious also for vegetarians and not to expensive. Looking for something different in Eldoret this is the place to be.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:55', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4988, 'EKamaara', 'Ronald Ngala Street, Eldoret', 'Siam Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d8737142-r322179602-Siam_Restaurant-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Graet food.', 'This place has excellent service and great food.  The staff is pleasant and efficient. Everybody seems to know their role and to do it happily as art of a team. ', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:37:55', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4989, 'harunani k', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r679382506-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Gud place for kids and alcoholics', 'Nyc place for kids as there is a playground there.ample parking.food is very okay nothin special.after 6pm children not alowed due to alcoholics.its a place i avoid eating but bring my kids to play.', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4990, 'Bency', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r673886132-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Evening at 64 Club', 'We went for a group outing with friends, we cooked our food and enjoyed spending time there singing , making fun of friends.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(4991, 'nyagoti', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r652411598-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Saturday ', 'It is a nice place, especially for families with kids. There\'s is an open air space and different kinds of spaces for different groups. The meat is nice. Especially mbuzi fry, their ugali and vegetables are well done. Also a good place as its some sort of neighborhood joint\n', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4992, 'Mayur N', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r651961145-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great Ambiance', 'This pub is situated inside Rupa Mall and has got a very rustic feel. The atmosphere is good and the crowd is also decent. This is not a club and thus no loud music like a discotheque but rather a more like a bar.\n\nThis is also one of the best joints in town for a different experience.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(4993, 'Collins Kirwa', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r639209568-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'closes early', 'visited 64 resort on a thursday,at 10pm and I was turned away, as It was closed early,closes early for a night club', 2, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'negative', '[]'),
(4994, 'neemaalim', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r603373411-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Nice place', 'Has a kids play ground with loads of slides.  Food isn\'t bad at all. And the attendants are very helpful.', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(4995, 'Myra E', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r588808167-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Nice getaway', 'It is in the outskirts of Eldoret town . it offers the perfect getaway from the hustle and confusion of the everyday life. It has a playground for children and for sport lovers that is the best place to watch a game or two and play pool table.The meals are well prepared to give you a good African taste and the employees are just lovely. The prices are slightly high but affordable however I feel it is worth the money. The Bar is well stocked from beers to wine and spirits. I enjoyed the place it was indeed a perfect gate away.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4996, 'EKamaara', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r588777761-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Nice eating place escpailly for families', 'This is a ice eating place a walking distance from Eldoret town and only a few metres away from the Kisumu-Eldoret road. The grounds are great and there are nice amenities for children especially so families with children will love it. The road immediately leading to the resort is being  tarmacked. This will greatly improve access. ', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'positive', '[\"location_access\"]'),
(4997, 'Victor K', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r550559842-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good for parties', 'I went here for a class party and the place is beautiful. The food was amazing, you should really try their Bhajia. Staff are very clean and organised. The staff also allowed us to have a bonfire party, wonderful!!!! \nThe DJ is amazing, one of the best in the country, didn\'t make us feel bored even for a second.\nThe place is also ideal for business meetings during the day, family outings too. \nI can say its also one of the best for graduation parties', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4998, 'Jerry Y', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r548026737-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great Hangout', 'What i love most about, this particular Resort, is their service as well as the food they make exemplary cuisines as well as modern fast foods. I love the ambiance as well, the air around their place is well circulated, due to trees around the resort', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(4999, 'Dan Kuto', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r538656535-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Nice  place', '64 Resort  Eldoret is one of the best place to relax  out of town.. The space makes  it ideal  for family and Bussiness  outing. The food is good  and the staff  are very friendly.  ', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5000, 'Byron78', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r523192850-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great', 'A pleasant mix of a place.It has a dining section,a cosy lounge,outside seating with bandas,a clubby section with an upstairs vip section.Needs more parking space however.Has big screens for the sports and generally a good vibe though watch out for drunk fools showing off and starting fights as happened to us once.The food too has  a great mix of a menu and choma.\n Good service and good crowd generally.Eldoret definitely needed this.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5001, 'Roopi B', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r510413390-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'AMAZING FOOD', '64 resort has amazing food. Its a family place where children have a playground as the the parents sit and have a meal. They have very friendly staff and their service is good.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5002, 'Jimenairobito', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r477034916-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Amazing indian food', 'We had a very good experience in this restaurant. The place is massive with different environments, bandas, restaurant, club, coffee, small halls, garden... Everything under one roof. The service was quite good for being upcountry and the quality of the food was superb. We love it!!', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5003, 'James G', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r462132440-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'best outdoor spot in eldoret', 'went with my girlfriend for a day out and the experience was magnificent. from the service to the entrance everyone would afford a welcoming and warm smile. I would surely not miss a visit to this lovely resort at any day.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5004, 'Yahya Abdallah A', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r454961637-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Terrible', 'Had the most terrible nyama choma ever and very slow in customer responding. Though the hotel has a nice view but failed on the dishes.', 1, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'negative', '[\"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\"]'),
