(5006, 'Lisa K', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r432016356-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great food off the grill!', 'I had a milkshake which was authentic and meat platter- very delicious and well done! The service was a bit wanting however I visited the location on a busy family day, Sunday. I would certainly recommend 64 resort to travellers. ', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5007, 'Susan M', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r419040194-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'ENTERTAINMENT AND FUN GALORE,BEST HANGOUT SPOT', 'Went on a Thursday\n night with a group of friends,the place is located out of Eldoret town so as you would expect no hustle of parking space and security is ample.\nThe place is spacious and very well aerated .\n I especially loved the setting of the high round tables they are comfortable and you enjoy your drinks and party to the fullest.\nHOWEVER the music on that day kept on being repeated i actually think they put a CD and kept on replaying is to clients all in all its a good place .', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"events_entertainment\"]'),
(5008, 'Foxychiri88', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r417084245-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Food menu needs work', 'This place is ideal for laid-back afternoon and evening drinks. However, the food menu is quite clumsy to say the least. A whole page of breakfast items, surely. There\'s really no variety at all for the palate of a foodie. Everything on there seems like a platter of grilled meats. Kindly revise your menu to include bitings and a la carte options. Had to go to Boma Inn for lunch because of this!', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5009, 'WSaula', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r415985466-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Quite cozy!', 'I have been to this resort on several occasions! The environment is cozy and quite comfortable! The food is good and the staff are professional! Nice playground for kids!', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5010, 'Martin Tairo', 'Old Nairobi Road Aka Plateau Road', '64 Resort And Sporting Club', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d10359516-r402737760-64_Resort_And_Sporting_Club-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Good location and good food', 'The ambience in this large bar and restaurant is homely. Different tiny spaces that make up the large space and a huge external space. The food was also good. I liked the alcove that even had a fireplace which was handy in this cold weather. I would definitely come back again.', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:41:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5011, 'Toka S', 'Eldoret-Nakuru Road Rupa Mall 2nd Floor', 'Zaika Lounge, Rupa\'s Mall', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d13984225-r905993177-Zaika_Lounge_Rupa_s_Mall_2nd_floor_Eldoret-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Poor food. Good music.', 'Poor food. Cockroach infested couches. Would not recommend. Lovely staff. Very helpful with recommendations. Would hope they improve on the general cleanliness of the place. Good ambience. Awesome music\nNice hangout all in all.', 2, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:45:28', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5012, 'Guylord Logedi', 'Eldoret-Nakuru Road Rupa Mall 2nd Floor', 'Zaika Lounge, Rupa\'s Mall', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d13984225-r825905988-Zaika_Lounge_Rupa_s_Mall_2nd_floor_Eldoret-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Perfect', 'The food, the service, the atmosphere, it\'s simply serene. A great place to relax and have a meal on both social, romantic and professional occasions. definitely a place to go to. ', 4, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:45:28', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5013, 'Gloria K', 'Eldoret-Nakuru Road Rupa Mall 2nd Floor', 'Zaika Lounge, Rupa\'s Mall', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d13984225-r776554700-Zaika_Lounge_Rupa_s_Mall_2nd_floor_Eldoret-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Fun', 'Such a cool place to relax and catch a drink...so cozy and calm\nTheir services are great\nHas a great view of Eldoret\'s kapsoya', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:45:28', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
