(5017, 'Love On Fire', 'Eldoret-Nakuru Road Rupa Mall 2nd Floor', 'Zaika Lounge, Rupa\'s Mall', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d13984225-r650287115-Zaika_Lounge_Rupa_s_Mall_2nd_floor_Eldoret-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', '5 STAR RESTAURANT', 'The service was so good, so comfortable. The food was delicious and healthy. Atmosphere was so serene. The best is the atmosphere.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:45:28', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5018, 'Kblessing254', 'Eldoret-Nakuru Road Rupa Mall 2nd Floor', 'Zaika Lounge, Rupa\'s Mall', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d13984225-r646036771-Zaika_Lounge_Rupa_s_Mall_2nd_floor_Eldoret-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Can do better ', 'Mmmh! The restaurant leaves me with mixed experiences every time I patronize. One visit leaves me with a wow experience while the next one leaves me with alot of disappointments. Probably the staff needs training to allow them offer uniform services. I once order for a roast chicken accompanied by roast potatoes, and to my shock I was served fried French fries and the waiter insisted that it was roast potatoes. Out of pity for her (probably they could have deducted the amount from her pay should I had declined from paying for something not consumed), I paid for the entire meal though I had consumed chicken only. The ambience and decor is superb. The place has a fusion of restaurant/club experience. Good place for a person who likes \"club like music\" but not in a crowded and electrified crowd. ', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:45:28', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5019, 'EKamaara', 'Eldoret-Nakuru Road Rupa Mall 2nd Floor', 'Zaika Lounge, Rupa\'s Mall', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d13984225-r639349770-Zaika_Lounge_Rupa_s_Mall_2nd_floor_Eldoret-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Great food and great service', 'I have been there twice, first on Valentine day for dinner and earlier this month for brunch. On both occasions i enjoyed both the food and the service. Awesome.', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:45:28', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(5020, 'nyagoti', 'Eldoret-Nakuru Road Rupa Mall 2nd Floor', 'Zaika Lounge, Rupa\'s Mall', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d13984225-r631427215-Zaika_Lounge_Rupa_s_Mall_2nd_floor_Eldoret-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Easy Saturday ', 'The place looks awesome. I really love the decor and design.. The grilled mutton tasted really good and was enough for two.. However never order the  chocolate smoothie it\'s really the worst smoothie I\'ve ever had', 3, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:45:28', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
