(5025, 'Dipankar H', 'Eldoret-Nakuru Road Rupa Mall 2nd Floor', 'Zaika Lounge, Rupa\'s Mall', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g681265-d13984225-r575185756-Zaika_Lounge_Rupa_s_Mall_2nd_floor_Eldoret-Eldoret_Rift_Valley_Province.html', 'Restaurant and bar', 'The most happening  place in  eldoret , kenya..........Good  ambiance and  affordable  food  with VIP treatment...................the restaurant  has  live dj from 7pm to 12 pm..so everyone  can experience  club night also......................', 5, 'Eldoret', '2025-11-24 18:45:28', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5026, 'Getaway14579307007', 'Mega City, Kisumu', 'Garam Masala', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d15062100-r949780962-Garam_Masala-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Amazing takeaway', 'It was just amazing. The chicken, naan and Malai kofta came in hot and I just enjoyed every bite. The portions were incredible it was worth every penny. From the packaging to the arrangement. Thank you for the treat', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:48:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(5027, 'Tom D', 'Mega City, Kisumu', 'Garam Masala', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d15062100-r885929432-Garam_Masala-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Over rated', 'So over rated. The atmosphere is nice but the food lacks real flavor. I rate it the lowest of the 5 Indian restaurants in Kisumu that I\'ve eaten at. Don\'t bother.', 3, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:48:08', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5028, 'Byron78', 'Mega City, Kisumu', 'Garam Masala', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d15062100-r843207180-Garam_Masala-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Sizzling tastebuds.', 'Open kitchen,out and inside seating.Cosy environment.Pleasant manager.Dishes are quite heavenly.Service fairly good.', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:48:08', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5029, 'mango93', 'Mega City, Kisumu', 'Garam Masala', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d15062100-r815899522-Garam_Masala-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Delicious', 'This is a must stop for dinner anytime I\'m in Kisumu. Fabulous dishes, lots of variety, and great service. ', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:48:08', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5030, 'Ms K', 'Mega City, Kisumu', 'Garam Masala', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d15062100-r780584878-Garam_Masala-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'North Indian Cuisine ', 'Perfection is what Garam Masala achieves with ALL its dishes every single times. Do your taste buds justice & pay them a visit. ', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:48:08', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(5031, 'Byron78', 'Mega City, Kisumu', 'Garam Masala', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d15062100-r739788008-Garam_Masala-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Excellence', 'Located in the Mega City compound.Warm cosy place with attentive service and an open kitchen so one can watch the chefs at work.They have seating outside too which is ideal on balmy days.\nWell planned menu and good portions results in a great experience.The paneer,tandoori wings and ribs hit the spot just right.The rice and curry dishes we ordered after eventually packed to takeaway.\nGo splurge and enjoy oneself.', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:48:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5032, 'Didier de Villiers', 'Mega City, Kisumu', 'Garam Masala', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d15062100-r728817766-Garam_Masala-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Great food and service', 'Was only in Kisumu for the weekend and a friend of mine recommended we eat at Garam Masala! She was dead on. The food was absolutely delicious. We had the Kadai Ghost and the Veg Makhanwala on the waiter\'s recommendation. Both dishes were superb and the portions generous. Our waiter (Edwin) was very quick at and attentive and gave excellent recommendations about dinner and portion sizes etc. Would happily come back to Kisumu just to eat here!', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:48:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5033, 'Fekuchand', 'Mega City, Kisumu', 'Garam Masala', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d15062100-r726331819-Garam_Masala-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Indian Restaurant ', 'Garam Masala is the only high class Indian restaurant in Kisumu, or for that matter the only restaurant of superb class and standard.\nThe menu is delicious Indian cuisine bursting with flavours; hot and mild, veg and non veg curries, the Tandoori fare on the menu is mouthwatering.\nService staff are attentive,  the ambiance is first class  Pascal the manager is a gracious host.\nI recommend this restaurant  to anyone desiring a fantastic meal experience. ', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:48:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5034, 'John S', 'Mega City, Kisumu', 'Garam Masala', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d15062100-r696050407-Garam_Masala-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'One of my must-visits', 'I work in Kisumu annually, and Garam Masala has become one of my must-visits during any stay.  I am no Indian food connoisseur but this sure seems authentic to me. The menu is reasonably comprehensive, with plenty of great options, the service is good and quick, and the prices are good. After you order, you\'ll get a dish of papadum with various sauces, then the curry dishes do come with a single naan. Drink prices are fantastic as well if you are a drinker.\n\nGaram Masala opens a little later in the evening - 6:30pm I believe, and if you\'re standing at the door you may beat the chef, but they can seat you and it doesn\'t take too long for food to be prepared.', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:48:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5035, 'Rahul Amin', 'Mega City, Kisumu', 'Garam Masala', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d15062100-r691401505-Garam_Masala-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Brilliant Food', 'All the food we ate was terrific. Best meal in Kisumu. Lollipop chicken, tandori wings, sheek kebabs were all top quality along with a few vegetarian dishes. In all the years eating out in London this was the best butter chicken I had ever eaten. ', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:48:08', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(5036, 'Brian C', 'Mega City, Kisumu', 'Garam Masala', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d15062100-r661746710-Garam_Masala-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Excellent!!', 'I attended this restaurant as part of a large group of about 25 people. ƒéespite that, the service was great and the food was excellent. I have no hesitation in highly recommending this restaurant.', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:48:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5037, 'Byron78', 'Mega City, Kisumu', 'Garam Masala', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d15062100-r615697109-Garam_Masala-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Exquisite', 'Relatively quaint new restaurant in the Mega city mall compound.Has benches in the lawn outside and comfortable seating inside opposite the open plan visible kitchen.Unique and flavorful dishes ,tikka wings and paneer were superb.Brings some much needed style and finesse to the Kisumu dining scene.', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:48:08', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5038, 'Tokatours & Safaris', 'Oginga Odinga Rd, Kisumu', 'Oriental Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214119-r637143771-Oriental_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'good for the stomach', 'As  did visited the restaurant with my clients all of us were very happy as its was good,staff are very just what i did want in the restaurant ,my clients were very as the food was very great n i would visit them again when am in Kisumu end of November with other clients too on our way to Ruma national park then to masai mara', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:50:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5039, 'hilltopfwb', 'Oginga Odinga Rd, Kisumu', 'Oriental Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214119-r635603960-Oriental_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Enjoyed our Meal', 'We brought eight adults into the restaurant and ordered three Cantonese sweet and sour chicken and one beef with Bellpepper and onions. We ordered three chicken fried rice and two of the noodles with chicken. We thoroughly enjoyed our meal and would recommend this restaurant to eat any of the Westerners traveling through Canyon at Kisumu', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:50:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5040, 'wayne y', 'Oginga Odinga Rd, Kisumu', 'Oriental Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214119-r625905073-Oriental_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Great once again!', 'We ate here again a few nights ago. The sweet and sour chicken was wonderful again!  We usually order it with delicious plain fried rice. For 8 of us, 6 adults and 2 preteens, we ordered 3 platters of chicken an 1 large and 1 small rice. We had plenty. We also ate 12 spring rolls. The service was excellent!  We got our spring rolls in maybe 10 minutes and the rest of our order within about 20 minutes. We love this place. The price is very reasonable. Thank you!', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:50:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
