(5042, 'Mayur N', 'Oginga Odinga Rd, Kisumu', 'Oriental Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214119-r555398459-Oriental_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Little China', 'This place is very authentic and one of the best or maybe only CHINESS resturant in KISUMU. The food is made fresh and service is also good. Though The prices are also reasonable as their portions are also big. Being a vegetarian I am a bit fussy about the test and environment but this place is a must when in KISUMU town. And also don\'t forget the Laughing Budda resturant in Tuffoam mall.', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:50:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5043, 'wayne y', 'Oginga Odinga Rd, Kisumu', 'Oriental Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214119-r555322025-Oriental_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Awesome Chinese Food!', 'This is a family favorite.  Their sweet and sour chicken is exceptional as are their spring rolls!  We love going here!  The service is good and the prices are reasonable.', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:50:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(5044, 'anneharmon', 'Oginga Odinga Rd, Kisumu', 'Oriental Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214119-r479677092-Oriental_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Delicious', 'Always enjoy eating here. Food served with chopsticks.\nFor a large group, we ordered early and it was ready for us.\nLike most places, everything is made from scratch after it is ordered. We have loved everything we have tried.', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:50:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5045, 'ejk632', 'Oginga Odinga Rd, Kisumu', 'Oriental Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214119-r470626536-Oriental_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Does what it says on the tin', 'Possibly my favourite restaurant in Kisumu. Went in a small group for dinner, arrived quite early when the restaurant was quite quiet. We were served very quickly and the food was hot, tasty, plentiful, and good-value. The restaurant is on one of the main streets and only a short walk from the lake.', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:50:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5046, 'Jacqueline J', 'Oginga Odinga Rd, Kisumu', 'Oriental Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214119-r416724657-Oriental_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Okay Oriental Place..', 'We ordered pork in peanut sauce and chicken teriyaki. The food was good but the meats were cut in tiny pieces which took away from the taste. The vegetable rice was great especially the portion. The ambiance is very Chinese but it could do with some revamping to reflect modern China. The service from the first waiter was so-so but a second waiter was more helpful. Overall, it was okay.\n', 3, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:50:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5047, 'Shabnam Z', 'Oginga Odinga Rd, Kisumu', 'Oriental Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214119-r398269143-Oriental_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Tasty and convenient', 'we arrived quite late the one evening and we went to the oriental. The food arrived quickly and was tasty', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:50:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"speed_wait\"]'),
(5048, 'Byron78', 'Oginga Odinga Rd, Kisumu', 'Oriental Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214119-r371848800-Oriental_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Maturing well.', 'Went for dinner on a rainy Tuesday evening,a group of 4 guys.They have seating outside though once the rain started it was necessary to move.The starters we ordered were quickly there and fairly good portions of ribs and wings.The mains of pork,beef and chicken were similarly generous which resulted in leftovers.The quality of food was very good,tasty and fresh and pleasant atmosphere and service.All in all a pleasant evening with quality food and an enjoyable evening,what else can one ask for.', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:50:29', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]');
