(5208, 'Charles A', 'Gor Mahia Rd, Kisumu', 'New Victoria Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214111-r353788532-New_Victoria_Hotel_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Good food at friendly rates.', 'I was in Kisumu and needed a hearty meal, being mindful of hygiene and affordability. New Victoria Hotel didn\'t disappoint on these. I love the simple menu of local cuisines. And the pastries are ever fresh!', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:59:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5209, 'Abby254', 'Gor Mahia Rd, Kisumu', 'New Victoria Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214111-r348063148-New_Victoria_Hotel_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Meh', 'It\'s okay for booze and chips. That\'s about it.  The pool is clean though...now I am just going to type out a sentence to get to the requisite 100 words. Meh', 3, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:59:47', 'positive', '[\"drinks\"]'),
(5210, 'Stewart F', 'Gor Mahia Rd, Kisumu', 'New Victoria Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214111-r346575969-New_Victoria_Hotel_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Something about this place', 'Like the title says I love it here. Food is simple but simply good, stay are friendly and location is great. They do the simple things well here: service quality price and comfort. Would I eat here regularly? Yes. Would I recommend? Yes. It\'s not luxury but for the price range they\'ve got everything right.', 3, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:59:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
