(5212, 'Odhiambo O', 'Gor Mahia Rd, Kisumu', 'New Victoria Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214111-r305689524-New_Victoria_Hotel_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'The local tea place', 'These guys are good with swahili dishes. I often prefer having my milk tea from this place. I highly recommend this restaurant for those who want to feel the taste of local Kenyan dishes, apart from fish.', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:59:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5213, 'Tom G', 'Gor Mahia Rd, Kisumu', 'New Victoria Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214111-r288903705-New_Victoria_Hotel_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'dinner by the pool', 'The hotel has very high standards for the area. The food is excellent and the drinks are cold. The staff are very friendly, and nothing is too much trouble for them. If you have a yearning for something that is not on the menu, they will go out of their way to bring it to you.', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:59:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5214, 'sam N N', 'Gor Mahia Rd, Kisumu', 'New Victoria Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214111-r284114980-New_Victoria_Hotel_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'I enjoyed the food.', 'Good food,Nice service and value for money.Best African Tea.Well located within the CBD.Though the space is a bit squeezed.', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:59:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5215, 'kendy696', 'Gor Mahia Rd, Kisumu', 'New Victoria Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214111-r237930172-New_Victoria_Hotel_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'tasty chicken', 'the place is very clean,has very friendly waiters and the food is worth its price.i went there to have a taste of their chicken and i have always insisted that it is the place for the customer who wants to have a taste beyond the spices', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:59:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5216, 'Alfons v', 'Gor Mahia Rd, Kisumu', 'New Victoria Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214111-r234863623-New_Victoria_Hotel_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Victoria restaurant', 'Had a late lunch / early dinner. The service was good and also the food was good al do not served at the same time. ', 3, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:59:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\"]'),
(5217, 'Margaret B', 'Gor Mahia Rd, Kisumu', 'New Victoria Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214111-r230634223-New_Victoria_Hotel_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Good Basic Food', 'Good basic food at very economical prices.  I had their special, the fish biryani, which was quite good.  It was a whole tilapia, with sauce, over rice.  It\'s a small, simple restaurant, with lots of locals eating there.', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:59:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5218, 'sally l', 'Gor Mahia Rd, Kisumu', 'New Victoria Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214111-r208141674-New_Victoria_Hotel_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Not suitable for all palates.', 'As we were near there we had a meal of hamburger type.. it was not to my liking although i saw many locals having a good feed.. i guess i still prefer chinese, or a Fresh salad.. this didn\'t suit me and the place is so small and it was a bit rundown.. But thats just my opinion..', 3, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:59:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5219, 'Maddy K', 'Gor Mahia Rd, Kisumu', 'New Victoria Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214111-r196954898-New_Victoria_Hotel_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Quaint Kisumu accommodation', 'The New Vic hotel is a little gem is Kisumu. I stayed here with a large group for several nights. By the relative standards of other establishments in the area, rooms are clean, have ceiling fans and mosquito nets are provided. The breakfast is great (the chai tea and Spanish omelette is highly recommended) and door staff are friendly. The cafe downstairs provides basic and cheap food.', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:59:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5220, 'Byron78', 'Gor Mahia Rd, Kisumu', 'New Victoria Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214111-r166056915-New_Victoria_Hotel_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Does Basics well', 'This is a restaurant located in a shopping centre smack bang in the middle of town.It is not the hotel,which is located  on Odera street in another part of town.The restaurant has the same name as the hotel.\n Its a clean basic restaurant serving the basics quiet well.There are fish,chicken,beef dishes plus the usual samosas,mandazis etc.They also have products from their bakery located at their hotel in town like chicken and beef pies,cheese pies and cakes.The service is quick,the place is clean and some of the waiters are quite attentive.The steak i had was reasonable and quite good for the cost.Its a convenient location for the courts and anything within the centre of town including Maseno Uni.It can get packed at lunch naturally though service does not suffer.\nIts an ideal place for a cheap meal', 3, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:59:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5221, 'MissTravelFiend', 'Gor Mahia Rd, Kisumu', 'New Victoria Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214111-r149479738-New_Victoria_Hotel_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Good option if you\'re in a hurry', 'If you\'ve ever visited Kenya then you will know that fast service is not a strong point in most restaurants and hotels. With this in mind, the New Victoria Hotel Restaurant is a good place for a quick breakfast or lunch or snack if you are in a hurry and want something cheap(ish). \n\nThe food is average, just normal fast-food-style stuff like chips and chicken, samosas, pies, etc. But, it\'s always really busy at lunch time, which is usually a good sign for a restaurant. \n\nThey also have things like pizza and sub sandwiches, although my advice, and this goes for most restaurants around Kisumu and in any more rural areas, would be to keep it simple and order things that you know they will be able to prepare. (So, no soups, sandwiches, pizzas, burgers, etc, as you will be disappointed).', 3, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:59:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5222, 'dudiegirl', 'Gor Mahia Rd, Kisumu', 'New Victoria Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214111-r136096075-New_Victoria_Hotel_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'basic rooms, amazing staff + great breakies!', 'I have stayed at the new victoria numerous times. The staff were always so friendly and happy, the rooms although basic were clean. Breakfast was included and good as well. as for location it\'s about a 10 min walk to the markets or a very short tuk tuk ride. all in all i recommend this for those looking for basic accommodation. ', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:59:47', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5223, 'Linda M', 'Gor Mahia Rd, Kisumu', 'New Victoria Hotel Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214111-r130122290-New_Victoria_Hotel_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'great place for breakfast', 'Center of town,  Its a good place to get a cup of coffee and hot breakfast and its pretty fast and cheap', 3, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 18:59:47', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
