(5228, 'KenyanStarfish', 'Imperial Hotel Jomo Kenyatta Highway', 'Victoria Terrace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d2050045-r437406937-Victoria_Terrace-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Good food, but the ambiance would be improved', 'This is the old imperial hotel which has very old, dated furniture. The place could do with some livening up. The service staff were a bit confused at first but warmed up and gave us excellent service through out our meal. We ordered traditional/staple food to avoid disappointment- fish, ugali (maize meal) and local vegetables. The food was prepared well, and tasted OK. ', 3, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 19:01:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5229, 'Senkumba E', 'Imperial Hotel Jomo Kenyatta Highway', 'Victoria Terrace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d2050045-r354077928-Victoria_Terrace-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Dinner at the Victoria', 'Had dinner at the Victoria,tried their fresh water fish from lake victoria,was very fresh and well prepared,staff was very polite and at our beck and call all through out our dinner', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 19:01:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\"]'),
(5230, 'Calvins O', 'Imperial Hotel Jomo Kenyatta Highway', 'Victoria Terrace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d2050045-r253723328-Victoria_Terrace-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', '\'\' Cool enough \"', 'My 30min stay at this place was not disappointing. Though I did not eat, my cold tusker was served with a lot of care and within time. Expect me back when I come to kisumu ', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 19:01:23', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5231, 'Byron78', 'Imperial Hotel Jomo Kenyatta Highway', 'Victoria Terrace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d2050045-r213282624-Victoria_Terrace-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Anachronism', 'Dropped in on a Saturday evening,only 2 other tables occupied,waited 15 mins then went to the bar to get a drink before the waiter came rushing.Left to seek a place with more of a crowd to watch a WC game.Waiter informed me,wifi ws 100/- for 15 mins.Quite ludicrous in hospitality today.Thankfully Java has opened just down the road.\n\n Putting the first experience down to a one off,arranged to meet and have coffee with colleague from the nearby courts a week later.Friendly guard welcomed us in.Service noticed us after 15 mins,truly remarkable and then 2 waiters rushed up after i went to the bar to ask for service.\n\n Suffice to say,customer service is not a gd point here notwithstanding other reviews.Tragically the service actually ruins the great  WC package for snacks and a drink which they have on offer.', 2, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 19:01:23', 'negative', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"events_entertainment\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5232, 'Andrew F', 'Imperial Hotel Jomo Kenyatta Highway', 'Victoria Terrace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d2050045-r210923496-Victoria_Terrace-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Relaxing & Quiet Drink By The Pool', 'On the sports ground side of the Imperial Hotel in the centre of town, and not beside the lake as the name might suggest, is this very pleasent and proffessionally run bar & restuarant. There is a small pool which is situated in the cool shade of the hotel buildings with umbrellaed tables around it. The staff are very efficient and polite and considering you\'re just off the main street it is nicely clean and quiet. You can access the Victoria Terrace either from the main street via a security guarded gate or through the hotel. The bar food menu has a good range of well prepared dishes. This is a nice place for couples, families or casual business meetings.', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 19:01:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5233, 'Lucas M', 'Imperial Hotel Jomo Kenyatta Highway', 'Victoria Terrace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d2050045-r205658983-Victoria_Terrace-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Very Nice', 'If you are looking for the coldest beers in Kisumu or a great Burger then this place is it ! They have a swimming pool as well for those warm days . ', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 19:01:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5234, 'lupesh', 'Imperial Hotel Jomo Kenyatta Highway', 'Victoria Terrace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d2050045-r199251531-Victoria_Terrace-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Meglio del ristorante', 'Il bar interno all\'hotel imperial che serve la piscina a parer mio e del collega che era con me serve piatti migliori che il ristorante ufficiale dell\'albergo, anche le pizze sono migliori. Il men√π √® differente, pi√π semplice, ma cucinato meglio', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 19:01:23', 'positive', '[]'),
(5235, 'Rykie H', 'Imperial Hotel Jomo Kenyatta Highway', 'Victoria Terrace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d2050045-r189948966-Victoria_Terrace-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Excellent food!', 'I visited Kenya from South Africa and stayed in Kisumu, I really enjoyed every meal at Imperial Hotel, not only was the food excellent, but the presentation and service was very great. I really highly recommend a stay at the Imperial Hotel.', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 19:01:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5236, 'hsbirgi', 'Imperial Hotel Jomo Kenyatta Highway', 'Victoria Terrace', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d2050045-r164358120-Victoria_Terrace-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Fantastic Burgers', 'My son brought these chicken burgers from Imperial Hotel, takeaway.\nFirstly, the packing was great, well organized.\nThen the quantity was filling, we were really stuffed.\nThis is a good option for a quick and large meal eat in or takeaway from the center of Kisumu.\nPrice was OK, definitely our first choice next time!\n\nThey also have a beef burger offer, I took a snapshot.', 5, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 19:01:23', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5237, 'Gary J', 'Jomo Kenyatta Highway, Imperial Hotel', 'Florence Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214122-r897309234-Florence_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Great food, love the renovation ', 'Came here with my family to celebrate my wife\'s and mine 26th anniversary.  We hadn\'t been here in years as the place was under renovation.  Love the new look!  The food was the same great offering I remember from years back.  I had the pesto chicken and it was excellent.  My wife had the steak, very tender and tasty.  All in all an excellent meal with excellent service.', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 19:03:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5238, 'VC009', 'Jomo Kenyatta Highway, Imperial Hotel', 'Florence Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214122-r385998554-Florence_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'nice family meal on sundays', 'The restaurant is one of the oldest in town. Features the traditional italian menu on sunday evenings. Decor needs to be redone as its now old and tired.', 3, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 19:03:05', 'positive', '[\"menu_variety\"]'),
(5239, 'Byron78', 'Jomo Kenyatta Highway, Imperial Hotel', 'Florence Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214122-r371852593-Florence_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Mediocre', 'Had dinner here decades ago and hope it would be of the same standard.Misplaced is the correct word to describe my optimism.The deep carpets,paintings and lovely bar are long gone.Instead a plain open space with simple tables and chairs greet one,a far cry from the past.A small menu and mediocre service added to the sadness of a limping giant heading into the abyss.The nondescript food was quickly disposed of and we made our exit.A real shame as Kisumu does need a better level of dining.', 3, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 19:03:05', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5240, 'GENEZANNO', 'Jomo Kenyatta Highway, Imperial Hotel', 'Florence Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214122-r321200333-Florence_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Extremely disappointing - why did the hotel let go the brilliant South African Chef?', 'I stayed for two nights at the renovated Imperial Hotel and the rooms were very good. However, dinner during my two night stay was just awful ( as I told the restaurant manager) and since the principal Chef from South Africa left,the restaurant is almost empty and the quality of food and presentation has seriously plummeted. I order freshly grilled Talapia from lake Victoria but got frozen and rotten fish fried up with rice. I won\'t go into details of the second nights food. Other than to say that if the hotel wants to attract residents back to the restaurant- it needs to do something urgently and dramatically,', 2, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 19:03:05', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(5241, 'frasson72', 'Jomo Kenyatta Highway, Imperial Hotel', 'Florence Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g317064-d1214122-r280952354-Florence_Restaurant-Kisumu_Nyanza_Province.html', 'Stupito', 'Ristorante interno all\'hotel Imperial, personale molto gentile, stile coloniale, cibo buono, assoluta assenza di zanzare, fattore molto importante vista la zona, prezzo un po\' al di sopra ma accettabile, accettano Amex!', 4, 'Kisumu', '2025-11-24 19:03:05', 'positive', '[]'),
