(5477, 'Daniel V', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r883617544-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'Nice place, but service‚Ä¶', 'Nice place, but definitely needs a gear up in service. We waited over 45‚Äô to get an omelette, really quite a time. Ordered water never arrived, service is low quality', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5478, 'Tish', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r878369390-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'Superb coffee and nice food/baked goods', 'We feel this is THE coffee place in Nairobi. They know coffee. And the Kilimanjaro was killer (fresh cream on it so sweet and coffee so smooth that I didn\'t need sugar - and this is the only time I can say this has happened for my sweet tooth)!  We enjoy their salads, wraps and sandwiches, but come for the coffee and baked goods. Always take home some milk bread and croissants. Owner is a very lovely and diligent lady committed to her customers and quality. Highly recommend!  Also note, it can get quite busy during weekends and even though they expanded about a year ago, it fills up. A nice place to sit and work, but come early!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5479, 'Alexey A', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r878025387-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent coffee', 'Put 5 stars for coffee - the best in Nairobi. Food was nothing special.  Place called Connect coffee Roasters on the map - don\'t confuse.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5480, 'Neel G', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r870616492-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'Rating', 'Coffee was good. Must say the Cafe Kilimjaro was good. Atmosphere is also quite good. Challenge is lack of ventilation. Almost feels as if you are grasping for fresh air.\n\nOtherwise its good.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"atmosphere\"]'),
(5481, 'E. W. Mollel', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r848504405-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'best coffee in Nairobi', 'Visited many, many coffee shops in Nairobi as my wife was on the quest for best latte she could find.  We both agreed - Connect coffee was a notch above all the rest!  Also cool ambience and good breakfasts.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5482, 'Michel P', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r826101174-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'Coffee specialist - to visit for an authentic taste of kenyan best coffee', 'This place is an upscale coffee serving all types of coffee. They also offer barista classes. Espresso was an absolute delight! I bought some coffee from them afterwards and came back to try other types of coffee.\n\nThey are located a bit outside of Westlands - in a very calm environment. You can easily chill there for hours. They provide free Wi-Fi. I also had breakfast there and it was both times delicious (pancakes and waffles). The staff is really nice. If you\'re a coffee lover - don\'t miss the chance to visit Connect Coffee.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5483, 'aidatesfa', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r777398334-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'A cup of excellence every time!', 'Having been to both branches (Riverside and Gigiri), I‚Äôm impressed by the overall consistency in the dining experience. The coffee is always fantastic and the decadent waffles are a great meal on their own, or as an indulgent dessert after a light meal. Also, the service is top notch at both branches. The staff are efficient, friendly and happy to help.\n\nThis was an afternoon very well spent.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5484, 'David A', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r761930071-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'Best coffee in town', 'Fabulous Kenya AA coffee beans, best in Kenya in my opinion.  They brew a great cup, too.  Lovely interior design, friendly staff.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5485, 'Madhulika L', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r742313988-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'Superb coffee, and a pleasant place', 'Connect Coffee is a wonderful coffee shop that specializes in Kenyan and Ethiopian coffees. Situated on the ground floor, with large windows overlooking the greenery outside (and with colourful butterfly decals decorating the windows), this is a very pleasant little place.\n\nThey offer a range of hot and cold coffees (for each, we were also asked to choose an option of coffee blend we wanted‚Äîthe Romeo, a blend of 50% each Kenyan and Ethiopian coffees, has tones of chocolate, while the Juliet is more fruity and flowery). Other beverages like tea and fruit drinks are also available. The snacks on offer include sandwiches, panini, savoury pies, waffles, and several types of doughnuts. \n\nI ordered a mocha (Romeo), along with half a strawberry waffle to share with my husband. He ordered a cappuccino (also Romeo) and our daughter had a chocolate doughnut. The coffee, true to Connect Coffee‚Äôs promise of a cup in two minutes, came very quick‚Äîand both coffees were excellent. Our waffle took much longer, but was delicious, topped with a scoop of vanilla ice cream, sliced strawberries, some whipped cream, and a drizzle of chocolate sauce. Personally, I would have liked more strawberries in a strawberry waffle (and strawberry sauce instead of chocolate), but still, it was good. Our daughter liked her chocolate doughnut so much, it disappeared before I could even ask for a tiny taste.     \n\nWe paid KSH 1350 for our coffees and desserts. Good value for money‚Äîand, given that this place offers free wifi, very convenient if you want to sit and work in a pleasant environment.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5486, 'Natasha LB', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r724170418-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'Coffee Oasis', 'Great place to work and be productive while drinking great coffee. Their food was a great bonus too.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5487, 'GGDangel', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r722047738-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'Quality Coffee', 'Their Riverside Drive branch is easily accessible via public transport from where I stay. In addition, the interior is well-lit, and the atmosphere is just the right blend for me‚Äìnot too noisy but not too quiet either. Speaking of blend, my favourite so far is Juliet brewed via Kalita. It‚Äôs the kind of fruitiness and aroma I love in a coffee. I‚Äôll be trying Romeo next.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5488, 'HowieKE', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r720245073-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'Vibe-y', 'Excellent concept, coffee and comfort. The owners are pleasant and the staff knowledgeable. Great space for meetings or to read a book while you enjoy their brews.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5489, 'fawash', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r717532234-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'perfect ambiance', 'One of the best places in Nairobi.The interior design and ambiance is perfect.I loved the fact that i could just read my book and enjoy my food without disturbance.Execellent services.Will definately recommennd to anyone who loves quiet places.Definately going back there.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5490, 'Aliyah O', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r699350128-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'Moving the bar on coffee quality in Nairobi', 'This is the first place where I have been able to get a consistently excellent cappuccino.  Feels like they are forcing all other establishments to step up their game and encouraging people interested in starting really good quality coffee places by showing them that there is a market. This would be an obvious 5-star place for me but they need to expand their lunch/snack options.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
