(5499, 'Kavita Shah', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r643109918-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'I might as well live here!', 'I go here so often they should rent me a space to sleep in! It is hands down the best place for coffee in Nairobi. The owner and staff are amazing and super friendly, and the ambience at their Riverside branch is conducive to hours of chilling. Their waffles are amazingly delicious too, but they do take some time to prepare so go with a reasonable amount of patience if those are what you might order.\n\nThey offer two blends, the Romeo and the Juliet and my preference is the less strong, more fruity, Juliet blend. \n\nIn addition, a rarity for Nairobi, both service and quality have been consistent since they opened.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
