(5501, 'Simon D', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r624873458-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'Great coffee and amazing waffles', 'A great new coffee place and for me some of the best coffee in Nairobi (and i like my coffee!!) The staff really know their stuff about the coffee too. They have two blends Romeo (Kenyan, Ugandan and Rwandan blend) and Juliet (Kenyan and Ethiopian blend). Very modern ambiance and great tech set up with power sockets everywhere and good wifi.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
