(5518, 'Lauren S', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r486383797-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'Best cup of coffee in Nairobi', 'I love this place so much. The coffee and tea is perfect. Love to study here and meet up with friends. Lots of light and cool place to hangout. Staff is also amazing!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
