(5520, 'Alykhan2014', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r475979580-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'Amazing coffee, a hidden gem', 'This place is a hidden gem run by a Korean brew master. There are several blends brewed on site and served with a selection of pastries. There is no main course food per se but there is fresh sushi available.\nThe urban interior with the roasting machine on view makes for an aromatic ambiance. \nThey have good WiFi and the location is very convenient being on riverside drive just past the Chiromo mortuary and before the Australian High Comission.\nIt\'s a hidden gem and a must try for coffee lovers!  \n', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5521, 'Summaya', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r474886663-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'Good ambience', 'The ambiance here is great and the staff are really friendly.The owners of the place interact with customers which is a good thing. The waffles and coffee are just amazing,cant wait to go back and enjoy.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5522, 'alkenya', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r468325027-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'Something Different, Something Authentic!', 'I\'m so tired of going to places where I order a hot chocolate and what I get is drinking chocolate mixed with milk. Connect Coffee has my vote - their beverages are authentic and certainly know how to elevate the flavor profile of their hot chocolate. I am not a coffee or tea drinker and so I cannot provide any feedback on that. Their food/bitings are very delicious. So far I have had their strawberry waffle (I love it!), glazed donut and chicken and leek basket. I will try their other offerings when I go next!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5523, 'dvick_or', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r455206525-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'Awesome Coffee', 'As a Coffee snob, I am always looking for that perfect cup. I had a cold brew and a delicious dense chocolate dessert that was beautifully presented. The coffee was outstanding, the service friendly, and the cafe spotless. Definitely the place to go for coffee if you are visiting Nairobi. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5524, 'Bhavesh M', 'Riverside drive road Ground floor Riverfront building', 'Connect Coffee', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d12076406-r454885225-Connect_Coffee-Nairobi.html', 'Great coffee roastery and cafe', 'I visited this place for the first time and was impressed by both the coffee and the food options. The service is nice and friendly, ambience is great and one can select the blend they want', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:35:40', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5525, 'Rick C', 'Argwings Kodhek Road Timau Plaza', 'Kesh Kesh Coffee Roastery & Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13505255-r953681175-Kesh_Kesh_Coffee_Roastery_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'The best coffee in Nairobi.', 'If you love coffee, especially pour over coffee, this is the place for you. The coffeeis prepared by a barista at your table, scale and all. The service is excellent and the food is delicious!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:37:53', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5526, 'Tamika T', 'Argwings Kodhek Road Timau Plaza', 'Kesh Kesh Coffee Roastery & Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13505255-r930011527-Kesh_Kesh_Coffee_Roastery_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Relaxing and quiet', 'I got an ethiopian vegetarian meal with coffee. Service was amazing. \nI took what I didn\'t eat home. It lasted me 2 more meals.\n\nThe coffee was amazing. In total thr price came to 2050 kenya shilling. And the place was very well kept with very friendly and accommodating staff.\n\nI went mid morning do it was nice and quiet for this time of day to chill and relax', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:37:53', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5527, 'Eric_Thered_USA', 'Argwings Kodhek Road Timau Plaza', 'Kesh Kesh Coffee Roastery & Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13505255-r903202462-Kesh_Kesh_Coffee_Roastery_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent coffee with confusing location change', 'Had this one on my list of visits before arriving in Nairobi and took an Uber there, ordered my latte before realizing I was in the wrong place.  I didn\'t quite understand the server\'s explanation but I think I was at the old location that was now called \"Afro Centric Cafe\" or something like that.  The next day, I went to the new location just the other side of the block and had some great coffee and got some ground coffee to go that I french-pressed at the hotel and it was fantastic!  I also asked if fresh beans were  available and they said, yes, they roast them right there.  I ordered 500g of beans to go but noticed the roasted date wasn\'t written on it.  When I asked when it was roasted, they said \"Maybe two weeks ago\" ... not quite the same fresh that I was hoping for but they didn\'t have any that were newer.  There was also an African woman there seated on the floor brewing some type of African coffee (Eritrean?) that was fascinating to watch.  Small location on an ally but pretty cool place with good coffee.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:37:53', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5528, 'yyy', 'Argwings Kodhek Road Timau Plaza', 'Kesh Kesh Coffee Roastery & Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13505255-r880176578-Kesh_Kesh_Coffee_Roastery_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'ABSOLUTE WORST Business in Nairobi', 'I called to pick up some coffee Beans ‚Äì I selected a 1 kg bag that was clearly marked and paid for it.  I was then told it was only 800g ‚Äì Okay whatever.\n\nI was then told that I could not have one off the shelf but they would get it.  A couple of minutes later, I was told that it would be 15 minutes.\n\nI was running late, so I said that I could not wait and could I please have my money back.  The staff just ignored me.  I asked again and again ‚Äì politely at first.   Not one of the staff did anything ‚Äì they did not even have the courtesy to answer me.\n\nThey kept me waiting until they brought the coffee ‚Äì by this time I was very angry as I have never been so badly treated by so many staff members in my life.\n\nI insisted that I get my money back and will never go back.  If they cannot even label their coffee the right weight and if that is how they treat customers, I would not be game to eat or drink there.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:37:53', 'negative', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\"]'),
(5529, 'Lisa', 'Argwings Kodhek Road Timau Plaza', 'Kesh Kesh Coffee Roastery & Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13505255-r877436864-Kesh_Kesh_Coffee_Roastery_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Great Coffee and Breakfast In Nairobi', 'Delicious, freshly roasted and brewed coffee and coffee drinks. Beautiful industrial interior and shaded garden seating. \nDelicious eggs, oatmeal, wraps and french toast were available. Friendly staff. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:37:53', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5530, 'Wanderer Traveler', 'Argwings Kodhek Road Timau Plaza', 'Kesh Kesh Coffee Roastery & Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13505255-r836522779-Kesh_Kesh_Coffee_Roastery_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Calmness', 'Wonderful experience \n\nFood was fresh \n\nStaff was attentive \n\nService for drinks were fast but for food took 15 mins, but the freshness and quality made it worth the wait. \n\nDo check this place out.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:37:53', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5531, 'Jonas F', 'Argwings Kodhek Road Timau Plaza', 'Kesh Kesh Coffee Roastery & Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13505255-r781125296-Kesh_Kesh_Coffee_Roastery_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent!!!', 'So good, I liked that they had good cakes, excellent coffee, ethiopian food and even burger. Nice and clean.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:37:53', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\"]'),
(5532, 'Anduvate', 'Argwings Kodhek Road Timau Plaza', 'Kesh Kesh Coffee Roastery & Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13505255-r743703171-Kesh_Kesh_Coffee_Roastery_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Working ', 'Great ambiance, great lighting. The service was also good. The hosting was amazing with very friendly and warm service. They also play good music and it‚Äôs a really great working environment. You could carry your laptop and move your ‚Äúoffice‚Äù to this place. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:37:53', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5533, 'Barbara S', 'Argwings Kodhek Road Timau Plaza', 'Kesh Kesh Coffee Roastery & Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13505255-r742760010-Kesh_Kesh_Coffee_Roastery_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Great coffee and Ethiopian food', 'Love the atmosphere and coffee at Kesh Kesh. Good service albeit sometimes a bit slow. Ethiopian food is good, the other dishes can be a bit boring tase wise. Great place to hang out, meet friends or have a meeting and work. ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:37:53', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5534, 'Amolo N', 'Argwings Kodhek Road Timau Plaza', 'Kesh Kesh Coffee Roastery & Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13505255-r739201520-Kesh_Kesh_Coffee_Roastery_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Good coffee but never has fresh pastries', 'Inexplicably popular Ethiopian/continental cafe with excellent coffee but terrible service and never has fresh pastries in the morning. ', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:37:53', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\"]');
