(5535, 'katet431', 'Argwings Kodhek Road Timau Plaza', 'Kesh Kesh Coffee Roastery & Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13505255-r721168474-Kesh_Kesh_Coffee_Roastery_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Lovely atmosphere and great food/drink', 'Great service, delicious coffee (including great non-dairy options) and food. Also love the decor/atmosphere.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:37:53', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5536, 'phyllism663', 'Argwings Kodhek Road Timau Plaza', 'Kesh Kesh Coffee Roastery & Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13505255-r702031215-Kesh_Kesh_Coffee_Roastery_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Lovely place to have coffee and work', 'There are many nice coffee places in Nairobi, but Kesh Kesh is great.  The place is warm, not crowded and their menu great.  I have had several meetings there in the last two months and it has been great to have them think of warming the seating area as the weather has been quite cold.  I have not seen that level of detail in any other coffee house.  Oh, and the manager remembers his clients and makes a point to say hello to everyone.  You do certainly feel at home.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:37:53', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5537, 'Lawrence W', 'Argwings Kodhek Road Timau Plaza', 'Kesh Kesh Coffee Roastery & Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13505255-r671614626-Kesh_Kesh_Coffee_Roastery_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Nice Place', 'Kesho Kesh is not just a coffee place but offers nice food options and has  good value for money. The set up is also very nice, being clean and artistically arranged.  It‚Äôs a place to return again and again. ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:37:53', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5538, 'LuciaBG', 'Argwings Kodhek Road Timau Plaza', 'Kesh Kesh Coffee Roastery & Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13505255-r661847591-Kesh_Kesh_Coffee_Roastery_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Fancy place to work in Nairobi', 'Nairobi has not so many places where you can work peacefully and in a nice entourage. Wood, good food and good juices, green and a subtile air if you decide to stay in the terrasse. I totally recommend this place if you want to work a while with your computer and avoid city\'s noise.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:37:53', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5539, 'TheRidge_Mgmt', 'Argwings Kodhek Road Timau Plaza', 'Kesh Kesh Coffee Roastery & Cafe', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d13505255-r633129039-Kesh_Kesh_Coffee_Roastery_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Great coffee!!! ', 'Was very impressed with the coffee here. Medium roast was a proper medium roast and I was pleasantly surprised. Great quality Ethiopian coffee - as per usual! ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:37:53', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
