(5583, 'Pb E', 'JW Marriott Hotel Nairobi Chiromo Lane', 'Midi Caf√© & Patisserie', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d33191110-r1022977461-Midi_Cafe_Patisserie-Nairobi.html', 'Elevated Dining, Exceptional Taste', 'I had an outstanding dining experience at JW Marriott, where I enjoyed one of the best steaks I\'ve ever had tender, flavorful, and cooked to perfection. What truly elevated the moment was the impeccable service from Stephen at Midi Caf√©. His attentiveness, warm demeanor, and professionalism made the experience feel personal and exceptional. It‚Äôs moments like these that define true hospitality', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:40:01', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5584, 'Rose C', 'JW Marriott Hotel Nairobi Chiromo Lane', 'Midi Caf√© & Patisserie', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d33191110-r1022603141-Midi_Cafe_Patisserie-Nairobi.html', 'Wonderful experience from Erick and Sally', 'We got served by Erick who is very professional  he recommend some drinks for us and we loved them.\nSally the manager also very professional and calm dispite the place being busy, the situation was contained and checked on us too. A very good place indeed to chill after a long day . We loved the soft music too, it was very relaxing.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:40:01', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5585, 'Albert K', 'JW Marriott Hotel Nairobi Chiromo Lane', 'Midi Caf√© & Patisserie', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d33191110-r1022602760-Midi_Cafe_Patisserie-Nairobi.html', 'Proffesinal and Welcoming', 'The Welcoming was Great and Top Notch. The Team is Very warm and welcoming. \n\nSpecial shoutout to Eric who was Professional and well Versed with the Menu, and His Recomendations were Great. Sally was Equally Friendly, Warm and Welcoming. \n\nDefinitely a Place to Visit and Unwind.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:40:01', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5586, 'Njeri G', 'JW Marriott Hotel Nairobi Chiromo Lane', 'Midi Caf√© & Patisserie', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d33191110-r1021314177-Midi_Cafe_Patisserie-Nairobi.html', 'Great time, great food.', 'It‚Äôs a great spot for coffee or lunch hang out. Enjoy my time there as I go often. \nI recommend their prawns, risotto, and deconstructed lasagna.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:40:01', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
