(5617, 'Michel P', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r826100362-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Laid back restaurant with good food and amazing service - check out their terrace', 'Located on the third floor of the building, the restaurant offers a mix of swahili and indian food. Prices are decent (500-1000khs for food and 200khs for a fruit juice) and service is absolutely amazing. I experienced some rude service in Nairobi but Valley Coffee Shake was absolutely top! They have a nice terrace where you can enjoy your meal in the center of the city, but far away from the crowd/stress.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5618, 'moureen l', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r784175775-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'GOOD FOOD', 'I have visited this place a few times and I have never been disappointed. They have good quality food and the standards are consistent. Would not hesitate to recommend this place as the food both affordable and quality.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5619, 'Roselyn G', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r744873543-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'They have great boardroom facility for meetings', 'Their coffee is great the location itself is somewhere popular but hidden,they have a great boardroom facility I always host my business meetings there with affordable prices. Great place to chill with friends and family and also holding parties', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
