(5621, 'Lucy Mwaura', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r692769447-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'MILKSHAKES', 'Their milkshakes are to die for.\nWe usually hold our meetings here, every once or twice in a month.\nIts a great place, not too noisy with affordable meals', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5622, 'Nats1198', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r604458658-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', ' lovely rooftop terrace ', 'We visited this place for late lunch after reading some cool reviews. We weren‚Äôt disappointed. This place has a really nice menu though no alcohol is served. It definitely serves the best milkshakes as voted by my son. We enjoyed very tasty burgers on the rooftop terrace, with some lovely fresh homemade lemonades. This place is a great place to dine, affordable prices and cool city views. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5623, 'Rosebell East Africa luxury travel', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r603174550-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Best place ever', 'I love valley coffee coz of many things, location with an open view of the city, the service is awesome the meals servings are quite big... And mouth watering.. thanks guys love the atmosphere of this place.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5624, 'Sharz P', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r597253768-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Interesting Menu', 'The ambiance is great though no views really outside.Service is a bit slow but the food is delish ....', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5625, 'wilzmuriithi', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r564795213-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Worth it', 'Quite a nice place.Service is excellent,the food is good and not overpriced.Its a bit hard to locate as its inside a building but the ambience and the tranquility that welcomes you makes you forget.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5626, 'Christine M', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r543405456-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Good Cheap Eats', 'The Valley Coffee restaurant is a lovely space in the middle of the busy CBD. It has both indoor and balcony seating. The balcony is on the 3rd floor, so it difficult to notice it from the street level and is great for taking in the hustle and bustle of the town. \n\nThe food is tasty and well priced, and the service is efficient and friendly.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5627, 'Jelimo', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r497501212-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Quiet ambiance and great food!', 'I visited it for brunch thus it wasn\'t really packed. The food was really great but I had to wait really long for it. The juices were great although the mango was a bit sour. The salsa was a bit heavy on the onions. The staff are really polite and seating area is great for one-on-one talks. I would recommend sitting on the balcony area if you find a seating area.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5628, 'Shuff2014', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r482712815-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Just one word for it .... EXCELLENT ', 'This was my second visit to the place. It has a relaxing atmosphere, fantastic food (try the pizzas) and very helpful, polite and enthusiastic staff. Definitely the place to go if you\'re in town and you need to chill. Prices are good too.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5629, 'misskinyua', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r459919861-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Girls meet-up', 'Its a quiet place within the busy town of nairobi, We sat at the balcony which offered a view of the town and we appreciated the cool breeze(as the afternoon was a hot one). We loved the food and their juice choices!!!! I recommend this mostly for meet ups, you could talk for hours as this place offers a relaxed feel.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5630, 'Jeannie18star', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r442196349-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Good food and decent prices', 'Nice place in the Centre.it was in the same street as our hotel so no problem of walking there in the eventing.you can sit outside on a balcony.the food was tasty  (we had mexican food) and the portions were huge.good value for your money!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5631, 'Valerie N', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r386951225-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Friends Hang Out Joint', 'Valley Coffee House offers a nice environment to hang out with friends and catch up with workmates after office hours.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5632, 'Charity M', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r376652865-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Great Food', 'Came here on a Sunday afternoon and sat in their balcony area for a meetup with a friend. Located on the 3rd floor, it offers a great view of Nairobi, atmosphere is superb. Had fries and fish fingers and a shake. Food came before the drink which was peculiar but a great place overall. ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5633, 'Msfoodie01', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r376409525-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Amaizing food at good prices!!', 'They have really good food and if you want to splurge a little on good food this is the place to go..ya\'ll should try the ice tea with orange juice its tah die for!!love!love!love!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5634, 'rosie320', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r340908250-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Quiet Nook in the CBD', 'Great place for a small meeting with friends over coffee. You can hide away from the hustle and bustle of CBD. The service was okay - quite reminded me of Java. Clean and airy environment.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5635, 'Haley B', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r325171897-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Nice break above busy Nairobi', 'It can be a little tricky to find because it is on the top floor of a small shopping center but once inside it doesn\'t disappoint. You will find yourself comfortable and able to relax which is a nice change from the CBD area of Nairobi. Great shakes and lovely food as well.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5636, 'Lorna M', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r319508131-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Delicious food', 'Great service and delicious food! Quiet away from the storms of Nairobi traffic and crowds! Its a great place!!!! ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5637, 'Angela W', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r308008838-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Amazing!', 'The service was fast and efficient; the waiter got exactly what I was looking for and even made some useful suggestions. The Pizza was amazing! Way over my expectations. The ambiance is so nice and homely; the color use goes a long to making it comfortable. This is one of the few places in Nairobi that I feel comfortable eating.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5638, 'Mary K', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r288449657-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent eatery in CBD', 'The patio is especially nice for hot Nairobi summers. Food was good. I\'m yet to try their coffee. I loved the cafe-like ambiance.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5639, 'AlyssaMugo', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r275207485-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Crunchy fries and a great smoothie!', 'I went for lunch around 1.15 pm. We found a good table but the place filled up really quickly, some bit of noise from the other diners. Despite this, the service is above average, and the staff will answer your questions. One manager was particularly attentive.\n\nI had a wrap which came with fries. You can always get a healthier side. Also got some veggies on the side, and the dip was really good. The strawberry smoothie was quite delicious and not too sugary for an anti-sweet tooth like me. The Vanilla shake was also great. \n\nI\'d totally go back again.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5640, 'Lillemusen', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r273407038-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Still one of my favourite places in Nairobi', 'There is a special offer on Thursdays - you can get pizzas significantly cheaper if you are taking two. They are big and yummy. Batido is still unsurpassed, though a bit expensive. You can do business here or simply enjoy on the balcony. The toilets are a bit run down and there is never any soap...', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\"]'),
(5641, 'ngarius', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r231344085-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Business meeting ambiance', 'Relaxed atmosphere, excellent for meetings or simply whipping out a portable computer and catching up with work over a latte.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5642, 'Lillemusen', 'Yalla Towers. 3rd flr, Junction of Koinange St. and Biashara St.', 'Valley Coffee Shake', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d5570668-r218185445-Valley_Coffee_Shake-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent food, excellent balcony, wifi, reasonable prices', 'We keep coming back to this place because the food is really good (similar to Java, but greater variety and larger portions). The desert menu is not that marvelous, but everything else is mouth watering. Even ordering just sides (guacamole and roasted potatoes) turns out to be a great meal. As for the juices and smoothies, do not mis batido, it is really good and allegedly they do not put any sugar in it. It is really pleasant to sit out on the balcony and enjoy the fresh air. The service can be a bit too slow sometimes, but generally it is ok. The only downside is the toilet - does not look too clean, never paper, rarely soap...', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:45:15', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5643, 'herine t', 'Off Parklands Road Ground Floor, 9 West Building, Mkungu Close', 'Bambino x Meso Kitchen & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23794120-r1039843642-Bambino_x_Meso_Kitchen_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'My experience at Bambino Restaurant', 'Everything at Bambino restaurant was amazing! From the ambience, to the service and not forgetting the sushi I ordered how good it was. I give it a 10/10 because I didn\'t have to even wait for long, it was approximately 10 minutes and the price is affordable too. I\'d highly recommend', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:48:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5644, 'Michelle W', 'Off Parklands Road Ground Floor, 9 West Building, Mkungu Close', 'Bambino x Meso Kitchen & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23794120-r1039705381-Bambino_x_Meso_Kitchen_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Highly recommend 10/10', 'Nice food nice ambience 10/10 highly recommend \nThe servers are kind and kevin made us have a good experience and made our visit comfortable as well', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:48:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5645, 'Karimi M', 'Off Parklands Road Ground Floor, 9 West Building, Mkungu Close', 'Bambino x Meso Kitchen & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23794120-r1039629452-Bambino_x_Meso_Kitchen_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Good time', 'It was first time here and Kevin gave us great service and the cheese cake was exceptional.\nThe ambience is so calm and inviting', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:48:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5646, 'Eve A', 'Off Parklands Road Ground Floor, 9 West Building, Mkungu Close', 'Bambino x Meso Kitchen & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23794120-r1039629403-Bambino_x_Meso_Kitchen_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Loveed it', 'Excellent service from Kevin - looved the food!There is a perfect view of Westlands from the restaurant. Looking forward to visiting again', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:48:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(5647, 'Joseph N', 'Off Parklands Road Ground Floor, 9 West Building, Mkungu Close', 'Bambino x Meso Kitchen & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23794120-r1039626994-Bambino_x_Meso_Kitchen_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Memorable!', 'The unlimited sushi is what brought me here and the experience was to die for!\nCollins was super helpful!\nI will definitely be back again for another round!!!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:48:54', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5648, 'Jackline W', 'Off Parklands Road Ground Floor, 9 West Building, Mkungu Close', 'Bambino x Meso Kitchen & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23794120-r1039626225-Bambino_x_Meso_Kitchen_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Of solo experiences...', 'I was looking forward to this sushi date for weeks and I am not disappointed. My favourite was the spicy tuna and fried shrimp, and my service delivered to the notch by Kelvin. He kept checking whether I was okay and even made the recommendations for me. I love it and I\'ll be back soonü•Ç it\'s solo-date friendly, and I enjoyed people watching üòÖüòÖ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:48:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5649, 'Felix O', 'Off Parklands Road Ground Floor, 9 West Building, Mkungu Close', 'Bambino x Meso Kitchen & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d23794120-r1039623310-Bambino_x_Meso_Kitchen_Bar-Nairobi.html', 'Collin', 'Good service from Collins. He entertained us a lot and made sure we had a good time. \nThe food was really hot and on time. I loved it', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:48:54', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
