(5693, 'Nick S', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r1038069805-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Tasteless and a waste of money', 'Ordered a 4 cheese pizza deliver. There was no blue cheese on the pizza,the base was not light and crispy, cheap ingredients used. Totally tasteless and will certainly not order from this vendor again.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(5694, 'Jashumati', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r1008966496-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Very disappointing.', 'Very disappointed.  Service was slow. Food was mediocre and the bill was crazy.\nWas a big fan when they were at Green house, won\'t be going back.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5695, 'Charleen Lozi', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r1008079772-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'A nice discovery in Nairobi!', 'La Terraza exceeded our expectations in a nice way executing services above expectations. We ordered salads and pasta with a bottle of Italian wine. Everything was delicious and ELIUD, our waiter, made us feel welcome and important.\nThe wine was served to perfection, slightly chilled. The salads were super fresh and the seafood and carbonara pasta were as good as being in Italy. \nThe ultimate test was if they would offer limoncello‚Ä¶and they did. All this for ksh 10k. So good value.\nStefano, the owner came, over. We talked about his cousins restaurant, KOBE in Watamu that we know well. We‚Äôve decided to put them on the same level ‚Ä¶.for now. Keep up the good work cousins!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(5696, 'Go25910660525', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r1007483333-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Recommended Italian restaurant', 'Good Italian food and authentic atmosphere. Service was fast and staff very welcoming. Recommended for Italian cuisine lovers.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5697, 'Flyer117706', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r991757516-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Italian restaurant in Nairobi', 'It‚Äôs in new location in Westlands . Tge good Sas average . Need to improve greatly on taste and presentation ( not good for photography ) it‚Äôs probably a 50 seater restaurant . Atmosphere is good . Average price pp is kshs 3000/- inc tips and wine bottle .', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5698, 'Matteo B', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r966384904-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Ottimo ristorante italiano in Kenya', 'Un ottimo ristorante. Torneremo certamente se passiamo da Nairobi.\nSi mangia molto bene, la proprietaria √® molto simpatica e presente. \nC\'√® la giusta attenzione alla qualit√† del cibo e l\'igiene. \nOpzioni semza glutine come pasta e molti piatti anche per vegetariani. \nPer essere in Kenya altissimo livello consigliato!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(5699, 'Marco M', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r930190775-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'La vera Italia a Nairobi', 'Siamo venuti a Nairobi per un torneo di tennis e ci siamo ritrovati ad un albergo a due passi da questo ristorante. Che dire‚Ä¶ una volta provato non l‚Äôabbiamo pi√π lasciato! Siamo alla quarta cena consecutiva (+ 2 pranzi) e ne avremo ancora per una settimana. Ogni giorno Stefano e Muriel ci fanno provare un piatto diverso (ogni tanto anche fuori men√π ;) facendoci sentire a veramente casa e mandandoci a dormire sempre belli pieni e felici. \nCiliegina sulla torta: le canzoni italiane di sottofondo‚Ä¶ se potessi dare 10 stelle le darei subito!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'negative', '[]');
