(5700, 'Diletta C', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r930186224-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Come stare a casa in Italia!!', 'Ristorante Italiano da 5 stelle!!! Proprietari super alla mano, √® stato come stare a casa in Italia! Cibo fresco e di alta qualit√†, servizio e personale davvero impeccabile! Che dire? Non mi aspettavo di trovare un pezzo di casa In Africa!!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'positive', '[]'),
(5701, 'Gavin D', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r914833709-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Good Italian food on Ngong Rd', 'Quite a good meal was had. Caprese and beef capaccio for starters, followed by chicken and mushroom fettuccine plus chicken limone scallopi for mains. Only red by the glass was merlot - an Italian variety would have worked better. Good vibe, excellent sunset view. Overall, I‚Äôd recommend La Terraza for fine dining in Nairobi!', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5702, 'TONINO S', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r911671219-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Cena italiana', 'Arrivato alla terrazza grazie ad un suggerimento di un‚Äôamica, sono stato accolto dalla proprietaria del ristorante come a casa sua! Immerso in una galleria d‚ÄôArte üé≠ e sapori della vera cucina italiana, una vetrina di Vini di pregio delle varie regioni italiane, tra cui Cannonau e Vermentino  di Sardegna ‚Ä¶ non facile da trovare all‚Äôestero ma soprattutto nel continente Africano. Inizio subito con un prosecco ü•Çdi ben venuto e una bruschetta per rompere la fame, a seguire spaghetto alla chitarra üçù panna e salmone üç£ una delizia dai sapori autentici cucinata da mani esperte, secondo piatto di carpaccio di pesce(smoked fish ) pi√π una tagliata di manzo rucola e grana come nelle migliori tradizioni italiane, per concludere non poteva mancare l‚Äôoriginale Tiramis√π al bicchiere servito su piatto con decorazione al cacao. La Terrazza restaurant di Nairobi ti da il piacere di vivere e assaporare gusti e sapori della vera cucina italiana, senza trascurare nessun particolare dal servizio all‚Äôigiene,  veramente impeccabile.Un grazie üôè di cuore üíñ particolare a Murriel e ao suo socio per il suo modo di ospitare e accogliere i suoi clienti nel  sentirsi a casa Italia üáÆüáπ  suggerisco e consiglio vivamente.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'negative', '[\"food\"]'),
(5703, 'Foxychiri88', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r906739526-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Very small portions', 'It was my 1st time  and being a fan of Italian cuisine, I was pretty excited to try out this restaurant in particular.\nService was fair, attentive but slow in some instances. \nThe meal was generally tasty however, that portion of tagliatelle bolognese for 1350 was a rip off. Not filling at all. And after mentioning this to the manager/owner on my way out, she literally laughed and said it was the first ever comment she had received in 5 years. No apology and no remorse. \nI would not recommend and definitely not coming back here.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5704, 'holidaylover55', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r903340316-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Never Again', 'Following a fantastic experience at this restaurant I wanted to return. Sadly that is where the fantastic experience ended.  We ordered a bottle of Prosecco and a meat and cheese platter to start. The Prosecco arrived warm. The waiter told us he would get an ice bucket and poured us two glasses of warm Prosecco. Then 10 min later he returned asking what we would like as a starter , we had already ordered it with when we ordered the Prosecco. Eventually the started arrived. For mains we ordered the gnocchi  Gorgonzola / walnuts and Red Snapper Putanesca . The pasta was good same as per our last visit. The fish however was not Red Snapper , it had an unpleasant taste and smell . Characteristic of Nile Perch. The waiter had a total lack of attention we had to refill our own drinks. I have been involved in fish exports from the Seychelles and Red Snapper is my favorite fish. My partner comes from lake Victoria and knows fish from the lake. When we confronted the waiter about the fish he just smile , when we asked him why we had to pour our own drinks and why he served warm Prosecco his reply was ‚Äú it‚Äôs cold now ‚Äú. My partner did not touch her fish. The owner of the restaurant then appeared at our table and was quite confrontational. She advised us she took offense to what we said about her fish. We suggested she try it but to no avail. On pointing out that we had to pour our own drinks and that her staff are serving warm drinks her reply ‚Äú what‚Äôs to difference hot or cold Prosecco ‚Äú. \nWe prompt asked for the bill and left two glasses of Prosecco on the table. \nThis has truly been my worst experience in a restaurant in Nairobi. \nA neighboring table of Chinese guests also did not eat the fish. Now I know why. On a Saturday evening the restaurant was also not full.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5705, 'Jeff C', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r893400569-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Great Pizza‚Ä¶.Crappy Mains', 'Awesome atmosphere.  Ordered pizza as an appetizer and it was the best pizza I‚Äôve had outside of Italy.   My wife and I both ordered Beef Filet.  Mine came out perfect but hers was way over cooked.   The steaks took 30 minutes to come to the table after ordering as well. \n\nI will return for the pizza and amazing atmosphere but will not order Mains.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5706, 'holidaylover55', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r892295927-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Perfecto', 'Had a most enjoyable dinner experience. From the time I called to make my reservation to paying my bill everything was top notch.  We started our dinner with a bottle of Prosecco and the Meat and Cheese platter. The Prosecco was excellent that it resulted in us ordering a second bottle to accompany the mains. The platter was a tasty selection of Salami , Parma Ham , Mordadella and a range of cheeses. The mini warm mandazi added a Kenyan twist to the platter. For mains we had the Walnut and Gorgonzola Gnocchi , Spaghetti Cabonara and the fried Calamari. Again all three dishes where fabulous. Finally we need our meal with Parfait and a gelato. The meal was outstanding the service excellent. We need more restaurants of this caliber in Nairobi. It‚Äôs located in Green House Mall , Ngong Road.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5707, 'Alessio', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r891561150-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Ottimo serata con mia moglie', 'Cena alla terrazza ottima , titolare molto presente e al contatto con i clienti ( fondamentale in questo lavoro ) personale gentile cibo ottimo con prezzi piu che accettabili , ambiente veramente curato ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'positive', '[]'),
(5708, 'Paul S', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r886397933-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Smoked Fish Carpaccio a great way to start', 'Wow, what a gem. \nMy fianc√© took me for a candlelight dinner and we were wowed.\nWorld class restaurant hidden away on the 4th floor of the greenhouse. \nService was top notch\nFood was delightful\nSmoked Fish Carpaccio was such a great way to start the meal. \nSteak cooked to perfection\nLight meals left us full and satisfied\n5/5 would recommend\n', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5709, 'Mr P', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r885253239-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Very Good', 'Consistently good Italian cuisine set against charming ambience and attended by excellent service. Eliud on this occasion stands out, attentive without being intrusive, witty with excellent food knowledge. Special mention to the kitchen for accommodating adjustments to a couple of the dishes due to some preferences. Overall, it was a great experience. It\'s definitely worth a first, second, and third visit ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5710, 'Kenyan Traveller', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r881998752-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Authentic Italian Cuisine', 'I have been to loads of \"Italian\" restaurants in Nairobi, possible even almost all that there are in this city, and though a couple do come close to but none of them can actually be said to be providing a genuine authentic Italian cuisine.\n\nLast night my search came to an end. In La Terrazza, I found the authentic Italian restaurant in Nairobi. Excellent food prepared with love and passion. I will definitely become a regular here.\n\nDownside - Very crowded and hence quite noisy. But then, if it\'s so good, it is but obvious that it\'ll get so crowded.\n\nRemember always to make a reservation before you go otherwise you\'ll probably miss out on a table.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5711, 'stefykenya', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r877104402-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', '....sentirsi a casa..  ', 'La terrazza di Nairobi √® meta fissa per me e mia moglie quando vogliamo mangiare italiano con la sensazione e l\'emozione di essere a casa a Roma. Posto elegante, servizio ineccepibile,un plauso particolare a Murielle e Stefano per la loro passione e professionalit√†.\nCinque stelle meritatissime, posto da non perdere', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'positive', '[]'),
(5712, 'Husker-heel', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r876763914-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Ridiculous!', 'Ridiculous. Was looking forward to trying the place. Came from 15-20 minutes away arriving at 9:20pm on a Sunday. Online says they close at 10:00pm. (TripAdvisor actually says they close at 10:30pm!). Was sat down, waiter told me to put in order as kitchen would be ‚Äúclosing soon‚Äù. Some other person, assume owner ? came by and rudely said kitchen is closed. I told him I came from far away and that their hours online say 10pm; he looked confused and said ‚Äúnooo‚Ä¶.‚Äù; he seemed super apathetic. I try and favor a lot of restaurants but clearly they don‚Äôt care for service here. Never trying again. Don‚Äôt recommend üòä. So many excellent places in Nairobi!', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'negative', '[\"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5713, 'xavierg934', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r874161020-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Belle terrasse', 'Tres beau roof top et superbe exposition de tableaux ce mois ci. . Quant au principal , les. Plats , ils sont bons . √âquipe sympathique', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'positive', '[]'),
(5714, 'Elisa', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r869304062-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Buonissimo!', 'If you want to try true Italian cuisine this is you place. Beautiful location, excellent service, amazing food.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5715, 'Martin C', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r859809339-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Terrible service and food', 'This was my 2nd visit and this time it was very busy. They couldn\'t cope with the numbers as we had to ring the doorbell to get in 5 times before opening. We then waited ages for drinks.\nI ordered beef lasagne witch was excellent last time but this time was a small portion and it was burnt on the bottom and mostly was inedible.\nI ordered a side of fries which came virtually raw and a long time after the lasagne. They then proceeded to charge me for the fries until I raised it.\nThe girl who served us was unattentive, didn\'t apologise for the burnt and raw food.\nSuch a shame as it\'s a very nice setting. It\'s quite a drive to get there and I\'m afraid I won\'t be going back', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5716, 'Maik L', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r857191073-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Closed kitchen', 'We arrived at 9:25pm just to  hear \" i\'m sorry today you\'re not lucky the kitchen is closed already\".\n\nSorry but you should publish the kitchen opening hours and thanks for wasting my time and money.\n\nIf you closing the kitchen so early like 8pm or whatever you should provide that information.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'negative', '[]'),
(5717, 'Ravina', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r854809206-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Lunch', 'I really love the service offered by the receptionist \"Hawa\"...cheers to her i also loved the food and the space', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5718, 'Louloutiti', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r838830968-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Tr√®s bonne soir√©e', 'Tr√®s bon restaurant .. tr√®s bonne ambiance . Tr√®s bon service. Belle d√©coration et tr√®s reposant .l accueil est tr√®s chaleureux √† la mode italienne.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5719, 'kathyhan1', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r833387548-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'Definitely overpriced', 'Just visited the place for a Sunday lunch (that you have to ring a bell and wait for someone to let you in, was a bit funny).\n\nFor the food side, I must say that it is definitely overpriced. Order a caprese salad which was served with 4 (four) slices of mozzarella and 4 (four) slices of tomatoes for KES 1.500.\nAlso the spaghetti putannesca was not a real generous portion.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
