(5721, 'Mickey', 'Ground Floor,The Rhapta Promenade Mall, Rhapta Road', 'La Terrazza Italian Restaurant & Caf√©', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d15360946-r828276887-La_Terrazza_Italian_Restaurant_Cafe-Nairobi.html', 'One of the top Italian restaurants in Nairobi', 'The ambience was good from the start we were welcomed very well and given a table. The restaurant has a large array of dishes available and we ordered the fillet steak and red snapper (grilled fish on the menu). It was fantastic and well cooked. I ended with a dessert of almond parfait which was top quality.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:50:47', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
