(5743, 'Tbbsotwcd', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r1039374185-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Attentive service for groups, comfortable outdoor setting', 'We were a group of 8 friends. The service was attentive and patient as we waited for a  delayed friend to arrive. The bread basket had lots of different offerings and included sweet and spicy dips. I had the crab pasta special and while the pasta was tasty and perfectly cooked the crab sauce was disappointing - shreds of it not lumps and too salty for my liking. I would not order it again. The creme br√ªl√©e was the best I\'ve ever had and I\'m a senior so I\'ve eaten a lot of it in my life. Creamy, burnt sugar top cracked perfectly and all in all was a delight to eat.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(5744, 'Jan A', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r1029012323-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'The perfect dinner', 'There were twelve of us for dinner at Matteos last night. The restaurant was quite full by the time we arrived. As usual the atmosphere was perfect and the garden and lighting looking great. Orders were taken quickly and dinner was served quickly for the whole group. I had a Porcini Pasta dish and have to say that it was undoubtedly the most delicious pasta dish that I‚Äôve ever had. Well done Matteos and I‚Äôll be back again and again to have this dish.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
