(5746, 'Elizabeth M', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r1007022452-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Authentic Italian Gem!', 'A truly special family-owned spot serving real Italian food made with love. From handmade pasta to rich, traditional sauces, every bite tastes like Italy. Warm, welcoming atmosphere and a great selection of artisanal goods to take home. Don‚Äôt miss it!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
