(5748, 'Wanjiru K', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r994242361-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Excellent food! Pretty bad service!', 'A very gorgeous restaurant with a lush green environment that perfectly compliments the cozy, authentic Italian food. There are plenty of activities for the little ones. Furthermore, there are a plethora of vegetarian, dairy-free, and gluten-free options for people, such as myself, who have these dietary restrictions. Finally, the staff were very kind and accommodating.\n\nThe service, however, could use some work:\n1. They were extremely slow. My family and I waited for nearly 40 minutes before our drinks and bread came. The food took more than an hour to arrive!\n2. They made far too many mistakes in our orders. My sister ordered a caramel ice cream and got a flan instead. My dad and sister also got rare steaks after requesting for well-done. Furthermore, for them to rectify the mistakes and fix the order would take another 20 minutes of waiting. \n3. I perceived a level of preferential treatment for... let\'s say a certain demographic of clientele (e.g., such customers would receive their food faster, drinks quicker and generally had faster service). This was very dissapointing to witness.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5749, 'Jeff K', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r988234652-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Nice Restaurant', 'Our tour guide took us here for lunch during a tour of the area. The place is large and very nice.\n\nThe menu is pretty heavy for lunch with a lot of dinner type main courses,  We had pizza which was good.  Service was also very good.\n\nWe liked the place and were glad we ate here.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5750, 'Passport12892351499', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r985146665-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Horrible food', 'Horrible food.\nNot worth the cent\nWe were 6 folks and everyone was not happy with the food.\nTasteless, not at all the VERY EXPENSIVE rates.\nThe wine was hardly a quarter of a glass.\nThe food was bland. I ordered Sirloin steak and it was horrible.\nAll my fellow guests were aghast that also their inpatabile food could be provided for such an exorbitant price.\nWe are not poor people nor are we rich folks but for the sake of calling yourselves a RESTAURANT ... You are not worthy of the title.\nRemove yourselves from the cheat that you are.\nGood folks in Kenya, Nairobi \nStay away from this abomination.\nIt\'s not worth your good taste and it\'s not worth your good money.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5751, 'Steve E', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r978379064-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'The best.', 'Probably the best restaurant for family, food, atmosphere, and just enjoyment if a night out in Nairobi. How do these guys produce meals so fast with top notch service and quality of food?', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5752, 'Bchgrlie', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r977185003-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Great food, service and ambiance', 'Amazing food, service and ambiance. We loved eating under the stars and light and the food was fantastic. We had the pizza and pasta and it was very tasty and authentic. Great wine menu. Willis, our server was fantastic. We loved our experience so much we returned a second night for dinner on our return from our safari. I really wish I lived in Nairobi, Matteo‚Äôs is that good', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5753, 'Arnie-Mc', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r968842819-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'friends get together', 'Have been to the restaurant several times and the quality of food is always on par. I have noticed over the last couple of times that a good proportion of the wines on their list are not available! Attention to detail is missing by way of the waiters coming to pour the wine when you have already started, trying to get extra glasses when a late guests arrived. Would I go back! Yes it‚Äôs a nice outdoor setting and fair prices.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\"]'),
