(5755, 'Tiffany I', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r958223433-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Amazing Italian food!', 'We asked our driver for a good Italian restaurant as soon as we landed from the Masai Mara-  he delivered!  All of our dishes were outstanding.  My son ate every bit of the filet he ordered, my gnocchi was just like what I have had in Rome.  Perfect meal!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[]'),
(5756, 'afong138', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r957379376-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Very good food, excellent service and delightful surroundings.', 'Very nice indoor/outdoor ambience. The food is very good and the servings are generous. We shared an entree, had a main each, shared a desert and finished with a Kenyan coffee and tea. The cold Tusker beer was very refreshing. The service is excellent and the staff are friendly and helpful especially Sarah who is engaging and very attentive. Sarah made our lunch extra special.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5757, 'Myrtle D', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r945476478-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Enrich flavours of Italy under the Kenya sunshine', 'Wonderful ambience at Matteo‚Äôs.  Warm welcome and excellent service.  Delicious food, with a balance of flavours and good presentations. Love the outdoor setting creating a fusion of Little Italy under the sunshine of Kenya!  We shall definitely be back!!!!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5758, 'Joy M', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r945356029-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Fantastic food and excellent service', 'The service by everyone was welcoming and warm, but mark the server did an excellent job. The food was amazing- ordered pizza. Definitely recommending this place, and will be coming back.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5759, 'Lox', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r944233721-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Overrated and overpriced', 'The ambiance in the evening is nice, but avoid the - black plastic- chairs they have at tables for two, they are very uncomfortable.\nPizzas are good, but toppings could be more generous. Main portions are fairly stingy and I loathe restaurants where you order steak and it comes with nothing at all; every side dish has to be ordered and paid for extra. A proper restaurant has a website, not just a Facebook account. There is far too much staff, all evening a bunch of them stood huddled in the corner chatting, while the manager turned a blind eye. Wine glasses are huge, but if you order wine by the glass the amount you get is minimal at a maximum price.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5760, 'Shyle M', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r942972829-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Great ambience and staff, but a few issues to be noted', 'Everything was great about the restaurant. One of the issues we had when seated outside were all the smokers surrounding us, plus the heavy smoke drifting out from the kitchen. If you suffer from asthma or any lung related issues, be weary please. The manager very kindly rescued the situation and reseated us inside.\n\nThe service was outstanding as was the attention. \n\nUnfortunately, my lasagne was not edible. It contained no pasta whatsoever, but instead, was made -up of thick layers of mozerella with very dry and bland minced meat in-between. It was a great disappointment as this was our first visit and our expectations were high.  My husband\'s ravioli was good as was our friend\'s pizza.\n\nThe ambience is great and the manager and serving staff need to be highly commended. They are professional, polite and courteous.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5761, 'DISSAPOINTED CUSTOMER', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r937740859-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'TERRIBLE!!!', 'They gave away our reservation!!! We had a reservation for 2pm and we were there at 1:53pm. They then took us to a table under a table full of leaves!!!! \n\nWaste of time!!! Went next door to Tamarind. Thank you Tamarind for showing us that class and service still exists when Matteo‚Äôs failed miserably!', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'negative', '[\"service\"]'),
(5762, 'Jeffy', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r935700981-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Brilliant lunch', 'Each of our party of four described their lunch meal as the best Italian meal that they\'d ever eaten. No further comment necessary.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[]'),
(5763, 'Sebastian M', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r934200556-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Familjelunch i sk√∂n milj√∂', 'Underbar milj√∂ och bra mat. Trevlig service. Restaurangen k√§nns som en oas mitt i stan och kan verkligen rekommenderas', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(5764, 'Maria', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r928260723-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Belissimo Italian Experience in Kenya ', 'Absolutely deeeeelicious food üòã\n Ambience is breathtaking!\n Customer Service  is excellent üëå Grazie Trizah for ensuring we got our reserved table Grazie Trevor for excellent table service well done! \n', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5765, 'Virgile', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r925124540-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Excellent food', 'Amazing ambience, food and very spacious. The parking was huge, lots of space so no issue with parking. The food was reasonably priced. It gives high end romantic restaurant..', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]');
