(5766, 'SZeru', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r905394411-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'One of the top restaurants in Nairobi', 'It‚Äôs surprising to go to a restaurant and enjoy every aspect of your experience. \nThe quality of the service, the waiters, the food, drink, ambience, pricing - even the bread and butter! \n\nFar too many restaurants in Nairobi charging more for poor food, copy/paste style and untrained service staff. \n\nThe waiters at Matteos know the menu, they can recommend wines based on your preferences and they exude polite professionalism. The food is fresh and made well, the menu is diverse and the kitchen is clearly very efficient - food arrives after a short and reasonable wait.   \n\nThe ambience is great, with open air and indoor or more private areas too. I can‚Äôt fault the place. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5767, 'in2kenya', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r887945001-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'una bella esperienza a Nairobi ', 'Un ristorante veramente bello, si mangia benissimo, location molto bella, si puo\' mangiare sia nel giardino che in interno. Varier√† di piatti italiani, ottimi. Buona la pizza. Vengo qui quando sono a Nairobi, portando anche turisti a pranzo. Sempre tutti felici . Super Mario il responsabile . Personale veramente gentile e veloce', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5768, 'Scenic34055878370', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r887334319-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Matteo\'s at Karen offers great food, wine and service', 'Our group of 10 adults went to Matteo\'s in November 2022 to celebrate a friend\'s birthday.  Fortunately, we booked as the place was crowded. The food was great as everyone enjoyed what he / she ordered. Most restaurants in Nairobi would charge a corkage for bringing your own birthday cake, even though they don\'t offer them in their menu. At Matteo\'s they allowed us to bring the cake, kept it in their fridge until it was time to serve as it was a surprise for the birthday girl. Their staff sang happy birthday and served the cake with a smile. The great quality of food, service and the well maintained garden are reasons why those who have not eaten at Matteo\'s should make an effort to dine there. Ask for Mario, the Manager.\n\nLinda from Nairobi \n\n', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5769, 'Jeff L', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r886326437-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Best Restaurant!', 'Mateo\'s is our favorite restaurant in Karen! The food and service is great! We feel like family. Mario is the best!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(5770, 'Feisal H', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r886215141-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'great Pizza and Home-made Burrata.', 'its hard to describe in my experience at Matteo Restaurant in Karen, definitely not far from Lavington- 7mins drive from Junction mall. 100% recommendation! the food was really delicious and the staff are wonderful, friendly. what is magic about the place is the atmosphere in the garden, having dinner on the full moon evening. meet the guy with the silver hair( manager) is such great team player and constantly buzzing around the client. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5771, 'Cris Trip', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r886142640-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Un ristorante delizioso nel cuore di Nairobi', 'Siamo stati a pranzo domenica. Accolti da Mario che abbiamo rivisto con molto piacere.\nUna delizia i ravioli con taleggio e tartufo nero, il palato ringrazia. \nLe pizze, ben cotte e pasta ben lievitata.\nPer dolce una buonissima creme  br√ªl√©e.\nAbbiamo conosciuto con molto piacere la Signora Loredana, la proprietaria\nUn angolo di piacere per il palato e gli occhi a Nairobi\nTorneremo sicuramente', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[]'),
(5772, 'nyangeri t', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r885425778-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Matteo\'s restaurant Karen - the best garden', 'I have visitedMatteo\'s restaurant today with my family and the food is excellent. The the receiption is above board where the waiters are friendly. This is the place to be for lunch and for dinner also. A very good service.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5773, 'Maurizio S', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r885314477-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Taste and emotional  explosion ,through very high standard Italian traditional legendary food&beverage,cousine. &Notonly', 'If you are in Nairobi for sure you can\'t miss Matteo\'s restaurant ,it is a must ! Nice spectacular nature environmental ,amazing after sunset ,and also at lunch ,everytime we are in Nairobi we stop there ,and you never have enough of it\'s incredible delicious food ,cheese , meet ,fish ,pasta , everything is super huge.The menu is various and very abundant , the wine list is superb ,the staff ,all are very welcoming ,it is like to be in a family when you start to go there more than once .They have particular researched row material ,and the Italian specialities obviously reign,it is a real experience for your taste ,and your soul .The ambient as for dinner as for lunch is perfect ,you can meet there very  very interesting people ,and cream of the Capital .Special mention to all the staff as above said ,waiters ,chef ,cookers ,and the manager Mr Mario , very professional and wizard in the art of restaurants  and leisure ,in customers care ,and welcoming .Great persons ,great place ,great food and wine !! Don\'t miss it ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5774, 'Gabriele Pirola', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r885200754-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Best italian restaurant in Nairobi', 'Stunning location with a beautiful exterior garden , You can find the best Italian restaurant in Nairobi,\nAll the dishes were cooked very well, using \nproducts imported from Italy.\nFriendly and professional staff compared to other restaurants in Nairobi.\nI am Italian and I feel home in this beautiful place. \nAbsolutely worth the visit !!!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5775, 'mirko a', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r885198007-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Lovely location ', 'Been here twice already. Lovely location with excellent Italian food. One of my favorite restaurant in Nairobi. Very recommended . ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5776, 'MATTEO C', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r885016893-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Un tocco di classe', 'Posto incantato fuori dal caos del centro di Nairobi \nAtmosfera magica in giardino e piatti deliziosi \nNon √® facile gustare la vera cucina italiana all estero ma Mario porta alti i nostri colori e il nostro gusto a tavola. Bravi !!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[]'),
(5777, 'Britney N', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r884941644-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Matteos Italian Restaurant- A must visit Restaurant', 'The best Italian Restaurant in Nairobi. Very afforable space with friendly staff. The wine swlwction is great too very wide variety to choose from. Very spacious place yet so cosy. Would highly recommend.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5778, 'Dino A', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r884914074-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Great Pizza and Wine, Lovely Atmosphere, Friendly Staff', 'I visited Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant last week and I have to say, I was blown away by their amazing pizza and wine selection. The crust was perfectly crispy and the toppings were fresh and flavorful. And let\'s talk about the wine - they have an incredible selection that perfectly complemented our meal.\n\nThe atmosphere at Matteo\'s is also very nice. It\'s cozy and intimate, with dim lighting and charming decor that made us feel right at home. The staff were so friendly and welcoming, and really went out of their way to make sure we were comfortable and had everything we needed.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5779, 'Judith W', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r884910000-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Genuine Italian cuisine in Nairobi', 'Great Italian food with beautiful ambiance. I really loved the pizzas! The service was excellent. Would recommend to all my friends and family in the Netherlands. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5780, 'Caroline P', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r884892410-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Good value, good service, cleanliness, quality food and drink', 'YOU have to go! It‚Äôs the cutest restaurant with an alfresco garden, beautiful ambience, amazing service & Excellent food!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5781, 'Giuseppe F', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r884875168-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Amazing lunch', 'Nice and beautiful place. Food is delicious and the staff is well organised.  Mario, the.manager, is professional and kind. I will go back for sure', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5782, 'Stefano460', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r884562369-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'BEST ITALIAN NAIROBI ', 'SIMPLY FANTASTIC FOOD, OWNERS VERY FRIENDLY, BY FAR BEST ITALIAN RESTAURANT IN NAIROBI, PIZZA, MEAT, AND PASTA AT TOP LEVEL ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(5783, 'Lina', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r884500194-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'A victim of their succes.', 'Sadly after a great start the restaurant became a total victim of their succes. They keep on increasing the number of tables, catering for larger and larger groups, and sadly this has completely ruined the quality of the food as well their service.\nThe waiting time can add up to 1 hour‚Ä¶ waiters forget half the order, risottos have become overcooked rice, the tuna comes frozen inside- I am afraid the list is endless over the past 3 visits.\nSo this is the end of Matteos for us and of recommending it to others.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5784, 'Vincent B', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r884496850-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Terrible experience !!! Avoid ‚Ä¶.', 'Sitting at the restaurant for 45 min now and still waiting for our food. Asked for water, still waiting, asked for bread sticks and still waiting, asked for glass of wine, still waiting. \nPut your s ‚Ä¶ together Mattheos restaurant, poor service, you can‚Äôt handle a full restaurant. \nAvoid that place over weekends !', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5785, 'olivetreecanada', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r881376203-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'lovely atmosphere, good food, good service', 'Our group of 5 had reservations on a Friday night. Reservations are recommended as there are many tables on the sprawling grounds but as far as the eye could see every one was full. There are many wait staff bustling around and the vibe is somehow both chill and relaxed yet vibrant and alive. The food was delicious, though our table agreed that the main courses were better than the desserts. You\'d be hard-pressed to find more authentic Italian pasta and pizza in Nairobi. The Italian owner could be seen greeting regular customers here and there and even picking up dropped forks and such. Very well run place.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5786, 'Bannister', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r880399156-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Una garanzia di bellezza e qualita culinaria!', 'Bellissimo come immaginavo. Aspettative confermate. Locale e giardino meraviglioso. Servizio accogliente, bella atmosfera notturna. Mario √® Mario ed il cibo ottimo. Una garanzia italiana a Nairobi. Provato pizza e fettuccine ai funghi porcini + uno special tiramisu al panettone.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\"]'),
(5787, 'si t', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r877130764-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Nice eats and setting', 'Came for dinner as it was close to where I was stopping.  The surroundings are really nice, plenty for kids to do in the grounds and the complex is pretty secure.  The restaurant area itself is massive both inside and out.  Food is really good, I recommend the beef carpaccio for a starter and spag bol was not to be sniffed at either.  Service good but it was pretty quiet so I couldn\'t comment if it was busy.  Overall a really nice place for eats, well recommended.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5788, 'Tino C', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r874470068-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Ambiente,  location e cucina: Semplicemente ok!', 'Tanto spazio, tanto verde, tanta buona cucina. Nei miei  diversi viaggi a Nairobi non c‚Äôero mai stato e me ne pento. Non esagera chi parla di questo ristorante italiano come istituzione. Dalla focaccia, alla pizza, a due risotti, al pesce alla griglia, tutto ineccepibile. Cos√¨ come il servizio. Premuroso e accurato, ma questo a Nairobi non √® infrequente, almeno nei buoni ristoranti. Non conosco il padrone, ma al cuoco, italiano, abbiamo mandato i complimenti. Spero di rimettere le gambe sotto un tavolo, all ombra di un albero rigoglioso nell‚Äôoasi che protegge dal,caos della Ngong road karen', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'negative', '[\"food\"]'),
(5789, 'CossyWombat', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r874465633-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Excellent food and service accompanied by fine wines', 'This is my favourite restaurant in Karen with consistently good food and a very wide range of good wines to choose from.  The only advice I have is to make sure you are warmly dressed if you sit outside because Karen at night can be chilly, especially if there is a breeze.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5790, 'Nina', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r870230117-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Birthday Dinner', 'The pizza was really good and so was the grilled fish. Those who had the steak thought it was a bit too charred. Our waiter looked like he had better things to do than serve us though.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(5791, 'Giovanna Ilaria V', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r867007403-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Eccezionale!', 'Mi √® stato consigliato questo ristorante per caso, in aeroporto, da una hostess che conosce i proprietari. Il posto √® veramente favoloso, un‚Äôoasi di pace nella caotica Nairobi. Il giardino √® meraviglioso, i colori e gli odori dell‚ÄôAfrica pervadono l‚Äôanima. Sono capitata con la mia famiglia il gioved√¨ sera , con la musica dal vivo, che trasforma il tutto in una location superchic! Per non parlare del cibo, forse non ho mai mangiato cos√¨ bene nemmeno in molti posti italiani. Tutto super fresco , rispettano la nostra tradizione con piatti succulenti e materie prime di qualit√†.\nUn ringraziamento speciale va al direttore Mario , molto competente , simpatico e super accogliente: insieme ai proprietari super squisiti hanno ricreato una piccola Italia nel cuore dell‚ÄôAfrica!\nGrazie di cuore\nSpero di tornare presto!\nConsigliatissimo!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"location_access\"]'),
(5792, 'LukeAndrews', 'Ngong Road Karen Road Junction, Karen', 'Matteo\'s Italian Restaurant & Bar', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g12559418-d23441650-r865095993-Matteo_s_Italian_Restaurant_Bar-Karen_Nairobi.html', 'Definitely worth a lunch trip', 'Matteos on Karen (there is also one in Naivasha) is a bit of an institution. Good Italian food set in beautiful gardens. Service was good. Recommended.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:52:22', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5793, 'Eva N', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r1039834766-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'An unexpected and lovely evening in downtown Nairobi', 'I paid an unplanned visit to this lovely restaurant. The first thing that struck me is how professional, friendly yet formal the staff all are. Dalla was attentive and her recommendations were spot on. \n\nA late seafood lunch turned into a sundowner then dessert and coffee. \n\nThe Paragon experience is one to be enjoyed by coffee lovers, connoisseurs, enthusiasts and novices alike. Baristas Kennedy and Regan were knowledgeable about coffee and very patient. The idea is to raise the profile and appreciation of coffee as a beverage to be enjoyed by all. It‚Äôs worth asking for the Paragon Experience, learn about where your coffee has been and enjoy an aromatic and smooth cuppa. \n\nA jazz band topped off my early evening crooning old Sinatra, Mathis and other tunes. I left happy and sated. \nI‚Äôll be back.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5794, 'Hans-Juergen G', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r1038955020-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Be aware, it‚Äôs a smoker‚Äôs restaurant!', 'We had a nice place next to the pool and we enjoyed excellent seafood and good service. \nThen, unfortunately, a guy entered and took a seat next to us and started smoking a cheap very bad smelling cigar. For both of us this was so unbearable that after some time, we really decided to escape from this disaster. We would have loved to enjoy another drink and order for dessert, but under these circumstances, it was fully impossible.\nSo a small thing when not taking care of can spoil the whole evening, what a big disappointment for us. \nAnd let me add it is not a cheap place. The bill was still already pretty high. \nUnder those circumstances, the place is a no go!', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5795, 'Caleb W', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r995408851-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'This food was amazing!', 'This place has extremely delicious seafood, and the crab tastes delicious! Has a fun vibe and deco, allowing you a great taste and a fun atmosphere. I went online but I felt it would be a great place to bring your friends and family. If your in Nairobi, you need to go here!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5796, 'Levi H', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r991629899-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'cozy seafood dining experience', 'This seafood spot offers a delightful dining experience with fresh catches and vibrant flavors. The ambiance is cozy, making it perfect for a night out. Service was friendly but could use a bit more attention during peak hours. Overall, a solid choice if you\'re craving some good seafood!', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5797, 'Gene S', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r990892370-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Okay', 'Overrated, over salted food, over priced restaurant. Poor making drinks.\nBut Good service and nice interior.\nOverall OK‚Ä¶', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5798, 'Barb H', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r990008243-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Lovely nightime experience', 'We had a delightful experience at Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant. Well booked earlier in the day and we were well looked after. When we arrived we were shown to our table promptly. Maria provided food service and she was well informed about the menu, made suggestions and talked to us about local experiences. We felt very well looked after arriving in Nairobi less than 24 hours earlier. We recommend Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant for a relaxing night out and good food.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5799, 'Sallie A', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r988146947-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Incredibly disappointing‚Ä¶', 'Went for New Year‚Äôs Day, absolutely terrible place, I went after hearing so many good things but was gravely disappointed. My family of 5 paid ¬£372 for the night, it started off well, good music and the first 4 starters were alright but when it came to the main seafood, my mum and aunt got a really cold plate of seafood and they no longer had enough plates so they just put all the seafood on one plate and gave us to share. An absolute mess. We paid quite a high price but the service was nowhere near the standard. The seafood was very dry and the dessert tasted very cheap. It was supposed to be a good new years but we left with a bad taste in our mouths. The singer they had to as singing super slow rnb and it was quite boring at times. Requested for a birthday song for my mum who is born new years but instead all they did was write happy birthday on a plate, meanwhile others got a birthday song', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5800, 'Jeff K', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r988115108-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Great Experience', 'My wife and I had dinner here.  I had an octopus soup and we shared a grilled seafood dish for two called the Neptune. I‚Äôve never had octopus soup before but this dish was excellent.  It was more of a bisque with small pieces of octopus.  The grilled seafood was also very good.  It offered a good assortment of seafood with an emphasis on shrimp.\n\nThey offer a decent assortment of wines but the prices by the bottle were high.  Most were $100 USD or higher.  Wine by the glass appeared to be a better value.\n\nOur primary server was Godfrey.  He was excellent - friendly and professional.\n\nPrices are high for Kenya but reasonable for the US or Europe.  We paid about $135 USD with tip, for the food, 2 beers and 2 glasses of wine.\n\nOverall, we thought that Mawimbi was an excellent choice for seafood.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5801, 'L J', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r987096319-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Great service from Jane', 'Great food and great service - especially Jane. She made sure my picky daughter was happy and full. The ambience was also beautiful.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5802, 'Wanjiru M', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r985475909-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'A great night in December', 'Maria Mutheu was phenomenal. She served us with such grace and care. I absolutely loved her service. The vibes were amazing and the food was amazing.  10/10 experience.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5803, 'Denis K', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r985268028-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Great Experience', 'Poseidon was great. The best infusion of cocktails, brain power tea and mulled wine. The environment was serene for a dinner date. Served by Godfrey.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'positive', '[\"drinks\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5804, 'Marjorie M', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r980938383-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Ambiance is the greatest highlight.', 'Cocktails 5/10\nFood 3/10\nAmbiance 11/10\nHad the Caribbean mixed plate... not worth 3,500.  Ambiance is ok perfect overall.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5805, 'Ossi', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r980615987-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Good seafood and live music', 'If you‚Äôre looking for good seafood in Nairobi, this is a solid option. A bit pricy but I think it was worth it. It‚Äôs a nice setting since there‚Äôs a swimming pool in the middle of the restaurant. There‚Äôs also live music. The band was playing some nice latin tunes - maybe the volume could‚Äôve been a little lower.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5806, 'Catherine', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r978456702-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Happy turnings', 'I had an exceptional dining experience at Mawimbi Seafood restaurant, thanks to my wonderful waitress, Maria. From the moment I sat down, she greeted me with a warm smile, making me feel comfortable right away. She took the time to explain the menu in detail and offered fantastic recommendations for the seafood dishes, which I thoroughly enjoyed.\n\nMaria was attentive without being intrusive, ensuring my glass was always full and regularly checking in on my experience. To make my birthday even more special, she and the staff sang a lovely birthday song for me, adding a delightful touch to the celebration. Her genuine care and passion for the menu truly made all the difference. I left feeling satisfied and appreciated. I highly recommend asking for Maria if you visit‚Äîshe was incredibly friendly and made my day memorable!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5807, 'JoDuNord', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r976644222-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Awsome birthday!', 'Exceptional!! Fresh food perfectly cooked. Amazing service. Special thanks to Maureen. Awsome ambiance. Live music. Special dance for my husband\'s birthday. We appreciated sooo much. All was perfect. We\'ll be back soon.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5808, 'Alicia R', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r974438342-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', '10/10', 'Everything was amazing!The vibe the food and especially our waitress JANE! 10/10.The live band was the icing on the cake .', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5809, 'Adria E', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r974437546-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Top Notch Service', 'This place was amazing and the service was spectacular! Jane really took care of us and provided a great dining experience.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5810, 'King W', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r973851845-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Birthday', 'Took my girlfriend for dinner on her birthday,we took a seafood platter Poseidon,it was a good choice by our server Maureen then boom a surprise birthday cake chocolate fondant which she also recommended for us , definitely we will be back for another birthday and I recommend it .', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5811, 'ODO O', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r973850759-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Birthday experience', 'Brought my mom for a birthday, Maureen recommended the food , the food was great,delicious to my surprise how Maureen organized the birthday with the team something that we didn‚Äôt expect. Definitely another birthday at Mawimbi', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5812, 'LorenzG933', 'Kijabe Street Longonot Place', 'Mawimbi Seafood Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d20151172-r973403962-Mawimbi_Seafood_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Great Food and Service. Try the ‚ÄûBrain power‚Äú DAWA', 'Family Of 3. We had an excellent lunch with super delicious Food and extremely friendly Service (Jane). \nCrab and Lobster at it‚Äòs best. Recommended by Matteo, the Sympathic Manager, we tried the ‚ÄûBrain power‚Äú Dawa, which was an experience Of it‚Äòs own. An Explosion Of different tastes prepared by the ‚Äûbarrista‚Äú.\nLunching at 4 pm, we had a quiet Atmosphare. In the evening probably there is a lot Of movement.\nWe will surely come back!!!!!!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:55:05', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5813, 'Stavros C', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r734730091-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Pros more than cons, but the last thing you expect is to be frustrated!!!', 'Environment and ambiance clean but not that inspiring, willingness to serve -well will give them the benefit of doubt, food cooked to perfection - complements to the Chef who knows his/her stuff, BUT:\n\nYou do NOT serve extra side dishes after the MAIN meal, that I am afraid, is a NO GO, especially when there were only two tables being served in the whole restaurant...\n\nFurthermore, we had ordered a main dish called: \'Garlic Prawns Indulgence\' as a starter, which was cooked to perfection served with an amazing sauce, but in my humble opinion, it was anything but main dish... I do not think that any adult could eat that dish as a main and feel his/her appetite fulfilled simply because the volume/weight was lacking... two few shrimps in size and weight...\n\nYou see, when you visit a fancy restaurant you expect to get a fair return, not unnecessary aggravation, I am afraid that the owners need to read carefully what the commentators advice and take relevant action. Even though I do wish to go back again to the restaurant, I am not convinced that management will take corrective action. All it takes is to just read the reviews, and one will notice a certain apathy or lack of willingness to make the extra effort to improve... At the end of the day, it is to their advantage if they listen to their customers... All this as constructive criticism...', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:56:36', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
