(5815, 'Lexar', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r723550091-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'wrong expectations', 'have seen the TV shows of owner Mr Jetwa many times and was really looking forward to finally eating in his restaurant. I expected to enjoy things he was cooking on TV, a kind \nof modern African fusion. instead we got a euro-ameri mix which could have been served anywhere. My friend ordered a steak which was advertised as amazing and perfectly matured. It was an ok steak but nothing special. I ordered a slipper lobster risotto which was brought to my table way too fast for a fresh risotto and it contained lots of cream which a real Italian risotto doesn\'t have. Lots of staff who were quite busy with themselves, cocktails were weak and watery,in short I was disappointed.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:56:36', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5816, 'Vakarathiwe', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r722016755-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Made my holiday', 'Excellent meal and perfect service. The cocktails were to die for. Loved the ambience and the meal. \nStaff could do better on sitting arrangements. Though the restaurant was not full they seated all diners in close proximity so having private conversation was near impossible.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:56:36', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5817, 'Amber D', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r711401642-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Crab tortellini!', 'Finally tried this place out and was not disappointed. The decor is nicely done and does a good job of making you forget you are right in Waiyaki Way. The menu has just enough selection for all tastes. The crab tortellini was so great. The steak was cooked just right and cut just like butter. The only thing missing from this pls e was hot towels to wipe your hands before dinner is served', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:56:36', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5818, '', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r708135462-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Boring ', 'It was a extremely boring place, very cold inside. Can‚Äôt you put some heaters during raining season to make the room warmer? Will never come back. Âú®‰∏Ä‰∏™Èõ®Â≠£ÁöÑÊòüÊúüÂ§©Êôö‰∏äÊù•Âà∞Ëøô‰∏™È§êÂéÖÔºåÊï¥‰∏™È§êÂéÖÂ∑®ÂÜ∑Êó†ÊØîÔºåËèúÂíåÊúçÂä°ÈÉΩÂæà‰∏ÄËà¨ÔºåËøôÊòØ‰∏Ä‰∏™Ë¢´TripAdvisorËøáÈ´òËØÑ‰ª∑‰∫ÜÁöÑÈ§êÂéÖ„ÄÇËøôËæàÂ≠êÂÜç‰πü‰∏ç‰ºöÊù•‰∫Ü„ÄÇ', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:56:36', 'negative', '[\"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5819, 'armantheman', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r695632930-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent food, albeit a bit pricy', 'Some of the best seafood in Nairobi, complemented by tasty red wines and a modern decor. The waiters are very attentive and knowledgable, making any visit alwaysa pleasure.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:56:36', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5820, 'Anne Sofie L', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r689000691-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Wonderful food & service!', 'I had the pleasure of having lunch at Seven, and could not be more pleased! Everything from the service to the wine and especially the food was exceptional! Shout out to James, my host - you were so kind and attentive and WAY TO GO on your recommendation on the lobster thermidor - it was amazing! Will definitely be back and recommend to anyone I know who will be in Nairobi! THANK YOU!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:56:36', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5821, 'Hez M', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r687636560-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Anniversary dinner', 'Had an awesome experience at Seven seafood while celebrating our 12th anniversary with my wife, excellent service from the staff, great food and an amazing ambience!! loved their seafood platter, delicious!!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:56:36', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5822, 'WW Traveler', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r683439439-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Very average ', 'Average service with very little attention to the customer taking in consideration the high restaurant level. Also we have ordered 500gr lobster and we got 2 small lobsters. Will not be back', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:56:36', 'negative', '[\"service\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5823, 'Beeth0veen', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r674937886-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent service, quality food and finished off with great desets', 'An overall awesome experience. Even a short journey in Nairobi is taxing. When you arrrive at a venue that then off a good variety of food, friend staff and a good menu, a blessing. The creme br√ªl√©e is awesome. A must recommend.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:56:36', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5824, 'Christie C', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r674178296-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Trendy ', 'Great restaurant and very cool vibe. Nice touch of the complimentary fish tempura bite size starter. I had the Garlic Prawn Indulgence and wow, super tasty but extremely rich and hard to finish. Menu stated queen prawns but they were more like shrimp.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:56:36', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5825, 'Jos√©', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r673854015-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Nairobi at its best', 'it is not my first time here but what I really enjoy in a restaurant is the continuity of food and service quality. Again a wonderful dinner with a excellent note for the wine recommended by staff', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:56:36', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5826, 'Menaka M', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r670396414-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Dinner at Seven Seafood and Grill', 'This place was honestly quite a disappointment. We‚Äôd read rave reviews, and decided to eat there at our one night in Nairobi.\nNot sure whether the chef was off his game that night, or whether the seafood was just not fresh, given we‚Äôd eaten there on Easter Monday, at the very end of a four day weekend in Kenya.\nWe ordered the ocean platter, which was quite honestly a lot of food, and had it been good, we would‚Äôve loved the quantity, but given how it was, it was just more food to waste.\nThe calamari was too chewy, the lobster was so tough that we couldn‚Äôt get chunks of it out of the shell.\nThe octopus was bland, and had no real taste.\nThe only redeeming factor on the platter  was the prawn. \nWe were really disappointed, especially since we had high expectations of this meal.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:56:36', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5827, 'matheka', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r667000182-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Ambience and Service', 'The service was amazing!!! The waiters are really good at explaining the different meals and giving recommendations. The food was 5-star!!!! Just amazing.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:56:36', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(5828, 'Dan W', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r664556717-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Great food and excellent service', 'Rented out the private room for a group of 27 people. The service was top notch and the food was great! Would highly recommend if you like seafood and are staying in the area', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:56:36', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5829, 'Alsacienne', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r646741652-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'DELICIOUS!', 'This is a high-end restaurant with excellent seafood and innovative ideas of what to do with fish meat and vegetables.   Portion size is good, hot food is hot, cold food is cold and the service exemplary.\n\nThe bill might raise your eyebrows if you\'re not prepared for it, but get the credit card out and relax.   It will be excellent value for money and leave a very good impression.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:56:36', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5830, 'wanjikuk63', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r641959588-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'AMAZING!', 'The food is out of this world really. I initially thought it was overpriced but it was worth every single penny. We had the seafood platter for two which was more than enough. The flavours were sooo mindblowing and the wine selection is pretty good! I have also never had such good cabbage my goodness. The butternut and spinach side was also really good. Our waiter was really nice and helfpul and gave excellent recommendations. Was quite impressed with how well he knew the menu. Such an amazing place for a special dinner to take a special someone. :)', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:56:36', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5831, 'Ziad H', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r641588380-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Awesome seafood speciality', 'Place quite ambient just perfect for dining. Ordered seafood platter for two was more than enough. Service and waiters very friendly. Had 2 alcoholic drinks and 2 coffees bill came to $100 price on the high side but it was worth for a 1 off.  \nCool classy place and diners.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:56:36', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5832, 'Neil S', 'ABC Place Waiyaki Way', 'Seven Seafood & Grill', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1986396-r641530195-Seven_Seafood_Grill-Nairobi.html', 'Under-whelming', 'A fine dining restaurant in Nairobi, pleasant setting, well furnished restaurant.  A nice ceviche to start with, although not a lot on the plate given it was very thin shavings.  Mains were a Singapore crab, a much too spicy spider crab, completely swamped in an indian spice mix rather than a light Singapore chilli, overwhelming the crab meat.  The prawn masala used very small prawns and I would have expected a creamier flavour. The desert was delicious.  Wine was overpriced for what was a fairly cheap and common bottle.  Overall, food could have been better to justify status and price.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:56:36', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]');
