(5833, 'Mrbillone', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r1033187347-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'The best as always.', 'The best as always. I absolutely love this place and have since visiting 2021. The food is outstanding along with the service and atmosphere.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5834, 'Zinma O', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r1030963602-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'I have no notes!', 'I have never had a bad experience every time I have gone to Open House; whether im Karen or Parklands. The food is very sumptuous and it arrives fast! The stafd are friendly and very quick on their feet! \n\nAlways a pleasure going there.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5835, 'Anon', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r1022015452-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Delicious Indian food served by welcoming staff', 'We had a wonderful lunch at Open House. It\'s a lovely Indian restaurant in Nairobi with an extensive menu. We loved the Tawa Chicken so much that we ended up ordering two portions of it. The staff is attentive and service is lightning fast! Would love to be back some day.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5836, 'Vicky T', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r1004240750-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Wonderful Palak Paneer', 'Writhing was great including the service. I was disappointed that they had no samosas.  But other than that, it was great!', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5837, 'Axel', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r995362687-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'The best chilli paneer', 'I never miss a chance to visit my favourite Indian restaurant when in Nairobi . \nThe chilli paneer with extra crispy ginger on top is a must try', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(5838, 'Sebastian T', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r995262242-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Great place for Indian food', 'Excellent food, flavorful dishes, friendly staff, generous portions.  Great wines too.  Easy reach in the city.  Happy to come back here', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5839, 'Bipin J', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r988626114-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Great ambience, service and food. However, disappointed with final billing honesty.', 'Today had lunch at Open House, Parklands Road, Nairobi.\nGreat service and food.\nEnjoyed the dishes ordered for pax of eight.\nTotal Bill Kes27,500/-.\nFood & service 4.3‚≠ê\nBilling 2.5 ‚≠êüò°\n\nHowever, the restaurant cheated on some drinksü•É which were added to the Bill and only realised when checking the bill at home \nDon\'t understand why most restaurants do the dishonesty ü´£ \nRather disappointed with such cheating from Restaurants.‚ùå‚õîüö´', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5840, 'Thomas D', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r987333781-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Easily among the best  - if not the best - Indian restaurant in Nairobi', 'Top Indian food - with even a great house wine to accompany it. Furthermore, this restaurant is not as expensive compared to the other ones! Highly recommended.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5841, 'JP', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r984469147-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Great Indian restaurant worth trying ', 'Fantastic experience at Open House, the service was impeccable, the food bursting with authentic flavours, and the convenience of the undercover car park made the visit even better.\nOutstanding dishes: Chilli Paneer, Corn Masala and the fried ginger is worth trying and will clear the sinuses!\nOnly complaint is the food can be very spicy even after we asked for mild.\n Highly recommend a visit.\n\n', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5842, 'Sioux M', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r982661896-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Perfect Paneer!', 'We were visiting for work from South Africa and a friend had recommended Open House. It\'s in a shopping centre but once you enter, the ambience is lovely. The service was attentive and our waitron was highly informed about the dishes. I had the paneer, which was delicious. As with everywhere in Kenya, the alcohol is expensive (except for local Tuskers), but the exceptional quality of the food meant I will certainly return to this spot next time I am in town.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5843, 'Directors PA', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r961684721-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'APPRECIATION', 'We were there on Tuesday for dinner and were indeed very impressed with the ambience, the cleanliness and warm welcome accorded to us.   \n\nThe staff are very friendly and cordial.\n\nIndeed, Open House has the best of the best Indian cuisine not only in Nairobi, Kenya but around the world with excellent consistency and wonderful staff. \n\nKeep it up...   Truly appreciate.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5844, 'Little_Summers', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r960860844-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent Indian cuisine', 'Excellent Indian cuisine, guaranteed by the fact that the restaurant was full with Indians. Not the menu we are used to in Europe, but everything we tasted was wonderful, flavourful and as spicy (or not spicy) as requested. We had the garlic chicken, the mutton sheekh kebab, the chicken dahiwala, the methi mutton along plain and garlic nan and we enjoyed every bite. Definitely worth the visit.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5845, 'Yantrip', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r953706572-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Unpleasant food, unloved vibe and aggressive service', 'Very baffled by the other reviews and even more so considering Nairobi has a well established community of Asian background. Whenever I see a very extensive menu it is always a red flag - can they really cook so many dishes well and that should have been our hint to leave immediately. Table was sticky so felt a bit dirty and overall the decor looks very tired. \n\nFood was very bland and reminded me more of a poor quality UK Indian takeaway. Don‚Äôt order the Goan fish curry - poor quality fish and watery tasteless gravy. Other dishes did not taste freshly prepared with the only exception being the chilli paneer. Condiments were tasteless and watery and popadoms not included. We left a large proportion of the food and overall it was one of those meals that you want to quickly get the taste out of your mouth. \n\nService started ok but when asked if we enjoyed our meal, I said fish curry was poor and simply ignored. There was a very aggressive attempt to get a service charge added and again my comment that we didn‚Äôt enjoy our meal so didn‚Äôt want to pay a service charge ( which is discretionary!) was simply ignored. As we were leaving the owner simply stared at us, unsmilingly and not bothered if we enjoyed our meal. Worst meal on this visit to Nairobi and one of the worst ever - we have been visiting for many years. Honestly completely baffled how others think this is a great restaurant - it does a disservice to the rich flavour traditions of Indian cuisine', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5846, 'vijay v', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r952448396-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'HOrrible and Stale food', 'The food I was served was stale food with bacteria - I got food poisoning after having their food - I ordered their DABELI and the bread was stale with bacteria and fungus in it - I immediately vomited it as it was a disgusting feeling. The restaurant acknowledged the poor quality of bread from their vendor and said it was old stock. I was refunded 200 KSH.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'negative', '[\"food\"]'),
(5847, 'Directors PA', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r945800778-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'APPRECIATION', 'As usual, this is the excellent restaurant with the best of the best cuisine in Nairobi.   \n\nWe greatly appreciated and enjoyed the mouth-watering food and services by the staff spearheaded by Victor, Fred and the entire team. \n\nCongratulations and keep it up always. \n\nThanking you,', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(5848, 'JP', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r943871174-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'An institution in Nairobi!', 'Excellent food, nice ambience and friendly and attentive staff, a great experience overall and would highly recommend.\n\nLittle touches:\nUndercover secure parking\nHand towels provided prior to your meal\nWell appointed table service', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5849, 'Jose M', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r939154444-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Bland and weird ', 'Went for dinner after reading the amazing reviews. May be vegetarian dishes are not there area of strength. Ordered a Malai kofta, spicy. It was anything but Malai Kofta. Quite bland. Forget being spicy it was lower than mild. May be their other dishes are good. But I had very forgettable dinne', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5850, 'Directors PA', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r934985581-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'APPRECIATION', 'We were there yesterday evening.   \nFrankly speaking, the name should be changed from Open House to Full House as it was really full with excellent services. \n\nWe appreciate the excellent services by \"Mrefu\" and Dan.   It was also great to meet Vanch, Anilbhai, Victor and all the other staff.\n\nThe food was delicious and truly world class. \n\nCongratulations for the excellent work.  Keep it up...\n\nRegards,\n\nMAYUR SHAH', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(5851, 'IndianTravellerGuy', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r934862611-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Disappointed!!', 'Once used to be a very good place .. now taste is comparable to any third grade eatery. Very disappointed with the food quality.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5852, 'Alok Jolly', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r929844511-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Africa !!!  Dinner in the dark continent.. amongst almost fellow Indians ‚Ä¶.  but with a sting !!', 'What began as a long-shot discussion amongst family to someday go on an African Safari turned rapidly into reality when things evolved and tickets were purchased.  All of a sudden, a group of 6 of us were going.  For real !!\n\nAll reservations for travel and stay in Kenya and Tanzania were arranged as an all-inclusive package by our tour operator.  Our first night‚Äôs stay on arrival in Nairobi was at Movenpick.  For dinner that night, we were taken to this Indian restaurant ---  because we were Indians ?  From America ??   Or because the restaurant was then at their old location, near our hotel ?\n\nWell.. fatal error, as Indians from everywhere do not have to behave and act as from India.  We do like Indian food and have a lot at home (which is why I do not like going out for Indian meals) but I was looking for more of a local food experience..  Kenyan barbecue would have been the right ticket.\n\nAnyhow:  the food looked great and tasted good, but was overspiced ! ‚Ä¶even though we asked for mild spices.  It left me with indigestion for the rest of my 13-day trip in Kenya and Tanzania‚Ä¶  not good, trip planners !!', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"delivery_takeout\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5853, 'Shemina S', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r928336556-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Open house', 'Good food.\nGood service \nLifts available \nParking a bit if an issue in the basement. \nVery tasty sweet dishes,  loved the ras malai', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(5854, '1854', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r925452490-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Excellente soir√©e', 'Nous avons din√© au restaurant en famille pour un anniversaire. Les plats indiens sont vari√©s et d√©licieux. Le service est souriant et attentif. \nUne tr√®s bonne soir√©e\nIl faut juste savoir que le restaurant se trouve au 1er √©tage d‚Äôun mall, accessible par ascenceur.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(5855, 'Directors PA', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r924136409-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'APPRECIATION ', 'We were there yesterday in celebration of my wife\'s belated birthday. \n\nThe staff, spearheaded by Victor, Fred, Sehej, Vansh and most importantly Anilbhai made us feel appreciated and at home.\nThey welcomed us so well and accorded us excellent services. \n\nThe menu was mouth-watering and the best of the best.    Indeed, I must say, open house has the best cuisine in the world. \n\nKeep it up. \n\nOpen House Juu....\n', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5856, 'YoJat', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r920153558-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Not great, not bad, a normal Indian restaurant', 'Had dinner here following recommendations. But it wasn\'t anything special, not great, not bad, just a normal restaurant. Food was ok.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\"]'),
(5857, 'jbez2015', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r920069060-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Fabulous Dining', 'My colleague and I went to this restaurant and were pleasantly surprised.  The food is absolutely fantastic and the waiters are well trained.  Our waiter, Alfonds, was brilliant.  We can highly recommend this restaurant.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5858, 'Mr P', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r893946000-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Tasty fare, unpretentious setting ', 'A long-time favourite of mine ever from their previous location. Tasty Indian cuisine, decently priced and great portion sizes. Ever smiling and friendly servers complement the efforts of the kitchen staff. The restaurant is a bit dated, but that notwithstanding still a favourite ', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5859, 'Chuckycharlie', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r887961875-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent, tasty Indian food.', 'Excellent Indian restaurant, delicious food, great service and keen prices. I took a while to decide which Indian to go to and very glad I chose this. Don‚Äôt be out off by it‚Äôs location upstairs in a mall, it‚Äôs definitely worth a visit. Pleasant surroundings, attentive service.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5860, 'Shariffa Bholla', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r875533356-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Dinnner', 'Third time food poisoning. No courtesy of the Manager to call and ask even though we reported it. My son was taken in emergency.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(5861, 'Directors PA', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r875268322-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent service', 'On behalf of Mr. Sundip and my family, I would like to congratulate Open House restaurant for the excellent services accorded to us on Saturday.  \nThe food was world class and par with the Indian restaurants - one of the best. \n\nThe staff spearheaded by:  Fred, Victor, Vansh, Sehej among others did an excellent job. \n\nThe ambience is excellent.   \n\nCongratulations to Anilbhai, one of the co-founders of Open House Restaurant.  We surely miss the Legendary Mathew who left this world a couple of years ago. \n\nKeep up the excellent work.   In our opinion, it is not Open House but Full House. \n\nKind regards,', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5862, 'Aage F', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r874714691-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent Meal', 'We had a late lunch visit to the restaurant. Met by helpfull and great staff and topped with an excellent tasty meal. Maybe one of the very best meals had in Nairobi. The restaurant environment is also relaxed and calm.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5863, 'Shariffa', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r874435974-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Dinner', 'We have been to open house several times but the last three times unfortunately some of us have had food poisoning.The last time we ordered prawns and chicken and a family member landed up in emergency.Sadly when I spoke to the Manager I was told call us when he is better and will send u a free meal!Like we really needed a free meal.Not once did he call to ask how he was doing.We found out later that there was a problem in the chickens and this partucular time the prawns had not been deveined properly. After talking to several people we now learn that there have been a lot of cases of food poisoinkngafter eating here.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(5864, 'Directors PA', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r860064927-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent service', 'We were at the Open House restaurant with our special VIP guests from the USA - a doctor and a business consultant. \n\nAnilbhai, Fred, Aly, Victor, the chefs and all other staff accorded us excellent services that we all enjoyed so much.  \n\nThe ambience was excellent and the meals:  the main and the bitings were mouth-watering.\n\nIndeed, the guests said that indeed, this is the best restaurant and they will for sure be back. \nThe family members were also very impressed - brilliant services.\n\nKeep it up..... \n\nKenya Juu....\n\nAsanteni Sana and keep up the excellent services.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"service\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5865, 'Rozafa', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r849599100-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Great food and service', 'Dinner was great, my chicken tikka masala was good but lacked being more spicy. Next time I will tell them extra hot. The wine was great and the service attentive and timely. Great atmosphere', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5866, 'DGWanderer25', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r847459414-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Decent Indian food. Snacks stand out, and they have Casatta !!', 'We went for a dinner with a big group.\n\nOrdered a lot of snacks. Most of those were decent. Paneer Tikka and Chilli Paneer was best. I would avoid any deep fried snacks if you are coming from India.\n\nIn main course, turbo naan is unique. Must try.\n\nThe highlight was dessert as I could find Casatta, which is a type of ice cream sandwich. Relived my childhood memories as it is not easy to get.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5867, 'mark c', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r845541529-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Poor value for money', 'BE AWARE. PRICES SHOWN DO NOT INCLUDE VAT AND SERVICE CHARGE.\nALSO A Beer IS 5$. Manager just laughed when i questioned it. SO check prices befire ordering.\nPortion size is small for the price. Overall poor value for money', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"portion_size\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5868, 'smwelu', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r844173572-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Great food, great ambience', 'I liked the ambience and food. A bit of a wait especially in the evenings as the place can get crowded. It has several restaurants and sitting is limited. A great place to hang out with friends.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5869, 'RichWilx', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r843357459-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Great food.', 'We came here on a Saturday lunchtime and the restaurant was bustling.  Service here is fast and attentive. \n\nThe star here is the food.  Authentic and delicious, cooked quickly and with care, every dish was supremely good.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\"]'),
(5870, 'BVFO', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r841437059-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Evening meal on June 4', 'Most delicious vegetarian meal we‚Äôve had during our trip to Nairobi. We had vegetable Tikka Masala and vegetable Malai Kofta with Rice and garlic Naan.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(5871, 'Janak URPL', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r834180640-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Horrible experience', 'Made a reservation for 7 pax for the 10th April 2022 for Dinner. Arrived sharp at 7.30pm and were shown to the table. The menus were brought and we ordered the drink\'s. Waited for the drinks but we weren‚Äôt served until after complaining to the Manager, who reasoned that they were understaffed!!! He wasn‚Äôt apologetic.\nThe starters came before the drinks and were served without serving spoons. The garlic chips were raw!! The Biryani was bland. This place is not worth it.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5872, 'Tish', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r824650149-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent Indian food', 'The new location is much more open and roomy. It was very quiet when we went, but service was very good, and food excellent as always. We consider this one of the best Indian restaurants in Nairobi.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5873, 'Aaron p', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r823988005-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Great place ', 'Best place with great food , Must try Indian cuisine. Overall it was a great experience, would suggest anyone to go there. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5874, 'Scott M', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r813507751-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Great place', 'Great place all around.  Service, food, location, etc.  It‚Äôs now in a new location, with plenty of parking in a brand new building.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\"]'),
