(5876, 'Pesh AB', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r806209807-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Superb', 'The menu has lots of options so we asked our waiter to recommend some things within our preference for us. We were not disappointed! The service was absolutely attentive, friendly and professional. We have found our spot for Indian food in Nairobi.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5877, 'msafirimbili', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r795263827-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Wonderful new location! ', 'The food has always been very tasty, and authentic. Been going for years. \nDelicious ginger chicken wings, and also  the other dishes.\nSo glad they moved, airy and bright, and decor greatly improved. The last place was dingy. Sorry Open hse! ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5878, 'Will Stephens', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r789196099-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'EXCELLENT TAKEAWAY', 'I did not go to this restaurant but had food delivered to a hotel\n\nThe delivery was on time. The dishes were truly excellent.The prawn curry in particular,also egg biryani and Chicken tikka.\nThere was so much tasty food it kept me going for three days.All packaged well and presented.\nHats off to the chefs\nYou certainly know your trade.\nWell done', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"speed_wait\", \"delivery_takeout\"]'),
(5879, 'africanman_840', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r782452415-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Another superb visit', 'I just ate at Open House Restaurant for the first time in years, and have to say that I was as favorably impressed as I have ever been. The food and service were both excellent. Furthermore, the menu is quite extensive and offers plenty of options for vegetarians. \n\nI will definitely return again.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5880, 'ss4548', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r781724110-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Delicious indian food', 'This is in my opinion the best indian restaurant in Kenya. Food is always delicious. Management is on point ensuring good service. Try the chilli paneer it\'s their signature dish.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(5881, 'Jason', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r781026061-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'This place is amazing!!!', 'This place is amazing. Great atmosphere, great food and great service. Building is clean and comfortable. Definitely recommend this place.\n', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5882, 'Anne H', 'Parc d\'Elx, Platja de Ponent Gallant Mall on Parklands road', 'Open House Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d1898496-r778943121-Open_House_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent food', 'I only did take away, so i can\'t speak about in-person dining. The food was excellent! I went back 3 times during a one week stay.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 19:59:07', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(5883, 'Munawwar Alam', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r745649548-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Expensive!', 'This restaurant is exorbitantly expensive and not a good value for money. Charges KSH 350 for a bottle of coke that is not more than KSH 50 outside.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'negative', '[\"price_value\"]'),
(5884, 'Tish', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r741065853-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'A gem in the wall', 'Unassuming entrance leads to a busy/popular place known by many to have really good food. Attentive waitstaff, and consistently good dishes. If you like mushrooms, try the special dish topped with fried ginger strips! Really interesting and different from what we‚Äôve had before. It gets very busy after 7:00, so go early.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5885, 'PL2w', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r740022023-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Delicious!', 'Tried their original chicken garam masala this time and it was so delicious!! The service was great. The Bila Shaka beer wasn\'t that great but the food: delicious!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\"]'),
(5886, 'William G', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r738579784-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Good Indian dinner', 'Had good Indian dinner and well patronized by the Indian population in Nairobi.   Quality well prepared food with good service.   ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(5887, 'GOLF KENYA', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r730542931-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'best services', 'Best Location best services and best food. \nThe location of the Haandi is at the heart of Westlands the Business Center', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5888, 'olivierjat', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r722504782-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent Indian food, we had a great evening!', 'Went there with 2 colleagues and the food was really good.\nHad some tika juicy chicken as an appetizer, then Dal, Basmati rice, Naan bread, lamp curry and coconut chicken curry...everything was really good.\nThe waiter was really helpful and tending to our needs very well.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(5889, 'Jonid D', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r721619132-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent Indian', 'Probably the best Indian in Nairobi.\n\nWent with a Friend from Norway and we had a most excellent meal. Just right.\nChicken tikka, yellow daal, potato and cauliflower, naan, stuffed paratha ... lassi .., can‚Äôt fault either service or the food.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(5890, 'RSLT', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r718808123-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Very expensive and OK food', 'We decided to try Haandy after reading the great reviews but it was a huge disappointment. The waiters were all very professional and the food was decent, but we were surprised at how pricey it is, especially compared to similar restaurants (Chowpaty, Open House). I usually order Paneer Makhani at Indian restaurants in Nairobi and the price is always around 800 shillings, but it was 1500 at Haandi. Add an outrageous 400 shillings for a bottle of Coke and it ends up being quite a pricey meal.', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(5891, 'Paula B', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r716793262-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Dinner', 'I was taken to Haandi by a local Indian friend who told me this restaurant is rated as the best Indian restaurant in Nairobi. The food was excellent, the menu very varied and the service very good. I think it‚Äôs the type of restaurant that never disappoints. ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5892, 'Adam', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r713968068-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'authentic indian cuisine', 'Excellent indian food.Authentic cuisine with wide variety of veg and non veg options.is quite pricey but well worth it for special occasions', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5893, 'Nathalie P', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r713528724-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent restaurant indien', 'Ce restaurant est un r√©gal! J‚Äôy suis all√©e deux fois et n‚Äôai pas √©t√© d√©√ßue. Le choix est immense, la qualit√© au rendez vous et le service impeccable. Je recommande ce resto vivement!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"service\"]'),
(5894, 'William G', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r709586813-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Indian lunch', 'They don‚Äôt do the roomali roti at lunch time so decided to forgoe the curry and went for fried papadum masala and samosas instead.   Recommended for dinner.   ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(5895, 'Alan M', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r709365234-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Service way BELOW the expected standard and hype, Decided to revisit Zen Garden instead. Pull up your socks!!!!!', 'I visited Haandi a week ago. I\'ve always wanted to visit Haandi due to viewed positive online reviews on the food. However, my experience from the building security guard stationed at the parking to the waiter that was assigned to our table was poor and way below standard for a restaurant of your repute. I would easily get better service any day from the average estate eat out hence my silent walkout from your restaurant. See you after you take your staff for PR and service delivery lessons.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"delivery_takeout\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5896, 'Carlo B', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r707829104-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'cena tra amici', 'In otto persone abbiamo potuto ordinare piatti diversi per potere degustare pi√π pietanze . Cucina ben organizzata a rispondere alle richieste della clientela , qualche piccola smagliatura nel servizio al tavolo . \nNell\'insieme tutte le pietanze ordinate al tavolo erano all\'altezza delle aspettative . \nLa frutta grande assente nella serata , in altre occasioni una variet√† veniva portata al tavolo per rinfrescare le papille gustative  provate dai sapori indiani . Ottimo e sicuro  il parcheggio al piano primo per entrare al ristorante .', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'positive', '[]'),
(5897, 'M&S Travels', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r699232043-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Delicious food. Good service ', '\nThis was my first time here. Friends have been recommending this for years. And I can see why. \n\nThe food was delicious and the service was good. I especially liked the paneer folks and the chilli naan. ', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5898, 'armantheman', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r698369864-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Nice decor. Average food. ', 'You can\'t normally go wrong with Indian cuisine in Nairobi. Unfortunately Haandi is on the lower end of the spectrum. Open house, hashmi and chowpatty all offer more flavor for your buck. Haandis upscale modern decor of course gives it bonus points, but it just isn\'t worth it given the other available options at your disposal around the corner. ', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5899, 'WSaula', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r697760939-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'What a great deal of experience?', 'This Indian restaurant is truly exquisite! Great delicacies! The ambiance, very friendly & hospitable staff, the location is great too! Wanna have an epic dinner, this would be your ideal restaurant! I had the tastiest wine ever in Nairobi!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5900, 'FraDubai123', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r695501298-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Perhaps one of the best Indian restaurants worldwide', 'I am not a huge fan of Indian food (personal taste) - but this place is exquisite, delicious to an extent that is difficult to explain. Went there for dinner with friends, came back the following day for lunch, and ordered take-away dinner from it on the third day. Just couldn‚Äôt get enough!\n\nI later found out they catered to Indian prime minister Modi when he visited Kenya - no surprise given the calibre of this restaurant (perhaps better than Bukhara in new Delhi). Will be back for sure!', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"location_access\"]'),
(5901, 'LanCReviews', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r690854177-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Flavorful and reasonable ', 'We visited in 2012 and returned July 2019. Place looks the same. We had lamb curry, chicken lollipop, yellow dal curry, raita, garlic nana. I would rate everything a 5 and the dal a 4. The dal was a bit too liquidy and not enough dal. Felt more like dal soup. However it was still very flavorful. Rasmalai (desert) was delicious and so was the kulfi ice cream. Dinner for 3 with bottle of water came to about 80 dollars without tip. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"location_access\", \"portion_size\"]'),
(5902, 'Chetan V', 'The Mall Shopping Centre Ring Rd Westlands', 'Haandi Restaurant', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d802603-r687591749-Haandi_Restaurant-Nairobi.html', 'Good food', 'Good south Indian food. Loved the services provided. Not tasted such good food since last trip to south India. ', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:01:09', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(5903, 'wambui lisa', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r1001359265-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'üëéüèæüëéüèæ', 'Unfortunately it‚Äôs a no for me ! The staff gave noticeably more attention to white customers, making it clear that white privilege is alive and well in this restaurant. On top of that the food was underwhelming and didn‚Äôt live up to the hype .', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(5904, 'Mokhinur', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r998241760-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Bad', 'I ordered a medium steak, but what I got was tough, dry, and almost impossible to chew. The meat was completely pink inside but lacked any tenderness‚Äîit felt like chewing rubber. A properly cooked medium steak should be juicy and easy to eat, but this one was overcooked on the outside and poorly cut, making it unpleasant. Definitely not worth the price.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"price_value\"]'),
(5905, 'MiGauch', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r943250639-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Best steaks in Nairobi', 'Excellent juicy steaks - the best in Nairobi. I recommend warmly striploin steak, 30 days aged steak, which melts in mouth. Wines are well selected top quality wines mostly from South Africa. Service is quick and knowledgeable. I warmly recommend this restaurant to any steak  lover.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5906, 'John G', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r928826701-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Great Steak', 'The executive chef is good at his job. Whenever I call the floor manager Stanley he and the executive chef prepare my meal according to my taste and I love it. \nMtume Yohana Gobanga', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(5907, 'Nel', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r923412686-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Dinner date', 'i loved the interior, so cool. The was great , the starers were so filling and tasty too- loved the calamari and the strip loin, the dessert my Fav of all. kudos to that\ni appreciate the good service from our waiter,he did a good job looking after us.\nI would come back to try out the burgers.', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5908, 'Kui the Foodie', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r914624038-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'BEST SIRLOIN STEAK EVER!', 'I LOVED LIVE LOVED my medium-to-well done sirloin steak SO MUCH OH MY WORD! One of thee Best I\'ve EVER HAD!!! HIGHLY HIGHLY RECOMMEND! I\'ll definitely be back and thanks Veronicah for the awesome service, such a sweet pleasant lady', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(5909, 'Faker R', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r905191244-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Excellent Cheese Burger', 'Grill Shack food never disappoints. Had the cheese burger and it was excellent. I will be back for sure.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(5910, 'Mr P', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r890276497-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Standards slipped a bit, but still okay', 'Hadn\'t been here for a couple of years, so we were excited to patronise The Grill Shack once more. This time, we decided to venture away from the usual fare of burgers and ribs, much to a little disappointment. Portion sizes seem to have diminished somewhat. The prawns and platters were also lacking in flavour. The lemonade was a saving grace. Service was attentive, but perhaps we\'ll be giving this yet more time before coming back', 3, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"menu_variety\"]');
INSERT INTO `restaurant_reviews` (`id`, `author_name`, `place_address`, `place_name`, `review_url`, `review_title`, `review_text`, `review_rating`, `location`, `created_at`, `predicted_sentiment`, `predicted_aspects`) VALUES
(5911, 'Sam', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r887871117-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Bad experience', 'Good ambience, food not so good, bad service, we had to return the food for proper cooking, seems the staff was in a hurry to close,the waiter seemed in a hurry to leave, at the end the lights were switched of on us and we complained to the manager who claimed ignorance of this.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"atmosphere\"]'),
(5912, 'Charity C', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r881823048-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Poor service', 'The service was extremely slow...our main meal came first. Before the. Starter....so...take from that way u want...but the food was awrite', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\"]'),
(5913, 'Jabke S', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r870021571-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Good Grilled Meats.', 'Located right in the centre of the Mall. Good grilled meats. Portions are large and offered very good value for money.\n', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'positive', '[\"price_value\"]'),
(5914, 'Go40397129943', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r846883484-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Courteous service. Good food.', 'I ate at The Grill Shack on a couple of occasions when I recently visited Nairobi. The food was very good, especially the steaks, and the service was awsome. I will definitely eat here again when I return.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\"]'),
(5915, 'dokumentiert', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r846516758-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Leckere Burger & Fritten', 'Wir haben im Westgate Mall hier nachmittags einen Burger mit Fritten gegessen. Die Burger waren sehr saftig und lecker, die Fritten sch√∂n kross. Die Bedienung war super freundlich und das Essen kam schnell. Zu empfehlen!', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(5916, 'Jackie M', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r846109302-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Team Lunch', 'Good ambiance and even better cocktails. I ordered the classic mojito which was great even though the excessive amount of ice shavings completely watered it down. The menu was detailed and had a variety of options. I had the Beef BBQ ribs which were grilled to perfection, as they were tasty and moist. The rest had pork ribs, chicken breast and chicken burrito. Service was quite prompt. I absolutely loved the sticky toffee pudding for dessert. I\'ll be keen to visit again to try out the seafood options as well as the burgers. Only downside was the shaky Wi-Fi connection.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"speed_wait\", \"atmosphere\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5917, 'Brenda B', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r842927871-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Best burger ever', 'Liked the vibe\nOverall nice experience\nIt did take a minute to get the burgers but it was worth the wait\n10/10', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'positive', '[\"price_value\", \"atmosphere\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
(5918, 'Beryl A', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r842575368-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Good food and vibes', 'Amazing food and services. We were specifically served by Robert and will definitely return just so we can enjoy his services.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
(5919, 'Karen S', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r841893077-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Horrible staff double charged me for a meal!', 'Chicken is not bad but not my taste, the chicken is dried for me.\nWhen settle the bill, the waitress asked me if I add tips to credit card chard. I replied no thanks. Then she charged my credit card and told me the charge was failed. Asked me to pay through m-pesa again. She didn‚Äôt provide me the void credit card slip and also refuse to give the receipt.', 1, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(5920, 'MrChristopherAdam', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r840792474-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Australian foodie says GO!!!!!!', 'For the price, the  food is really good, exceeds expectations,\n\nThe staff are also really nice, I mean everyone I knows how to wait tables and everyone smiles, can‚Äôt fault them.\n\nKitchen has a proper grill and I gave the kitchen the ultimate test, steak strips COOKED RARE!\nCharred on the outside, rare (but not raw) on the inside, perfection.\nI challenge you to fine this in Africa in a similarly priced restaurant.\n\nMy beer glass came prechilled,\nI mean could you be a more perfect restaurant?????\n\nChristopher', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"drinks\", \"service\", \"price_value\"]'),
(5921, 'Sheetal B', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r838110488-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Phenomenal Food', 'Hands down the best Lamb chops and flavourful barbecue in Nairobi city. Trust me, you won\'t find anything that compares to Grill Shack at the Westgate Shopping Mall, Westlands.\n\nFriendly staff and the Manager, Wesley was really sweet and we enjoyed the meal immensely. And I forgot to mention that their burgers are really good üëå\n\nLove Love Love the Grill Shack in Nairobi and it\'s one of my favourite places to eat at! You must try everything on their menu!!! I could go on and on about it but just try the food for yourselves! ‚ù§Ô∏è', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"location_access\", \"menu_variety\"]'),
(5922, 'Mzungubabe', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r823612845-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'American style restaurant', 'I was in the Westgate shopping mall and decided to get a bite of lunch.  This is like an American diner, the fries were good and the corn on the cob (rare in Nairobi restaurants) was excellent.', 4, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'positive', '[\"food\"]'),
