(5925, 'EVerghese', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r813029506-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'What on earth?!', '3 times here and each time more disappointed. South Africans rave about this place, but we just seem to be ripped off. The waiter kept going on about the special steak and persuaded us to order it. They said it was Ksh 1000 per 100g but never confirmed the weight. The food arrived - a massive T-bone steak with a huge additional bone of marrow (there‚Äôs the weight). Decent enough though nothing out of the ordinary - annoyingly having to order sides on top. Bill arrived at a whopping 180k!!!!! We were absolutely stunned. \nIt‚Äôs one thing to pay for fine dining and be totally blown away. This was a con at its finest. The joke‚Äôs on us...never again...', 2, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'negative', '[\"food\", \"service\", \"price_value\", \"location_access\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
