(5927, 'Zayn A.', 'Westlands Road Westgate Mall', 'The Grilll Shack Kenya', 'https://www.tripadvisor.com/ShowUserReviews-g294207-d16658568-r803197332-The_Grilll_Shack_Kenya-Nairobi.html', 'Sumptuous, scrumptious, stunning, super.', 'I had the steak; absolutely exceptional steak. It looked brilliant. The vibrance and colour of the fries and lettuce, that accompanied it, spoke to the freshness of the two; they were an apt indication that predicted the bold flavours that were to come. And boy, were the flavours good. I pride myself in having visited a vast majority of restaurants in Nairobi, of all price ranges. Grill shack nailed everything. While there, I have no reservations in recommending that you try the sirloin steak. Ask for it pepper crusted, and have a steak that\'s brimming with flavour, exceptionally juicy, and luxuriously tender.', 5, 'Nairobi', '2025-11-24 20:25:20', 'positive', '[\"food\", \"price_value\", \"overall_experience\"]'),
